NK094(nge)001:1: // snga 'gyur bka' ma'i chos sde'i glegs bam go gsum pa bzhugs so ////
NK094(nge)001:2: dpal spyi mdo dgongs pa 'dus pa'i 'grel pa rnal
NK094(nge)001:3: 'byor nyi ma gsal bar byed pa'i legs bshad gzi
NK094(nge)001:4: ldan 'char kha'i 'od snang gi glegs bam bzhi pa
NK094(nge)001:5: bzhugs so // dgu pa mthun par 'jug par bya ba la gsum ste /
NK094(nge)001:13: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14: le'u 'dis drang don ldems dgongs kyi bshad pa ston no //
NK094(nge)001:15: me long brtag pa bstan ma thag pa de nas
NK094(nge)001:16: yang 'khor lang ka'i badga po la sogsa pa damna
NK094(nge)001:18: ston pa gasnga ba pa'i badga po la /
NK094(nge)001:19: skabs gang 'dira le'u zhe lnga par mdo don 'gro
NK094(nge)001:20: ba'i chos kyi rnam grangs bcu bkod pa'i dagu pa
NK094(nge)001:21: gang gi don gyi dri ba yongsa su dris pa
NK094(nge)001:22: / kye gasnga ba pa'i bdag po /
NK094(nge)001:23: nyid kyis sngar cha mthun par sbyar bar bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:24: zhes dam bca' bar dgongsa pa de nyid ji ltar yongas su shes par bagyi /
NK094(nge)001:25: de skad ces yongs su dris pa lasa /
NK094(nge)001:26: skye bu chen po gasnga ba pa'i badga posa lan du bka' stsal te smras pa /
NK094(nge)001:28: de daga nye bar ston pa ni gang zhe na lam pas gzhan don gyi spyod pa nyid de /
NK094(nge)001:29: de yang 'di ltar yongsa su shes par bya ste /
NK094(nge)001:30: 'gro ba ma rig pa'i mun pa chen po kun
NK094(nge)001:31: nas 'khrigsa pa yi gnyid kyis 'thibs pas don la
NK094(nge)001:32: shed ma bye bas byis pa'i khamsa kyi grong khyer
NK094(nge)001:33: gsum gyi gnas su dus gsum du 'khyams pa'i gdul
NK094(nge)001:34: bya rnams drang ba'i ched du /
NK094(nge)001:35: dus rtag pa rgyun gyi 'khora mor nyan rang byang
NK094(nge)001:36: sems las dgar te 'dir 'khor bar 'gro don la
NK094(nge)001:37: nges par 'jug pa'i don bya ba'i thabs kyi 'dren
NK094(nge)001:38: tshul rnam pa mang po dag kyang /
NK094(nge)001:39: thabs la mkhas pas don mdzad pa'i dgongsa pa dam
NK094(nge)001:40: pa thams cad kun 'dus pasa rgyal ba ril 'dus
NK094(nge)001:41: nas bka' stsal ba'i mdo rgyud chos kyi me long
NK094(nge)001:42: 'di las dam pa gang gi spyod yul gang gis
NK094(nge)001:43: 'dren pa'i sgor gyur par nges pa gdul bya'i don
NK094(nge)001:44: du 'gyur ba'i thabs mang po ji ltar gsungas pa
NK094(nge)001:45: ji snyed pa thams cad bsdus na /
NK094(nge)001:46: 'dir ni gzhan don gyi spyod pa rnam grangs gsum du shes par bya ste /
NK094(nge)001:47: cha mthun sbyor ba'i spyod pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:48: mthun 'jug thabs kyi spyod pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:49: thabsa 'dzud bsre ba'i spyod pa dang gsum yin te /
NK094(nge)001:51: gzhan dang cha 'dra ba la brten nas don la sbyor ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:52: gzhan ji bzhin du spyod pas grol thabs ston pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:53: res rang ltar dang res gzhan ltar spyod de bsre ba yisa gdul bar byed pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:54: des na de gsum gyi khyad par bstan na /
NK094(nge)001:55: cha mthun sbyor ba'i spyod pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:56: dpe na rtse lde mnga' ris gcod pa dang 'dra ste /
NK094(nge)001:57: sngon la gzhan dang mthun par byas nas gzhug tu rang ltar bsgyur ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:59: dper na dug za ba la dug sngags byin nas
NK094(nge)001:60: zas su 'jug pa dang 'dra bar gdul bya nyon
NK094(nge)001:61: mongs pa la zhen pa la nyon mongs lam du
NK094(nge)001:62: khyer ba'i thabs khyad par can bstan nas nyon mongs
NK094(nge)001:64: thabs 'dzud bsre ba'i spyod pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:65: dper na gnyen kha len byed pa dang 'dra bar
NK094(nge)001:66: gdul bya dang spyod pa 'dren mar spyod nas 'dul
NK094(nge)001:67: ba'o // de ltar thabs kyi spyod pa gsum gyis
NK094(nge)001:68: dus sam gdul bya blo che chung thamsa cad skabs
NK094(nge)001:69: sam thabs thamsa cad ji ltar rigas para 'gro don
NK094(nge)001:71: theg pa chen po nges pa dam pa'i don gyi
NK094(nge)001:72: chos nyid du rigs ngesa para sbyar bar bya ba'o
NK094(nge)001:74: cha mthun sbyor ba'i spyod pa bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:75: thabs 'dzud bsre ba'i spyod pa bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:76: mthun 'jug thabs kyi spyod pa bshad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:79: de nyid lo rgyus kyis bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:84: dam pa'i yul la 'jug /ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:85: lang ka'i bdag po zhes sdud pa po la bos nas /
NK094(nge)001:86: de dag so so nas nye bar ston pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:87: thog mar cha mthun sbyor ba'i sgo nas su zhig
NK094(nge)001:88: gis 'gro don byed pa'ang ji lta bu zhe na
NK094(nge)001:89: 'di lta ste / thabs la mkhas pa'i dam pa
NK094(nge)001:90: gang gis cha mthun sbyor bar brten nas gdul bya
NK094(nge)001:91: gang gi don la 'jug pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:92: 'gro ba gang zhig spyod yul gang du mtshan ma
NK094(nge)001:93: can der spyod pas log par 'gro bar ngesa pa
NK094(nge)001:94: la / rnal 'byor dam pa rngon dang smad 'tshong
NK094(nge)001:95: sogs skye ba rang dbang can du gyur pas kyang
NK094(nge)001:96: thabs kyi sgo nas gdul bya kho'i spyod pa de
NK094(nge)001:97: dag nyid dang ngo bo mthun par spyad de rnal
NK094(nge)001:98: 'byor mchog gi thabs yongsa kyis mtshan ma can de
NK094(nge)001:99: dang cha mthun pa'i spyod pa bsten cing brid par
NK094(nge)001:100: la / byas na / rim pas gdul bya'i 'gro
NK094(nge)001:101: ba de nyid yang dag pa'i don de la kha
NK094(nge)001:103: des na sems can de dag dam pa'i don la
NK094(nge)001:104: 'dzud par bya ba'i phyir du gdul bya de dag
NK094(nge)001:105: gam 'gro ba drug po rnams dang bdag gis mthun
NK094(nge)001:106: pa'i spyod par spyad de byis pa gang dag rnams
NK094(nge)001:107: tshul de la sbyar basa yid kun nas drangsa te
NK094(nge)001:108: rim par kha lo bsgyur nas gsang sngags ma nor
NK094(nge)001:109: ba'i don la nges par bcug nas rtogs pa la
NK094(nge)001:110: btsud cing de las mi ldog par nan tan la
NK094(nge)001:112: de ltar gdul bya gang gi bsam pa'i mos phyogs
NK094(nge)001:113: dang 'tshams par yid 'phrog nas rang dbang med par
NK094(nge)001:114: 'jug pa'i cha mthun gyi spyod pas dga' bar byas
NK094(nge)001:115: te thabs la mkhas pas 'drena cing don la 'jug
NK094(nge)001:116: pa yang / kho'i 'dod phyogs ji ltar yin pa
NK094(nge)001:117: de ltar de dag gi yid du 'ong ba'i spyod
NK094(nge)001:118: pa de kho na la spyod du bcug nas des
NK094(nge)001:119: chud ma gsan par gsang chen nges pa'i don la
NK094(nge)001:120: nan tan du sbyor ba'i thabs kyis rjes su 'dzin
NK094(nge)001:121: pa nyid ni cha mthun gyi spyod pa de yis
NK094(nge)001:122: gdul bya don la sbyor bar bya ba nyid do
NK094(nge)001:123: pa yang / // de skad du rtsa ba'i rgyud las /
NK094(nge)001:124: mtshan ma yin phyir der nges pa //
NK094(nge)001:125: mtshan ma can dang mthun bya'i phyir //
NK094(nge)001:126: thabs kyis de dang mthun spyod la //
NK094(nge)001:127: yang dag don la kha lo sgyur //
NK094(nge)001:128: de dag rnam par sbyang ba dang //
NK094(nge)001:129: 'gro drug shin tu g.yeng ba can //
NK094(nge)001:130: yid rnams drangs te brten byas nas //
NK094(nge)001:131: thabs kyis don la sbyar ba'i tshig /rgyu drug 'dus pa'i sa gzhi la //
NK094(nge)001:132: glu bro gar gyi rol pa yis //
NK094(nge)001:133: srid gsum zil gnon dbang sdud pa //
NK094(nge)001:136: de nyid nye bar mtshon pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:137: dper na srid pa'i 'jig rten ma rig pa'i mun pa'i khamas kyi gnas dag na /
NK094(nge)001:138: mi la sogs pa'i 'gro ba mkhas shing mdzangs pa
NK094(nge)001:139: gang gis mi sogs mi shes pa'i 'gro gzhan ganga
NK094(nge)001:140: daga rnams la gang gis 'dul bar gyur pa'i spyod
NK094(nge)001:141: pa mthun par spyad pas 'gro ba mi shes pa
NK094(nge)001:142: de yi yid dga' ba'i shes pa la 'dul byed
NK094(nge)001:143: kyi thabs de zhugsa te zhen pa'i ngor 'dul byed
NK094(nge)001:144: de dang gdul bya de nyid spyod pa gcig pas
NK094(nge)001:145: so so ba med par mi gzhan pasa yid gcug
NK094(nge)001:146: tu mdza' bar gyur pa'i don du gnas pa de
NK094(nge)001:147: nas 'dul byed mchog des pha rol po de yi
NK094(nge)001:148: bsam pa'i drod de rig cing lon nas mjug gdul
NK094(nge)001:149: bya'i 'gro ba de yi bsam pa dabnga du byas
NK094(nge)001:150: te kha lo bsgyur bar btub pa'i thabs la dabnga
NK094(nge)001:151: thob ste skabs su bab pa na gzod gdul bya
NK094(nge)001:152: de nyid kyi 'du shes bsgyur ba'i tshig gi lam
NK094(nge)001:153: 'byung ba ni dpe don mtshungs par rnal 'byor dam
NK094(nge)001:154: pas kyang de ltar mthun par spyad zin nas 'di
NK094(nge)001:156: de ltar 'adsa par gyur pa'am da snga yan chad
NK094(nge)001:157: du grogs mchog dam pa dag gi mthun 'jug thabs
NK094(nge)001:158: kyi spyod pa kho na yi tshul yin pas rang
NK094(nge)001:159: rang dang mthun par dgongs pa can gyi spyod par
NK094(nge)001:160: zad de / nges par khyod kyi yid la zhugsa
NK094(nge)001:161: pasa zhen pa'i spyod pa ngan pa 'di ni spyod
NK094(nge)001:163: mar la ngam pas e ma'o zhes 'u cag gi
NK094(nge)001:164: spyod pa 'di ni shin tu 'khrul zhing nor te
NK094(nge)001:165: / tshul 'dir spyod pa ni shin tu nyes pa
NK094(nge)001:166: che bas 'dira log spyod 'di las phyir log la
NK094(nge)001:167: bshags pa bya ba dang dge ba'i las kyi ltang
NK094(nge)001:168: bsags pa ni bgrang zhing spel ba sogsa kyis byang
NK094(nge)001:169: chub chen por bsngo bar gyis shig pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:170: kho bo cag gi spyod pa de ni 'di ltar
NK094(nge)001:171: nyes pa yin na yang sngar gyi skabs 'di na
NK094(nge)001:172: kho bos khyed cag dga' bar byas te /
NK094(nge)001:173: khyed rnams dang dang mthun pa kho nara spyod pa byas pa yin pas /
NK094(nge)001:174: deng gi skabs gang 'dir bdag dga' ba'i lam dama
NK094(nge)001:175: pa ma nor bar yang dag pa'i don du 'jug
NK094(nge)001:176: pa'i spyod pa 'di dang bstun la khyod rnams kyang
NK094(nge)001:177: nges pa dama pa de kho nar shin tu 'jug
NK094(nge)001:178: par 'osa shing rigs pa yin pas grogs po dag
NK094(nge)001:180: zhes zer ba bzhin dpe don mtshungs te /
NK094(nge)001:181: de ltar brjod pa desa na pha rol po'am gdul
NK094(nge)001:182: bya da yi sems de nyid de ltar mthun par
NK094(nge)001:183: bdag gis / 'un zhes bru sha'i skad de bod skad du zin zhes par 'gyur bas /
NK094(nge)001:184: thabs kyis zin pasa pha rol lam gdul bya ganga
NK094(nge)001:185: dag gi phyis kyi sems de nyid kyang 'un nam
NK094(nge)001:186: zin te bdag gi ngag nyan cing yid dga' bas
NK094(nge)001:187: dama par nges pa yang dag pa'i spyod yul la
NK094(nge)001:188: 'jug par 'gyur zhing slar mi ldog par yang nges
NK094(nge)001:190: dper na 'jig rten khams dag na //
NK094(nge)001:192: de dag'i las la de zhugs te //
NK094(nge)001:193: de dang bsam pa mthun spyad pas //
NK094(nge)001:194: de dang 'dris nas de dga' byas //
NK094(nge)001:195: de nas de yi drod lon na //
NK094(nge)001:196: de yi 'du shes sgyur ba'i tshig /de snga bdag gi grogs khyod kyi //
NK094(nge)001:197: las la zhugs pa shin tu nor //
NK094(nge)001:198: 'dir nyes las kyi bsags pa bgrang //
NK094(nge)001:199: nyes kyang bdag gis khyod dgar byas //
NK094(nge)001:200: da ni bdag dag'i las 'di la //
NK094(nge)001:201: grogs khyod shin tu 'jug dgos so //
NK094(nge)001:202: byas pas de yi snga sems de //
NK094(nge)001:203: zin pas gcig gi phyi sems kyang //
NK094(nge)001:204: 'dzin cing de dag'i las la 'jug /ces so //
NK094(nge)001:206: cha mthun gyi spyod pa gyis shig par bskul ba /
NK094(nge)001:207: 'khor gyis de ltar byas pa'i tshul lo //
NK094(nge)001:212: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:213: de dag sngon gyi lo rgyus kyis yid ches par bsnyad pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:214: 'chad pa'i skyes bus lang ka'i bdag po zhes sdud pa la bos nas /
NK094(nge)001:215: ji ltar na sngon byung ba de yang ji lta bu zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:216: tshul de nyid gsal bar brjod pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:217: ston pa gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rto rje
NK094(nge)001:218: kho bosa 'di nyid kyis cha mthun gyi spyod pa
NK094(nge)001:219: dngos su mthong zhing thosa pa'i dus skabsa gcig na
NK094(nge)001:220: bdag gi ston pa bshes gnyen dam pa gsang ba
NK094(nge)001:221: mchog gi bdag po desa sngon byung ba'i 'dus pa'i
NK094(nge)001:222: 'khor tshogs phala mo che de dag rnams la rgyud
NK094(nge)001:223: mchog 'di nyid bka' stsal te rmad byung gsang ba'i
NK094(nge)001:224: lam 'di rgya cher bstan pa'i dus de'i tshe na
NK094(nge)001:225: / 'khora der gtogsa shing lhan cig tu 'dus par gyur pa yi /
NK094(nge)001:226: lha mo dang klu mo dang mi dang lha ma
NK094(nge)001:227: yin dang yi dwags la sogs pa rigsa ngana mo
NK094(nge)001:228: ste 'gro ba rigs drug tu gtogs pa'i bu mo
NK094(nge)001:229: drug gi tshogs 'khora dang bcas te 'dus pasa gtso
NK094(nge)001:230: 'khor rnams bro glu la dga' basa ston pa glu
NK094(nge)001:231: bro gar gyis stabs la brten nas dgyes pa chen
NK094(nge)001:232: po mnyes pasa mchod pa phul zhing bstabsa pa'i dus
NK094(nge)001:233: de yi tshe na glu bro gar rnams yang dag
NK094(nge)001:234: dam pa'i spyod yul min yang /
NK094(nge)001:235: ston pa dam pa gsang ba mchog gi bdag po
NK094(nge)001:236: nyid kyis gdul bya bu mo drug 'khor dang bcas
NK094(nge)001:237: pa de nyid spyod pa mthun pas dgrol bar bya
NK094(nge)001:238: ba yisa dgos ched kyi phyir thugs rjes gzung ba'i
NK094(nge)001:239: yul gyi dam pa nyid du dgongsa nas /
NK094(nge)001:240: gang der gdul bar byed pa'i sras kyi tshogs 'dus
NK094(nge)001:241: pa phal mo che'i 'khor rnams la bka' stsal pa
NK094(nge)001:242: ni / kye ma 'dus pa chen po'i tshogsa //
NK094(nge)001:244: bu mo drug la don mthun pas don spyod par bskul te /
NK094(nge)001:245: gang gi ston pa nga yi gdung 'tshob cing rgyud
NK094(nge)001:246: 'dzin pa'i rigsa can du byung ba gang yang rung
NK094(nge)001:247: ba dag gis / lha yi rol mo dang glu dang bro dang gar dang snyan pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:249: sgeg pa dang mdzes shing legs pa'i stabsa sna tshogs
NK094(nge)001:250: byas pas gdul bya gang gi yid rang dbang med
NK094(nge)001:251: par 'phrog nas don la 'jug cing 'dren pa'i thabsa
NK094(nge)001:252: / glu yi rtsa ba drug la yan lag bcu
NK094(nge)001:253: bcu dang de re re la drug drug ste sum
NK094(nge)001:255: rkang lag gi stabsa dang gar thabsa sna tshogs pa mang po mi zad cing tshad med pas /
NK094(nge)001:256: 'jig rten gyi gdul bya kun sdud cing rgyal ba
NK094(nge)001:257: kun mnyes par byed pas de dag dang cha mthun
NK094(nge)001:258: du sbyor ba'i glu bro gyis shig ces /
NK094(nge)001:259: ston pa dam pa de yisa de skad ces gsungsa te bka' stsal pas /
NK094(nge)001:268: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:269: de nas sras kyi dam pa de kho na lang
NK094(nge)001:270: ka'i bdag po sprul pa'i blo gros thabsa ldan zhes
NK094(nge)001:271: bya ba nyid kyis ston pas drang bas 'dira gdul
NK094(nge)001:272: bya gang dag rnams glu bro gang gis thabs kyis
NK094(nge)001:274: 'jig rten drug gi bu mo 'khor bcas dang cha
NK094(nge)001:275: mthun gyi spyod pas don la sbyor ba drang ba'i
NK094(nge)001:277: lang ka gang gi nyid kyis gnas nas 'jig rten
NK094(nge)001:278: pa dang spyod pa mthun pa kun tu snang bar
NK094(nge)001:280: tshul ji ltar na gzhi ma nges pa las cir
NK094(nge)001:281: yang snang la dngos po med pas gar mchog myur
NK094(nge)001:282: ba glog ltar 'gyu bas 'khor ba'i mun nag tu
NK094(nge)001:283: skad cig la don gsal bar gyur pa yi sgo
NK094(nge)001:284: nas bdag gzhan gyi don phun sum tshogs pa'i dapala
NK094(nge)001:285: gnyis dang ldan pa'i rtags su lag pa g.yas g.yon
NK094(nge)001:286: bye ba snyed du gyur pa yisa nam mkha'i khamsa
NK094(nge)001:287: 'di kun rig pa rang snang ba'i skus yongsa su
NK094(nge)001:288: bkang nas gdul bya'i don la gshegs bzhud lta bur
NK094(nge)001:289: cir yang snang ba'i gom pa'i stabsa dang mthun par
NK094(nge)001:290: lag pa rnams kyis gar sna tshogs byed cing gdul
NK094(nge)001:291: bya gdul ba'i thabs kyi sgyu 'phrul mdzad do //
NK094(nge)001:293: glu yi yan lag /ces pa nas /
NK094(nge)001:295: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:296: bshad pa lta bu'i glu yi yan lag sum brgya'i
NK094(nge)001:297: sgra skad srid khams 'brug gi sgra yisa ganga ba
NK094(nge)001:299: mu mtha' thug pa med pa'i 'jig rten drug gi
NK094(nge)001:300: gnas rigs kun glu'i sgras gang basa gdul bya 'gro
NK094(nge)001:301: ba drug gi yid 'phrog cing byang chub chen po'i
NK094(nge)001:302: don la 'dren par mdzad pas dbyangs kyi byed par
NK094(nge)001:303: snang ngo // 'o na glu'i tshig nyid ji lta bu zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:304: theg pa chen po'i lta spyod rmad du byung ba
NK094(nge)001:305: nyid phal gyis yul min pas gasnga sngags gsang ba
NK094(nge)001:306: dam pa'i tshig las tshig gcig bsgyur bas kyang gdul
NK094(nge)001:307: bya'i ngo la sgra dbyangs tha dad kyi tshig gi
NK094(nge)001:309: de'ang blo che ba la tshig lam gyi brjod pa
NK094(nge)001:310: dang rab tu bral ba'i gsang ba mchog gi dona
NK094(nge)001:311: zab mo shin tu rtogs par dka' ba rgyal ba'i
NK094(nge)001:312: dgongs pa sangsa rgyas nyag gcig gi spyod yul mtshon
NK094(nge)001:313: cing rtogs par dka' ba nyid ston pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:314: de lta na'ang thabs khyad par can gyi bka'i tshig
NK094(nge)001:315: las don mtshon pa'i sgo mang po 'byung ba la
NK094(nge)001:316: ngam pas e ma'o zhes pas drangs te /
NK094(nge)001:317: gdul bya log pa can rnams rang la gnas kyang
NK094(nge)001:318: ma rtogs pa la bsting ba dang smre bas ngo
NK094(nge)001:319: mtshar zhing lta spyod rmad kyi chos zab mo de'i
NK094(nge)001:320: ched du bro glus don mchog khyad par can la
NK094(nge)001:321: sbyor bas rmad du byung ba'i rola pa la spyad
NK094(nge)001:322: pas gsang sngags bla na med pa'i don gsal bar
NK094(nge)001:323: 'byung ngo // de yang mdzad pa gdul bya dang
NK094(nge)001:324: cha mthun pas don la sbyor ba'i spyod pa'i khyad
NK094(nge)001:325: par las 'jig rten drug gi gnas su mthun pas
NK094(nge)001:326: don mdzad pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi rol pa'i sprul
NK094(nge)001:327: pa 'byung ba des 'khora ba'i las dang nyon mongs
NK094(nge)001:328: pa'i rgyu'i lam rgyud rtsa ba nas gcad pa'i phyir
NK094(nge)001:329: du 'jig rten drug gi ngo bo bde bar gshegs
NK094(nge)001:330: pa'i snying po gsang sngags dam pa nyid kyi rang
NK094(nge)001:331: 'byung ngo // bzhin can la / thugsa rje chena
NK094(nge)001:332: po'i thabsa kyi rtsal las glu bro gar gyi sprul
NK094(nge)001:333: pa shar ba'i 'oda zer 'gag med du 'phros pasa
NK094(nge)001:334: 'byung ngo // bzhin can la / / rgyud drug
NK094(nge)001:335: gi 'gro ba rnams kyi sgo gsum gyi dngosa po
NK094(nge)001:336: thamsa cad sbyangs shing bsregsa par mdzad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:337: de lta bu'i cha mthun gyi spyod pa la zin
NK094(nge)001:338: chags med pas ma chagsa pa'i ye shes kyis gdul
NK094(nge)001:339: bya'i 'gro ba dang cha mthun pa'i thabsa su shar
NK094(nge)001:340: ba'i mdzad pas drang ste don la sbyor ba'i phyir
NK094(nge)001:341: du / 'jig rten pa don la shed ma bye
NK094(nge)001:342: ba byis pa'i spyod pa kho na bzhina du 'jig
NK094(nge)001:343: rten gyi bu mo drug dang rol pa'i sbyor bas
NK094(nge)001:344: glu dang gar gyis don mdzad pa nyid de /
NK094(nge)001:346: spyod pa'i las kyang 'di lta ste //
NK094(nge)001:347: rgyu drug 'dus pa'i phung po la //
NK094(nge)001:348: ngan song gnas 'joms rdo rje'i rtags //
NK094(nge)001:349: ye shes thabs kyis snyan pa'i glu //
NK094(nge)001:350: rmad byung gsang chen sgrogs pa'i tshig /ces so //
NK094(nge)001:359: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:360: 'chad pa'i gom stabsa drug gi bskyod pasa 'gro ba rigs drug gnas nas bsgral ba ste /
NK094(nge)001:362: dpa' bo tsham rngam gyi stabs /
NK094(nge)001:366: khro bo ma rangs pa'i stabs rnams so //
NK094(nge)001:367: 'chad pa'i glu drug blangsa pasa gdul bya'i yul drug drangsa pa ste /
NK094(nge)001:373: srin mo khros pa'i rnams so //
NK094(nge)001:374: so so'i bsam skad dang mthun pa'i tshig drug bsgragsa
NK094(nge)001:375: pas gsang sngags kyi dona drug rdzogsa par byed pa
NK094(nge)001:376: ste / don grub rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig /zhi gnas mi rtog nam mkha'i tshig /
NK094(nge)001:377: 'dzin pa'i rtod phur 'byin pa'i tshig /ye shes don
NK094(nge)001:378: gyi gsal ba'i tshig /yid bzhin nor bu 'bar ba'i
NK094(nge)001:379: tshig /rdo rje bu yug skar mad'i tshig rnams so
NK094(nge)001:383: bu yug skar mad'i tshig /ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:384: de dag re re nas rgyas par bstan pa'i phyir //
NK094(nge)001:385: dang po lha 'dul ba'i bro ni /
NK094(nge)001:386: lha 'du byed kyis le lo can rnams 'dod pa'i
NK094(nge)001:387: yul la g.yeng ba'i ngo bo ni glu bro'i sa
NK094(nge)001:389: stabs ni le lo'i gnyen po shin tu brtson 'grus
NK094(nge)001:390: che ba ste myur mgyogsa cang shes rta mchog gi
NK094(nge)001:391: stabsa mdzad pa'o // glu ni tshangsa pa'i dbyangs kyis
NK094(nge)001:392: snyan pa'i glu dung nge ba nyid shes rab ma'i
NK094(nge)001:393: skad la dpe blangs te bzlas pas ma mo thams
NK094(nge)001:394: cad rdo khab len la lcags 'du ba'i tshul du
NK094(nge)001:396: tshangs pa'i dbyangs kyis 'dren tshul gyis //
NK094(nge)001:397: srid pa'i bu mo dbang du sdud //
NK094(nge)001:398: ces gsungs pas le lo med par 'bras bu'i dona
NK094(nge)001:399: grub pas rdo rje gsang ba'i sngags kyi tshig lha
NK094(nge)001:401: lam dbang du don drug las 'khor sdud pa'i gsang sngags kyi tshig ston pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:402: gnyis pa lha ma yin 'dul ba'i bro ni /
NK094(nge)001:403: lha ma yin nga rgyal bsgyur dka' bas ri bo'i sa yi bro gzhi'am yul la /
NK094(nge)001:404: khro gtum nga rgyal 'joms pa'i gnyen po lha ma
NK094(nge)001:405: yin rnams dpa' ba la rtsi bas dapa'a bo tsham
NK094(nge)001:406: ngama gyi rtsal tshad 'gran zla med pa gyad kyi
NK094(nge)001:407: dor stabsa kyis / g.yul pham rgyal gyi sgra 'byung
NK094(nge)001:408: bas rol mo sil snyan 'bum gyis snyan pa'i dbyangs
NK094(nge)001:409: lha ma yin gyi yid 'phrog pa'i glu breng nge
NK094(nge)001:410: dor stabsa kyis / ba nyid / dpe sbrang ma
NK094(nge)001:411: rdza mar bcug pa ltar mchu btsum la 'khur ba'i
NK094(nge)001:412: dbyangs su blangs pas shangs dang zhal gyi dbugs dang
NK094(nge)001:413: bcas te khyab par byung nas 'bros thabs med par
NK094(nge)001:417: ces pa'i don rdzogs te tshig ni nga rgyal zhi
NK094(nge)001:418: ba chen por gansa gyur pas cir yang mi rtog
NK094(nge)001:419: pa nam mkha' lta bur ston pa dang lam pa'i
NK094(nge)001:420: dbang du zhi gnas nam mkha'i tshiga kyang yin no
NK094(nge)001:421: // gsum pa 'gro ba kun gyi sa bon gsogs pas mi 'dul ba'i bro ni /
NK094(nge)001:422: mi rnams nyon mongs pa lnga po kun nasa 'dus
NK094(nge)001:423: te cha mnyam par yod pas bdag gzhan du 'dzin
NK094(nge)001:424: pa'i sa yi bro gzhi'am yul la /
NK094(nge)001:425: nyon mongs pa lnga'i gnyen por 'dod yon lnga'i zhen
NK094(nge)001:426: pa 'joms pa'i glang po'i gtso bo khyu mchoga rigs
NK094(nge)001:427: lnga yisa rol pa'i stabsa chen 'gying bgas can gyis
NK094(nge)001:428: / glu dang gar gyis mi'i yid 'phrog par byed
NK094(nge)001:429: pas snyan cing yid du 'ong ba'i pang ka de'u'i
NK094(nge)001:430: / glu dbyangs nyid / dpe 'brug gi sgra la
NK094(nge)001:431: blangs te gdug pa zil gyis gnon pa'i gsung ru
NK094(nge)001:432: lu'i sgra bsgrags pas ma tram 'khor bcas rnams kyis
NK094(nge)001:433: sems can za 'phro bcad nas nyan pa lta bus
NK094(nge)001:434: gdul zhing grol bar byed pa ste /
NK094(nge)001:435: drag cing 'brug ltar sgra bsgrags pas //
NK094(nge)001:436: drag po gtum po'ang lhan ner 'gyur //
NK094(nge)001:438: des sgo nas mi rnams kyis bdag gzhan du 'dzina
NK094(nge)001:439: pa'i nyon mongs lnga'i rtod phur drung nas 'byin par
NK094(nge)001:440: byed pa'i don ston pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:441: lam pa'i dbang du bdag lta'i 'dzin rtog nges par
NK094(nge)001:442: dgrol bas bdag med ston pa'i tshig kyang yin no
NK094(nge)001:443: // bzhi pa dud 'gro 'dul ba'i bro ni /
NK094(nge)001:444: byol song ma rig pas non te kun rmongs gti
NK094(nge)001:445: mug 'dus pa'i sa yi bro gzhi ni yul yin
NK094(nge)001:446: la / de nyid 'dul ba'i gnyen po senga ge
NK094(nge)001:447: yi dam brtan pa lta bu rngama pasa 'gying zhing
NK094(nge)001:448: zil gyis gnon pas rol pa'i stabsa kyis klu la
NK094(nge)001:449: bya khyung grags pas dkon mchog la skyabs 'gro dran
NK094(nge)001:450: pa lta bur gsungs pas kyang mtshon te bya ka
NK094(nge)001:451: la ping ka'i sgra dbyangs snyan pas byol song gi
NK094(nge)001:452: yid 'phrog pa cang ka de'u'i glu nyid /
NK094(nge)001:453: dpe g.yang dkar lug khyu lam du bcug pa la
NK094(nge)001:454: blangs te bzlas pas kho'i phung khams skye mched thams
NK094(nge)001:455: cad lha'i dkyil 'khor du brlabs shing rig pa gsal
NK094(nge)001:457: sngags kyi yi ge'i sgra bsgrags pas //
NK094(nge)001:460: rmongs pa'i gti mug ye nyid nas don gyi ye
NK094(nge)001:461: shes su gasla ba'i gsang ba mchog gi tshig ston
NK094(nge)001:462: pa dang / lam pa'i dbang du /
NK094(nge)001:463: rang byung gi ye shes rang grol du 'char ba'i tshig kyang yin no //
NK094(nge)001:464: lnga pa yi dwags 'dul ba'i bro ni /
NK094(nge)001:465: yi dwags rnams 'dod chagsa kyis bskyed pa dang sems
NK094(nge)001:466: chags pas bsdus pa can kun 'dus pa'i glu bro'i
NK094(nge)001:468: 'dul ba'i gnyen po rdo rje khyung chen ldingsa pa'i shags rtsal lta bu'i gar stabsa byas shing /
NK094(nge)001:469: 'brug gyi sgra chen ldir bas char 'bebs pa dang
NK094(nge)001:470: 'dra bar mchod sbyin thob par grags pa'i sgra snyan
NK094(nge)001:471: gyis yi dwags rnams yid 'phrog par byed pa g+har
NK094(nge)001:473: dpe mdzo mo bu stor ba'i ngur sgra la blangs
NK094(nge)001:474: te bzlas pas ma tram zil gyis mnan te kha
NK094(nge)001:475: t+w+aam rtse gcig brgyab pas mgo bo lho nub tu
NK094(nge)001:476: bstan nas 'gyel ba'i mkhun sgra dang bstun te lhang
NK094(nge)001:477: tser du brjod pas 'khrul snang gcod par byed pa
NK094(nge)001:478: ste / mkhun zhing gdung ba'i sgra 'byin pas //
NK094(nge)001:479: gdug byed thams cad thal bar rlog /ces pa'i don rdzogs te /
NK094(nge)001:480: ltogs dbul sel zhing 'dod pa 'byung bas re ba
NK094(nge)001:481: skong ba yid bzhina nor bu 'abra ba'i yon tan
NK094(nge)001:482: lta bu'i gsang ba'i tshig ston pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:483: lam pa'i dbang du 'dod rgu rang rdzogs kyi tshig kyang yin no //
NK094(nge)001:484: drug pa dmyal ba 'dul ba'i bro ni /
NK094(nge)001:485: dmyal ba zhe sdang can rnams 'dus shing rdzogs pa'i bro yi sa gzhi'am yul la /
NK094(nge)001:486: zhe sdang gi gnyen po thugs rje'i khro bo a
NK094(nge)001:487: ba glang mgo khros pa'i tshig gis las bgrang ba
NK094(nge)001:488: lta bur ma rangas khros pa'i stabsa chen byas shing
NK094(nge)001:489: / ha dang pa tsa lta bu srin po ma rangas khros pa'i glu sha ta pa nyid /
NK094(nge)001:490: dpe rdza rong nas chu 'bab pa la blangs te bzlas pas /
NK094(nge)001:491: longs sku'i khro bor bzhengs te /
NK094(nge)001:492: ma tram gi gam du sdigs mdzub dang bcas par sngags bzlas pas kho 'dar yed yed /
NK094(nge)001:493: 'khor rnams snying zhum nas mig rtsa rig rig tu
NK094(nge)001:494: 'dug pa dang mthun par gnas ngan yongs su sgrol
NK094(nge)001:495: ba ste / rdo rje srin po'i ngur sgra yis //
NK094(nge)001:496: gdug byed thams cad spa yang bkong //
NK094(nge)001:498: rdo rje theg pa'i ye shes rlung gi bu yug
NK094(nge)001:499: dang skar mad'i 'od kyis zhe sdang 'joms shing 'khor
NK094(nge)001:500: ba'i tsha grang yang sel ba'i tshig brjod pa dang
NK094(nge)001:502: gdug pa 'dul ba'i nus rtsal 'gyed pa'i sngags tshig kyang yin no //
NK094(nge)001:505: nyon mongs lnga yi sa gzhi la //
NK094(nge)001:506: yi ge ye shes lnga gsal bas //
NK094(nge)001:508: khyu mchog lnga yi stabs kyis rol //
NK094(nge)001:509: seng ge'i nga rol rngam pa'i glu //
NK094(nge)001:510: rdo rje don rab sgrogs pa'i tshig /rmad byung rol pa'i don 'byung ba //
NK094(nge)001:511: e ma ho ngo mtshar ya mtshan che //
NK094(nge)001:512: dgyes pas rol pa'i byin rlabs las //
NK094(nge)001:513: rgyud drug rtsad gcod ngo mtshar che //
NK094(nge)001:514: zhes shar du dug lnga 'a joms shing ngan song gnas sgrol gyi bro dang /
NK094(nge)001:515: mnyam pa chen po'i nam mkha' la //
NK094(nge)001:516: ye shes 'bar ba'i me byung bas //
NK094(nge)001:517: 'khor ba khrag gi rgya mtsho bskams //
NK094(nge)001:518: sdug bsngal dbyings su zad mdzad pa'i //
NK094(nge)001:519: mi gnas klong nas cho 'phrul ba //
NK094(nge)001:522: srid gsum khrag mtsho rngo nas skams //
NK094(nge)001:523: dpa' bo tsham ngam gyad kyi stabs //
NK094(nge)001:524: srin po ma tram khros pa'i glu //
NK094(nge)001:525: theg chen rmad byung gsang ba'i tshig /chags pa'i rtod phur gting nas phyung //
NK094(nge)001:526: zhes lho ru khrag 'thung rol pas 'dul sbyong grags pa'i bro dang /
NK094(nge)001:527: mkha' bzhi dbyings kyi bde klong nas //
NK094(nge)001:529: dgyes mchog rol pa'i phrin las las //
NK094(nge)001:530: la la shes rab thabs la rol //
NK094(nge)001:531: la la thugs rje las la rol //
NK094(nge)001:532: la la gdul bya'i yul la rol //
NK094(nge)001:533: la la ye shes dbyings la rol //
NK094(nge)001:534: thabs kyi rgyal po rtogs pa'i dbang //
NK094(nge)001:535: che ba lung gi khyad par las //
NK094(nge)001:536: rgyal ba kun dang mnyam par sbyor //
NK094(nge)001:537: rdo rje pad+ma rol pa'i stabs //
NK094(nge)001:538: chags med mkha' la gsal ba'i tshig /dug gsum zil gyis gnon pa'i glu //
NK094(nge)001:539: 'jig rten rim gyis sbyar ba'i phyir //
NK094(nge)001:540: 'jig rten khams su rol pa byung //
NK094(nge)001:541: 'jig rten drug gi snying la rol //
NK094(nge)001:542: bdag po gtso bo zil mnan nas //
NK094(nge)001:543: 'khor ni snyan pa'i tshig gis bsten //
NK094(nge)001:544: 'khor ba'i lam lnga rgyun bcad nas //
NK094(nge)001:545: rnam thar nam mkha'i ngang du brlan //
NK094(nge)001:546: gar mchog glog ltar 'gyu ba yin //
NK094(nge)001:547: rmad byung gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK094(nge)001:550: khams gsum bud shing thal bar rlags //
NK094(nge)001:551: rdo rje bu yug skar mad'i stabs //
NK094(nge)001:552: rdo rje 'brug chen ldir ba'i glu //
NK094(nge)001:553: don grub rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig /gdug pa'i dpung rnams rnam par 'joms //
NK094(nge)001:554: zhes nub tu rta gdong zhags kyi bro dang //
NK094(nge)001:555: rdo rje sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor pas //
NK094(nge)001:556: thabs kyi byang chub sems sprin 'phros //
NK094(nge)001:557: dbang sdud chags pa'i khyad par las //
NK094(nge)001:558: 'jig rten bu mo drug dang rol //
NK094(nge)001:559: seng ge rnam par rol pa'i stabs //
NK094(nge)001:560: rdo rje khyung skad 'gyur ba'i glu //
NK094(nge)001:561: chags pa rtsad nas gcod pa'i tshig /rdo rje rol pa'i don chen po //
NK094(nge)001:562: zhes byang du bu mo drug dang rol pa'i bro dang bzhir gsungs so //
NK094(nge)001:567: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:568: bro stabs kyis don ci 'grub snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:569: yon tan rmad du byung ba'i ston pa'i thugs kyi bkod pa'i chos dbyings gsang ba'i dkyil 'khora nas /
NK094(nge)001:570: ye shes 'od lngar 'bar ba'i me nyid byung basa /
NK094(nge)001:571: lha'i le lo sogs khamas gsum 'khor ba'i bud shing bsregsa pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:572: yi dwags kyi chags pa sogs srid gsum 'khor ba'i khrag gi rgya mtsho bskamsa shing /
NK094(nge)001:573: lha ma yin sogs nga rgyal gyi ri bo rming nas bshig ste /
NK094(nge)001:574: dmyal ba sogs kyi zhe sdang 'bar ba'i me dbal basda nas /
NK094(nge)001:575: byol song sogs kyi gti mug gi mun pa gtan nasa bcoma pas /
NK094(nge)001:576: mi la sogs pa rigs drug gi sa bon gsogs
NK094(nge)001:577: pa'i 'khor ba 'dus pa'i 'dam rdzab bskamsa par mdzad
NK094(nge)001:578: pa ni thugs rjes don grub pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:579: de dag ni lo rgyus brjod pas rgyal ba'i mdzad pa ste rjes su 'jug pa'ang mthun no //
NK094(nge)001:584: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:587: gdul bya gang gi cha dang mthun par sbyar ba'i
NK094(nge)001:588: spyod pas gzhug tu dam pa'i don la sbyor bar
NK094(nge)001:590: don la shed ma bye bas byis pa rnams thabs
NK094(nge)001:591: kyis 'drid pa'i rol pa cir yang 'char bas yid
NK094(nge)001:592: 'dren pa'i spyod pa ste cha mthun sbyor ba'i lung
NK094(nge)001:602: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:605: gazhana yang thabs mkhas kyi spyod pa gang zhig /res
NK094(nge)001:606: kho'i spyod pa ltar dang res rang gi spyod pa
NK094(nge)001:607: ltar byas nas gzhug tu don mchog rdzogs pa'i thabs
NK094(nge)001:608: kyi theg pa chen po la gzud pa'i mdzad pa
NK094(nge)001:609: thabsa 'dzud bsre ba'i brtul zhugsa ni mi mthun pa
NK094(nge)001:610: brtul zhing don chen po la zhugs pa'i phyir ming
NK094(nge)001:611: yang 'grub bo // de'i don rgyas par 'chad pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:612: 'jig rten na log sred can rnams kyi spyod pa ji lta ba de dang mthun par /
NK094(nge)001:613: gsang ba bas kyang 'og gi brtul zhugsa kyi spyod
NK094(nge)001:614: pa'i khyad par nyer gsum po 'di dag de ltar
NK094(nge)001:619: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:620: de la brtul zhugs spyod pa'i dam tshig bcu tshan gnyis dang gsum ni /
NK094(nge)001:621: thog mar wa yi brtul zhugs ni srog la bab
NK094(nge)001:622: na rang gi lag pa'ang bcad de 'bros pa ste
NK094(nge)001:623: / de bzhin du rnal 'byor mchog gis bla ma
NK094(nge)001:624: dang mched kyi nang du srog la bab kyang mi
NK094(nge)001:625: 'da' bar bsrung zhing skyon spang ba'i tshul gyis bsrung
NK094(nge)001:626: bya la 'dzem pa'i brtul zhugs te /
NK094(nge)001:627: bshad rgyud sgyu 'phrul rngam glog las /
NK094(nge)001:628: wa yi brtul zhugs chen po yis //
NK094(nge)001:629: spang bar bya ba'i thabs su spyad //
NK094(nge)001:631: 'o na de nyid bshad pa'i log sred can gyi spyod par 'gyur ram zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:632: mu stegs pa dag ni wa dang cang shes la
NK094(nge)001:633: sogs pa las mtho ris su 'gro ba mngon par
NK094(nge)001:634: shes pas mthong nas rgyu dngos ma shes pa de
NK094(nge)001:635: dag gi spyod pa'i dngos por gyur snyam nas sems
NK094(nge)001:636: can de dag gi spyod pa ci 'dra bar spyod
NK094(nge)001:637: pa'i log pa'i brtul zhugs can dag ste /
NK094(nge)001:638: 'dir rnal 'byor chen po bas kyang bsrung ba'i dper yang 'gyur la /
NK094(nge)001:639: spyod pa dngos mthun par spyad pas drang ba'ang yin te /
NK094(nge)001:640: de ltar kun la'ang sbyar bar bya ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:641: cang shes ni rdzu 'phrul myur mgyogs dang ldan pa
NK094(nge)001:642: ltar dam tshig bsrung mtshams shes pas thogs pa med
NK094(nge)001:643: par mthar phyin par mkhas shing shes bya kun la
NK094(nge)001:644: zhugs te gang yang skad cig gis 'grub pa bya
NK094(nge)001:645: ba'i myur mgyogs brtson 'grus drag po'i brtul zhugs te
NK094(nge)001:646: / cang shes brtul zhugs chen po yis //
NK094(nge)001:647: shes bya kun la 'jug par bya //
NK094(nge)001:650: lus kyi rtsa phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan pas
NK094(nge)001:651: bdag po'ang gnas min las srung bar byed pa ltar
NK094(nge)001:652: lus kyi rtsal gyi bya ba'ang gsang don bsrung zhing
NK094(nge)001:653: gdams pa mi g.yel bar rtsal shugsa che ba'i brtul
NK094(nge)001:654: zhugs te / lus kyi rtsal gyi bya ba dag /gyi ling brtul zhugs chen pos bya //
NK094(nge)001:656: shin tu stobs drag pa'i glang chen rgun chang gis myos pas pha rol gyi dpung 'joms pa ltar /
NK094(nge)001:658: dgra bzhi'am gdug pa dang gdul bya ril 'dul zhing
NK094(nge)001:659: tshar gcod pas blang dor med pa'i brtul zhugs te
NK094(nge)001:660: / glang chen myos pa'i brtul zhugs kyis /
NK094(nge)001:661: mi 'byed rmongs tshul bstan par bya //
NK094(nge)001:663: dapa'a rtul ldan pa'i za byed stag ni gtum rngama
NK094(nge)001:664: 'khrug pa'i rang bzhin gyis gsod bya 'joms pa ltar
NK094(nge)001:665: / thugs rje'i thabs kyis zhing bcu sgrol ba'i rnal 'byor mchog gi spyod pa'i brtul zhugs te /
NK094(nge)001:666: stag mchog rngam pa'i brtul zhugs kyis //
NK094(nge)001:667: dpa' rtul gtum pa'i las chen bya //
NK094(nge)001:669: mkha' lding gi rgyal po khyung chen gyis gyen phyogs
NK094(nge)001:670: gang la mi lta ba'am khob 'og thams cad ma
NK094(nge)001:672: bla ma dang grogs las rang bzang bar mi lta zhing rang gsal lta ba'i brtul zhugs te /
NK094(nge)001:673: khyung chen mkha' lding brtul zhugs kyis //
NK094(nge)001:674: lta ba'i spyi rgya rlabs kyis gcad //
NK094(nge)001:676: don ni zhe sdang che bas lus gtum zhing sems
NK094(nge)001:677: thung ste sdong chen 'jigsa pa 'dril ba bzhin rming
NK094(nge)001:678: nas pha rol tshar gcod pa ltar rnal 'byor mchog
NK094(nge)001:679: gis khro bo'i mdzad pa drag po'i las gcig tshugs
NK094(nge)001:680: su byed pa'i brtul zhugs te /
NK094(nge)001:681: gtum thung dom gyi brtul zhugs kyis //
NK094(nge)001:682: re ba med pa'i las chen bya //
NK094(nge)001:684: gsang ba'i don mchog gang yang srung thub pa dper
NK094(nge)001:685: na slar mi ldog nges pa rgya mtsho'i gting du
NK094(nge)001:686: gser gyi gar bu lhung ba khar mi 'ong ba
NK094(nge)001:687: ltar don chen po las mi ldog cing snod min
NK094(nge)001:688: la gsang ba mi spel ba'i brtul zhugs te /
NK094(nge)001:689: rgya mtsho gter gyi brtul zhugs kyis //
NK094(nge)001:690: yid thub mi ldog brtan par bya //
NK094(nge)001:692: phag gam lug ni yid kyi mun pa gti mug
NK094(nge)001:693: che bas blun zhing las gdong tshugs su byed pa
NK094(nge)001:694: ltar rnal 'byor pas lkug pa'i blo yi tshul dang
NK094(nge)001:695: ldan pas sngags dang phyag rgya gzhan la mi ston
NK094(nge)001:696: cing gang la'ang ris su mi 'byed par mthar phyin
NK094(nge)001:697: par byed pa mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs te /
NK094(nge)001:698: lkug pa lug gi brtul zhugs kyis //
NK094(nge)001:699: gti mug bzhin du shes rab ldan //
NK094(nge)001:701: dpe la lar lkug pa lta bu'i /
NK094(nge)001:702: zhes kyang bzhugs te phag dang lug gang yin kyang don 'dra'o //
NK094(nge)001:703: ri rab lhun po ltar bla ma la lci bar
NK094(nge)001:704: sems shing mi 'gyur bar brtan pa che ba'i brtul
NK094(nge)001:705: zhugs te / ri bo lta bu'i brtul zhugs kyis //
NK094(nge)001:706: mi 'gyur rab tu brtan par bya //
NK094(nge)001:708: dper na nam mkha'a la yang dog med pa ltar
NK094(nge)001:709: rnal 'byor pas kyang ting nge 'dzin rgod 'phyar gyi
NK094(nge)001:710: dbang du mi 'gyur ba dang mched lcam gyi nang
NK094(nge)001:711: du shong yangsa che zhing gu dog med par gang
NK094(nge)001:712: la'ang spong len dang re dogs kyi rnam rtog kun
NK094(nge)001:713: dang bral ba'i brtul zhugs te /
NK094(nge)001:714: nam mkha' lta bu'i brtul zhugs kyis //
NK094(nge)001:715: yangs dog kun dang bral bar bya //
NK094(nge)001:717: dpe ganma lcagsa lce yi thogs chen gang la bab
NK094(nge)001:718: kyang 'joms pa ltar 'khro ba'i bzlas pa drag po'i
NK094(nge)001:719: phrin las gang btsug pa mthar phyin te drag shul
NK094(nge)001:720: can du byed pa'i brtul zhugs te /
NK094(nge)001:721: gnam lcags lce yi brtul zhugs kyis //
NK094(nge)001:722: drag shul las la sbyar bar bya //
NK094(nge)001:724: dpal phyag na rdo rje drag shul chen po ni
NK094(nge)001:725: gdul dka' 'joms pa'i phrin las kyi brtul zhugsa mchog
NK094(nge)001:726: gi bdag po yin pa ltar rnal 'byor pas kyang
NK094(nge)001:727: khro bo sgoms nas phrin las drag po'i mthu stobs
NK094(nge)001:728: kyis dgra bgegs 'joms pa'i brtul zhugs te /
NK094(nge)001:729: lag na rdo rje'i brtul zhugs kyis //
NK094(nge)001:730: mthu stobs dag la spyad par bya //
NK094(nge)001:732: khwa'am bya rog ni zon che zhing khu 'phrig dang
NK094(nge)001:733: ldan pa lta bu'i rnal 'byor pa'ang bla ma dang
NK094(nge)001:734: mched kyi nang sogs gang la yang khu 'phrig dang
NK094(nge)001:735: zon bag chen po can gyi blo dang ldan pa'i
NK094(nge)001:736: brtul zhugs te / khwa rog brtul zhugs chen po yis //
NK094(nge)001:737: zon bag khu 'phrig spyad par bya //
NK094(nge)001:739: ngesa pa'i don la nga rgyal gyis gding skyed pa
NK094(nge)001:740: dper na stobs ldan glang chen rba klong la mi
NK094(nge)001:741: lta bar chu rgal ba bzhin du yin pa'i don
NK094(nge)001:742: la nges par bstun te sran tshugs pas ci la'ang
NK094(nge)001:743: mi lta ba'i brtul zhugs te /
NK094(nge)001:744: glang chen chur 'jug brtul zhug kyis //
NK094(nge)001:745: nges pa'i nga rgyal spyad par bya //
NK094(nge)001:747: zla spangs te grogs med par seng ge gcig pur
NK094(nge)001:748: gnas te mi 'jigs par brtan pa ltar rnal 'byor
NK094(nge)001:749: pas dgon par grogs ngan spangs te gcig pur gnas
NK094(nge)001:750: pas lta sgom gyi brjid pa don chen po 'grub
NK094(nge)001:752: ri dwags seng ge'i brtul zhugs kyis //
NK094(nge)001:753: grogs ngan la sogs spang bar bya //
NK094(nge)001:755: dper na reg 'jam gyi bya ni /
NK094(nge)001:756: gshog pas bskyabs pas mtshon gyis mi tshugs shing khyo
NK094(nge)001:757: shug gcig la gcig brtse bas shin tu chags nas
NK094(nge)001:759: bla ma dang mched kyi bar du dbyen gyis mi
NK094(nge)001:760: tshugs par thabs shes sam sems can rnams la brtse
NK094(nge)001:761: ba'i chagsa sems dang mi 'bral ba'i gdung ba'i yid
NK094(nge)001:762: kyis 'grogsa pa bde ba'i brtul zhugs te /
NK094(nge)001:763: reg 'jam bya yi brtul zhugs kyis //
NK094(nge)001:764: 'grogs na bde zhing chags par bya //
NK094(nge)001:766: dper na sgyu ma mkhan gyis slu sems kyis rta
NK094(nge)001:767: dang glang po byed de sgyu ma'i tshul gyis 'drid
NK094(nge)001:768: pa ltar rnal 'byor chen po bas sku phyag rgya
NK094(nge)001:769: sgyu ma'i dkyil 'khor bsgom nas de la'ang mi gnas
NK094(nge)001:770: par thabs la mkhas pas don byed pa'i brtul zhugs
NK094(nge)001:771: te / sgyu ma'i phyag rgya'i brtul zhugs kyis //
NK094(nge)001:772: thabs la mkhas pa'i las chen bya //
NK094(nge)001:774: kun 'dus ltar na phag gong du song bas khyi'am
NK094(nge)001:775: phag pa rnams zas gang la yang gtsang sme'i rtog
NK094(nge)001:776: pa med par kun za zhing spyod pa ltar /
NK094(nge)001:777: rnal 'byor pa'ang kha zas la blang dor med pa'i brtul zhugs nyid de /
NK094(nge)001:778: phag gi brtul zhugs chen po yis //
NK094(nge)001:779: gtsang sme med pa kun la spyad //
NK094(nge)001:781: lce spyang gis thogsa pa med par myur du gsod cing spyod pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:782: za byed khra ni de ltar gsod cing mang po za bar byed pa'i dpe ltar /
NK094(nge)001:783: rnal 'byor pa'ang zhing bcu la sogs pa skad cig
NK094(nge)001:784: la sgrol zhing zhal du gsol ba'i brtul zhugs te
NK094(nge)001:785: / ce spyang khra yi brtul zhugs kyis //
NK094(nge)001:786: thogs med gsod la brtson par bya //
NK094(nge)001:788: 'dir spar ma la rkang pa gsum yod kyang /
NK094(nge)001:789: phyag mchan gnyis su drangs par mi 'dug go //
NK094(nge)001:790: dpe yud ltar myur mgyogsa ldan pa glog ltar du
NK094(nge)001:791: 'gyu ste thugs rje chen pos yud tsam la'ang bdag
NK094(nge)001:792: gzhan gyi don mdzad pa'i brtul zhugs te /
NK094(nge)001:793: bar snang glog gi brtul zhugs kyis //
NK094(nge)001:794: ci la'ang myur mgyogs brtson par bya //
NK094(nge)001:795: zhes phyag dpe gnyis la drangs so //
NK094(nge)001:797: che ba'i nga rgyal stag mchog blo //
NK094(nge)001:799: rnal 'byor pa theg mchog rgyal por zhum pa med par 'jug pa'i brtul zhugs te /
NK094(nge)001:800: nga rgyal stag mchog brtul zhugs kyis //
NK094(nge)001:801: che ba'i nga rgyal bskyed par bya //
NK094(nge)001:803: dper na bya rgod gang gis srog mi gcod par
NK094(nge)001:804: sdom pa srungs shing gzhan gyi god gang la 'brang
NK094(nge)001:805: ste bsrung bas nama mkha'a lding gi dbang po ltar
NK094(nge)001:806: / rnal 'byor pas bla ma dang mched kyi dkor
NK094(nge)001:807: dang kha na ma tho la 'dzem zhing gdul byar
NK094(nge)001:808: gyur pa'i rdzas ma byin par blangs pas kyang gzhan
NK094(nge)001:809: don sgrub pa'i brtul zhugs te /
NK094(nge)001:810: mkha' lding lta bu'i brtul zhugs kyis //
NK094(nge)001:811: kun tu 'dzem pa'i las chen bya //
NK094(nge)001:813: sa bdag gang rgyal sa thub cing gdan non la
NK094(nge)001:814: dgongs pa'i nyams bag chen pos blo rtsal len pa'i
NK094(nge)001:815: rgyal po mchog gis yul 'khor nges par skyong ba'i
NK094(nge)001:816: dpe ltar / rnal 'byor pas dgongs pa mnyam pa'i
NK094(nge)001:817: gzhi las ma g.yos par gsal zhing rig pas nyes
NK094(nge)001:818: pa thub la gdul bya rnams thabs kyis 'dren cing
NK094(nge)001:819: skyong bas byin rlabs che ba'i brtul zhugs te /
NK094(nge)001:820: rgyal po 'khor skyong brtul zhugs kyis //
NK094(nge)001:821: sa thub 'khor dang ldan par bya //
NK094(nge)001:824: cang shes dang gyi ling gnyis gcig tu byas te /
NK094(nge)001:825: blang dor mi 'bral khon chen bdag /ces gsungs pas
NK094(nge)001:826: nyi ma'i brtul zhugs ni kun la snyoms pa'i blang
NK094(nge)001:827: dor med pa'i las dang mi 'bral bar khon chen
NK094(nge)001:828: mun par 'joms pa'i bdag nyid yin pa ltar /
NK094(nge)001:829: rnal 'byor mchog gis ci la'ang rnam rtog med pa'i
NK094(nge)001:830: ye shes mnga' bas ma rig pa 'joms pa'i brtul
NK094(nge)001:831: zhugs bsnan nas grangs nges su mdzad de 'grel chen
NK094(nge)001:833: 'dir chos rje dam pa rin po che'i phyag mchan
NK094(nge)001:834: sogs na bzhugs pa ltar rngam glog gi lung dang
NK094(nge)001:835: bcas pa drangs te bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:840: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:841: de ltar rnal 'byor mchog gi spyod pa'i brtul zhugsa
NK094(nge)001:842: chena pa thabs 'dzud bsre ba'i dam tshig kun gyi
NK094(nge)001:844: bcu phrag gnyis dang slar ni gsum ste nyer gsum
NK094(nge)001:845: gyi spyod tshul rnams la mkhas blor ldan pas dam
NK094(nge)001:846: pa gang su zhig gis sgo 'dir nyamsa su blangs
NK094(nge)001:847: te dang du len cing spyod par byed pa de
NK094(nge)001:848: dag rnal 'byor dam pas gasnga chen theg pa'i rgyal
NK094(nge)001:849: pos gdul bya 'dren pa'i thabsa mchog phul du byung
NK094(nge)001:850: ba ste / tshul des bdag nyid theg pa chen
NK094(nge)001:851: po gang la zhugs nas gdul bya gzhan yang 'dzud
NK094(nge)001:852: par byed pasa bdag dang kho'i spyod pa bsre ba
NK094(nge)001:853: yi tshul gyis gdul bya thamsa cad dang spyod pa
NK094(nge)001:854: rnam dbye med par gcig tu bya ba'i phyir thabs
NK094(nge)001:856: spyir na dka' thub dang brtul zhugs ni dka' thub
NK094(nge)001:857: dam tshig tu 'gyur zhing spyod par yang ston to
NK094(nge)001:858: // brtul zhugs ni spyod pa kho nar 'chad de /
NK094(nge)001:859: 'dir yang gdul bya'i dbang gis spyod par rigs so //
NK094(nge)001:860: 'o na brtul zhugs kyi dpe dag ni log sred can yin no zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:861: de dag log pa la snang ba yin kyang log sred can du mi 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:862: mu stegs can kho nar nges par de dag gi
NK094(nge)001:863: sgo nas thabs kyis gzud pa la the tshom med
NK094(nge)001:864: do // gsum pa la gsum ste /
NK094(nge)001:872: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:874: zhes sdud pa po la bos nas gazhana yang gang
NK094(nge)001:875: gdul bya'i cha dang mthun pasa don la 'jug par
NK094(nge)001:876: byed pa'i thabs kyi spyod pa'i lung 'chad pa ni
NK094(nge)001:877: / gdul bya gang yang rung ba nyid kyi spyod
NK094(nge)001:878: pa de nyid dang mthun pa de ltar bdag gi
NK094(nge)001:879: spyod pa'ang de ji lta ba bzhin du mthun 'jug
NK094(nge)001:880: tu spyod pas drang thabs te /
NK094(nge)001:881: gang gdul bya 'jig rten pa'i spyod pa dang tshul
NK094(nge)001:882: 'dra bar cha mthun dang spyod pa ganga yin pa
NK094(nge)001:887: mun par snang ba mthun 'jug spyod //
NK094(nge)001:888: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:889: de dag gi tshul nyid ji ltar spyod snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:890: chags pa ni zhe sdang dang gti mug gnyis ka'i gzhir gyur pas gnyis ka la'ang smos te /
NK094(nge)001:891: 'gro ba rnams kyis gdoda pa la chagsa pasa las
NK094(nge)001:892: kyi rgyu rkyen gyi dbang las pho mor smin te
NK094(nge)001:893: chags yul gyi lus su gyur pa la /
NK094(nge)001:894: 'khrul pa'i spyod yul pho mora snang nas 'dod chags la zhen pa dag la /
NK094(nge)001:895: 'dul byed kyang lha yab yum la sogs pa rnam pa pho mor snang ba gang yina pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:896: sems kyi chos nyid rang 'od gsal ba ji lta
NK094(nge)001:897: ba'i ngang la pho mo ma dmigs pas med par
NK094(nge)001:898: gyur pa la thugs rje'i byin rlabs yab yum gyi
NK094(nge)001:899: dkyil 'khor la sogs par pho mor shar ba'i tshul
NK094(nge)001:900: gyis yab yum du rnam par snang ba dag gis
NK094(nge)001:901: 'dod chags can dang mthun par 'jug pa'i spyod pas
NK094(nge)001:903: de bzhin du rgyu 'dod pa la chagsa pas sam
NK094(nge)001:904: yang na zhe sdang gi las la zhen pasa gzhan
NK094(nge)001:905: la khro bar gyur pa la /
NK094(nge)001:906: 'khrul pa la zhen nas khro bar 'dod pa'i dbang
NK094(nge)001:907: gis las kyi khro bor snang ba la 'dul byed
NK094(nge)001:908: thugs rje'i khro bo'i skur rnam par snang ba gang
NK094(nge)001:909: yin pa yang / chos nyid mnyam pa chen po
NK094(nge)001:910: la rang rgyud pa'i khro bor snang ba med pa
NK094(nge)001:911: lasa las kyi ke'u seng la ye shes kyi ke'u
NK094(nge)001:912: seng gis don mdzad pa la sogs pa lta bur
NK094(nge)001:913: byin rlabs kyis khro bar snang ba mthun 'jug gi
NK094(nge)001:914: spyod pas don mdzad cing 'dul ba yin pa lta
NK094(nge)001:915: yin pa yang / bu'o // de bzhin du rgyu
NK094(nge)001:916: 'dod pa la chagsa pasa dbang las ma rig pa'i
NK094(nge)001:917: mun pas non par snang ba dag la /
NK094(nge)001:918: blang dor ma shes pas gti mug gi mun par
NK094(nge)001:919: 'dod pa'i dbang lasa gdul bya'i ngo la gti mug
NK094(nge)001:920: chen po 'byed pa med pa'i mun par snang bar
NK094(nge)001:922: chos nyid dbyings kyi ngang la log pa'i mun pa med pa lasa /
NK094(nge)001:923: blang dor gyi dmigs pa med par yang dag pa'i
NK094(nge)001:924: mun par snang ba de yang mthun 'jug gi spyod
NK094(nge)001:925: pa yul dang mthun pas 'dul zhing don mdzad pa
NK094(nge)001:930: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:931: de bas na gdul bya ji ltar spyod pa dang
NK094(nge)001:932: gang ltar spyod pa de bzhin du spyad cing don
NK094(nge)001:933: mdzad pa'o // dug gsum 'dul ba de dag dang
NK094(nge)001:934: la sogsa pa zhes dngos po gzhan bsdu ba'i sgras
NK094(nge)001:935: 'gro ba'i nyon mongs pa'i spyod pa mtha' yas par
NK094(nge)001:936: snang ba rdul snyed pa'i gnas thamsa cad ril du
NK094(nge)001:937: 'das pa dang ma 'das pa'i spyod pa nang ris
NK094(nge)001:938: mi mthun pa ji snyed pa thamsa cad gang gis
NK094(nge)001:939: 'dul ba'i dus la bab pa de dang der so
NK094(nge)001:940: so'i snang ba dang mthun par 'jug pa'i tshul gyis
NK094(nge)001:941: byin rlabs snang ba'i spyod pasa don byed cing gdul
NK094(nge)001:947: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:949: bshad pa de daga ni mthun par 'jug par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:950: zhes sngar dam bca' bar mdzad pa'i dgongsa pa yongsa su bgros par shes bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:951: zhes bka' stsal te rjes su 'jug pa'ang mthun no //
NK094(nge)001:952: de skad ces smras pasa lang ka'i bdag po la
NK094(nge)001:953: sogsa pa 'khor dman pa dam pa rnams kyis mtha'
NK094(nge)001:954: thug pa meda pa'i lta spyod la nges pa'i gdengs
NK094(nge)001:955: rnyed de yongsa su rtog pa med par gyur to
NK094(nge)001:957: sangsa rgyas kun gyi dgongsa pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po lasa /
NK094(nge)001:958: sgyu ma lta bu'i mdzad pa gsum gyi rola pasa
NK094(nge)001:959: mtshan ma can dang log sred can dang nyon mongs
NK094(nge)001:960: pa can gyi gdul bya gsum gzung 'dzin rnam para
NK094(nge)001:961: grol te thar pa la sbyor bar bstan pa'i le'u
NK094(nge)001:962: zhes bya ste drug cu rtsa bzhi pa nyid rnam
NK094(nge)001:963: par 'grel te bshad pa'o ////bcu pa nad gso bar
NK094(nge)001:965: nad gso ba'i thabs kyi khyad par spyir bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:966: bye brag tu sman gyi dris lan lo rgyus kyis bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:975: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:977: rnam grangs dgu pa bstan ma thag pa de nasa yanga /
NK094(nge)001:978: sdud pa po lang ka'i bdag pos /
NK094(nge)001:979: ston pa gsang ba pa'i bdag po nyid la dri ba yongsa su dris pa /
NK094(nge)001:980: kye gsang ba pa'i bdag po /
NK094(nge)001:981: nyid kyis le'u zhe lnga par chos kyi rnam grangs bcur bkod pa las /
NK094(nge)001:982: bcu pa nad gso bar bya'o zhes dam bca' bar dgongsa pa de nyid /
NK094(nge)001:983: tshul ji ltar yongsa su shes par bgyi /
NK094(nge)001:984: de skad ces yongas su dris pa lasa /
NK094(nge)001:992: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:993: skyes bu gsang ba pa'i badga posa lan gsungs te smras pa /
NK094(nge)001:995: dris pa de dag ni 'di ltar te /
NK094(nge)001:996: bsod nams dang ldan pa'i bdag gzhan khams kyi grong
NK094(nge)001:997: khyer gsum gyi 'gro ba nad gcong chen po can
NK094(nge)001:998: rnams thabs dam pa rmad du byung bas gso bar
NK094(nge)001:999: bya'o // nad kyi gzhi rtsa la makhasa pas lta bas thag bcad par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:1000: nad sbyang ba'i thabsa sngon du chos mnyan pa la brtson par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:1001: sman pa dam pa bla ma rnams bsten par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:1002: gnyen po dam pa'i sman sgom pa'i ngo bo srel zhing spel bar bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:1003: sman sbyar ba la makhasa pas blo bzhag par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:1004: sman gyi lam mchog skyon bcos thabs kyis bsrung bar bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:1005: 'bras bu gzhan don gyi spyod pa nad pa'i tshogsa dang mi 'bral bar bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:1006: 'bras bu bdag don gyi spyod pa nad kyi rgyun gcod par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:1007: don du nad kyi gnyen por gyur par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:1008: zhes rnam grangs bcu gsungs pa ni grangs kyi rtsa ba bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:1012: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:1015: de la sems bskyed pa'i yul grong khyer gsum ni /
NK094(nge)001:1016: gzugs med pa'i khams mi snang ba'i grong khyer dang /
NK094(nge)001:1017: gzugs kyi khams kun snang ba'i grong khyer dang /
NK094(nge)001:1018: 'dod pa'i khams phyed snang ba'i grong khyer rang gi nyon mongs pa'i nad kyis gzir ba dag ste /
NK094(nge)001:1023: nad kyi gzhi rtsa ni lhan cig skyes pa'i ma
NK094(nge)001:1024: rig mun pa chena po dang kun tu brtags pa
NK094(nge)001:1025: las byung ba'i gzung 'dzin gyi snang ba dang nyon
NK094(nge)001:1027: lta bas thag gcad pa la mkhas pas chos nyid du ngo shes pa bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:1029: sman gyi mchog tu gyur pa dam pa'i chos zab
NK094(nge)001:1030: mo nyan pa dang sman para nges pa'i bla ma
NK094(nge)001:1031: man ngag can gyis bstan pa blo la 'jog ste
NK094(nge)001:1034: dge ba'i bshes gnyen mkhas mchog bla ma dam pa
NK094(nge)001:1035: gser la nag mtshur gtong ba lta bu las khungs
NK094(nge)001:1036: kyi dbang dang man ngag thob cing dgongs pa gsal
NK094(nge)001:1037: ba ste 'chad pa'i mtshan nyid rnams dang ldan pa
NK094(nge)001:1039: nad kyi gnyen po dam pa'i sman ni /
NK094(nge)001:1040: sgom pa'i ngo bo zhi gnas kyi ting nge 'dzin
NK094(nge)001:1041: dang shes rab rang gsal sgrib pa med pas gsang
NK094(nge)001:1044: lta bas rtogs pa'i don de /
NK094(nge)001:1045: ting nge 'dzin gyis nyams su blangs te zhi gnas
NK094(nge)001:1046: dang lhag mthong de dag gzung du 'brel ba nyid
NK094(nge)001:1047: du sbyor bar byed pa'i bzhag thabs la mkhas pa'o
NK094(nge)001:1048: // sman gyi lam bsrung ba ni skyon bcos pa'i thabs te /
NK094(nge)001:1049: ci spyad thams cad mnyam pa'i don dang ma bral
NK094(nge)001:1050: bar chos nyid de bzhin nyid lasa mi mda' bar
NK094(nge)001:1051: spyod pa nyid du bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:1052: sgom pa'i 'bras bu nad pa'i tshogsa dang mi 'bral
NK094(nge)001:1053: ba ni gzhan don gyi spyod pa ste 'khor ba
NK094(nge)001:1054: sgyu ma'i rang bzhin du rtogs pa las bskal pa
NK094(nge)001:1055: rgya mtshor 'gro don mdzad pa la mi skyo ba
NK094(nge)001:1056: dang dub pa'ang mi mnga' ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:1057: nad kyi rgyun gcad par bya ba ni /
NK094(nge)001:1059: dngos po dang dngos po med pa'i chos thamsa cad
NK094(nge)001:1060: rang rig pa de kho na nyid rang bzhin 'od
NK094(nge)001:1061: gsal ba nyid du ngesa par mjal te gdengs dang
NK094(nge)001:1062: ldan pa'o // nad kyi gnyen por gyur pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:1063: 'adi'ang gzhan don phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK094(nge)001:1064: thugs rje chen po'i mdzad spyod kyis 'khor ba yongas
NK094(nge)001:1065: su sgrol bar byed pa rgyal ba nyid kyi mdzad
NK094(nge)001:1066: pa'o // gnyis pa la gsum ste /
NK094(nge)001:1069: lan gyi yon tan bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:1074: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:1075: de dag skyes bu chen pos sngon gyi lo rgyus kyis yid ches par bya ba'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:1078: de yanga chos kyi rnam grangs bcu pa'i don gang
NK094(nge)001:1079: sngon gsang bdag nyid kyis thos pa'i lo rgyus brjod
NK094(nge)001:1080: pa ni / gsang ba'i bdag po kho bosa sngon
NK094(nge)001:1081: ma nor bar mthong zhing thos pa'i skabs gcig gi
NK094(nge)001:1083: sangs rgyas kun gyi dge ba'i bshes gnyen ston pa
NK094(nge)001:1084: rdo rje sems dpa' gsang ba dam pa he ru
NK094(nge)001:1085: ka des / dur khrod kyi bdag po chen po ru tra btul ba'i tshe nyid na /
NK094(nge)001:1086: 'jig rten so so'i gtso bo lha chen dang phyogs
NK094(nge)001:1087: skyong kun spyan sngar rang dbang med par 'dus nas
NK094(nge)001:1088: rigs nges pa'i sras kyi tshogsa su bkod par gyur
NK094(nge)001:1089: pa yi 'khor dman pa'i lus can 'dus pa phala
NK094(nge)001:1090: mo che yi tshogs dag las kyi khyad par mtho
NK094(nge)001:1091: dman mang po lasa thugs rje'i mdzad pa rlabs po
NK094(nge)001:1092: che'i 'khor der 'dus par gyur pa yi nang nas
NK094(nge)001:1093: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa'am 'khor 'dus pa'i zhar la
NK094(nge)001:1094: byung ba dregs pa 'khor bcas brtul ba'i zhor la
NK094(nge)001:1095: dbang du 'dus par gyur pa'i lta spyod log pa'i
NK094(nge)001:1096: sde pa mu stegs kyi cha 'dzin pa gang zhig
NK094(nge)001:1097: dam rdzas la rang rgyud du spyod pas sman gyi
NK094(nge)001:1098: brtul zhugsa cher spyod de zhen pas 'dzin cing des
NK094(nge)001:1099: 'bras bu sgrubs pa 'di dag drang srong rang rgyud
NK094(nge)001:1100: kyi skabs las gdul ba'i 'khor du gyur pa rnams
NK094(nge)001:1101: te / gtso bo ru tra nyid gsang sngags la
NK094(nge)001:1102: spyod pa'i ming ni sgo gsum drag pas log pa'i
NK094(nge)001:1103: sde pa drang srong nag po k+aa la zhes bya
NK094(nge)001:1104: te / ba yisa / ston pa gang de yi
NK094(nge)001:1105: spyan sngar gus pas 'dun nas sman gyi don gsol
NK094(nge)001:1107: ston pa dam pa che mchog sman gyi rgyal po /
NK094(nge)001:1108: zhes drang srong gis bos nas /
NK094(nge)001:1109: rang nyid sman gyi brtul zhugs 'dzin pa'i ngos nas /
NK094(nge)001:1110: ston mchog khyod ni 'gro ba'i log dug thams cad
NK094(nge)001:1111: 'jomas shing sel ba'i bdud rtsi chen po sman gyi
NK094(nge)001:1112: dkyil 'khora 'dzina pa'i mnga' bdag /nyon mongs pa phra
NK094(nge)001:1113: rags su grags pa'i nad do cog gi dgrar gyur
NK094(nge)001:1114: pa'i gnyen po 'joms byed chen po lags pasa /
NK094(nge)001:1115: ston pa dam pa khyod kyis 'gro ba'i rgyud la
NK094(nge)001:1116: yod pa'i las dang nyon mongs pa'i kun rtog gis
NK094(nge)001:1117: gzir bas zug rngu'i nad rnams zhi nas med par
NK094(nge)001:1118: mdzod cig par gsol ba btab pa ste nag po
NK094(nge)001:1119: k+aa las gzhan don du de skad zhu ba 'dun
NK094(nge)001:1120: te gus pas gsol ba lasa /
NK094(nge)001:1121: lan du rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dam rdzas
NK094(nge)001:1122: kyi mnga' bdag /ston pa che mchog he ru kar
NK094(nge)001:1123: snang ba'i sman gyi rgyal po desa drang srong de
NK094(nge)001:1124: la thugs rje chen pos rjes su dgongsa nas lta
NK094(nge)001:1125: ba log pa rnams 'dul ba'i phyir zhu ba po
NK094(nge)001:1126: la dgyes pas sngon du 'dus pa'i 'khor la gsungsa
NK094(nge)001:1127: te bka' stsal zin pa nyid de /
NK094(nge)001:1128: phyis zhar la btul nas 'dus pa'i 'khor la yanga lo rgyus su bka' stsal bar gsungsa pa /
NK094(nge)001:1129: khamsa gsuma nyid mgo bcad pa'i dung chen te za ma tog chen po'i snod kyi nang du /
NK094(nge)001:1130: 'chad pa'i srid pa gsum gyi semsa can kun gyi
NK094(nge)001:1131: lta ba ngan pa'am nyon mongs pa lnga'i dug chen
NK094(nge)001:1133: de dag tu snang ba nyid na'ang ye nas ma
NK094(nge)001:1134: bcos ma bslad par mtha' gnyis las grol bas dus
NK094(nge)001:1135: gsum gyi rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangsa rgyas thams cad
NK094(nge)001:1136: kyi bdud rtsi chen po'i ngo bo rang byung gi
NK094(nge)001:1137: ye shes su mjal ba ni sbyar ba ste /
NK094(nge)001:1138: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa nyid sbyangs pa las
NK094(nge)001:1139: byung ba'i dam tshig gi rdzas su grub pas rgyu
NK094(nge)001:1140: rkyen gyis 'phral du ma byas pas ranga byung chen
NK094(nge)001:1141: por rtog pa'i bdud la rang rig mnyam pa'i rtsi'i
NK094(nge)001:1142: dkyil 'khora yongs su rdzogsa pas lhag pa'i byang chub
NK094(nge)001:1143: kyi sems su shar ba nyid na don dam pa'i
NK094(nge)001:1145: rdzogs sku ye shes kyi rtsis phung khams skye mched
NK094(nge)001:1146: kyi bdud 'joms par rang byung don gyi bdud rtsi
NK094(nge)001:1147: chen por sangs rgyas te mthar thug par gyur pas
NK094(nge)001:1148: skyed du bya ba med pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:1149: zhes de skad ngesa para gsungsa te bka' stsal pa las /
NK094(nge)001:1151: rdzas lnga bdud rtsi lnga yin par zhus pa /
NK094(nge)001:1152: lan du rang byung ye shes nyid bdud rtsir gsungs pa /
NK094(nge)001:1153: rdzas lnga rang byung gi bdud rtsi yin pa'i dris lan 'phros su bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:1158: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:1159: nag po chen po nyid k+aa la'i sgra ste /
NK094(nge)001:1160: des na k+aa lasa slar yang ston pa la don gsol te zhus pa /
NK094(nge)001:1161: ston pa mchog gi thugs rje'i byin rlabs rang bzhin
NK094(nge)001:1162: lhun grub tu snang ba'i ngang nas sgro skur med
NK094(nge)001:1163: par bka' stsal ba'i rgyud kyi lung chen po 'di
NK094(nge)001:1164: nyid lasa ni / lus la bkod pa'i rmad du
NK094(nge)001:1165: byung ba'i yo byad chen po dam rdzas lnga ru
NK094(nge)001:1167: des dug lnga dang nad lnga la sogs pa sel
NK094(nge)001:1168: ba'i bdud rtsi chen po 'grub pa'i rgyu lngar gsungs
NK094(nge)001:1169: pa ste 'gro ba'i dug lnga 'byin pas bdud rtsi
NK094(nge)001:1170: rgyal ba dang drang srong rnams kyi spyad par bya
NK094(nge)001:1171: ba'i sman gyi mchog chen po nyid lags so //
NK094(nge)001:1172: zhes de skad ngesa par 'dun pa'i sgo nas zhus pa lasa /
NK094(nge)001:1177: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:1178: ston pa gsang ba mchog gi bdag po sman pa
NK094(nge)001:1179: dam pasa lan du k+aa la'i zhu ba'ang ma nor
NK094(nge)001:1180: ba'i don du bka' stsal pa 'di skad gsungsa te
NK094(nge)001:1181: / gsang sngags gsang ba'i sman gyi khyad par phyi
NK094(nge)001:1182: nang gsang ba'i skabs kyis 'dir nang dang gsang bar
NK094(nge)001:1184: nang gi smad pa'i rdzas lnga'i yang rgyu ru gyur
NK094(nge)001:1185: pa 'byung ba nyid kyang gsang ba rang rig pa
NK094(nge)001:1186: byang chub kyi sems rang byung gi ye shes su
NK094(nge)001:1187: rang byung ba nyid las gdod nas rgyu rkyen gyis
NK094(nge)001:1188: ma bskyed par rang shar zhing mtha'i skyon nyid rnam
NK094(nge)001:1189: par dag pa nyid kyi phyir rang bzhin lha'i dkyil
NK094(nge)001:1191: rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyud las /
NK094(nge)001:1192: rgyu yi mtshan nyid dag pa ni //
NK094(nge)001:1193: phyi rol chen po lnga rnams te //
NK094(nge)001:1194: rgyu nyid rang gi sems yin pas //
NK094(nge)001:1195: 'byung ba chen po rgyu las dag /
NK094(nge)001:1196: 'bras bu yongs su dag pa na //
NK094(nge)001:1197: sems can kun gyi rus pa ste //
NK094(nge)001:1198: rdo rje byang chub sems yin la //
NK094(nge)001:1200: dri chen dri chu gur gum chu //
NK094(nge)001:1201: so so'i lus la gnas pa dag /ces gsungs pa'i don to //
NK094(nge)001:1202: de bas na gsang ba'i sems rnam par shes pa'i tshogs brgyad kyi rtsa ba las /
NK094(nge)001:1203: rig pa snang stong gnyis su med par rtogs pa'i sman pa chen po ste /
NK094(nge)001:1204: tshogs brgyad nyid rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i dngos gazhi'o //
NK094(nge)001:1205: nang du byang chub sems kyi rtsa ba brgyad ni /
NK094(nge)001:1206: yab kyi rgyu bzhi yum gyi gnas bzhi'o //
NK094(nge)001:1207: de ltar m+aam sa la sogs pa gcig kyang rtsa ba brgyad brgyad snang bas na /
NK094(nge)001:1208: yan lag stong du byung ba rnams lasa sbyar te gcig tu bsres pa'i sman gyi bdud rtsi ni /
NK094(nge)001:1209: gdod nas rigsa lnga dang ye shes lngar grub pa'i
NK094(nge)001:1210: ngo bo dama tshig mchog gi rdzas lnga yi dngosa
NK094(nge)001:1212: bdud rtsi chen po'i rgyud las /
NK094(nge)001:1213: dri chen gser mdog rnam snang mdzad //
NK094(nge)001:1214: byang chub sems ni dkar bas na //
NK094(nge)001:1215: m+aam sa 'byung ldan yid bzhin sngo //
NK094(nge)001:1216: rak+ta chags med dmar bas na //
NK094(nge)001:1217: dri chu dag byed ljang gu'i mdog /ces gsungs shing /
NK094(nge)001:1219: dri chen snang mdzad gtso bo yin //
NK094(nge)001:1220: dri chu gdon mi za grub pa //
NK094(nge)001:1221: rak+ta snang ba mtha' yas sku //
NK094(nge)001:1222: m+aam sa rin chen 'byung ldan gtso //
NK094(nge)001:1223: byang chub sems ni rdo rje sems //
NK094(nge)001:1224: zhes sogs shin tu mang ngo //
NK094(nge)001:1225: de lta bas na ye shes lnga nyid rdzogsa pa'i
NK094(nge)001:1226: don gyi dngos grub sgrub par byed pa'i rten gyi
NK094(nge)001:1227: phyir rdzas te / 'dis na don kyang nang gi tshul kho nar rigs so //
NK094(nge)001:1228: des gtsang sme la sogs pa'i rtog pa'i grangs ji
NK094(nge)001:1229: snyed pa las grol ba'i byin rlabs kyis 'gro ba
NK094(nge)001:1230: lam rgyud lnga'i semsa can kun dbyings su sgrol bar
NK094(nge)001:1231: byed pa'i phyir gyi gtan tshigs des na /
NK094(nge)001:1232: dug lnga rtsa ba nas gcod cing sel ba'i yang bdud rtsi chen po mchoga tu gyur pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:1233: de skad ces gsungsa nas k+aa la'i rtogs tshad brtag pa'i ched du cang mi gsung bar bzhugs so //
NK094(nge)001:1235: rdzas lnga rang byung bdud rtsi yin pa'i dris lan /
NK094(nge)001:1236: de min na rang byung mi rnyed pa'i dris lan /
NK094(nge)001:1237: spang du mi btub pas na rang byung yin par smras pa'i lan /
NK094(nge)001:1238: phan 'dogs pas bdud rtsi yin par smras pa'i lan /
NK094(nge)001:1239: rgyal ba'i dam tshig yin pas bdud rtsi yin par smras pa'i lan /
NK094(nge)001:1240: rtag cing mi 'bral bas dam tshig yin par smras pa'i lan /
NK094(nge)001:1241: spang na mnyam pa dang 'gal bar smras pa'i lan no //
NK094(nge)001:1246: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:1247: de nas k+aa la nag pos yang rang gi 'dod
NK094(nge)001:1248: pa'i don gyi rtogs tshad ston pa dang mi mthun
NK094(nge)001:1249: pa'i khyad par snyan du gsola ba ni /
NK094(nge)001:1250: dam rdzas lnga bdag ranga nyid kyi lus las byung
NK094(nge)001:1251: ba'i phyir te de bas na gzhan las byung ba
NK094(nge)001:1253: 'byung ba dang bza' btung gi dwangsa ma dang snyigsa
NK094(nge)001:1254: ma kho nar nges par gzung ba tsam du zad
NK094(nge)001:1255: pa dag las gzhan med pas phyi nang gi rtsa
NK094(nge)001:1256: ba brgyad brgyad dang yan lag stong gnas pa'i kun
NK094(nge)001:1257: rdzob byang chub sems kyi rtsa ba dang yan lag
NK094(nge)001:1258: tu smos pa gnyis sbyar bas ye shes lnga dang
NK094(nge)001:1259: rigs lnga'i go 'phang dag kyang mthar thug tu rdzogsa
NK094(nge)001:1260: par 'gyur ro // de skad ces zhu ba 'dun te gsol pa lasa /
NK094(nge)001:1261: dus de'i tshe ston pa la bkur ba dang k+aa la'i rtog pa bsal ba'i tshul gyis /
NK094(nge)001:1262: 'khor der 'dus par gyur pa 'chad pa'i ston mchog
NK094(nge)001:1263: gsang bdag chen po'i thugs kyi sras dam pa lang
NK094(nge)001:1264: ka blo gros thabsa ldan khyod kyang 'khor de na
NK094(nge)001:1265: gnas pa nyid kyis k+aa la'i zhen pa dgrol ba'i
NK094(nge)001:1266: phyir thabsa 'di nyid lan du smras pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:1267: lus kyi zag pa phyir 'byung bas phyi sa dang
NK094(nge)001:1268: dri chu la sogs pa dwangs ma dang snyigsa ma'i
NK094(nge)001:1270: lus kyi 'byung ba bzhi dang ni zas khamsa kyi
NK094(nge)001:1271: bza' btung la spyod pa rgyun du ma bral ba
NK094(nge)001:1272: nyid kyi rgyu lasa 'byung basa na /
NK094(nge)001:1273: k+aa la khyod kyis smras pa ni ranga lasa ma
NK094(nge)001:1274: byung bas rang byung min te gzhan zas kyi rgyu
NK094(nge)001:1275: mthun las byung ba kho na yin no /
NK094(nge)001:1276: zhes bdud rtsi'i gol sa gcod pa'i phyir grogsa po
NK094(nge)001:1277: dam pas sun dbyung ba gtar ka gegs sel gyi
NK094(nge)001:1278: tshul du rdzas lnga rang byung ma yin pa'i tshig
NK094(nge)001:1284: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:1285: k+aa la nag posa grogs po chos kyi spun lang
NK094(nge)001:1286: ka la yang de'i don nyid dri ba'i tshig smras
NK094(nge)001:1287: pa / tshul ji ltar na gal te dam rdzas
NK094(nge)001:1288: lnga po gzhan las byung ba de ltar na rang
NK094(nge)001:1289: byung ma yin par 'gal ba nyid du 'gyur ba
NK094(nge)001:1291: ranga byung rang byung zhes bya ba'i chos de nyid
NK094(nge)001:1292: gang nas rnyed par 'gyur te gzhan gang las kyang
NK094(nge)001:1294: zhes de skad du dri ba dris pa lasa /
NK094(nge)001:1295: lang ka'i bdag po dam pa nyid kyis de la slar yang lan blan te smras pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:1296: gang rgyu dang rkyen la ma brten par gang zhig
NK094(nge)001:1297: rang byung du 'byung ba'i chos shig yod par gyur
NK094(nge)001:1298: na / de ni rgyu rkyen gzhan lasa ma byung
NK094(nge)001:1299: zhing de la skyed par byed pa'i mkhan po gang
NK094(nge)001:1300: yang med par nges pas na /
NK094(nge)001:1301: chos de nyid ni rang byung nyid du 'byung bar nges par 'dod pa yin te /
NK094(nge)001:1303: rang byung zhes ni bya ba ni //
NK094(nge)001:1304: rgyu rkyen med pa'i snying po bas //
NK094(nge)001:1305: rtsol sgrub kun las 'das pa yin //
NK094(nge)001:1310: 'gag na de rgyun 'gag /ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:1311: zhes de skad ces smras pasa /
NK094(nge)001:1312: de yi lan du slar yang k+aa la nag posa 'di skad du smras te /
NK094(nge)001:1313: nyon mongs pa lnga dang dam rdzas smad pa rnams
NK094(nge)001:1314: ched du spangsa pasa spongsa par mi 'gyur te bdag
NK094(nge)001:1315: nyid kyi lus dang sems lasa dus kyi rgyun du
NK094(nge)001:1316: 'byung ba'i chos su gyur pa nyid /
NK094(nge)001:1317: rgyu rkyen gzhan las ma byung bas gzhan gyi rgyu 'brasa meda pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:1318: rdzas lnga'i chos de gang yin pa ni ranga 'byung yin par nges pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:1319: zhes smras pa de la lang ka de yisa slar yang lan du 'di skad du smras te /
NK094(nge)001:1320: mi spang zhing dang du blang ba'i chos nyon mongs
NK094(nge)001:1321: pa lnga dang dam rdzas lnga po rnams khyod ltar
NK094(nge)001:1322: rang kho na las byung ba yin na /
NK094(nge)001:1323: dus dang rnam pa thamsa cad du bdag nyid dang
NK094(nge)001:1324: thog mar 'adu ba dang tha mar 'bral ba med
NK094(nge)001:1325: par gtan du gnas pa nyid du 'os shing rigs
NK094(nge)001:1326: pa yin na / sems kyi bag chags dang lus
NK094(nge)001:1327: kyi 'byung ba dang bza' btung gi rgyun 'gag cing
NK094(nge)001:1328: chad de shi na de dag kyang rgyun 'gag ste
NK094(nge)001:1329: chad par 'gyur bas bdag las gtan du mi 'byung
NK094(nge)001:1330: ba'i phyir mi bden par gsal lo //
NK094(nge)001:1336: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:1337: lang ka'i gtam de la k+aa las 'di ltar yang lan 'di skad du zhus te /
NK094(nge)001:1338: nag po k+aa lasa slar blan pa /
NK094(nge)001:1339: smad pa lnga nyid bcud mchog bdud rtsi yina pasa /
NK094(nge)001:1340: ranga gnyer gyi lasa rnams so sora byed par nus te /
NK094(nge)001:1341: dri chus skad snyan pa la sogs pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:1342: dri chen gyi dug thub pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:1343: sha chen yi mdze thub pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:1344: pad+ma'i rak+tasa thor smyon dang gzhan du grang pa thub pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:1345: byang chub sems kyi tsha ba'i nad thub pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:1346: dri chus glang sna dang gag pa thub pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:1347: rigs lnga grub pa'i nus mthu yod pas /
NK094(nge)001:1348: 'jig rten dag na yang de lta bur phan 'dogas
NK094(nge)001:1349: pa gang gis nus pa yod pa de la bdud
NK094(nge)001:1350: rtsi zhes gragsa pas 'jig rten dang mi 'gal ba'i
NK094(nge)001:1352: zhes smras pa de la 'dir ni 'di skad du /
NK094(nge)001:1353: chos kyi grogsa mchog dam pasa lan de nyid nye bar blan pa /
NK094(nge)001:1354: chos kyi spun k+aa la khyod kyis de ltar ma yin te /
NK094(nge)001:1355: spyir bdud rtsi zhes ni de ltar grags shing brjod
NK094(nge)001:1356: pa la bdud rtsi'i lasa ni nges tshig rnam pa
NK094(nge)001:1357: gnyis kyis grub pa yod de /
NK094(nge)001:1358: rtog pa'i nad rnams gso ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:1359: 'khor bar shi ba slong bar byed pa yin pa'i phyir na /
NK094(nge)001:1360: khyod kyis bdud rtsi la las de gnyis kyisa mathu
NK094(nge)001:1361: dang yong ye mi ldan pa'i phyir ma yin no
NK094(nge)001:1364: phyin chad bdag nyid kyi rgyun 'gags pa mi rigs pa'i phyir ro //
NK094(nge)001:1370: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:1371: lang ka thabs ldan gyis de skad smras pa'i lan
NK094(nge)001:1372: du slar yang 'di skad du k+aa la nag po
NK094(nge)001:1373: des blan pa / sngon gyi rgyal ba grangsa med
NK094(nge)001:1374: pa rnams kyis bka' rgyud las dam rdzas kyi brtul
NK094(nge)001:1375: zhugs 'di lnga spyad par bya ba'i gtsor byas nas
NK094(nge)001:1376: des blan pa / / dang du blang ba'i dam tshig dam par bzung ste gsung bas na /
NK094(nge)001:1377: sngon gyi dam tshig yin par gragsa pa'i phyir bdud rtsi yin no //
NK094(nge)001:1378: zhes lan btab pa de la lang ka dam pasa lan 'di skad du mdzad de /
NK094(nge)001:1379: gal te rdzogs pa'i sangsa rgyas kyi dam tshig rgyal ba'i thugs dam yin par ngesa na /
NK094(nge)001:1380: rgyal ba'i thugs dam la 'du 'bral med pas dam
NK094(nge)001:1381: rdzas lnga yang dang po sems bskyed blangs nas dam
NK094(nge)001:1382: tshig tu bzung ba dang mthar mngon par rdzogsa te
NK094(nge)001:1383: sangs rgyas pa'i bar du dam rdzas de dag dang
NK094(nge)001:1384: mi 'bral bar ldan zhing 'grogs dgosa pa yin na
NK094(nge)001:1385: / 'di ni mthar zag pa zad pa'i dngos grub
NK094(nge)001:1386: thob na yang mi 'byung ba'i phyir mi bden pa
NK094(nge)001:1387: / dang / 'byung ba dang bza' btung gi rgyun
NK094(nge)001:1388: chad na yang 'bral bar 'gyur zhing mi 'byung ste
NK094(nge)001:1389: 'gag pas mi bden pa'i phyir rgyal ba'i dam tshig
NK094(nge)001:1396: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:1397: de skad smras pa la k+aa lasa slar yang lan 'di skad du zhus te /
NK094(nge)001:1398: gang zag gi bdag de nyid rtag pa can du nges para gyur pa yisa phyir na /
NK094(nge)001:1399: dam rdzas kyi zag pa lnga po de yang rtag
NK094(nge)001:1400: pa yin te des na kun nas kun tu mi
NK094(nge)001:1401: 'brala zhing ldan pa la de zad nas bral bar
NK094(nge)001:1402: gyur pa ga la yod de med do bar zhus
NK094(nge)001:1403: pa'o // tshig 'dis kyang mu stegs zhar byung ba'i ched du zhus par gsal lo //
NK094(nge)001:1404: de la yang lan du lang ka dam pasa 'di skad du gsungs te /
NK094(nge)001:1405: de la phyi yi zag pa dam rdzas lnga dang nang gi zag pa nyon mongs pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:1406: dam pa rin po che'i zhal nas /
NK094(nge)001:1407: zhar la gsang ba'i zag pa bdag tu rtog pa dang gzung 'dzin no //
NK094(nge)001:1409: de ltar lus la gnas shing rten pa'i phyi dang nang gi zag pa rnams /
NK094(nge)001:1410: chos nyid de kho na nyid rtogs pa'i skabs na
NK094(nge)001:1411: phyi'i zag pa thamsa cad dang nang dang gsang ba'i
NK094(nge)001:1412: zag pa thamsa cad kun zad cing bral bar gyur
NK094(nge)001:1413: pa ni / sa bcu dang rnam par thar pa'i lam bcu po rnams la gnas pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:1414: cig char ba rnams kyis bgrod mi dgos par shes
NK094(nge)001:1415: shing rtogs pa na nges par bral bar lta yang
NK094(nge)001:1416: ci smos te / gzugs khams pa kun snang ba'i grong khyer dang /
NK094(nge)001:1417: gzugs med pa la'ang bshang gci'i zag pa zad de
NK094(nge)001:1418: med pa yin na bdag dang mi 'bral ba ga
NK094(nge)001:1419: la btub ste mi btub bo //
NK094(nge)001:1422: nang gi nyon mongs pa'i dgra bcom pa'i dus su
NK094(nge)001:1423: zag pa zad pas phyi'i zag pa dang yang bral
NK094(nge)001:1424: te gsang ba'i zag pa ni tshogs lam gyi dus
NK094(nge)001:1426: sbyor lam gyi dus su zad pa'i rkyen du gyur
NK094(nge)001:1427: te mthong lam du zad pa yin kyang gzhan don
NK094(nge)001:1428: du zag pa len pa 'bag gyon pa lta bu'o
NK094(nge)001:1429: // zhes gsungs te zag pa dang bcas pa'i mtshan nyid dang bstun pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:1437: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:1438: de la yang k+aa lasa 'di skad du lan zhus te /
NK094(nge)001:1439: gong du bstan pa ji lta ba de ltar gal
NK094(nge)001:1440: te'am brgya la dam rdzas lnga po yang dag pa'i
NK094(nge)001:1441: bdud rtsi ma yin pa de ltar du nges pa
NK094(nge)001:1442: na dang / bdag gis smras pa'ang 'gal ba nyid du gyur te log pa yina du zin na /
NK094(nge)001:1443: chos thams cad mnyam par smra ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:1444: dam rdzas lnga bdud rtsi yin pa 'gog pa gnyis 'gal bas /
NK094(nge)001:1445: rgyal ba rnams kyis chos thamsa cad mnyam pa yin
NK094(nge)001:1446: par bka' stsal zhing zhal gyis 'ches pa rnams dang
NK094(nge)001:1447: mi mthun pas mnyam pa nyid du gsungs pa dang
NK094(nge)001:1450: ma rtogs na mnyam pa'i spyod pa'ang log par 'gro ba /
NK094(nge)001:1451: rdzas lnga ma bcos par rtogs na bdud rtsir 'gro ba /
NK094(nge)001:1452: yang dag pa'i bdud rtsi'i nges tshig bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:1457: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:1458: de la yang lang ka thabs ldan dam pas lan 'di skad du gsungs te /
NK094(nge)001:1460: ma skyes pa dang ma byung ba //
NK094(nge)001:1461: mi gnas pa la chags pa med //
NK094(nge)001:1462: don gyi khyad par rtogs chud na //
NK094(nge)001:1463: kun tu bzang po mchog gi sa'o //
NK094(nge)001:1465: chos thams cad kyi rang gi mtshan nyid kun tu
NK094(nge)001:1466: ma 'dres la ngo bo ji bzhin par mnyam pa'i
NK094(nge)001:1467: gnas lugs yang dag pa'i don mchog phyogs med rang
NK094(nge)001:1468: gsal chen por mi shes shing mngon sum du rtogs
NK094(nge)001:1469: pa med par / yongs su rdzogs pas bzang po'i
NK094(nge)001:1470: tshig tsam la blo gtod nas yid la byed cing
NK094(nge)001:1471: pa med par / / mnyam nyid kun tu bzang
NK094(nge)001:1472: pora chos thams cad gnas pa nyid du khas 'ches
NK094(nge)001:1473: te tshig gi lta ba brten nas spong len med
NK094(nge)001:1474: par spyod pa rnams ni gzugs med dang mu stegs
NK094(nge)001:1475: la sogs pa mun pa'i skye mched nyid du ltung
NK094(nge)001:1478: chos rnams thams cad rang bzhin thig le chen por
NK094(nge)001:1479: yongsa su rdzogsa pas rang rig chos kyi sku'i ngo
NK094(nge)001:1480: bor che chung med par kun nas mnyam pa nyid
NK094(nge)001:1482: rang gi mtshan nyid tha dad du bzang ngan la
NK094(nge)001:1483: sogs par so sor ma 'dres para yang kun tu
NK094(nge)001:1485: de bas na ma 'dres yongsa rdzogs dbyer med pa'i
NK094(nge)001:1486: don du rang gsal spyod yul dang bral bar ma
NK094(nge)001:1487: mthong bar blang dor med par 'khor ba'i chos la
NK094(nge)001:1488: rdzogsa tshul du spyod par byed pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:1489: lta ba kha la yod kyang snying la med par
NK094(nge)001:1490: spyod pa rtsing por zhugs pas loga pa'i lam pa
NK094(nge)001:1491: zhes bya ba yin te ngan 'gro'i rgyud du zhugs
NK094(nge)001:1492: pa'i phyir ro // gnyis pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:1496: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:1497: gsang ba chen po bla na med pa'i theg pas don mtshon pa'i tshig dang sgra ni /
NK094(nge)001:1498: don gciga la sgra du mar 'byung ba dang sgra
NK094(nge)001:1499: gcig la'ang don mi gcig par tha dad so sora
NK094(nge)001:1500: snang ba yin pas gang sngags don gyi ngo bo
NK094(nge)001:1501: rtogs par dka' ba nyid kyis na gzhan dang khyad
NK094(nge)001:1502: par mthong ba dang ma mthong ba'i sgo nas rnam
NK094(nge)001:1503: par phye ste gnyis su snang ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:1504: rnal 'byor pa gang su zhig gis chos nyid ma
NK094(nge)001:1505: nor bar rtogs nas gdeng dang ldan pa ni 'ching
NK094(nge)001:1506: ba dang bral nas nges para grol bar snang la
NK094(nge)001:1507: / gal te don ji bzhin du ma nges nas
NK094(nge)001:1508: bcings pa'i ngo bo yin pas ma rtogs pa dag
NK094(nge)001:1509: gis ngesa par zag pa'i 'byung khams kho nar yang
NK094(nge)001:1511: don rtogs par gces pas 'di ltar shes par bya dgos te /
NK094(nge)001:1512: bshad pa'i zag pa'i dam rdzas de dag gi rang
NK094(nge)001:1513: bzhin chos nyid de bzhin nyid rgyu rkyen gyis ma
NK094(nge)001:1514: byas tha snyad kyis ma btags par de kho na
NK094(nge)001:1515: nyid ma bcos par lhun gyis grub pas ye gdod
NK094(nge)001:1516: ma nasa ngo bo med pas stong pa nyid la
NK094(nge)001:1517: / de nyid du'ang rtog pa med par dmigs pa
NK094(nge)001:1518: dang bral ba'i don ma nor ba yin par rtogs
NK094(nge)001:1519: na bshad pa'i bdud rtsi lnga'i yang dag pa'i bdud
NK094(nge)001:1520: rtsi chen po yina pas mnyam pa nyid dang 'gal
NK094(nge)001:1521: ba med par ngesa pa'i gsang ba ji bzhin pa'i
NK094(nge)001:1522: de kho na nyid du gnas pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:1528: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:1529: de dag gi yid ches pa'i rgyu gang snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:1530: don gyi nges tshig dang 'brel bar ston te /
NK094(nge)001:1531: bshad pa de dag gi rang bzhin stong pa chen
NK094(nge)001:1532: po la ci yi phyir bdud rtsi zhes bya zhe
