NK094(nge)001:1533: na / rnal 'byor pa lam pa rnams kyi nad
NK094(nge)001:1534: chen po'i ngo bo ni ched du byas pa dang
NK094(nge)001:1535: ma byas pa'i rnam par rtog pa gnyis dang /
NK094(nge)001:1536: gzung ba dang 'dzin pa'i rtsa ba'i rtog pa dang yan lag gi rtog pa rnams yin te /
NK094(nge)001:1537: de dag gis yang dag par sos nas grol du mi btub pa'i phyir te /
NK094(nge)001:1538: des na rtag par 'khor ba'i khri mun gyi nang
NK094(nge)001:1539: du 'ching nas srid pa'i gting mthar 'chi bar byed
NK094(nge)001:1540: pa'i phyir bdud ces bya la /
NK094(nge)001:1541: 'o na de dag bdud rtsir 'gyur ba'i tshul ji lta bu zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:1542: rtog pa 'byung ba'i gazhi'am rtsa ba phyi yi rdzas
NK094(nge)001:1543: lnga dang nang gi nyon mongs pa lnga dang bcas
NK094(nge)001:1544: pas kun nas gtsang mer lta ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:1545: 'khor bar zag par byed pa rnam pa lnga po
NK094(nge)001:1546: yina pas de dag las 'khor ba'i gzung 'dzin du
NK094(nge)001:1548: de dag ril ma lus pa kun de bzhin nyid
NK094(nge)001:1549: mnyam pa chen po ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi gnas
NK094(nge)001:1550: lugs rang rang gi de kho na nyid yod stong
NK094(nge)001:1551: gnyis ka las grol ba'i ngo bo nyid du thag
NK094(nge)001:1552: chod de / rtsa ba'i rgyud las /
NK094(nge)001:1553: mnyam nyid stong pa'i don 'di la //
NK094(nge)001:1554: don ldan stong par sgro mi 'dogs //
NK094(nge)001:1555: ma bcos rang bzhin zhi ba yi //
NK094(nge)001:1556: mtshan ma'i rtog bral shes ldan pas //
NK094(nge)001:1557: med do tsam du'ang mi dmigs na //
NK094(nge)001:1559: thams cad mi gnas byang chub pas //
NK094(nge)001:1560: btsal nas grub pa ma yin yang //
NK094(nge)001:1561: sgyu ma sangs nas 'khrul bral bzhin //
NK094(nge)001:1562: spros bral ye shes snying por gnas //
NK094(nge)001:1563: zhes gsungs pa ltar yang dag par rtogs na /
NK094(nge)001:1564: 'dzin rtog thams cad dang bral te yon tan mu
NK094(nge)001:1565: mtha'a med par 'byung basa rnam rtog 'jil zhing 'khor
NK094(nge)001:1566: bar mi ltung bas na bdud rtsi gang gi byed
NK094(nge)001:1567: las rtog pa'i nad gso ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:1568: 'khor bar shi ba las slong ba gnyis dang ldan
NK094(nge)001:1569: pa'i sgo nas bdud rtsi'i nges tshig 'grub pa'i phyir
NK094(nge)001:1571: rmi lam sgyu 'phul mi bzad pas //
NK094(nge)001:1572: shin tu nyam thag gdung ba'i tshe //
NK094(nge)001:1574: mgon btsun gzhan gyis mi phan te //
NK094(nge)001:1575: bdud sel rtsi dang 'dra bar ni //
NK094(nge)001:1576: yang dag lam mchog rtogs par bya //
NK094(nge)001:1578: de bas na yid ches nges pa'i rgyu de lta bu dang ldan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:1583: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:1584: de ltar lang ka dama pa thabs ldan mchog desa lan de skad du bla na te bstan pasa /
NK094(nge)001:1585: nges pa rnyed pa'i yon tan ni /
NK094(nge)001:1586: k+aa la sogs pa'i drang srong rnams mtshan mar zhen
NK094(nge)001:1587: pa'i 'dzin pa rang rgyud pa lasa de nyid du
NK094(nge)001:1588: grol te / de kho na nyid dera lta bas
NK094(nge)001:1589: ngesa pa rnyed nas lta spyod kyi gdeng khyad par
NK094(nge)001:1590: can dang ldan te don gzhan du gyur pa min
NK094(nge)001:1591: par rang rig pa'i chos nyid du rtogs pas /
NK094(nge)001:1592: bdag rtag par lta ba'i blo dang bral te don
NK094(nge)001:1593: gyi de nyid mthong ba'i che mchog sman gyi rgyal
NK094(nge)001:1594: po dam par 'gyur ba nyid yang dag par grub
NK094(nge)001:1599: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:1600: lang ka'i bdag po zhes bos nas /
NK094(nge)001:1603: zhesa pa'i don skyes bu ngesa par lo rgyus su
NK094(nge)001:1604: sngar gsan te thos pa nyid yang dag par rnam
NK094(nge)001:1606: don gyi ngo bo bstan pa 'di ltar ngesa para shes par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:1607: ston pa gsang ba pa'i bdag posa de skad ces
NK094(nge)001:1608: smras pas 'khor lang ka'i bdag po la sogsa pa
NK094(nge)001:1609: damna pa rnams bstan pa'i yon tan gyis rang byung
NK094(nge)001:1610: bdud rtsi'i don rtogs pas mtshan ma'i rtog pa lasa
NK094(nge)001:1611: yongsa su grol bar gyur to //
NK094(nge)001:1612: de dag ni le'u zhe lnga pa'i yan lag tu 'phros par mjal to //
NK094(nge)001:1614: sangsa rgyas kun gyi dgongsa pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po lasa /
NK094(nge)001:1615: sems nyid rang byung gi bdud rtsi'i don gyi no
NK094(nge)001:1616: pi ka'i bsam gtan bstan pa'i le'u zhes bya ste
NK094(nge)001:1617: drug cu rtsa lnga pa nyid rnam par 'grel te
NK094(nge)001:1618: bshad pa'o // e ma rmad byung che ba bdun ldan pa'i //
NK094(nge)001:1619: rgyal kun dgongs pa'i 'dus pa'i spyi mdo 'di //
NK094(nge)001:1620: ston mchog sku lnga'i thugs kyi gsang mdzod de //
NK094(nge)001:1621: rgyud lung man ngag kun gyi yang dems yin //
NK094(nge)001:1622: de phyir 'di na bshad pa'i rgyud chen gyi //
NK094(nge)001:1623: bka' yi nges gsang zab don phyi ma'i rgyud //
NK094(nge)001:1624: mkhas grub gong ma'i gsung sgros ji lta bar //
NK094(nge)001:1625: man ngag tshad ma'i lam nas deng 'dir gsal //
NK094(nge)001:1626: bsil sbyin dbang pos bco lnga'i thun gsum bsal //
NK094(nge)001:1627: snang byed rgyal pos 'dzam gling nyin mor byas //
NK094(nge)001:1628: lung rigs dag pas gsang chen mdo don bkral //
NK094(nge)001:1629: bstan 'dzin mchog rnams dgyes pa'i mchod rdzas lags //
NK094(nge)001:1630: zhes kyang smras so ////bam po dgu pa bshad zin nas /
NK094(nge)001:1631: bama po bcu pa ste tha mar zug pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:1632: da ni dgongs pa rnam par bgro ba'i gnyis pa
NK094(nge)001:1633: mtshan dang mdo gang du 'dus par bgro ba la
NK094(nge)001:1640: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:1641: rnam grangs bcu po bstan ma thag pa de nas
NK094(nge)001:1642: yang rigs can gyi 'khor lang ka'i bdag po la
NK094(nge)001:1643: sogsa pa dman pa'i lus kyi semsa dpa' dam pa
NK094(nge)001:1644: rnams kyis / ston pa gasnga ba pa'i bdag po la gsol pa /
NK094(nge)001:1645: kye gsang ba pa'i bdag po /
NK094(nge)001:1646: ston pa nyid kyis byung tshul bcu gnyis kyi don
NK094(nge)001:1647: rgya cher bgros pa'i lung gi mdo chen po gsang
NK094(nge)001:1648: ba dam pa 'di nyid kyi mtshan ni ji skad
NK094(nge)001:1650: don bsdus pa'i mdo ni gang du 'adus pa lagas /
NK094(nge)001:1651: de skad ces gsol pa lasa /
NK094(nge)001:1652: 'chad pa'i skyes bu chen po gasnga ba pa'i bdag posa lan smras pa /
NK094(nge)001:1655: gsang bdag rdo rje 'dzin pa kho bosa sngon thos
NK094(nge)001:1656: pa ji lta ba bzhin du don ma nor bar
NK094(nge)001:1657: khyed rnams la bgros te bstan pa'i gsang ba dam
NK094(nge)001:1658: pa 'di ni / rgyud kyi thun mong min pa'i
NK094(nge)001:1659: nges pa brjod pa'i mtshan ni rnam grangsa rnam pa
NK094(nge)001:1660: brgyad du brjod par rig par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:1661: mdo ni bslab pa'i mtha' bcur 'dus par shes par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:1664: mtshan gtan tshigs dang bcas pa bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:1665: mdo gang du 'dus par bshad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:1670: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:1672: de la mtshan gyi rnam grangsa brgyad bstan pa gang zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:1673: brgyad phrag gnyis kyi snga ma don dang phyi ma gtan tshigs su rim par sbyar bar bya ste /
NK094(nge)001:1674: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangsa rgyas kun gyi thugs kyi
NK094(nge)001:1675: dgongas pa ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su 'dus pa'i mdo
NK094(nge)001:1676: zhes kyang bya'o // 'bras bu thams cad rdzogs pas don gyi snying po zhes kyang bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:1677: ye shes rang la lhun gyis grub par ston pas rdo rje bkoda pa'i rgyud cesa kyang bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:1678: rnal 'byor bzhi bcu la sogs pa nges par lung
NK094(nge)001:1679: bstan pas rnal 'byora grub pa'am lam gyi bya ba
NK094(nge)001:1680: rdzogsa pa'i lunga zhes kyang bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:1681: rgyu 'bras kyi bstan pa kun 'dir 'dus pas kun 'dus rig pa'i mdo zhes kyang bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:1682: chos thams cad kyi snying por nges pa'i dgongs pa
NK094(nge)001:1683: rang gi mngon sum du ston pas theg pa chen
NK094(nge)001:1684: po mangna par rtogsa pa zhes kyang bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:1685: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lta ba
NK094(nge)001:1686: thams cad 'dir rdzogs pas chos kyi rnam grangsa rnam
NK094(nge)001:1687: para bkod pa zhes kyang bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:1688: byung tshul bcu gnyis kyi dus su gsang sngags 'byung
NK094(nge)001:1689: bar ston pas theg pa chen po'i byung tshul bstan
NK094(nge)001:1691: de dag gtan tshigs ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:1693: ganga de bzhin gshegs pa dam pa rnams la dkyil
NK094(nge)001:1694: 'khor gsum dbyer med pa'i dgongsa pa de nyid lasa
NK094(nge)001:1695: mi mnga' bar nges pas mtshon bya'i ming mtshon byed
NK094(nge)001:1696: la btags pa yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK094(nge)001:1697: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dang rgyud dag pa
NK094(nge)001:1698: gang gi spyod yul gzhan gyis yul ma yina zhing
NK094(nge)001:1699: / rgyu chos kyi dbyings dngos po med pa lasa
NK094(nge)001:1700: 'bras bu'i chos thamsa cad 'byung ba dang rtogs na
NK094(nge)001:1701: rnam kun mkhyen pa'i byang chub 'byung bas gsang ba'i
NK094(nge)001:1702: ye shes yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK094(nge)001:1703: rgyal ba sku lnga'i ston mchog gang gi ye shes
NK094(nge)001:1704: thams cad ma 'dres par yongsa su bkod pa yin
NK094(nge)001:1705: pa'i phyir dang / 'di ltar gang blo la ngesa
NK094(nge)001:1706: pa dag 'bras bu'i rnal 'byor du lunga ston pa
NK094(nge)001:1708: 'dira dam pa rnams kyi dgongs pa kun nas rub pa'am 'dus pa yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK094(nge)001:1709: don mchog bla na med pa 'di rgyal ba dama
NK094(nge)001:1710: pa rnams kyis mngon sum par thugs su chud de
NK094(nge)001:1711: byang chub pa yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK094(nge)001:1712: gang sku gsung thugs kyi gsang ba lasa chos kyi
NK094(nge)001:1713: tshul la ma 'dres para bkod pa yin pa'i phyir
NK094(nge)001:1714: dang / byung tshul gyi gnas skabsa bcu gnyis su
NK094(nge)001:1715: sngar ngesa par byung zhing phyis su 'byung ba yin
NK094(nge)001:1716: dang / pa'i phyir ro // de dag gi don rgyas pa ni klad du bkod pa bzhin no //
NK094(nge)001:1724: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:1727: mdor bcur 'dus par bslab pa gang zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:1728: gang bslab pa'i mtha' bcu kho nar 'dus pa ste /
NK094(nge)001:1729: de dag gi rnam grangs brjod pa yanga 'di ltar /
NK094(nge)001:1730: rtsa ba'i rgyud kyi le'u gnyis pa las gsungs pa'i
NK094(nge)001:1731: rnal 'byor gyi bslab pa'i mtha' bcu nyid 'dir rgyas
NK094(nge)001:1732: par le'u re res 'chad pa'i phyir te /
NK094(nge)001:1734: ji ltar sa gzhi gshin pa la //
NK094(nge)001:1735: brten nas sa bon btab pa las //
NK094(nge)001:1736: 'bras drug smin par gyur pa yis //
NK094(nge)001:1738: chos nyid kun gyi gzhir gyur pa'i //
NK094(nge)001:1739: dam tshig 'di la brten nas ni //
NK094(nge)001:1740: dngos grub lo rtog smin pa yis //
NK094(nge)001:1742: bslab pa 'di yi dam tshig ste //
NK094(nge)001:1743: bslab pa kun gyi gzhi 'dzin du //
NK094(nge)001:1744: goms par bya ba rab tu gces //
NK094(nge)001:1746: gzhi dam tshig gis gzung bar bslab par bya ste le'u 'di nyid las 'byung ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:1748: ji ltar cang shes kyi ling dag /sdom byed sgrog gis bcings gyur pa //
NK094(nge)001:1749: bkrol byas bde blag byang 'gyur na //
NK094(nge)001:1750: ci la'ang thogs med 'gro ba ltar //
NK094(nge)001:1751: sems kyi cang shes dbang po 'di //
NK094(nge)001:1752: mi shes bcings pas bcings gyur pa //
NK094(nge)001:1753: rnam grol thos pa'i sgo mo yis //
NK094(nge)001:1754: shes rgyud kun grol thogs med 'gro //
NK094(nge)001:1756: bcing bar bya ba bkrol ba ste //
NK094(nge)001:1757: rgyud nas dgrol ba'i bslab pa ru //
NK094(nge)001:1758: goms par bya ba rab tu gces //
NK094(nge)001:1760: rgyud thos pas dgrol par bslab par bya ste le'u
NK094(nge)001:1761: re bdun pa'o ////dper na bung ba khung tshol ba
NK094(nge)001:1762: // kun tu 'jug cing byung nas ni //
NK094(nge)001:1763: rang gi 'dzul khung gang yin par //
NK094(nge)001:1764: nges par 'jug cing gnas pa ltar //
NK094(nge)001:1765: rnal 'byor don gyi rjes tshol ba //
NK094(nge)001:1766: spyod sgo ci yod bstun te bsdu //
NK094(nge)001:1767: lta sgor 'jug cing brtags bsdur na //
NK094(nge)001:1768: ma nor nges pa'i dbu ma la //
NK094(nge)001:1769: chos nyid don gyi rjes gcad phyir //
NK094(nge)001:1770: sgo mo kun nas bsdur ba yi //
NK094(nge)001:1771: bslab par bya ba'i mtha' yin te //
NK094(nge)001:1772: goms par bya ba rab tu gces //
NK094(nge)001:1773: zhes gsungs pa ltar sgo kun nas bsdur te dbye
NK094(nge)001:1774: ba la bslab par bya ste le'u re brgyad pa'o
NK094(nge)001:1775: ////ji ltar ri mthon rtse mo la //
NK094(nge)001:1776: sgyid mi lug par brtson 'dzegs na //
NK094(nge)001:1777: mtho sar phyin cing rtse non pas //
NK094(nge)001:1778: yul khams rtogs shing lam la mkhas //
NK094(nge)001:1779: de bzhin shes rab mthon re la //
NK094(nge)001:1780: sgyid mi lug par mnyan bsam na //
NK094(nge)001:1781: kun gyi phul du shes rab phyin //
NK094(nge)001:1782: mkhas pa'i ye shes tshad med do //
NK094(nge)001:1783: don la mkhas par bya ba de //
NK094(nge)001:1784: phul du dbyung ba'i bslab pa ste //
NK094(nge)001:1785: shes rab chen po 'di dag la //
NK094(nge)001:1786: goms par bya ba rab tu gces //
NK094(nge)001:1788: phul du mkhas pas dbyung nas mthar phyin par bya
NK094(nge)001:1789: ba la bslab par bya ste le'u re dgu pa'o
NK094(nge)001:1790: ////ji ltar rgyal rigs rgyud byung ba //
NK094(nge)001:1791: mang po'i dbang por dpon bstabs te //
NK094(nge)001:1792: 'khor lo la sogs rin chen gyis //
NK094(nge)001:1793: kun la dbang sgyur thob pa ltar //
NK094(nge)001:1794: de bzhin rnal 'byor rgyud byung ba //
NK094(nge)001:1795: chos kyi dbang por dpon bstabs te //
NK094(nge)001:1796: phyag rgya la sogs rtags chen gyis //
NK094(nge)001:1797: rim par kun gyi thog mar 'gro //
NK094(nge)001:1798: 'di ni dbang gis khyad par te //
NK094(nge)001:1799: sa la rim par 'byung ba yi //
NK094(nge)001:1800: rtsal gyis bgrod cing bslab pa'i mtha' //goms par bya ba rab tu gces //
NK094(nge)001:1802: rim pa dbang gis bgrod de dbang thamsa cad 'adu
NK094(nge)001:1803: ba la bslab par bya ste le'u bdun cu pa'o
NK094(nge)001:1805: tsham tshom chags thogs yong med par //
NK094(nge)001:1806: dga' ba'i longs spyod brod tshul gyis //
NK094(nge)001:1807: mi ldog pha rol phyin pa ltar //
NK094(nge)001:1808: rnal 'byor nges par spyod pa'i blo //
NK094(nge)001:1809: brtul zhugs rgya mtsho'i chur 'jug pa //
NK094(nge)001:1810: rtsal chen sbyong ba'i brod tshul du //
NK094(nge)001:1811: chags thogs med par la dor ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:1812: bslab par bya ba'i mtha' yin no //
NK094(nge)001:1813: spyod pa'i bslab pa dam par ni //
NK094(nge)001:1814: goms par bya ba rab tu gces //
NK094(nge)001:1816: la spyod pas dora ba la bslab par bya ste
NK094(nge)001:1817: le'u don gcig pa'o ////ji ltar khung chen mkha' lding
NK094(nge)001:1818: ba // gshog pa'i rtsal gyis nam 'phang gcod //
NK094(nge)001:1819: ngam grog chu klung mtha' yas kyang //
NK094(nge)001:1820: gshog rlabs 'og tu kun chud ltar //
NK094(nge)001:1821: rnal 'byor mnyam nyid mkhar lding ba //
NK094(nge)001:1822: theg pa'i spyod sgo mtha' yas kyang //
NK094(nge)001:1823: mnyam pa chen po'i don gyis ni //
NK094(nge)001:1824: lta 'phang rlabs kyis thag gcod pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:1825: 'di ni re dang dogs pa yi //
NK094(nge)001:1826: the tshom gcod pa'i lta ba ste //
NK094(nge)001:1827: don la sems kyi blta ba ste //
NK094(nge)001:1828: bslab pa 'di dag goms pa gces //
NK094(nge)001:1830: thag lta bas bcad de sa gcad pa la bslab
NK094(nge)001:1831: par bya ste le'u don gnyis pa'o ////dper na rgya
NK094(nge)001:1833: sbrul dang chu srin sbrang ma las //
NK094(nge)001:1834: sogs pa gdug pa'i sdug bsngal kun //
NK094(nge)001:1835: dka' ba nyams su blangs nas 'grub //
NK094(nge)001:1836: de bzhin rnal 'byor bde tshol ba //
NK094(nge)001:1837: rnam rtog bying rmugs 'phyar g.yeng dgra //
NK094(nge)001:1838: gzhom par dka' ba'i las 'di dag /nyams su blangs na bde 'thob rnyed //
NK094(nge)001:1840: nyams su blangs pa'i bslab pa ste //
NK094(nge)001:1841: sems kyis goms par bya ba'i las //
NK094(nge)001:1842: 'dris par bya ba rab tu gces //
NK094(nge)001:1844: nyams su ting nge 'dzin gyis blangs te dgongs pa'i
NK094(nge)001:1845: nyamsa rnyed pa la bslab par bya ste le'u don
NK094(nge)001:1846: gsum pa'o ////ji ltar mun pa dug dang rdzas //
NK094(nge)001:1847: sman snang gser du bsgyur bas na //
NK094(nge)001:1848: 'gyur rtsi'i man ngag med pa'i mis //
NK094(nge)001:1849: dka' ba'i las chen sna tshogs pas //
NK094(nge)001:1850: sdug bsngal spyad kyang mi 'grub ste //
NK094(nge)001:1851: su zhig man ngag ldan pa'i mis //
NK094(nge)001:1852: tshegs med gyi na'i tshul gyis na //
NK094(nge)001:1853: bsgyur bas sman snag gser 'gyur ltar //
NK094(nge)001:1854: rnal 'byor chen po'i don sgrub pa //
NK094(nge)001:1855: kun gzhi gnas 'gyur man ngag dang //
NK094(nge)001:1856: gang dag mi ldan pas kyang ni //
NK094(nge)001:1857: dka' ba spyad kyang 'grub pa min //
NK094(nge)001:1858: sems kyi gsang 'di sus mthong ba //
NK094(nge)001:1859: de dag man ngag ldan pa ste //
NK094(nge)001:1860: 'dod pa'i don mchog gang yin pa //
NK094(nge)001:1861: de dag tshegs med gyi nas 'grub //
NK094(nge)001:1862: don rnams sgrub par gang byed pa //
NK094(nge)001:1863: man ngag can gyis 'grub pa'i phyir //
NK094(nge)001:1865: bslab pa 'di dag rab tu gces //
NK094(nge)001:1867: don man ngag gis sgrub pa la mkhas pas tshegsa
NK094(nge)001:1868: chung bar bslab par bya ste le'u don bzhi pa'o
NK094(nge)001:1869: ////dper na kun tu rgyu ba'i mi //
NK094(nge)001:1871: yul gyi rnam par mtha' yas kyang //
NK094(nge)001:1872: bgrod pa'i lam gnas gcig las med //
NK094(nge)001:1873: de bzhin bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i //
NK094(nge)001:1874: brgyad khri bzhi stong chos bstan kyang //
NK094(nge)001:1875: bkri zhing drang ba'i tshig yin te //
NK094(nge)001:1876: bsam pa'i yul ni gcig pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:1877: don rnams gcig tu sdud pa yi //
NK094(nge)001:1878: bslab par bya ba dam pa ste //
NK094(nge)001:1879: nges par gcig las med pa'i phyir //
NK094(nge)001:1880: 'di dag goms par bya ba yin //
NK094(nge)001:1882: mdo don gcig tu bsdu ba la bslab par bya
NK094(nge)001:1883: ste le'u don lnga pas gsal bar ston pa'o ////de
NK094(nge)001:1884: dag ni gsang sngags gsang ba chen po'i bslab pa'i
NK094(nge)001:1885: mtha' bcu ste / bslab pa de rnams la goms par byas pa'i yon tan yang /
NK094(nge)001:1887: bslab pa 'di la goms gyur na //
NK094(nge)001:1888: lobs pa'i yon tan mtha' yas te //
NK094(nge)001:1889: lobs pas lam la mkhas par 'gyur //
NK094(nge)001:1890: sngags kyi yon tan chen po yang //
NK094(nge)001:1891: rmad du byung ba thob par 'gyur //
NK094(nge)001:1892: zhes sogs spyi dang bye brag gi dgos ched shin tu mang ngo //
NK094(nge)001:1894: gzhi dam tshig gis gzung ba sa gzhi gshin pa ltar bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:1895: rgyud thos pas dgrol ba gyi ling sgrog bkrol ba ltar bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:1896: sgo kun nas bsdur te don gnad bsdu ba bung ba tshang tshol ba ltar bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:1897: phul du mkhas pas dbyung ba ri rab lhun po'i rtser phyin pa ltar bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:1898: rim pa dbang gis bgrod pa rgyal bu rgyal sar bton pa ltar bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:1899: la spyod pas dor ba glang po che chur 'jug pa ltar bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:1900: thag lta bas gcad pa khyung chen po nam mkha' la lding ba ltar bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:1901: nyams su ting nge 'dzin gyis blangs pa tshong dpon
NK094(nge)001:1902: mkhas pas rgya mtsho'i nor bu lon pa ltar bshad
NK094(nge)001:1903: pa / don man ngag gis sgrub pa gser 'gyur gyi rtsi ltar bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:1904: mdo don gcig tu bsdu ba tshong pa khe spogs sdud pa ltar bshad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:1908: bslab pa gces par gdams pa /
NK094(nge)001:1914: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:1915: le'u 'dis drang don dang nges don gnyis ka ston no //
NK094(nge)001:1916: khas blangs pa'i le'u re res 'chad pa'ang thog mar
NK094(nge)001:1917: gzhi dam tshig gis gzung ba le'u 'di nyid kyis
NK094(nge)001:1918: 'chad pa'i phyir / skyes bu chen pos lang ka'i bdag po zhes bos nas /
NK094(nge)001:1919: grangs la snyegs pas de la zhes dam tshig bkar
NK094(nge)001:1920: ba ni sgrub pa'i gzhi ste lam dang 'bras bu'i
NK094(nge)001:1921: chos thamsa cad kyi rten pa'i gzhi lta bu ni
NK094(nge)001:1922: dam tshig yin pas dper na sa gzhi chen po
NK094(nge)001:1923: nyid skye 'khrungs thams cad kyi rten du gyur par
NK094(nge)001:1924: gnas pa ltar shes dgos pas thog mar bstan par
NK094(nge)001:1925: rig par bya'o // des na kun 'dus las kyang /
NK094(nge)001:1926: chos thams cad kyi srog ni dam tshig yin par shes par gyis shig /ces gdams par mdzad do //
NK094(nge)001:1928: cig char bar srung du med pa'i dam tshig bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:1929: rims kyis par srung mtshams dang bcas pa'i dam tshig bshad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:1934: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:1935: de la dam tshig rang gi ngo bo ni lta
NK094(nge)001:1936: ba dang spyod pa yin zhing nges tshig ni bsrung
NK094(nge)001:1937: ba dang ma bsrung ba las 'khor ba dang 'das
NK094(nge)001:1939: de lta bu'i khe nyen can gyi dam tshig srung
NK094(nge)001:1940: ba'i gnas sam gzhi nye bar bstan pa ni 'di
NK094(nge)001:1941: lta ste / bsrung bar bya ba'i dam tshig ji
NK094(nge)001:1942: snyed pa la'ang theg pa chen po'i sgo 'dir blo
NK094(nge)001:1943: che ba'i yul du phyogs ris su bsrung du med
NK094(nge)001:1944: pas ched du srung mtshams ma dmigs pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:1945: cig char ba rnams kyi chos nyid lta ba'i dam
NK094(nge)001:1946: tshig dam pa blo dman gyis spyod yul min cing
NK094(nge)001:1947: rtogs par dka' bas mnyam pa chen por 'da' nyams
NK094(nge)001:1950: phyi nang gi chos so cog kun kyang dam tshig
NK094(nge)001:1951: dam pa ji bzhin pa'i chos nyid du ma gyur
NK094(nge)001:1952: pa ni gang yang med pa yina pasa 'da' nyams
NK094(nge)001:1953: ma dmigs te gang la'ang bkol ba med pas 'gal
NK094(nge)001:1954: bar mi 'gyur ba dang spang du med pa'i phyir
NK094(nge)001:1955: te / lta bas mi 'gal te phyogs lhung dang bral ba yin la /
NK094(nge)001:1956: spyod pas mi 'gal te spang blang dang bral ba yin zhing /
NK094(nge)001:1957: dam tshig gis mi 'gal te ris su srung ba dang bral ba'i phyir te /
NK094(nge)001:1958: ngang de las nam yang g.yo ba med par bya ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:1959: skyes bu su la de lta bu'i dam pa chen
NK094(nge)001:1960: po 'di nyid gnas te yang dag par 'chang ba
NK094(nge)001:1961: ni / rnal 'byor pa che ba'i yon tan dang
NK094(nge)001:1962: ldan pa rig pa 'dzin pa'i nang nas mchog dang
NK094(nge)001:1963: dam par gyur pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sa la gnas
NK094(nge)001:1964: ni / pa yin no // dam tshig mchog gi che ba bstan pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:1965: gsang sngags rmad du byung ba'i rtsa ba dang yan
NK094(nge)001:1966: lag gi dam tshig bsrung bar bya ba'i yul phyi
NK094(nge)001:1967: nang gsang bas bsdus pa rnams la /
NK094(nge)001:1968: yod pa la med ces pa sogs kyis sgyu dang
NK094(nge)001:1969: lhad btsud pa sogs kyis gsog dang bre phul kha
NK094(nge)001:1970: dma' ba lta bu sogs kyis g.yo ste de la
NK094(nge)001:1971: sogs pa skyon gyis gos pa med par dam tshig
NK094(nge)001:1972: dam pa nyid srung ba la nan tan du bya
NK094(nge)001:1973: ba'o // de lta bu'i dam tshig dpag par dka'
NK094(nge)001:1974: bas zab cing sgo yangsa la kun la khyab pas
NK094(nge)001:1975: rgya che ba'i phyir theg chen gsang ba mchog gi
NK094(nge)001:1976: dam tshig dam pa bsrung ba 'dir ni /
NK094(nge)001:1977: gdul bya la bsam dbang du ji skad gragsa pa'i
NK094(nge)001:1978: nyan thos kyi nyis brgya lnga bcu la sogs pa'i
NK094(nge)001:1979: tshul khrimsa dang / byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa rgya mtsho dang /
NK094(nge)001:1980: gsang sngags phyi nang gi dam tshig tu grags pa rdul snyed dang /
NK094(nge)001:1981: mi chos kyi mna' yan chad rtog pas srung ba'i
NK094(nge)001:1982: bya ba mang po ji snyed par gyur pa thams
NK094(nge)001:1983: cad kun 'dir 'dus pas dam tshig mchog 'di nyid
NK094(nge)001:1984: bsrung na kun bsrung ba yin la /
NK094(nge)001:1985: 'di dag la nyams ral gyi skyon yang med pas rnam par dag pa nyid de /
NK094(nge)001:1986: de bas na yon tan sangs rgyas dang mnyam pa'i
NK094(nge)001:1987: lta ba'i dam tshig dam pa 'di ni rmad du
NK094(nge)001:1988: byung ba chen po ngo mtshar mchog tu che ba'i
NK094(nge)001:1989: chos nyid gsang ba'i dam tshig yin te /
NK094(nge)001:1990: sems lung chen po'i mdo las /
NK094(nge)001:1991: tha tshig sdom dang mi sdom dang //
NK094(nge)001:1992: bsrung dang mi bsrung phyogs med bar //
NK094(nge)001:1993: mnyam nyid sdom par gang gnas pa //
NK094(nge)001:1994: mnyam pa chen po'i dam tshig ste //
NK094(nge)001:1995: nam mkha' lta bur mngon shes na //
NK094(nge)001:1996: de ni yang dag dam tshig ste //
NK094(nge)001:1997: lta ba rnam dag dam tshig mchog /dag pa zhi ba gang bsrung ba //
NK094(nge)001:1998: rnam dag dam tshig chen po yin //
NK094(nge)001:1999: yang dag chos dbyings zab mo la //
NK094(nge)001:2000: bsrung dang mi bsrung ga la yod /
NK094(nge)001:2001: bsrung med nam mkha' ltar shes na //
NK094(nge)001:2002: de ni yang dag gsang ba'i dam tshig go //
NK094(nge)001:2005: dam tshig ris su bsrung bar gdams pa /
NK094(nge)001:2006: ji ltar bsrung thabs kyi yan lag rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:2011: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2012: de lta bu'i mnyam pa chen po'i dam tshig ni /
NK094(nge)001:2013: rnal 'byor mchog gi spyod yul yin pas gsang ba'i
NK094(nge)001:2014: sgor zhugs pa'i blo dman pa dag gis bya ba
NK094(nge)001:2015: ston pa'i phyir / gong gi dam tshig 'di ni
NK094(nge)001:2016: lam pa blo dman zhing skal ba chung ba kun
NK094(nge)001:2017: gyi thun mong gi spyod yul ma yin pa'i phyir
NK094(nge)001:2018: gyi gtan tshigs des na gsang sngags kyi rnal 'byor
NK094(nge)001:2019: shes rab dang mos pa chung ngu rim gyis 'jug
NK094(nge)001:2021: blo dang 'tshams tshad du bsrung ba'i mtshamsa dang bcas
NK094(nge)001:2022: par rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig mtha'
NK094(nge)001:2023: dag gzung bar bya zhing yang dag par bsrung bar
NK094(nge)001:2026: dam tshig gi snod bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:2027: che ba'am thub pa'i yon tan bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:2028: ngo bo'i sgo nas dbye ba bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:2030: nyams na bskang thabs bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:2032: snod ngan pa'i khyad par bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:2033: bzang po'i mtshan nyid bshad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:2035: snod kyi skyon bzhi sogs la mi bstan pa'i tshul /
NK094(nge)001:2036: zhe sdang gis bskyed pa'i skyon gsum bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:2037: dam pa la ma mos pa'i skyon bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:2038: bslab bya'i yon tan dang bral ba'i skyon bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:2039: nyams pa'i snod ngan dang mi 'grogs par gdams pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:2041: snod ngan la sba zhing gsang bar bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:2042: snod ngan la mi bstan pa'i dgos pa bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:2043: snod kyi skyon bzhi ngos bzung ba /
NK094(nge)001:2044: ngan pa la bshad kyang mi go bas mi bstan par gdams pa /
NK094(nge)001:2045: bstan na 'di phyir phung ba'i skyon bshad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:2050: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2051: de la gsang ba'i man ngag mi spel ba'i tshul ni /
NK094(nge)001:2052: theg pa chena po yongsa su rnal 'byor gyi gasnga don shin tu zab pa dag ni /
NK094(nge)001:2053: snod ma yin pa'i gang zag 'chad par 'gyur ba ltar log par gyur pa rnams la /
NK094(nge)001:2054: phyi grol lam thun mong tsam dang nang steng sgo 'khor lo bzhi'i man ngag dang /
NK094(nge)001:2055: gasnga ba 'og sgo lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes
NK094(nge)001:2056: skyed pa gsum du phye ste 'jug pa yi sgo
NK094(nge)001:2057: nas sam / skyo ston chen po sogs rtsa rgyud
NK094(nge)001:2058: 'chad pa dag gis phyi kri yog sde gsum dang
NK094(nge)001:2059: nas sam / / nang bskyed rdzogs gnyis dang /
NK094(nge)001:2060: gsang ba rdzogs pa chen po gsum du yang gsungs te /
NK094(nge)001:2061: de ltar gsang don gyi khyad par bshad thabs gsum
NK094(nge)001:2062: du phye la nang dang gsang ba'i gnad rnams sba
NK094(nge)001:2063: ba'i thabas su bya zhing phyi rol gyi sgo tsam
NK094(nge)001:2064: thun mong du bstan te rjes su bsrung bar bya'o
NK094(nge)001:2069: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2070: bstan pa'i snod du ma gyur pa du zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:2071: gsang don ji bzhin du bstan pa'i gnas mina pa'i
NK094(nge)001:2072: snod ngan gyi rnam grangs shin tu mang yang gang
NK094(nge)001:2073: dag kha sbub la sogs pa 'chad pa'i rnam pa
NK094(nge)001:2074: bzhisa bsdus pa'i bye brag so sor gyur pa rnams
NK094(nge)001:2075: kyi mtshan nyid / phyis su 'byon pa'i ma 'ongas
NK094(nge)001:2076: pa'i rnal 'byor dam pa tshul ma nor bar spyod
NK094(nge)001:2077: pa rnams kyang nges pa'i blo yisa snod brtagsa te
NK094(nge)001:2078: ngo shes par byas nasa snod min pa de dag
NK094(nge)001:2079: la mi bstan par gsang bar bya ba'i phyir snod
NK094(nge)001:2080: ngan pa bzhi'i bye brag 'di dag bshad cing bka'
NK094(nge)001:2081: kyi mtshan nyid / stsal pa'o // de la gang
NK094(nge)001:2082: gsang na gsang sngags theg pa chen po yon tan
NK094(nge)001:2083: mchog tu gyur pa'i yid bzhin gyi nor bu 'di
NK094(nge)001:2084: kyi mtshan nyid / stsal pa'o // nyid do // gsang ba'i gtan tshigs ni /
NK094(nge)001:2085: 'o na skyon che bas gsang ngam zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:2086: skyon can dag mtshang yod pa'i nyes pas gsang ba
NK094(nge)001:2087: ma yin kyang gnad khyad par can dang ldan te
NK094(nge)001:2090: gsang sngags la mi mos pa'am ma rtogs pa'i blo chung ba rnams la'o //
NK094(nge)001:2091: 'o na gang gi phyir gsang ste thugs rje med dam zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:2092: blo chung de dag la'ang brgyud nas phan gdags pa'i dona gyi ched du gsang ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:2093: gang gis gsang na thugsa rje chen po'i brda dang thabsa kyis shin tu gsang bar byed pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:2095: snod kha sbub lta bu'i skyon bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:2096: snod zhabs rdol lta bu'i skyon bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:2097: snod gzhog ral lta bu'i skyon bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:2098: snod dug can lta bu'i skyon bshad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:2103: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2104: gsang ba'i yul bzhi khas 'ches pa rnams re re nas bstan pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:2105: dang po theg pa chen po'i snod ma yin pa kha sbub kyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK094(nge)001:2106: 'jig rten pa so so'i skye bo dang theg pa damna pa nyan rang dang /
NK094(nge)001:2107: loga sred can mu stegs pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:2108: de dang mthun par log lta'i dngos la chags pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:2109: byang chub sems dpa' dang gsang bar zhugs kyang lta ba'i phyogsa 'dzin la zhen pa can dang /
NK094(nge)001:2110: gsang sngags theg pa chen po la dad pa'i dbang po med pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:2111: shes rab kyi dbang po med pas rtogs pa'i blo gros kyi nus pa chung ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:2112: ting 'dzin gyi dbang po med pas bying rgod kyis g.yeng ba can dang /
NK094(nge)001:2113: dran pa'i dbang po med pas glen rmugsa che bar gnas shing /
NK094(nge)001:2114: brtson 'grus kyi dbang po med pas bslab pa'i don gang la yang mi brtson pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:2115: gti mug che bas gsang don gyi snang ba las
NK094(nge)001:2116: dben te blo muna par mtshungsa pa'i mtshan nyid 'di
NK094(nge)001:2117: dag ldan pas / gsang ba'i don mchog mi go
NK094(nge)001:2118: zhing mos pa dang bral te don du mi gnyer
NK094(nge)001:2119: bas snod kha sbub pa'i rgyab tu chu blug pa
NK094(nge)001:2122: theg chen gsang ba 'di log par 'dzin pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:2123: gang gsang ba'i dam tshig nyamsa pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:2124: gang theg pa chen po gsang ba 'di lasa slar log pa dang bcu bzhi ni /
NK094(nge)001:2125: byang chub tu 'dren pa'i thabs kyi thag pa gting nas chad de /
NK094(nge)001:2126: byang chub semsa kyi myu gu rtsa ba nas tshig
NK094(nge)001:2127: pa yin pa'i phyir mtshan nyid 'di dag ldan pas
NK094(nge)001:2128: ngan 'gro'i gnas ya nga ba gsum gyi 'dam du
NK094(nge)001:2129: spyi'u tshugs su lhung ste kha sbub pa yin pas
NK094(nge)001:2130: thar pa'i dus med par rigs chad 'bras bu med
NK094(nge)001:2131: par 'gyur ba dang gnyis kyis ming nges par 'grub
NK094(nge)001:2132: pa'o // des na snod ma brtags par de lta bu la smra bar mi rung ste /
NK094(nge)001:2134: snod med kha sbub de dag la //
NK094(nge)001:2135: gsang ba smra bar bya ba min //
NK094(nge)001:2136: smras na de nyid kha sbub 'gyur //
NK094(nge)001:2142: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2143: gsang sngags gsang ba'i dona rnams sgrar brjod de tshig tsam du gzhan la smra yang /
NK094(nge)001:2144: chos nyid gab ba'i gsang ba 'di nyid mi shes
NK094(nge)001:2145: pas gsang sngags kyi lta ba'i gdeng med par mi
NK094(nge)001:2146: shes bzhin du g.yon can shes pa'i tshul du bcos
NK094(nge)001:2147: nas nga shin tu mkhas snyam du rlom ste nga
NK094(nge)001:2148: rgyal byed cing gzhan la gsang sngags 'chad de sgrogsa
NK094(nge)001:2150: gzhan snod ngan pa kun la'ang gsang bar 'oosa pa'i
NK094(nge)001:2151: chos dam pa gsang rgyu de lhag par yang smra
NK094(nge)001:2152: ba dang / bsnyen bsgrub yan lag bzhi dang byang
NK094(nge)001:2153: sems spyir btang gi rtsa ba rnam pa bzhi yi
NK094(nge)001:2154: de nyid rnams la sgra yi tshig tsam thosa pa
NK094(nge)001:2155: yod kyang don bzhin du rtogs pa med pas yang
NK094(nge)001:2156: dag par bsgrub mi shes shing nyamsa su mi len
NK094(nge)001:2157: ba dang / la / bla ma dam pa'am mched
NK094(nge)001:2158: dam ldan gang gis gsang ba'i gnyer gang gtad pa
NK094(nge)001:2159: rnams mi thub pa rnams la gsang ba'i bcud khong
NK094(nge)001:2160: na meda par zag pas 'khor bar bying zhing zag
NK094(nge)001:2161: ste 'khyams pa yin pas snod zhabs rdol dang 'dra
NK094(nge)001:2162: ba'i mtshan nyid du bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:2163: de lta bu la'ang gsang ba smra bar mi rung ste /
NK094(nge)001:2165: gsang don mi thub snod ngan la //
NK094(nge)001:2166: gsang ba smra bar gang byed pa //
NK094(nge)001:2167: de dang snod med snod ngan gnyis //
NK094(nge)001:2168: 'khor ba'i khams su zag par mnyam //
NK094(nge)001:2171: lta dang dam tshig /ces pa nas /
NK094(nge)001:2173: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2174: gsang chen gsang ba dam pa'i sgor zhugs par khas 'ches nas /
NK094(nge)001:2175: bud+d+ha'am gsang ba mchog gi lta ba dang dam tshig
NK094(nge)001:2176: dang spyod pa yi dam pa'i mdzoda gsum nyid tshig
NK094(nge)001:2177: tu 'di lta bu'o zhes sgrar smra ba tsam yod
NK094(nge)001:2178: pa yin na yang gang dag rang nyid la de
NK094(nge)001:2179: gsum gyi don la zhen pa'i mthu med pas gzung
NK094(nge)001:2180: 'dzin yang dag par grol ba'i bsam pa'i nus pa
NK094(nge)001:2181: ma brtas te shes pa so so'i skye bo las
NK094(nge)001:2182: gnas ma gyur pa'i dbang gis g.yo sgyu dang phrag
NK094(nge)001:2183: dog dang ser snas sems gdung ste de bzhis rgyud
NK094(nge)001:2184: non pas rtsol ba'i bya ba dang bral bas spros
NK094(nge)001:2185: pa med pa'i chos nyid chen po la tshig tsam
NK094(nge)001:2186: du ngesa par 'dzin cing dngos zhen dang bcas pas
NK094(nge)001:2187: smra ba las gang zag de yang rang nyid la
NK094(nge)001:2188: bya bral de kho na nyid kyi don de nyid
NK094(nge)001:2189: rtogs pa'i gdengs dang rtsa ba dang ya na lag
NK094(nge)001:2190: gi dam tshig la gnas pa med par /
NK094(nge)001:2191: gzan theg pa chen po'i lta ba dang ting nge
NK094(nge)001:2192: 'dzin gyi rnal 'byor ldan pa can la'ang khyod kyi
NK094(nge)001:2193: lta ba ni damna pa yin no zhes zer zhing
NK094(nge)001:2194: smod pa smra ba dag ni /
NK094(nge)001:2195: dam tshig nyams pa dang 'bras bu'i go 'phang ngam
NK094(nge)001:2196: don zab mos phung ste phama par 'gyur bas 'khora
NK094(nge)001:2197: bar 'gro ba'i skal pa can du gyur te sdug
NK094(nge)001:2198: bsngal ba'i gnas su 'bo zhing ltung bar 'gyur ba
NK094(nge)001:2199: ni snod ngan pa gzhog ral gyi mtshan nyid yin
NK094(nge)001:2200: pas / gsang ba smra bar mi bya ste /
NK094(nge)001:2203: gsang ba'i don rnams smra byed pa //
NK094(nge)001:2204: gsang ba nyams pa'i dbang gis na //
NK094(nge)001:2211: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2212: gang dag theg pa chen po'i sgor zhugs nas pha
NK094(nge)001:2213: rol gyi tshul rtog cing tshod len te nga che
NK094(nge)001:2214: dang khyad tshig 'dren nas tshig smra ba dang kha
NK094(nge)001:2215: gsag dang ngo lkog gi lce gnyis sgyur bar byed
NK094(nge)001:2216: pas log tshig brjod cing bla ma dang grogs po
NK094(nge)001:2217: mkhas pa ganga dag rnams la smod pa dang rmongsa
NK094(nge)001:2218: pas nyes dmigs mi shes par dam tshig gi sri
NK094(nge)001:2220: da ltar gyi tshe gcig po 'di la rang che
NK094(nge)001:2221: rang btsan gyi che ba 'dod pas dregsa pa'i go
NK094(nge)001:2222: sa thob pa'i ched kyi phyir du /
NK094(nge)001:2223: mched lcam gyi nor rdzas la sogs pa rku ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:2224: ngan g.yo dang gya gyu'i sgyu dang ldan pas gzhan rnams slu zhing 'drid pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:2225: zang zing gi rdzas kyi phyir shes pa 'breng bas
NK094(nge)001:2226: gsang sngags kyi tshig tsam smra ba la dga' ste
NK094(nge)001:2227: / rang gis shes rlom dang mkhas semsa kyis brjod
NK094(nge)001:2228: 'dod dang bcas te pha rol gyi slob dpon du
NK094(nge)001:2229: tshul 'chos par byed pa yi log par smra ba
NK094(nge)001:2230: dag ni khong na dug chen 'khyil ba can gyi
NK094(nge)001:2231: skyon dang ldan pa'i snod ngan yin pas 'dod khams
NK094(nge)001:2232: kyi gnas tha mar lhung ste dmyal bar skye ba
NK094(nge)001:2233: / ni / snod dug can gyi mtshan nyid yin pas /
NK094(nge)001:2234: de la gsang don mi smra ste /
NK094(nge)001:2236: dug can ltung ba'i snod de la //
NK094(nge)001:2237: gsang ba'i dmigs rnams smra ba ni //
NK094(nge)001:2238: rnal 'byor nyams pa chen po ste //
NK094(nge)001:2245: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2246: 'di ltar gang zhig snod bzhi po tshul 'di bzhin
NK094(nge)001:2247: du don gyi 'bras bus dbul zhing phama par 'gyur
NK094(nge)001:2248: bas snod ngana pa rnams la rgyud 'di lta bu'i
NK094(nge)001:2249: gasnga sngags chen po gsang ba'i don dam pa de
NK094(nge)001:2250: kho na nyid kyi mdzod mchog nyid ni zaba cing
NK094(nge)001:2252: bstan par byas kyang don yang dag par mi go
NK094(nge)001:2253: bas snying po'i bcud kyis pham ste tshig tsam la
NK094(nge)001:2254: 'chel ba'i tshul des ngan 'gro'i 'gro bar lhung ba'i
NK094(nge)001:2255: gnas su 'gyur zhing grol bar mi 'gyur ro //
NK094(nge)001:2256: de basa na snod skyon can de dag la gsang ba bstan par bya ba mina no //
NK094(nge)001:2261: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2263: gal te bstan par gyur na ni /
NK094(nge)001:2264: ston cing smra ba'i slob dpon dang nyan par byed
NK094(nge)001:2265: pa'i slob ma de dag gang yin pa dper na
NK094(nge)001:2266: be'u sbrel g.yang du bskyur ba ltar mthong ba tshe
NK094(nge)001:2267: 'di la tshe thung nad mang sogs dang ma mthong
NK094(nge)001:2268: ba phyi mar bskal pa gsum la sogs pa'i yun
NK094(nge)001:2269: du phung bar byed cing gnyis ka rgyud bsreg pas
NK094(nge)001:2270: gdung bar 'gyur te gcig gi rgyu gcig gis byas
NK094(nge)001:2271: pa'i phyir ro // gnyis pa la gsum ste /
NK094(nge)001:2272: phrag dog gi skyon gnyis bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:2273: sgro skur gyi skyon bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:2274: khro zhing rang rgyud ngan pa'i skyon bshad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:2279: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2280: rnal 'byor gang zhig lta ba la makhasa shing ting nge 'dzin gasla ba'i don dang ldan pa la /
NK094(nge)001:2281: rnala 'byor pa byis pa'i blo can don mi shes pa gang dag gis /
NK094(nge)001:2282: nga rgyal gyi dregsa pa'i dbang gis phrag dog gi
NK094(nge)001:2283: bsam pas brnyas par 'dod pa'i rtog ngan gyi rnam
NK094(nge)001:2284: grangsa ci tsam bskyed par byed pa na yang /
NK094(nge)001:2285: bskyed pa de snyed dang bskal ba'i grangsa mnyam par
NK094(nge)001:2286: 'bras bu dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal mi bzad pa myong
NK094(nge)001:2287: bar 'gyur ro // gal te rnam smin zad nas
NK094(nge)001:2288: bde bar skyes pa'i lus rjes su len pa na
NK094(nge)001:2289: bar 'gyur ro // yang / phrag dog gi sems
NK094(nge)001:2290: ci tsam skyes pa de snyed tsam gyi bskal pa'i
NK094(nge)001:2291: grangs su nges par gzod go cha bsgos te gzhi
NK094(nge)001:2293: gal te rnal 'byor pa makhasa gsal don dang ldan pa nyid kyis kyang ni /
NK094(nge)001:2294: gong ma de bzhin du rnal 'byor pa'i nang ngam
NK094(nge)001:2295: mi mkhas pa la phrag dog gis ngan rtog de
NK094(nge)001:2296: nyid bsams na / de yanga don mi shes pas rmongs nas gnas ngan len pa ste /
NK094(nge)001:2297: tshig la makhasa pasa don nyams pa de la ngan song las skyob par byed mi nus so //
NK094(nge)001:2302: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2303: rnal 'byor ba lta spyod tshul bzhin du ldan par byung ba'i dam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:2304: ngag rtsub mo mtshon cha'i tshig gis de yi thugs rgyud dkrugsa shing /
NK094(nge)001:2305: skyon gyis sgro 'dogs pa dang yon tan gyis skur
NK094(nge)001:2306: pa 'debs pa'i tshig gis rku ba dang ngag barlanga
NK094(nge)001:2307: po'i sgo nas skyon gang dang gang gis ngan du
NK094(nge)001:2308: brjod na yang / rnam smin gyi 'bras bu dmyal ba rdo rjer de nyid ltung bar 'gyur zhing /
NK094(nge)001:2309: dmyal ba las thon nas kyang zhar lasa byung ba
NK094(nge)001:2310: rgyu mthun pa'i rnam par smin pa tshe thung nad
NK094(nge)001:2311: mang sdug bsngal ldan par skye ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:2312: tshe 'di rang la yang bdag gis phar la skur
NK094(nge)001:2313: pa btab pa ji lta ba nyid tshur la 'debs
NK094(nge)001:2314: pas de ltar smod de sems dkrugs par 'gyur ba
NK094(nge)001:2319: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2320: las 'phro zhan cing skal ba damna pas mi shes
NK094(nge)001:2321: par spyod pa'i rnal 'byor pa rtsa ba'i dam tshig
NK094(nge)001:2322: nyamsa pa'i skyon can rnams kyi ranga bzhin nam mtshan
NK094(nge)001:2323: nyid ni ji lta bu zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:2324: bsam ngana gyi sgyu dang khro gtum chen po dang ldana pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:2325: dge sdig las mi bzad pa phra men du sbrel
NK094(nge)001:2326: te 'dren ma'i tshul gyis lasa drag po spyod par
NK094(nge)001:2327: byed pa'o // gsum pa la gsum ste /
NK094(nge)001:2328: mi mos pa'i rgyu tshul 'chos can la brten pa /
NK094(nge)001:2329: mi mos pa dngos bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:2330: mi mos pa'i skyon bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:2335: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2336: rnal 'byor pa gang dag don zab mo mi shes
NK094(nge)001:2337: par ngan pa'i ngang tshul can gyi byis pa'i rang
NK094(nge)001:2338: bzhin blo zhan par gyur pasa bla ma'i mtshan nyid
NK094(nge)001:2339: brtags pa la mi mkhas pas shin tu damna pa'i
NK094(nge)001:2340: phyogs ris kyi lta ba can du gyur te /
NK094(nge)001:2341: klu rgyal yon tan snying pos rim pa gsum pa'i man ngag las /
NK094(nge)001:2342: phyogs 'dzin bdag rtogs rmongs pa la //
NK094(nge)001:2343: nam yang rang grol don mi ldan //
NK094(nge)001:2344: bdag phung gzhan brlag slu brid mkhan //
NK094(nge)001:2345: zang zing gdung bas che bcos slu //
NK094(nge)001:2346: zhes gsungs pa ltar chen po'i gos gzung ba la
NK094(nge)001:2347: brten pa yisa sgo nas bla mar tshul 'chos pa
NK094(nge)001:2348: can la ltos par byed de bshes gnyen ngan pa
NK094(nge)001:2349: rten pa'i dbang gis rang nyid don yang dag la
NK094(nge)001:2351: 'di ni kun mkhyen dam pa rin po ches slob
NK094(nge)001:2352: dpon ngan pa dang slob ma blun pa gnyis ka'i
NK094(nge)001:2358: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2359: rnal 'byor pa gang su dag /lta ba dam pa'i
NK094(nge)001:2360: dgongs pa dang spyod pa dam par ldana te byamsa
NK094(nge)001:2361: pa chen po dang tshul khrims phun sum tshogs pa
NK094(nge)001:2362: rtag tu bzod pa la gnas pa mi rgyud kyi
NK094(nge)001:2363: tshul shes shing gsang chen gsang ba'i yang gsang gi
NK094(nge)001:2364: don rnams rgyud rgyal 'di nas 'byung ba de bzhin
NK094(nge)001:2365: du ma nor bar gzhung srong bar byed pa'i rnal
NK094(nge)001:2366: 'byor dbang po ni byang chub chen po 'grub pa'i
NK094(nge)001:2368: dam pa de lta bu la yang skal ba zhan
NK094(nge)001:2369: pa gang yin pa de dag 'dun pa med cing
NK094(nge)001:2370: mi mos pas gsang don mi 'grub pa'i rgyu la
NK094(nge)001:2371: gnas pa'o // gsum pa la gsum ste /
NK094(nge)001:2372: sangs rgyas mi thob pa'i skyon bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:2373: thar pa mi thob pa'i skyon bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:2374: log pa'i lam par 'gro ba'i skyon bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:2379: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2380: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig rnams bya
NK094(nge)001:2381: ba mang la don gyi gtad med pa spre'u ltar
NK094(nge)001:2382: ched du srung ba med par kha la khyer te
NK094(nge)001:2383: ci rung rung dag spyod par byed bzhin du /
NK094(nge)001:2384: bla na med pa'i byang chub snying po thob pa
NK094(nge)001:2385: yi sangsa rgyas kyi go 'phang 'grub pa ni snga
NK094(nge)001:2386: phyi'i dus thams cad nam du yang mi 'byung bar
NK094(nge)001:2387: nges pa nyid du mthong ngo //
NK094(nge)001:2388: des na sngar yang ma byung bas na dus phyis
NK094(nge)001:2389: su yang 'byung bar 'gyur ba yang dag pa'i gnas
NK094(nge)001:2390: dang gnas min kun ma 'dres par mkhyen pa gsang
NK094(nge)001:2391: bdag chen po ngasa kyang ye shes dag pa'i spyan
NK094(nge)001:2392: gyis ma mthong bas tshul bzhin du spyod cig pa'o
NK094(nge)001:2397: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2398: rgyal ba'i sras su gyur pa'i rnal 'byor pa yang
NK094(nge)001:2399: dag pa'i lam ston zhing ngan pa'i skyon sel la
NK094(nge)001:2400: makhasa shing tshul dang ldan pa la gang dag mi
NK094(nge)001:2401: shes pa kha cig gi phrag dog dang dregsa pa'i
NK094(nge)001:2402: nga rgyal gyi dbang gis mkhas pa de nyid spong
NK094(nge)001:2403: bar byed pa'i thabsa kyis de la smod de dma'
NK094(nge)001:2404: bar byed pa de ni 'khora ba'i gting rdo nyid
NK094(nge)001:2405: du gnas pa yin pas dmyal bar ltung ste namsa
NK094(nge)001:2406: kyang thar pa yang dag pa'i khar mi 'byung bar
NK094(nge)001:2411: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2412: mi mkhas pa'i rjes su 'brang zhing log pa'i spyod
NK094(nge)001:2413: pa la 'dun nas mi shes rmongsa pa'i rnal 'byor
NK094(nge)001:2414: pa dman pa'i gang zag rnams yang dag pa'i don
NK094(nge)001:2415: la mkhas pa'i bla ma dam pa chos zab mo
NK094(nge)001:2416: la brten nas lam rab tu gsang bar zhugs te
NK094(nge)001:2417: go 'phang mchog la ngasa par 'gro ba'i rjes su
NK094(nge)001:2419: de'i gdams pa la mi slob par zang zing gi
NK094(nge)001:2420: nor rdzas 'dod cing sgrub para byed pa'i thabs la
NK094(nge)001:2421: gang lta ba'i phyogs su zhen pa'i bla ma'i rjes
NK094(nge)001:2422: su 'gro zhing der 'dun par byed de rnyed pa
NK094(nge)001:2423: la lta ba de dag ni lam gol ba la
NK094(nge)001:2424: zhugs pa'i log pa'i lam par gyur pa dag yin
NK094(nge)001:2425: no // bzhi pa la gsum ste /
NK094(nge)001:2426: bral bar byed pa'i rgyu log pa'i khe bsgrub pa /
NK094(nge)001:2427: yon tan yod med lus 'dra yang don yis khyad par yod pa /
NK094(nge)001:2428: tshig tu brjod cing don du mi gnyer ba'i skyon bshad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:2433: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2434: de la ni rnal 'byor dam pa lta sgom gyi ltang bsag pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:2435: byang chub chen po'i khe spogs sgrub pa'i bsam pas
NK094(nge)001:2436: thos pa'i bya ba la sogs pa dus nam du
NK094(nge)001:2437: yang 'ban thag chad para gyur te shes pa'i blo
NK094(nge)001:2438: la mi rgyu bas 'byung ba med do //
NK094(nge)001:2439: 'o na ci zhig 'byung zhing byed ce na /
NK094(nge)001:2440: zang zing gi nor rdzas la dung zhing 'dod pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:2441: de nyid g.yo sgyu dang tshong sprul gyis btsal ba'i khe spogs ngan pa la ni /
NK094(nge)001:2442: shin tu gdung ste zas nor chung ngu gcig nyid
NK094(nge)001:2443: thob tu 'dod na yang cis kyang sgrub ste srog
NK094(nge)001:2444: dang basdo bas don du gnyer bar byed do //
NK094(nge)001:2445: de ni yi dwags chen po'i gnas na shin tu snying rje bar gnas so //
NK094(nge)001:2450: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2451: de bas na don la sems mi 'bral bar bya
NK094(nge)001:2452: ba'i phyir lta sgom zab mo la rnal du 'byor
NK094(nge)001:2453: pa'i dam pa chen po ma nor ba'i don dang
NK094(nge)001:2454: ldan pa rnams kyi dgongs spyod kyi ranga bzhin can
NK094(nge)001:2455: ni / dper na bum pa'i snod kyi nang gi
NK094(nge)001:2456: sgron ma 'od gsal ba nang na snang yang gzhan
NK094(nge)001:2457: gyis mi mthong ba ltar du /
NK094(nge)001:2458: yang dag pa'i rig pa gsang ba'i mdzod gsum gyi
NK094(nge)001:2459: don dgongs pa la gsal ba dang ldan yang srog
NK094(nge)001:2460: chagsa byi la'am rkun mo'i sder mo bskungs nas rdzas
NK094(nge)001:2461: len pa ltar don zab mo khong nas gab cing
NK094(nge)001:2462: sbas te spyod pa'i thabs kyis gzhan la don ston
NK094(nge)001:2463: pa ni thabs la mkhas pas mngon du mi snang
NK094(nge)001:2464: ba'i phyir gang 'dir so so'i skye bo blun pos
NK094(nge)001:2465: tshogs rnams de la yon tan can du cir yang
NK094(nge)001:2467: dper na 'di gnyis don la 'byor bas khyad yod
NK094(nge)001:2468: kyang phyi nas 'dra tshul gcig tu gyur te 'gron
NK094(nge)001:2469: po gang gi lus la rin po che'i gter 'chang
NK094(nge)001:2470: ba'i mi dang / blun por gyur te nor ci
NK094(nge)001:2471: yang med pa'i mi dag dang gnyis ka gnas gcig
NK094(nge)001:2472: ba'i mi dang / tu 'dug na / de gnyis
NK094(nge)001:2473: phyi nas mir 'dra zhing mir mtshungsa par gcig ste
NK094(nge)001:2474: khyad med par mthong ba dang 'dra'o //
NK094(nge)001:2475: de bas na gsang don ni de bzhin du spyad na byang chub shin tu myur ro //
NK094(nge)001:2479: nyid dang phrad par dka' //zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2480: tshig tu brjod kyang dang du ma blangs pas mi 'grub pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:2481: gang zag kha cig spyir gsang sngags gsang chen dam
NK094(nge)001:2482: pa 'di yi basngags pa gzhan la tshig tu brjod
NK094(nge)001:2483: par byed cing / rang nyid kyis gsang ba'i nges pa zab mo dona du gnyer ba med la /
NK094(nge)001:2484: bye brag tu gsang ba'i sgo yi ting nge 'dzina gyi basngagasa pa brjod par byed cing /
NK094(nge)001:2485: dgongs pa'i ting nge 'dzina don du gnyer ba med pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:2487: yang dag lta ba'i basngagasa pa brjod par byed cing /
NK094(nge)001:2488: yang dag lta ba'i nges gsang don du gnyer ba med pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:2489: dam tshig mchog gi basngagasa pa brjod par byed cing /
NK094(nge)001:2490: dam tshig gi gsang mdzod don du gnyer ba med
NK094(nge)001:2491: pa'i mtshan gzhir gyur pa dag ni rtsa bar dam
NK094(nge)001:2492: tshig la dgongs pa'i phyir bsnyad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:2493: de nye bar mtshon pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:2494: dpe ji ltar na 'gro ba mi gang la la dag gis /
NK094(nge)001:2495: nor bu rin chen 'di ni dgos 'dod 'di 'dra ster ba ste /
NK094(nge)001:2496: 'dod pa'i yon tan kun 'byung ba yin no zhes /
NK094(nge)001:2497: de yi yon tan gyi basngagasa pa rgya cher brjod pa na /
NK094(nge)001:2498: de la 'gro ba mi gang gzhan dag gis /
NK094(nge)001:2499: de ltar dgos 'dod phun sum tshogs pa 'byung bar
NK094(nge)001:2500: 'gyur ba yi nor bu de dag las khyod rang
NK094(nge)001:2501: la cung zad yod dam zhes dris kyang rang la
NK094(nge)001:2502: med pasa slar lan du smras pa /
NK094(nge)001:2503: gang zhig dgos pa skong ba yi nor bu rin
NK094(nge)001:2504: po che'i yon tan cung zad smos par zada kyi
NK094(nge)001:2505: / de nyid bdag la med do ces smra bar
NK094(nge)001:2506: byed de des dbul ba sel mi nus pa dang
NK094(nge)001:2507: / 'dra'o // dpe de bzhin du rnal 'byor pa
NK094(nge)001:2508: yang dag pa'i dam tshig gi don la mi brtson
NK094(nge)001:2509: / 'dra'o // pasa ni / bslab par bya ba'i chos kyi gzhi rten dang bral ba yin pas /
NK094(nge)001:2510: dam tshig dam pa'i yon tan gyi basngagasa pa brjod
NK094(nge)001:2511: par byed kyang gang zag de daga la ni dam
NK094(nge)001:2513: de la sogsa pa'i log par spyod pa rnams ni /
NK094(nge)001:2514: mchog gi gnas dam pa nyid dang phrad par dka'
NK094(nge)001:2515: bas dam tshig med na yon tan brjod kyang mi
NK094(nge)001:2517: 'di la bus pa gsum chos slob tu 'ongs pas gnyis kyis lobs /
NK094(nge)001:2518: gcig mas yul du yang yang bos pas ma lobs
NK094(nge)001:2519: pa'i sgrung gi lo rgyus 'chad srol kyang yod do
NK094(nge)001:2521: rnal 'byor pas nyams pa spang bar bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:2522: nyams pa'i mgon byas pa'i nyes pa bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:2523: ma tshor te nyams pas gzhan gyi dam pa yin yang mi 'grogs par bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:2524: nyams pa dang 'grogs pa'i skyon bshad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:2529: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2530: rnal 'byor dam pa gsang ba mchog gi chos 'dzina zhing dam tshig la gnas pa gang dag gisa /
NK094(nge)001:2531: rnal 'byor pa dam tshig nyamsa par gyur pa'i log
NK094(nge)001:2532: sred cana dag ni gsang sngags gsang ba dam pa
NK094(nge)001:2533: nyid 'jiga par byed pa'i dgrar gyur par bltas nasa
NK094(nge)001:2534: nyams pa de dag dang mi 'grogs par dper na
NK094(nge)001:2535: sdiga pa mthonga ba ltar bka' chad dbab ste tshar
NK094(nge)001:2536: bacada cinga gnas nas bskrad de slar mi 'ong bar
NK094(nge)001:2537: sa bcingas pa dang bsgral ba'i zhing du gang byed
NK094(nge)001:2538: pa yi skyes bu de ni dam pa'i sras kyi
NK094(nge)001:2539: yon tan 'chang ba'i rig 'dzin du 'gyur ro //
NK094(nge)001:2540: de nyid nye bar mtshon pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:2541: dper na rgyal pos khrims bcas pa'i sa gang der /
NK094(nge)001:2542: mi ganga daga gis rgyal po gang gi bka'i rgya
NK094(nge)001:2543: dang 'gal te rgyal khrimsa las 'das par gyur na
NK094(nge)001:2544: / de nyid rgyal blon gyis ranga gang dgar mi
NK094(nge)001:2545: gtong bar rgyal po'i chos lugsa kyi khrims dang sbyor
NK094(nge)001:2546: te srog la 'bab pa sogs kyis rgyal po'i bka'
NK094(nge)001:2547: yi yo srong ba'i bka' pa rgyal khrims 'tsho ba'i
NK094(nge)001:2548: blon po de yis de ltar byed pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:2549: rgyal po'i thugs zin nas nyes pa sgrubs pa'i blon
NK094(nge)001:2550: 'bangs dam pa zhes mgo nag kun la snang zhing
NK094(nge)001:2551: mthong ba nyid kyis rgyal khams su yang de ltar
NK094(nge)001:2552: gragsa par 'gyur ba ltar rnal 'byor pa'ang rjes su
NK094(nge)001:2557: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2558: de bas na nyams pa'i mgon byed pa ni nyes pa che ste /
NK094(nge)001:2559: dper na ldum rar dug gi sdong po skyes pa na /
NK094(nge)001:2560: ldum ra'i bdag po gnyer pas dug tu ngo shes ma thag tu /
NK094(nge)001:2561: rtsad nas phyungsa te 'byin cing med par byed do //
NK094(nge)001:2563: gal te ma phyungs par ldum zas de dag la
NK094(nge)001:2564: dug 'phel bar gyur na bdag po la sogs pa
NK094(nge)001:2565: kun dug gis 'chi bar 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK094(nge)001:2566: dpe de bzhin du gang dag nyamsa par gyur pa'i
NK094(nge)001:2567: gang zag dug can de nyid spyod pa'i brtul zhugsa
NK094(nge)001:2568: can gyi rnal 'byor pasa thabs drag pos gnas so
NK094(nge)001:2569: sor bskal pa'ang lo yis mi slebs pa'i gnas sam
NK094(nge)001:2570: lo yisa yun du mi phrad par bshugsa te spangsa
NK094(nge)001:2572: gal te gang dag gis mi spang bar snying rje
NK094(nge)001:2573: dang dam tshig la mos par tshul 'chos shing zang
NK094(nge)001:2575: nyams pa'i gang zag dang 'grogs shing de'i skyabs grogs
NK094(nge)001:2576: dang mgon byed pa de daga ni gsang sngags gsang
NK094(nge)001:2577: ba'i dam sri chen po yin te rdo rje dmyal
NK094(nge)001:2578: ba las nam yang thar pa'i skabs mi srid do
NK094(nge)001:2579: // de la ma nyams par gzhan gyis kha yogs
NK094(nge)001:2580: byung nas 'gal ba lta bu la mgon byas pa
NK094(nge)001:2581: ni min te rtsa ba ma nyams pas so //
NK094(nge)001:2582: zhes chos rje'i phyag mchan las gsung /
NK094(nge)001:2584: gnod par byed pa'i dam sri /
NK094(nge)001:2585: las las grub pa'i dam sri /
NK094(nge)001:2586: rkyen las gyur pa'i dam sri gsum 'byung ba las tha mar ngos gzung ngo //
NK094(nge)001:2591: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2592: gsang ba'i don la rnal 'byor dang ldan zhing tshul
NK094(nge)001:2593: bzhin du byed pa gang zhig de dag gis dam
NK094(nge)001:2594: tshig dam par tha tshig zab mora bcas pa rnams
NK094(nge)001:2595: la srung ba'i bsam pa mi g.yo bzhin du yang
NK094(nge)001:2596: dran pa dang shes bzhin chung bas rtsa ba yan
NK094(nge)001:2597: lag dang bcas pa rnams lasa gal te ma tshor
NK094(nge)001:2598: bzhin du yan lag gi dam tshig 'ga' zhig nyams
NK094(nge)001:2599: te zhig pa ra gyur kyang yan lag nyams pas
NK094(nge)001:2600: nyes pa'i rnam smin yoda kyang rtsa ba mi nyamsa
NK094(nge)001:2601: pas ltung bar mi 'gyur ba ni dpe ji ltar
NK094(nge)001:2602: na glang po e na ya zhes bya ba kun
NK094(nge)001:2603: 'dus kyi mchan rnying las sa srung ngam gla ba
NK094(nge)001:2604: la gsungs te de nyid shi nas rora ni gyur
NK094(nge)001:2605: moda kyang / rna spabs sam gi wang rtsis ni
NK094(nge)001:2606: don byed pa ltar rnal 'byor pa'ang ma tshor bar
NK094(nge)001:2607: don gyi yan lag nyamsa te rora gyur kyang /
NK094(nge)001:2608: theg 'og pa gzhan gyi dam par de nyid 'gyur zhing /
NK094(nge)001:2609: de yi don kyang byed nus pa yin no //
NK094(nge)001:2610: ma tshor bar nyams pa rnam smin chung ba de
NK094(nge)001:2611: lta mod kyang gsang sngags rang gi nang du tha
NK094(nge)001:2612: na 'di kun rnams dang dngos su lta a cang
NK094(nge)001:2613: yang ches te rmi lam du yang mthong zhing phrad
NK094(nge)001:2614: par mi bya'o // bzhi pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:2618: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2619: de bas na nyams pa dang phrag cing bshes pa'i
NK094(nge)001:2620: skyon 'byung ba rgyu mtshan ci yi phyir zhe na
NK094(nge)001:2621: / mthun pa'i dpe 'o ma nyung ngu zhig rul
NK094(nge)001:2622: basa de dang 'dres pa'i 'o ma thams cad kun
NK094(nge)001:2624: don ni rnal 'byor pa nyamsa par gyur pa gcig gis ni /
NK094(nge)001:2625: rnal 'byor dam tshig can kun kyang ma rungsa par
NK094(nge)001:2626: 'gyur bas nyams pa bzhin spyad pa thams cad de
NK094(nge)001:2628: 'o na dge slong thub dkas sangs rgyas thob /
NK094(nge)001:2629: dan phag gis rtsal chen rdzogs /
NK094(nge)001:2630: thar pa nag po dmyal bar ltung ba de gsum 'gal zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:2631: gnyis pos sems la zhe sdang ma skyes /
NK094(nge)001:2632: spyod pa kho bzhin ma spyad pas mi 'gal lo //
NK094(nge)001:2633: de bas na dam tshig nyams pas 'khor bar 'gyur la /
NK094(nge)001:2634: de la brten pa mang pos 'khor ba 'phel bas /
NK094(nge)001:2635: 'khor ba'i g.yul nyid rgyal bar byed pa yi log pa'i rnal 'byor thamsa cad kun /
NK094(nge)001:2636: gsang chen don dam snying po yang dag par ngesa pa'i rnal 'byor pasa /
NK094(nge)001:2637: de dag brtags nas thamsa cad bsgrimsa te spang bar bya dgos la /
NK094(nge)001:2638: gal te gzhung dang mi 'gal ba ltar byas nas
NK094(nge)001:2639: ma spangsa par skyon can de dang lhan cig log
NK094(nge)001:2640: par spyod na / 'khor ba'i g.yul ni rgyal bar 'gyur te /
NK094(nge)001:2641: bsgrub pa la yun bskyal kyang nyams pa'i grib kyis
NK094(nge)001:2642: byin rlabs ma brtas pa ltar bden pa'i byin rlabsa
NK094(nge)001:2643: mathu chung bar 'gyur bas rang dang gzhan kun kyang
NK094(nge)001:2644: dge ba spyod pa don chung ngo zhes zer nas
NK094(nge)001:2645: yang dag pa'i don la yid 'byung zhing log pa'i
NK094(nge)001:2646: chos kyi rjes phyogs la gzhol bar 'gyur te kun
NK094(nge)001:2647: gyis dam tshig las log pa'i lasa lam spyod pas
NK094(nge)001:2648: chos skyong ba'i bsrung ma rnams mi dga' bas yid
NK094(nge)001:2649: du mi 'ong ba sna tshogsa 'byung bar snang la
NK094(nge)001:2650: / des na chos bsgrub pas 'di ltar 'gyur zhes
NK094(nge)001:2651: sgro 'dogs pa dang yon tan ma byung zhes skur
NK094(nge)001:2652: pa 'debs pa'am ci 'dod byas pas sgro 'dogs shing
NK094(nge)001:2653: dam tshig mi srungs pas skur pa gnyis byas pas
NK094(nge)001:2654: bka' yi chad pa drag po gang yin pa yang
NK094(nge)001:2655: / 'byung ste / de'ang ye shes can gyi lha
NK094(nge)001:2656: mchog lta bu 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lta ba
NK094(nge)001:2657: mnga' ba rnams rang bzhin shugs kyis thugs rje la
NK094(nge)001:2658: gnas pas namsa kyang gnod pa yong ye mi mdzad
NK094(nge)001:2660: gnas pa yi ma mo dang mkha' 'gro gang dag
NK094(nge)001:2661: ma rungsa shing mathu chen po can rnams kyis /
NK094(nge)001:2662: rnal 'byor loga par spyod pa rnams kyi skyon mthong
NK094(nge)001:2663: ba tsam na tshe 'di la chad pasa gcoda cing
NK094(nge)001:2664: phyi ma la thamsa cad ngana 'gror dmyal ba chen
NK094(nge)001:2665: po'i gnas su spyi'u tshugsa su lhung nas rnam par
NK094(nge)001:2666: smin pa dbal tsha ba myong bar 'gyur ro //
NK094(nge)001:2668: bzang po'i mtshan nyid bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:2669: bzang po la sngon du 'gro ba'i dam tshig bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:2671: bsgrub pa'i snod mchog /ces pa nas /
NK094(nge)001:2673: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2674: 'o na gsang sngags kyi snod ma nor ba ji lta bu snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:2675: theg pa chen po'i gsang ba'i bsgrub pa don du
NK094(nge)001:2676: gnyer bar byed pa'i thabs dam pa bstan pa'i snod
NK094(nge)001:2677: mchog bzang po rab tu gyur pa ni gcig ste
NK094(nge)001:2678: / de la dam pa'i mtshan nyid 'di ltar yod de /
NK094(nge)001:2679: snod ngan pa bzhi po 'di rnams dang mtshan nyid
NK094(nge)001:2680: mi mthun pas de las bzlog pa'i yon tan kun
NK094(nge)001:2681: rdzogsa par yod pa'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK094(nge)001:2687: ci la'ang 'dzin chagsa med pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:2688: gtong phod chen po dang ldan pa'i semsa dang /
NK094(nge)001:2689: shes raba kyi spyan mnga' ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:2690: rgyud sbyangs pa'i yon tan gyis rnam grol gsang ba'i
NK094(nge)001:2691: thabs la mkhas pa'i lde mig gisa gti mug rmongs
NK094(nge)001:2692: pa'i ma rig pa'i tha rama gyi sgo phye nas
NK094(nge)001:2693: chos kyi snying po'i don mthong ba'i blo gros kyi
NK094(nge)001:2694: mig dang ldan pasa gsang sngags ji lta ba'i gnas
NK094(nge)001:2695: lugs mtha' dang dbus kun bral ba'i skyes bu dam
NK094(nge)001:2696: pa'i spyod yul la nges pa rnyed de ma nor
NK094(nge)001:2697: ba'i lam du 'jug pa'i thabs shes pa ni sems
NK094(nge)001:2698: zhi bas yon tan gyi ljon pa'i sdong po chen
NK094(nge)001:2699: po nga rgyal gyi dug gi sdong po sogs nyon
NK094(nge)001:2700: mongs pa'i rtog tshogs dang bral zhing raba tu dul
NK094(nge)001:2701: ba'o // de lta bu'i snod dang ldan pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:2702: dam pa mchog gi tha tshig zab mo rgyud lung
NK094(nge)001:2703: lasa 'byung ba bzhin du yang dag par bsrung ba'i
NK094(nge)001:2704: mtshan nyid drug gnyis dang ldan pa'i drang srong mchog
NK094(nge)001:2705: gi dka' thub dam pa la gnas pa de nyid
NK094(nge)001:2706: theg chen gsang ba'i dam tshig rnams srung ste rgyal
NK094(nge)001:2707: ba'i sras rgyud 'dzin pa'i dam pa nyid yin pasa
NK094(nge)001:2708: de la gsang sngags kyi gab pa dang sbas pa'i
NK094(nge)001:2709: don rnams kyi man ngag gi gsang sgo dbye ste
NK094(nge)001:2710: bstan par bya'o // gnyis pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:2715: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2716: rnal 'byor gyi mchog dam pa gsang sngags bla na
NK094(nge)001:2717: med pa'i rgyal ba'i rigsa 'dzin cing rgyud du byung
NK094(nge)001:2718: ba dag /rgyud rgyal 'di lta bu'i don lasa ngesa
NK094(nge)001:2719: para brtagsa te gzhung gi dam tshig ji bzhin du
NK094(nge)001:2720: srung zhing spyod pa'i rgyal sras rigs kyi bu mchog
NK094(nge)001:2721: de ni / snod dam pa yin pa'i phyir lta
NK094(nge)001:2722: ba'i dam tshig zab mo gting dpag dka' ba'i shes
NK094(nge)001:2723: de ni / rab dang / bsgrub pa'i dam tshig nyi shu rtsa bzhi rdzogsa par bstan pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:2724: brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa mchog gi dam tshig ni nyi shu rtsa gsum dang /
NK094(nge)001:2725: rnal 'byor chen po'i spyod pa rgyun gyi dam tshig
NK094(nge)001:2726: bzhi la sogs pas 'bras bu la blo 'byor bar
NK094(nge)001:2727: nye bas bde ba mchog nyid ston pa yi man
NK094(nge)001:2728: ngag blo la shong ba de lta bu la ma
NK094(nge)001:2729: nor nges pa'i dam tshig gi lung 'di rnams bstan
NK094(nge)001:2731: de bas na lam gyi rim pa rkyen dang bcas pa dag bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:2732: de yang lam gyi thog mar dgos pa'i yan lag gang snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:2733: dam tshig 'di ni lam dang bslab pa kun gyi
NK094(nge)001:2734: sngon du 'gro bas gzhi dam tshig gis gzung dgos
NK094(nge)001:2735: pa'i phyir te des na lta ba zab mo la
NK094(nge)001:2736: sogsa pa bslab pa dgu po kun gyis kyang thog
NK094(nge)001:2737: mar sngon du 'gro ba yin zhing /
NK094(nge)001:2738: nyams ma nyams kyi rnam smin gnyis ka rlabs po
NK094(nge)001:2739: che'i phyir yang rdo rje lta bu'i 'da' bar dka'
NK094(nge)001:2740: ba'i tha tshig drag po'am dam tshig gi ming yang
NK094(nge)001:2741: thob ste / de ltar legs nyes stobs che ba
NK094(nge)001:2742: yi sgo nas shin tu'ang bsrung dka' ba gacana 'phrang
NK094(nge)001:2743: dog mo dang 'dra ba'i lam gyi dam tshig rnams
NK094(nge)001:2744: bsrung bar byas te skye rga na 'chi'i gnas las
NK094(nge)001:2745: gdon pa'i dgos ched kyi phyir du /
NK094(nge)001:2747: spyi'i dam tshig nyi shu rtsa brgyad dang /
NK094(nge)001:2748: gsang chen nang pa rang gi khyad par ram /
NK094(nge)001:2749: khyad par gyi dama tshig bzhi la sogs pa bshad
NK094(nge)001:2750: pa rnams gsang bar ngesa pa'i dam tshig la the
NK094(nge)001:2751: tshom mi za bar nan tan du byed pa'i don
NK094(nge)001:2752: gyis mnyam pa 'i ngang du blo brtan cing brtsan
NK094(nge)001:2753: par red nas ma nyams par bsrung na de ni
NK094(nge)001:2754: man ngag dang dngos grub kyi dbyig gi snod mchog
NK094(nge)001:2755: chena po yina par bstan pas don zab mo'i lam
NK094(nge)001:2756: gyi nang nas kyang 'bras bu'i sdong po'i gzhi dang
NK094(nge)001:2763: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2764: dam tshig gi yon tan dang dpe thun mong du bstan pa gang zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:2765: rgyud gzhung nas ji ltar bstan pa bzhin du dam
NK094(nge)001:2766: tshig gi daka'a thub ma nyams par bsrung thub pa
NK094(nge)001:2767: ltar / yon tan ji 'dod pa yang de ltar 'byung ba ni /
NK094(nge)001:2768: dper na yida bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che dang 'dra ste /
NK094(nge)001:2769: bdag gi yida du 'ong ba'i dngos grub rnam pa
NK094(nge)001:2770: gnyis kyi gnas skabs ji ltar 'dod pa dang mthar
NK094(nge)001:2771: thug mchog gi bde ba phun sum tshogs pa nyid
NK094(nge)001:2772: 'byung ba'o // des na rigsa 'dzin dang rgyal ba
NK094(nge)001:2773: kun kyang dam tshig ma nyams pa las 'byung ba'i
NK094(nge)001:2774: phyir de dag gi yang bskyed pa'i yum mo //
NK094(nge)001:2775: de bzhina du dka' thub mchog gi dam tshig dam
NK094(nge)001:2776: pa 'di ni dam la gnas pasa lam dang 'bras
NK094(nge)001:2777: bu kun rten pa'i gzhi yi phyir sa gzhi chen
NK094(nge)001:2779: dam tshig ma nyams na byang chub chen por 'tsho
NK094(nge)001:2780: zhing 'dzin pas yang dag pa'i dka' thub kun gyi
NK094(nge)001:2781: srog tu gyur pas srog gi dbang po dang 'dra
NK094(nge)001:2783: dper na nor dang 'dra bar rnal 'byor pa rab
NK094(nge)001:2784: 'bring tha ma dam tshig ma nyams pa kun gyi
NK094(nge)001:2785: 'dod pa 'byung ba'i rgyu yi nor rnams kyi'ang mchoga
NK094(nge)001:2786: go // dam tshig ma nyams pa 'di ni 'di
NK094(nge)001:2787: dang pha rol gyi 'khor ba'i 'jigsa pa'am 'jigs pa
NK094(nge)001:2788: brgyad kyis mi tshugs par skyob pa'i skyabsa su gyur
NK094(nge)001:2789: pas rdzong chen po dang yang 'dra'o //
NK094(nge)001:2797: gcan gzan khro bo dang brgyad du phyag mchan gcig las gsung /
NK094(nge)001:2798: gzhi dam tshig dam pa 'di la brten nas mthar
NK094(nge)001:2799: phyin par bya ba'i phyir bgrod pa byed pa'i lam
NK094(nge)001:2801: dam la gnas pa 'di nyid 'khor ba'i chu bosa las sgrol ba'i gru chen po'ang yin no //
NK094(nge)001:2802: de bzhina du sku gsung thugs kyi dngosa grub da
NK094(nge)001:2803: nga thun mong gi dngos grub sgrub pa'i thabs dam
NK094(nge)001:2804: pa'am gzhan nas btsal mi dgos pa'i phyir bsgrub bya'i
NK094(nge)001:2806: dam tshig dang ldan pa la bar chad kyis mi
NK094(nge)001:2807: tshugs pas byang chub chen po'i lam du zhugs nas
NK094(nge)001:2808: mthar thug gi bar du 'grogs shing des phan 'dogs
NK094(nge)001:2809: pa'i phyir grogsa kyi mchog kyang yin te /
NK094(nge)001:2810: dam tshig 'di ni blo gros kyi mig long ba
NK094(nge)001:2811: dag /yang dag pa'i lam ma nor bar khrid cing
NK094(nge)001:2812: g.yang sar mi 'gro bas dmigsa bu'i thag pa lta
NK094(nge)001:2814: dam tshig srung ba las ma nyams pa 'di ni
NK094(nge)001:2815: byang chub sgrub nas sgrib pa'i dpung dang sdug bsngal
NK094(nge)001:2816: dang bdud dang mu stegs la sogs pa gzhan gyi
NK094(nge)001:2817: sde rnams 'jomsa pa'i dmag dpung lta bu yang yin
NK094(nge)001:2818: no // dam tshig ma nyams pa 'di ni 'khor
NK094(nge)001:2819: ba'i g.yul lasa rgyal bar byed pa'i dpa' bo lta
NK094(nge)001:2821: de bas bsrung ba rnam pa gnyis kyang dus gcig tu tshang ngo //
NK094(nge)001:2826: gal mdo nges pa'i dam tshig gsum bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:2827: thun mong gi dam tshig nyer brgyad bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:2828: lhag pa'i dam tshig bzhi bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:2829: brtul zhugs kyi dam tshig nyer gsum bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:2830: bsgrub pa'i dam tshig nyi shu bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:2831: spyod lam rgyun gyi dam tshig bzhi bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:2832: tshogs su mi chud pa'i skyon zung dgu bsal ba /
NK094(nge)001:2835: lta ba'i dam tshig bshad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:2843: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2844: dam tshig gi yon tan rgya chen po de lta
NK094(nge)001:2845: bu yod pa des na dus gsum gyi rgyal ba
NK094(nge)001:2846: thams cad 'di las byung ba'i phyir gyi dam pa'i
NK094(nge)001:2847: gtan tshigsa tshad mar nges pa theg pa mchog gi
NK094(nge)001:2848: dam tshig 'di ni rnam pa ci yi sgo nas
NK094(nge)001:2849: kyang rnal 'byor dam pa gang dag rang gi lus
NK094(nge)001:2850: ngag yid kyi sgo gsum po nyid nyes byas med
NK094(nge)001:2851: par dag pa gsum dang ldan pas rtsa ba'i dam
NK094(nge)001:2852: tshig gsum gyi dag pa'i mtha' yi gzhi bzung nas
NK094(nge)001:2853: bsrung bar bya'o // gnyis pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:2857: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2858: dam tshig bsrung bar bya ba'i rtsa ba dang yan lag gang snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:2859: thog mar gal mdo nges pa'i dam tshig gi /
NK094(nge)001:2862: mthar phyin pa'i rtags gsum rim par ston te /
NK094(nge)001:2863: theg pa mchog la zhugs pas sgo gang 'dir dbang phyug chen po bla ma dang /
NK094(nge)001:2866: rang gi sems kyi dpang po bzhi lung las 'byung ba bzhin sun mi dbyung bar bkur te /
NK094(nge)001:2867: sri zhu bla mas ma khrel /
NK094(nge)001:2868: sgrub pa'am srung ba yi dam gyis ma khrel /
NK094(nge)001:2869: gdung sems mched lcam gyis ma khrel /
NK094(nge)001:2870: g.yo sgyu rang sems kyis ma khrel ba'i sgo nas /
NK094(nge)001:2871: lus ngag yid kyi tshul gsum dag pa'am /
NK094(nge)001:2872: dam par byung ba'i tshul dang /
NK094(nge)001:2873: sgo gsum nyes pa med pa'i tshul dang /
NK094(nge)001:2874: dam par ro gcig pa'i tshul dang gsum gyis dag pa'i tshul shes pas mnyes par bya ste /
NK094(nge)001:2875: khrel ba dang phyis gnong 'gyod kyis mi gnod par
NK094(nge)001:2876: byas te dam bcas pa'i tshul brtan par gzung ste
NK094(nge)001:2877: nges par bsrung zhing nam du'ang gtang bar mi bya
NK094(nge)001:2880: dbang bskur mchog gi bla ma /
NK094(nge)001:2881: man ngag ston pa'i bla ma /
NK094(nge)001:2882: ma rig pa 'dren pa'i bla ma dang bzhir gsungs pa'i 'chad tshul zhig kyang bzhugs so //
NK094(nge)001:2883: bla ma dang mched dang lha dang bdag nyid kyis
NK094(nge)001:2884: ma khrel ba bzhis yongsa su ma nyams pa'i mado'am
NK094(nge)001:2888: zlas yongs su ma nyamsa pa'i mdo bzhi po dag dang ldan pa ste /
NK094(nge)001:2890: yang na kun tu ma nyams pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:2891: rtsa ba dang yan lag ma nyams pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:2893: zhar gyis ma nyams pa'i ngo bo ni mdor bsdus
NK094(nge)001:2894: pa'i grangs te rtsa ba'i rgyud las lngar gsungs so
NK094(nge)001:2896: de ltar bsrung ba mthar phyin na phyag rgya chen
NK094(nge)001:2897: po bzhi'i rtagsa kyi dngos grub dam can 'du zhing
NK094(nge)001:2899: byin rlabs che zhing rig pa 'char ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:2900: yid 'ong 'byung zhing 'dod pa grub pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:2901: mang pos bkur zhing grags pa 'thob pa rnam pa
NK094(nge)001:2902: bzhir 'byung ba dang bacasa pas mdo gzung bar bya'o
NK094(nge)001:2903: // mdor na dam tshig gi don rnams dran pa
NK094(nge)001:2904: la btags te nyams pa dang ma nyams pa'i grangs
NK094(nge)001:2905: nyin zhag re bzhin bsngo bgranga bya zhing /
NK094(nge)001:2906: nyams pa rnams ni thabs bzhis bshags la /
NK094(nge)001:2907: ma nyams pa rnams byang chub chen por bsngo ste dper grangs ni phyug po nor bsngo ltar bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:2908: de skad du'ang rtsa ba'i rgyud las /
NK094(nge)001:2909: mdor na bdag gi sgo gsum po //
NK094(nge)001:2910: dag pa gsum gyi mtha' bzung nas //
NK094(nge)001:2911: lha dang grogs dang slob dpon dang //
NK094(nge)001:2912: bdag nyid dag pa ma khrel ba'i //
NK094(nge)001:2913: tshul gsum mi gnod dam bcas gsum //
NK094(nge)001:2914: yongs su ma nyams mdo bzhi po //
NK094(nge)001:2915: mthar phyin rgya rtags rnam bzhir bcas //
NK094(nge)001:2916: mdo don dran pa la bgrang bsngo //
NK094(nge)001:2918: de ltar sgo gsum dang nyon mongs pa'i khengs pa
NK094(nge)001:2919: dul ba'i rgyud dang ldan te tha tshiga brtan pa
NK094(nge)001:2920: la gnas pa can du gyur pa'i shes rab kyi
NK094(nge)001:2921: blo stobs dang mosa pa chung ngu'i sa par gnas
NK094(nge)001:2922: shing cig char du 'jug mi nus pa'i bu mchog
NK094(nge)001:2924: dge bcu dang 'dul sdom la sogs pa nying lag
NK094(nge)001:2925: phra mo'i phra mo dang yan lag phra mo yan
NK094(nge)001:2926: chada chud mi gsan par bdag dang gzhan gyi don
NK094(nge)001:2927: du nan tan gyis ni yongs su bsrung bar bya'o
NK094(nge)001:2932: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:2933: rtsa ba'i bsrung bya gang snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:2934: 'di bzhin du bsrung bar bya stee /
NK094(nge)001:2935: slob dpon lta bur sprul pa'i bdud nyid dang //
NK094(nge)001:2936: dngos grub len pa'i bar du gcod pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:2937: slob dpon rtsol ba'i tshig bcag ma gtogs par //
NK094(nge)001:2938: bka' yi zur yang bcag par mi bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:2939: dge la bskul dang phan 'dogs ma yin pa //
NK094(nge)001:2940: grogs mchog thugs ni nam yang dkrug mi bya //
NK094(nge)001:2941: zhes sku yi dam tshig dang /
NK094(nge)001:2942: ting 'dzin dkyil 'khor rnal 'byor bsam gtan dang //
NK094(nge)001:2943: snying po bzlas pa bar du mi gcad do //
NK094(nge)001:2944: zhes gsung gi dam tshig dang /
NK094(nge)001:2945: byang chub don du gnyer ba ma yin pa //
NK094(nge)001:2946: srog gi phyir yang gsang tshig mi spel lo //
NK094(nge)001:2947: sems can don du 'gyur ba ma yin pa //
NK094(nge)001:2948: gsang sngags phyi dang nang gi dam tshig dang //
NK094(nge)001:2949: byang chub sdom dang nyan thos tshul khrims dang //
NK094(nge)001:2950: sa bdag rgyal khrims 'gal bar mi bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:2951: zhes thugsa kyi dam tshig gi don te /
NK094(nge)001:2952: rdo rje theg pa chen po yi rtsa ba'i dam tshig bsrung ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:2954: rjes su rnal 'byor rang gi thun mong min pa'i
NK094(nge)001:2955: dam tshig snang srid dbyings dang ye shes su gsal
NK094(nge)001:2956: bas gnyis med kyi ngang du sgo gsum sku gsung
NK094(nge)001:2957: thugs su rtogs pa las mi 'da' ba'i tha tshig
NK094(nge)001:2959: snga ma rtsa ba'i rgyud las /
NK094(nge)001:2960: snod du gyur pa yum gyi dbyings //
NK094(nge)001:2961: bcud rnams rgyal ba yab kyi mkha' //
NK094(nge)001:2963: 'di ni rdo rje tha tshig yin //
NK094(nge)001:2964: srid pa'i sems can thams cad dang //
NK094(nge)001:2965: thar pa chos kyi rnam grangs kun //
NK094(nge)001:2966: so sor thams cad snang ba ste //
NK094(nge)001:2967: kun kyang mnyam pa'i ngang du gsal //
NK094(nge)001:2968: spyod pa'i las dang rtog pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:2969: mtshan mar gyur pa thams cad kyang //
NK094(nge)001:2970: sems kyi phyi nang spyod yul de //
NK094(nge)001:2971: brtags na longs spyod tshogs su 'gyur //
NK094(nge)001:2972: ma skyes stong pa sku yi rgya //
NK094(nge)001:2973: rang bzhin smon med gsung gi don //
NK094(nge)001:2974: mtshan med yid las 'das pa thugs //
NK094(nge)001:2975: rnam gsum bde chen sangs rgyas so //
NK094(nge)001:2976: mnyam pa'i lta bas dbang sgyur na //
NK094(nge)001:2977: 'khor ba thams cad dbyings la snang //
NK094(nge)001:2978: las kun rdzogs pa'i mchog yin te //
NK094(nge)001:2979: gzhan du phrin las lus pa med //
NK094(nge)001:2980: sdug bsngal byang chub chen po ste //
NK094(nge)001:2982: sgrib pa rnam dag chos kyi dbyings //
NK094(nge)001:2983: nyon mongs kun kyang byang chub don //
NK094(nge)001:2984: snang ba med pa'i don mthong dang //
NK094(nge)001:2985: sa dang sa yi rim par ni //
NK094(nge)001:2987: 'di ni snang med thob pa'i gnas //
NK094(nge)001:2988: sku dang gsung thugs mi g.yo ba'i //
NK094(nge)001:2989: ji bzhin nyid kyi ngang la gnas //
NK094(nge)001:2991: de nas yan lag bsrung ba ni 'di lta ste /
NK094(nge)001:2992: dam pa'i chos 'jig dam pa gsod pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:2993: mtshams med lnga byed kun la gnod pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:2994: chos kyi spun dang byang chub phyir gnod pa //
NK094(nge)001:2995: tshad med nan tan rdo rje mtshon gyis gsad //
NK094(nge)001:2996: don med gang yod ser snas 'jungs pa'i nor //
NK094(nge)001:2997: kha na ma tho med par blangs nas su //
NK094(nge)001:2998: de yi bsod nams chen po 'thob bya'i phyir //
NK094(nge)001:2999: mchod dang spyad dang sbyin pa chen por bya //
NK094(nge)001:3000: slob dpon dkor dang srog chags bskyabs pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:3001: sems can byang chub lam du drang ba'i rdzun //
NK094(nge)001:3002: med las yod smra yod las med smra dang //
NK094(nge)001:3003: bag dang ldan par rtag tu smra bar bya //
NK094(nge)001:3004: dam pa sun 'byin mi mthun gol ba dag /don dang ldan pas tshar bcad tshig rtsub smra //
NK094(nge)001:3005: dge sdig 'grogs 'bral bzang ngan lta dbye'i phyir //
NK094(nge)001:3006: phra ma'i tshig don rtag tu dbye bar bya //
NK094(nge)001:3007: rtogs nas bdag gzhan don phyir spyad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:3008: zhes spyad par bya ba lnga dang /
NK094(nge)001:3009: sha chen bshang gci khrag dang byang chub sems //
NK094(nge)001:3010: grub pa bzhi dang yin pa'i mthu ldan pa //
NK094(nge)001:3011: blang dor med par bsten pas mchog 'grub phyir //
NK094(nge)001:3012: gtsang dme med pa'i sems kyis mi 'bral lo //
NK094(nge)001:3013: zhes yid 'ong dang du blang ba lnga dang /
NK094(nge)001:3014: dngos dang gdug pa 'joms byed zhe sdang gnyis //
NK094(nge)001:3015: gang la'ang rnam rtog phyogs med gti mug dang //
NK094(nge)001:3016: gnyis med don dang mo rigs sbyor zhing chags //
NK094(nge)001:3017: yang dag don la sran 'dzugs dregs 'joms nga rgyal dang //
NK094(nge)001:3018: log dang snod ngan mi tshud phrag dog chen po rnams //
NK094(nge)001:3019: shes nas nam du'ang mi spang gnyis med spyod //
NK094(nge)001:3021: phung po lnga dang 'byung lnga yab yum lnga //
NK094(nge)001:3022: rnam shes nyon mongs rigs lnga ye shes lnga //
NK094(nge)001:3023: kha dog lnga dang dbang lnga yul lnga sogs //
NK094(nge)001:3024: rang bzhin sems phyir gcig dang tha dad grol //
NK094(nge)001:3025: de phyir lnga lngar sbyar zhing shes par bya //
NK094(nge)001:3026: zhes shes par bya ba lnga dang /
NK094(nge)001:3027: rnam snang mi bskyod 'byung ldan 'od dpag med //
NK094(nge)001:3028: don grub la sogs sangs rgyas lnga po rnams //
NK094(nge)001:3029: 'bras bu'i bdag phyir ting 'dzin brtson ldan pas //
NK094(nge)001:3030: phyi mar mi smon tshe 'di nyid la grub par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:3031: zhes sgrub par bya ba'am grub pa lnga ste mdor
NK094(nge)001:3032: na yan lag nyi shu rtsa lnga dang rtsa ba
NK094(nge)001:3033: gsum bcas dam tshig nyi shu rtsa brgyad do //
NK094(nge)001:3038: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:3039: shin tu bya ba med pa'i rnal 'byor gyi a ti yo ga'i dam tshig bzhi ni /
NK094(nge)001:3040: bsrung dang mi bsrung gi phyogs ris med par thams
NK094(nge)001:3041: cad chos kyi dbyings su nges pas grangs su bcad
NK094(nge)001:3042: la so sor bsrung du med pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:3043: gang yang dam par nges pas dam tshig la blang
NK094(nge)001:3044: dor med de gza' gtad dang bral bas phyal ba
NK094(nge)001:3045: dang / bdag nyid chen por thig le nyag gcig
NK094(nge)001:3046: gi ngo bor dbyer med pa ma gtogs gzhan med
NK094(nge)001:3047: pas mnyam pa chen po gcig gi ngang las mi
NK094(nge)001:3048: dang / 'da' ba dang / bsrung bya thams cad
NK094(nge)001:3049: ched du ma bsrung bar rtsol med bde ba chen
NK094(nge)001:3050: por bsrung mtshams dang bral bas lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK094(nge)001:3051: ngang chen por yongs su rdzogs pa nyid dang lhag
NK094(nge)001:3052: pa'i dam tshig dam pa bzhi ste /
