NK094(nge)001:9551: man ngag bzhag cing dbang dang dam tshig gi snod
NK094(nge)001:9552: du rung ba'i slob ma dag gzhug par bya ba'i
NK094(nge)001:9553: ched du / dapanga po dang mkhyen par gsol ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:9554: la sogsa pa zhes bsdu ba'i don gyis bshad pa'i slob ma la dam dbog pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:9555: dbang bskur ba'i las kyi rim pa kun rdzogs par bya ba yisa dbang bskur ba nyid de /
NK094(nge)001:9556: de yang dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i tshul la dang po rdo rje rgyal po nyid 'jug pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:9557: de nas slob ma gzhug pa'i rim pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:9558: de la yon dang sbyar te dbang bskur ba rgyas par bya ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:9559: de dag zin nas dngosa grub stsol par gsol ba
NK094(nge)001:9560: gdab ste blang ba'i bar bya zhing sgrub pa'i mjug
NK094(nge)001:9561: tu'ang dngos grub blang bar bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:9562: gnyis pa la bcu gcig ste /
NK094(nge)001:9564: bsgrub pa che chung 'dod pa ltar sbyin pa /
NK094(nge)001:9565: bsgrub mi nus pa la gsang bar gdams pa /
NK094(nge)001:9566: rmongs pa gsang sngags su mos pa bsgyur ba /
NK094(nge)001:9567: shes rab can la rim pa bzhin bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:9568: blo skyed can la sgom thabs bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:9569: spyod pa rtsing po la ltung ba'i nyen bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:9570: snod dang sbyar la dbang bskur bar gdams pa /
NK094(nge)001:9571: dbang dang gdams ngag sbyin lugs bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:9572: blo dang ldan pa la bslab pa'i rtsa sbyongs shig par gdams pa /
NK094(nge)001:9573: thog mar gral dbye zhing lha bsgom lugs bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:9575: rdo rje tha tshig /ces pa nas /
NK094(nge)001:9577: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:9578: de la thabs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi rdo rje lta
NK094(nge)001:9579: bu'i sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i dam
NK094(nge)001:9580: tshig gam bsod nams dang bsnyen sgrub bzhi'i rdo rje
NK094(nge)001:9581: tha tshig rnam pa lnga nyid dpog pa yisa dam
NK094(nge)001:9582: tshig gi bslab pa'i gnyer rnams rang rang dang 'tshams
NK094(nge)001:9583: par ci rigsa para blo'i rtsal gyi che chung gi
NK094(nge)001:9584: rima pa bzhin du skal ba dang sbyar la legs
NK094(nge)001:9586: rdo rje theg pa chen po las slar ma ldog
NK094(nge)001:9587: par gal chen btsug ste tshul bzhin du 'bras bu
NK094(nge)001:9588: bsgrub par bya bar bus mna' bora te rigs nges
NK094(nge)001:9589: par bya ba la sbyar ro //
NK094(nge)001:9594: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:9595: dbang thob cing rigs nges par byas pa'i rting de
NK094(nge)001:9596: nas slob bus ji ltar bzod cing gsang ba'i sgrub
NK094(nge)001:9597: pa che chung rnams gang zhu zhing ji ltar 'doda
NK094(nge)001:9598: pa de nyid bstan la chud mi gsan par nana
NK094(nge)001:9599: tan du sgrubs par gyis shig gdams par bya ste
NK094(nge)001:9600: / de phyin chad slob bu de'ang rdo rje theg
NK094(nge)001:9601: pa gsang sngags nang ba'i rnal 'byor sgrub pa lung
NK094(nge)001:9602: gi bka' la gnas pa'i dam par 'gyur bar bya'o
NK094(nge)001:9607: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:9608: shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin dang brtson 'grus chung
NK094(nge)001:9609: bas mi gshis kyis sgom sgrub chen po mi nus
NK094(nge)001:9610: pa dang la sogas pa'i don gyis bsdu bar gsang
NK094(nge)001:9611: ba'i spyod pa gzhung mi srong ba dang nyan sgom
NK094(nge)001:9612: gyi skal ba med pa dag la bla ma'i bkas
NK094(nge)001:9613: bsgrub par mi gnang bar gsang ba'i bka' rgya dam
NK094(nge)001:9614: par rdo rje'i tshig gisa nana chagsa bya ste /
NK094(nge)001:9615: gzhan la'ang gsang sgom zhig par bsgo bar bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:9620: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:9621: gsang sngags kyi don la rmongsa pa dag thabs kyis
NK094(nge)001:9622: rim par drangs te gsang sngags la gzud pa'i phyir
NK094(nge)001:9623: thog mar rang dga' ba la yid mos par byas
NK094(nge)001:9624: nas mthar gsang ba la semsa skyed par byed de
NK094(nge)001:9625: / de nas gsang sngags kyi che ba'i yon tan
NK094(nge)001:9626: brjod pa'i ngo mtshar gyi tshig gisa 'adu shes gyen
NK094(nge)001:9627: du bsgyur te gsang sngags la mos pa skyer gzhugs
NK094(nge)001:9628: / pa'o // des bas na rmongs pa'ang chud mi gsan te 'tshams pas don bya ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:9633: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:9634: slob bu shes rab kyi mig gam spyan dang ldan
NK094(nge)001:9635: pa can rnams la shes bya'i yul gyi snying po
NK094(nge)001:9636: lta ba'i don gyi gnas lugs mthar thug pa bstan
NK094(nge)001:9637: phyir gdams ngag bya thabs thamsa cad phyi nang gsang
NK094(nge)001:9638: ba'i rim pa ji bzhina blo goms tshul dang sbyar
NK094(nge)001:9639: te bstan para byas nas bslab pa'i mtha' bcu kun
NK094(nge)001:9640: chub par bya'o // drug pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:9644: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:9645: lta ba'i nyams drod can du gyur kyang da dung
NK094(nge)001:9646: blo dkyil che bas ting nge 'dzin ma brtan te
NK094(nge)001:9647: rgod 'phyar dang bying ba'i dbang du 'gro ba rnams
NK094(nge)001:9648: la rnal 'byor gyi ting nge 'dzin la bying rgod
NK094(nge)001:9649: kyis mi gnod par lta ba sgom par na spar
NK094(nge)001:9650: te bsgom thabs gong mar skyed du 'gro bas man
NK094(nge)001:9651: ngag gi gasnga sgo mthar thug pa dbye la ma
NK094(nge)001:9657: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:9658: slob ma blo rtsing po rnam rtog dang spyod sgo'i
NK094(nge)001:9659: 'gros kyi rta dmu rgod dang 'dra ba rnams la
NK094(nge)001:9660: khe nyen dang bcas pa'i dam tshig gi gacana 'phrang
NK094(nge)001:9661: rnams dang bar du gcod pa'i rtog tshogs kyis 'khora
NK094(nge)001:9662: ba'i gayanga sa ltung ba'i sgo dgu'i nyes dmigs rnams
NK094(nge)001:9663: bstan te ngan spyod las ldog thabs bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:9668: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:9669: rdo rje theg pa'i lung gi don tshad du phyin pa dang ldan pa can la /
NK094(nge)001:9670: bdag gzhan gyi don nam phrin las rnam pa bzhi
NK094(nge)001:9671: la sogs pa ji ltar nus pa de ltar dbang
NK094(nge)001:9672: lnga po rim par bskur te sbyin par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:9677: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:9678: shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin gyi rtsal meda pas
NK094(nge)001:9679: bdag gzhan gyi don du bsgrub par mi nus pa
NK094(nge)001:9681: phana pa'i dbang bcu bskur ba 'ab'a zhig basngagasa pa
NK094(nge)001:9682: yina pas de tsam sbyin par bya ste bum pa
NK094(nge)001:9683: la sogs pa'o // de bas na theg pa mchog
NK094(nge)001:9684: gi dkyil 'khor gyi gnas 'dira shes rab dang ting
NK094(nge)001:9685: nge 'dzin gsal ba dang de gnyis mi gasla ba'i
NK094(nge)001:9687: snga ma 'oda mi bsub par dbang gi man ngag mi gab par sbyin zhing /
NK094(nge)001:9688: phyi ma la mi 'tshams pa'i dbang dang man ngag
NK094(nge)001:9689: gi ljid kyi don mi dbab cing bstan par mi
NK094(nge)001:9690: bya ste / bstan na sgyid ma brtas par khal bkal ba bzhin du chud 'dza' 'o //
NK094(nge)001:9695: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:9696: rnal 'byor pa rdo rje gsang ba'i blo yi shes
NK094(nge)001:9697: rab chen po'i spyod yul can dang ting nge 'dzin
NK094(nge)001:9699: bslab pa bcu'i yul la rtogs pa dang ting nge
NK094(nge)001:9700: 'dzin gyi rtsal chena po shin tu 'bod la sbyong
NK094(nge)001:9701: bar gyis shig ces pa'i gdamsa ngag bstan para bya'o
NK094(nge)001:9706: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:9711: mched lcam mang po 'dus pa'i dabnga gral du /
NK094(nge)001:9712: rdo rje theg pa'i dbang zab mo sngar thob ma thob dang /
NK094(nge)001:9713: snga phyi'i rim pa'am lta ba dang sgom pa'i dona gyi stang chen po'i mtho dman ltar bsher la /
NK094(nge)001:9714: blo shes rab kyi rtsal dang dbang gi rima para
NK094(nge)001:9715: bstun te gral gyi khyad para mtho dman du dbye
NK094(nge)001:9716: bar bya'o // bu rnams rang rang gi yi dam
NK094(nge)001:9717: gyi lha gang yin gyi so so rigsa kyi phyag
NK094(nge)001:9719: thabs kyi phyag rgya spyi ltar tshang bar bsgom pa'am /
NK094(nge)001:9720: yanga na so sor bstan te mi res lha re bsgom pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:9721: blo che bas spyi dang chung bas re re bsgom pa'i khyad par gyi dbang du'o //
NK094(nge)001:9722: mi res lha re bsgom na slob dpon gyis spyir bsgom par yang gsungs so //
NK094(nge)001:9723: gnyis pa shes rab kyi sbas tshogs la gnyis te /
NK094(nge)001:9724: yab sbas la yum bsgom pa /
NK094(nge)001:9730: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:9731: gazhana yanga shes raba kyi sbas tshogs thabs dang mi
NK094(nge)001:9732: mthun pa la yab sbas la yum sgom pa'i shes
NK094(nge)001:9733: rab gzungsa kyi tshogsa 'chad pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:9734: ji ltar thabsa rdo rje dbyings yab kyi dkyil 'khor
NK094(nge)001:9735: gyi lha tshogsa nyer lnga'i grangs su sbyor te gzhung
NK094(nge)001:9736: du bstan pa ci lta ba de ltar lha grangs
NK094(nge)001:9737: mnyam pa'i yum nyer lnga'i tshogs nyid bud med gang
NK094(nge)001:9738: dag rnal 'byor mar gyur ba'i yum chen lnga'i tshom
NK094(nge)001:9739: bu'i dkyil 'khor gsal brtan dang ldana par sgom pa
NK094(nge)001:9740: rnams kyis / rdo rje 'dzina ma la sogsa pa rigs kyi gtso mo yum chen lnga dang /
NK094(nge)001:9741: 'khor sems ma bcu drug sgo ma bzhi ste lha'i
NK094(nge)001:9742: grangs nyer lnga yum chen lnga'i tshom bu la so
NK094(nge)001:9743: so'i 'khor gyi lha mo'i rigs kyi tshogsa su so
NK094(nge)001:9744: sor bkod nas sgrub pa nyid kyang /
NK094(nge)001:9745: bde gshegs rigs la brtan ma rdo rje dang /
NK094(nge)001:9749: rdo rje'i rigs la rdo rje sgeg mo dang /
NK094(nge)001:9750: rdo rje bdug pa ma dang /
NK094(nge)001:9751: rdo rje lcags kyu ma dang /
NK094(nge)001:9753: rin chen rigs la rdo rje phreng ba ma dang /
NK094(nge)001:9754: rdo rje me tog ma dang /
NK094(nge)001:9755: rdo rje zhags pa ma dang /
NK094(nge)001:9758: rdo rje dbyangs len ma dang /
NK094(nge)001:9759: rdo rje mar me ma dang /
NK094(nge)001:9760: rdo rje lcags sgrog ma dang /
NK094(nge)001:9762: las kyi rigs la rdo rje gar bsgyur ma dang /
NK094(nge)001:9763: rdo rje dri chab ma dang /
NK094(nge)001:9764: rdo rje dril bu ma dang /
NK094(nge)001:9766: de'i phyi rol du khro mo bzhi rnams sgor 'god pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:9767: de lta bur gnas dben par 'khor khang phyi nang
NK094(nge)001:9768: bar ldan du byas pa'i shes rab dbyings kyi dkyil
NK094(nge)001:9769: 'khor 'dira 'jug par mos shing dag'a bas 'dud pa'i
NK094(nge)001:9770: rnal 'byor pa la sogsa pa kun gyi thabas yab
NK094(nge)001:9771: kyi sku phyag rgya ni thugs kar stong pa yum
NK094(nge)001:9772: gyi ngang du dbyings kyi matshana mara sbas te rab
NK094(nge)001:9773: tu gnas pa yin pas bshad pa ltar bri ba'am
NK094(nge)001:9774: / ting nge 'dzin gyis lhar bskyed pa yan lag dang ldan par byas nas bsgom pa nyid do //
NK094(nge)001:9779: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:9780: de ltar las gzhung bsrang ste rdo rje yab dang
NK094(nge)001:9781: grangs mnyam pa'i gzungsa chen yum gyi lha tshogs rnams
NK094(nge)001:9782: la / ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs la
NK094(nge)001:9783: bstims te brtan par byas pa'i yum gyi sku rnams
NK094(nge)001:9784: la bshad pa ltar mnyam pa'i mchod pa phyi nang
NK094(nge)001:9785: gsang ba'i tshul du phul bas mnyes par bya zhing
NK094(nge)001:9786: dgyes pa skyed pa sogs las gzhung rgyas pa thabs
NK094(nge)001:9788: de nas srog dang ldan pa'i bro stabs dang gar
NK094(nge)001:9789: rnams bya bzhin glu tshig brjod pa la sogas pasa
NK094(nge)001:9790: yo byad dang dga' bdes rig 'dzin mchog gi rnal
NK094(nge)001:9791: 'byor ma rnams kyis lha mor bsgrub par bya ba'o
NK094(nge)001:9792: // dbang bskur ba dang gdams ngag bya ba thabs dang mthun pa nyid do //
NK094(nge)001:9793: 'o na thabs shes bral ba la dgos pa ci yod snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:9794: 'di dag ni thabs kyi dkyil 'khor la mos pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:9795: shes rab kyi dkyil 'khor la mos pa'i dbang dang /
NK094(nge)001:9796: 'gro ba pho mo so sor bsgrub pa'i ched du gsungs te dgongs pa can yin no //
NK094(nge)001:9797: 'on kyang don gyis yab yum bral ba ni ma yin te /
NK094(nge)001:9798: skabs gnyis su gnyis sbas pa'i phyir ro //
NK094(nge)001:9799: 'di dag ni rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor pa'i spyod yul du'ang rigs so //
NK094(nge)001:9800: las dang po pa dag ni skal pa dang sbyar zhing gzud pa'o /
NK094(nge)001:9801: gsum pa dus bzhi mnyam pa'i tshogs la lnga ste /
NK094(nge)001:9802: dus bzhi mnyam par lta bas thag gcad pa /
NK094(nge)001:9803: dus bzhi lha mor bsgom lugs /
NK094(nge)001:9805: bsgom lugs kyi bye brag bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:9811: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:9812: gazhana yanga dus bzhi'i tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor 'chad pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:9813: 'chad pa'i dus bzhi gsang sngags ji bzhin pa la
NK094(nge)001:9814: dus bzhi ma 'gag bral ba'i ngo bor lta bas
NK094(nge)001:9815: thag bcad pa ltar mnyam pa nyid du riga cing
NK094(nge)001:9816: rtogs na / dus bzhi so sor tha snyad brtags
NK094(nge)001:9817: pa dang bral bas mtshan ma tha dad pa'i dus
NK094(nge)001:9818: zhes bya ba de ltar gzung bar ga la rigas
NK094(nge)001:9820: des na dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid du raba tu
NK094(nge)001:9821: shes nas bden pa dbyer med kyi de kho na
NK094(nge)001:9823: de nyid dus bzhi mnyam pa'i rang bzhina yin pas
NK094(nge)001:9824: de ltar thag chod pa kho na chos nyid dbyings
NK094(nge)001:9825: kyi mtshan nyid du nges pa yin no //
NK094(nge)001:9830: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:9831: dus bzhi dbyer med rdo rje lta bu'i ngo bor
NK094(nge)001:9832: lha mo bzhir gyur pa'i ye shes dus kyi tshogsa
NK094(nge)001:9833: ni / 'gro ba'i ngo la rgyu rkyen 'bras bu spyad zin pa'i bdag nyid 'das pa'i dus dang /
NK094(nge)001:9834: rgyu spyad la 'bras bu ma spyad pa da ltar byung ba yi dus dang /
NK094(nge)001:9835: rgya rkyen tshogs la ma spyad pa'am mi 'byung ba ni ma 'ongs pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:9836: rgyu rkyen yod kyang rkyen la rag las pas 'byung
NK094(nge)001:9837: bar ma ngesa pa'i dus kyi cha rnams su snang
NK094(nge)001:9838: ba la / de nyid rang rig pas dabnga bsgyur
NK094(nge)001:9839: nas mnyam pa chen po'i mtshan nyid du rang snang
NK094(nge)001:9840: ba'i dus bzhi'i rgyal mo rnams ni lha mo d+hup+pe
NK094(nge)001:9841: ba la / ma dang / push+pe ma dang /
NK094(nge)001:9848: dgun stongsa para gyur ba de daga tu snang ba'i
NK094(nge)001:9849: dus bzhi po nyidarima par lha mo bzhi por snang
NK094(nge)001:9850: ngo // rdo rje theg pa'i thun mong ma yin
NK094(nge)001:9851: pa'i stong pa nyid la sogs pa'i rnam par thar
NK094(nge)001:9852: pa bzhi'i sgo mo bzhi dang /
NK094(nge)001:9853: tshad med pa bzhi'i sgo mo bzhi bsrung ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:9854: phyi nang gi semsa dpa' dang yang de bzhina grangs
NK094(nge)001:9855: mnyam pa'i sems ma d+hup+pe la sogs pa bzhi dang
NK094(nge)001:9856: / mnyam pa'i dbyings brjod pa las 'das pa'i ngo
NK094(nge)001:9857: bor rang snang ba'i la s+ye ma la sogs pa
NK094(nge)001:9858: bzhi yi lha mo brgyad shes raba kyi 'khor dang
NK094(nge)001:9859: / / dam pa'i dkyil rigs kyi gtso bo rnam
NK094(nge)001:9860: snang la sogs pa rigs bzhi nyid de bcu gsum
NK094(nge)001:9861: / / mam / yang na phyi nang gi sems
NK094(nge)001:9862: ma dang sgo ma bzhi ste lha mo bcu gnyis
NK094(nge)001:9865: bde ba chen po yab yum ni dam pa'i dkyil te bcu gsum du bsgom par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:9870: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:9871: de lta bu'i dkyil 'khor gyi sgom lugs bstan pa
NK094(nge)001:9872: ji ltar du cho ga'i las gzhung rima para bsrang
NK094(nge)001:9873: la / rdo rje yi glu gara bya ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:9874: la sogsa pa zhes bsdu ba'i don gyis mchod rdzas
NK094(nge)001:9875: kyi yo byad dang longs spyod rnams kyis tshul bzhin
NK094(nge)001:9877: dkyil 'khor der 'juga pa'i tshul yang thabs kyi sbas
NK094(nge)001:9878: tshogs nas bshad pa ji lta bar sgrub pa'i phrin
NK094(nge)001:9879: las kyi cha shas bsnyen bsgrub tu 'jug pa dbang
NK094(nge)001:9880: dang dam tshig phog pa rnams rang rang gi skabs
NK094(nge)001:9881: su 'byung ba'i dus lasa gang 'og tu mi 'ad'a
NK094(nge)001:9883: dus tshigs bzang po gza' pa sangs sogs gza' skar
NK094(nge)001:9884: shis pa rnams ni shin tu bkra shis pas lha
NK094(nge)001:9887: bkra shis lha yi nyi ma dang //
NK094(nge)001:9888: 'byor dang dus tshigs bzang po rnams //
NK094(nge)001:9889: 'jig rten mtshan ma'i rtog pa ste //
NK094(nge)001:9890: brtags na bkra shis mtshan ma 'byung //
NK094(nge)001:9891: zhes pa de lta bu rnams la bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:9896: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:9897: dbus kyi bde ba chen po gtso bo nyid dang
NK094(nge)001:9898: la sogsa pa yis bsdu ba'i don gyis rigs bzhi
NK094(nge)001:9899: dang tshoma bu lngar bsgom pa'am yanga na rnal 'byor
NK094(nge)001:9900: pas phyag rgya rnams lha spyi bsgom pa'am rnal 'byor
NK094(nge)001:9901: pa re res sku phyag rgya re rera bsgom pa'o
NK094(nge)001:9902: // 'dir yang rnal 'byor pa du yod pas re
NK094(nge)001:9903: rer lha rer bskyed de lha grangs dang mnyam par
NK094(nge)001:9904: sbyar te sgom para bya ba'ang 'thad pa nyid de
NK094(nge)001:9905: don du blo rim ltar ro //
NK094(nge)001:9910: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:9911: 'adsa pa'i dus kyi ngo bo la rnam thar bzhi'i tshogsa bskrun pa dang sbyar te bstan pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:9912: da ltar byung ba dang mi 'abyung ba ma 'ongs
NK094(nge)001:9913: pa la rim pa bzhin tshad med pa bzhi dang
NK094(nge)001:9914: sems ma l+aa s+ye sogs bzhi dang mnyam para sbyar
NK094(nge)001:9915: te tshogs kyi 'bras bu baskrun par bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:9916: de'ang 'das pa dang rnam thar ngo bo nyid ma dmigs pa'i phyir dang /
NK094(nge)001:9917: da ltar dang tshad med don bya byed mngon sum du yod pa'i phyir dang /
NK094(nge)001:9918: ma 'ongs pa dang sems ma don shes rab snang
NK094(nge)001:9919: bas brtag tu med pa'i rang bzhin gyi phyir rim
NK094(nge)001:9921: de ltar sus rtogs pa de ni mnyam pa'i rgyal
NK094(nge)001:9922: por chos sku chen po nyid du 'grub par 'gyur
NK094(nge)001:9923: ro // bzhi pa nyi zla'i tshogs la lnga ste /
NK094(nge)001:9924: bsgrub pa yon tan dang bcas pa /
NK094(nge)001:9927: bar chad byung na skong thabs bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:9933: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:9934: thabs shes rab zung du 'brel ba la mos pa'i ched du /
NK094(nge)001:9935: thabs kyi lam bstan pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:9936: dus bzhi'i tshogs las gzhan yang mi mthun pa ni nyi zla'i tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor 'chad pa ste /
NK094(nge)001:9938: yang dag pa'i lam la gnas pa'i rnal 'byor pas
NK094(nge)001:9939: gsang ba byang chub semsa kyi thig le 'bras bu'i
NK094(nge)001:9940: sa mchog mthar phyin par rdzogsa pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:9941: dpe tshes bcu drug la zla ba'i 'phel cha rgyas pa'i tshul dang 'dra la /
NK094(nge)001:9942: de yang thabs shes rab kyi chas thabs kyi byang chub sems dpa' bcu drug la /
NK094(nge)001:9943: shes rab sems ma bcu drug rdzogs pa ni zla
NK094(nge)001:9944: ba rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor nya gang ba lta bu'o
NK094(nge)001:9945: // snying rje'am thugs rje'i ye shes kun tu gsal
NK094(nge)001:9946: ba bcu drug shar ba ni sems dpa' bcu drug
NK094(nge)001:9947: tu shar bas dpe nam mkha' la nyi ma shar
NK094(nge)001:9948: ba'i tshul ji lta ba bzhin du 'gro ba'i don
NK094(nge)001:9949: // mdzad do // yang na byang sems rdzogs pa
NK094(nge)001:9950: zla nyi'i dkyil 'khor rgyas pa'i thabs shes su byas
NK094(nge)001:9951: te nyi zla rang ngo la sbyar ba'ang snang ngo
NK094(nge)001:9952: // mdzad do // // de bas na byang chub
NK094(nge)001:9953: kyi sems rnam gnyis bde stong gi chos nyid dam
NK094(nge)001:9954: pa gnyis su med pa'i ngang du rdzogsa te mnyam
NK094(nge)001:9955: pa chen po mthar phyin pa'i rnal 'byor pa ni
NK094(nge)001:9956: gsang chen thabs kyi snying po yang dag par ngesa
NK094(nge)001:9957: pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sa mchog la gnas pa yina
NK094(nge)001:9958: // mdzad do // // no // de lta bu'i
NK094(nge)001:9959: 'bras bu bcu gsum yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen
NK094(nge)001:9960: gyi sa la bgrod cing phyin par bya ba'i thabs
NK094(nge)001:9961: // mdzad do // // no // dam pa ni
NK094(nge)001:9962: / rdo rje lta bu'i dus bzhir bar gyi rgyun
NK094(nge)001:9963: ma chad par tshogsa kyi dkyil 'khor la gnas te
NK094(nge)001:9964: sems nyid dang ma bral bar lta bas mnyam par
NK094(nge)001:9965: // mdzad do // // no // dam pa ni
NK094(nge)001:9966: / rtogs pa dang / spyod pas dus bzhi'i tshogs
NK094(nge)001:9967: la ma 'gag par spyod de lhun rdzogs su sbyar
NK094(nge)001:9973: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:9974: de'i dpe yang skar ma'i tshogsa mang po'i dbus kyi
NK094(nge)001:9975: dkyil na zla ba'i thig le nya gang bar snang
NK094(nge)001:9976: ba'ang / bcu drug gi zhag gi zla ba tshad du phyin te cha shas rdzogsa pa bzhin du /
NK094(nge)001:9977: sa mchog bcu gsum pa yi ge 'khor lo tshogs
NK094(nge)001:9978: chen nyid sa lam gyi thabs dang brtson 'grus kyi
NK094(nge)001:9979: rtsal chen po rdzogsa pa'i mthus 'bras bu'i sa ru
NK094(nge)001:9980: lhun gyis grub cing thob par gyur pa'ang /
NK094(nge)001:9981: sems dpa' yab yum bcu drug zung gi dkyil 'khor
NK094(nge)001:9982: bsgom pa'i tshogsa kyis dga' ba bcu drug gi ngo
NK094(nge)001:9983: bor rdzogsa pasa snying po byang chub tu bsgrub pa'i
NK094(nge)001:9984: phyir na / mdzesa pa'i zla ba shes rab dbyings
NK094(nge)001:9985: kyi rang bzhin yum mchog sems ma bcu drug gis
NK094(nge)001:9986: phyir na / / ye shes nyi ma gsal ba'i
NK094(nge)001:9987: 'od kyi ngo bo sems dpa' bcu drug gi sku'i
NK094(nge)001:9988: phyag rgya so sor gsal ba la /
NK094(nge)001:9989: thabs dang shes rab zung 'jug gnyis su med par
NK094(nge)001:9990: gcig la gcig mdzesa para spras te legs par spel
NK094(nge)001:9991: mar bzhugs pa'i rol pa'i longs spyod chen po'i dgyes
NK094(nge)001:9992: pas bde ba dam pa de nyid kyang /
NK094(nge)001:9993: lha yab yum bcu drug gi tshogsa kyi mthar phyin
NK094(nge)001:9994: par rdzogsa para bskrun te 'bras bu sangs rgyas su
NK094(nge)001:9999: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10000: de ltar tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi 'bras bu mthar phyin par rdzogsa pa nyid na yang /
NK094(nge)001:10001: de la ngo bo 'di 'drar mi dmigsa pas bstan
NK094(nge)001:10002: cing bsam du med pa gnyis pa'i tha snyad bra
NK094(nge)001:10003: la ba'i byang chub kyi sems de bzhina nyid ma
NK094(nge)001:10004: bcos pa'i ngang du dag par sbyangsa pasa na /
NK094(nge)001:10005: dus bzhi'am chos thams ca da mnyam par shar bas
NK094(nge)001:10006: mtha' ril stong pa chen por gsal bar gyur ba
NK094(nge)001:10007: la dngos po thamsa cad dbyings spros bral gyi don
NK094(nge)001:10008: rigs pas mngon du byas pas chos skur rdzogsa te
NK094(nge)001:10009: byang chub chen po'i ngo bor byung thebs pas /
NK094(nge)001:10010: de lta bu'i gzhi'i ngang la 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal
NK094(nge)001:10011: dang byang chub chen po'i bde ba yang ris su
NK094(nge)001:10012: btsal gyis mi rnyed par gnyis su med pa nyid
NK094(nge)001:10013: de / don de rtogs shing grub par bya na /
NK094(nge)001:10014: theg pa chen po rmad byung gsang ba'i don la
NK094(nge)001:10015: sems bskyed de gnyis su med par blo la gsal
NK094(nge)001:10016: bar bya zhing / thabs dang shes rab kyi spyod
NK094(nge)001:10017: pa'i las lam chen po tshul bzhin du spyad par
NK094(nge)001:10018: bar bya zhing / bya ba dang / de las
NK094(nge)001:10019: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes kyi cha shas phra
NK094(nge)001:10020: mo tsam du shar ba'i nyams drod zin nas skyed
NK094(nge)001:10022: nang byang chub sems kyi rtogs pa dama pa dang
NK094(nge)001:10023: gnyis su med para spyad na mjug rang byung gi
NK094(nge)001:10024: ye shes chen po'i nyi ma rang las 'char bar
NK094(nge)001:10029: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10030: dang du ma blangs pa'i skyon bstan pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:10031: dus kyi rgyun du tshogs kyi dkyil 'a khor 'di
NK094(nge)001:10032: nyid bar mi gcad par bya rgyu yin pa las
NK094(nge)001:10033: gal te rgyun gyi dus su bar chad kyi dbang
NK094(nge)001:10034: du gyur na / 'di la bsnyen pa dang nye
NK094(nge)001:10035: bsnyen tsam byas pa daga gisa bzlog par dka' bas
NK094(nge)001:10036: du gyur na / mi skongs so // de bas na bsgrub pa nyid la bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:10037: de'ang le lo dang rkyen dbang gi bar chad byung na /
NK094(nge)001:10038: slar bskang ba dang gso ru gzhug pa'i las chen
NK094(nge)001:10039: po'i sbyor ba brtsam par bya ba ni bskang ba'i
NK094(nge)001:10040: mchog go // dper na nam mkha'a la zla ba
NK094(nge)001:10041: nya ba 'od gsal zhing gra zur rgyas pa bzhina
NK094(nge)001:10042: mchog go // du / sa la thabs shes dang
NK094(nge)001:10043: tshogs gnyis dang phyag rgya mang pos dngos grub sgrub
NK094(nge)001:10044: pa'i rnal 'byor pa yab yum gra rgyas par spyad
NK094(nge)001:10045: mchog go // du / pa'o // gang 'dira rnal 'byor pa gra rgyas par 'dod na /
NK094(nge)001:10046: bsoda namsa kyi dpung chen po bskyed pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:10047: dge ba rgya chen po 'gro ba dang thun mong
NK094(nge)001:10048: du byas te bsngo ba chen po'i thabs kyis bla
NK094(nge)001:10049: med byang chub tu 'gyur ba'i las rnams bsgrub ste
NK094(nge)001:10050: mi dmigs pa dang ldan par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:10055: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10056: de ltar sgrub pa desa ni 'bras bu ji ltar thob nas /
NK094(nge)001:10057: thog mar nyi zla zhon te 'gro ba'i rigsa 'dzina te /
NK094(nge)001:10058: thabs shes la dbang thob nas phyag rgya chen po'i sa thob pa la gnas par 'gyur ro //
NK094(nge)001:10059: de phan chad nas mthar thug bde ba chen po
NK094(nge)001:10060: bcu gsum pa yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi
NK094(nge)001:10061: sa mchog nyid la lhun gyis grub ste sangs rgyas
NK094(nge)001:10063: lnga pa yi ge'i tshogs la gsum ste /
NK094(nge)001:10071: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10072: nyi zla'i tshogs las mi mthun pa gazhana yanga yi ge'i tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor 'chad pa ste /
NK094(nge)001:10073: de yang dus bzhir bar mi gcad par rgyun du bya ba'i thabs dam pa ni gang zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:10074: phung khams skye mched sogs dngos po gnyis pa'i chos
NK094(nge)001:10075: rnams kun gyi ngo bo ye nas rgyal ba'i sku
NK094(nge)001:10076: gsung thugs kyi rang bzhin du sangs rgyas pa nyid
NK094(nge)001:10077: yin te / sangs rgyas kyi ngo bo sems dpa' yab yum sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK094(nge)001:10079: gtso bo yab yum bcu ste lha lnga bcu'i rgyal
NK094(nge)001:10080: ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi sku gsunga thugsa su snang ba
NK094(nge)001:10081: nyid do // de'i sku dang gsung thugsa su btags pa'i phyag rgya dag gi yon tan /
NK094(nge)001:10082: yi ge'i phreng ba nyid kyi rang bzhin la rdzogsa pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:10083: de ltar thag chod nas +aa li k+aa li'i yi ge gsung phyag rgya'i ye shesa rnams ni /
NK094(nge)001:10084: rnal 'byor pa lam pas dus bzhi'i rgyun gyi rgyun
NK094(nge)001:10085: ma chad pa nyid du sgom par bya ba yina
NK094(nge)001:10086: no // de ltar 'bad pa des ni rgyun gyi
NK094(nge)001:10087: ting nge 'dzina 'thoba par 'gyur ba nyid de bsgom
NK094(nge)001:10093: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10094: 'di nyid rgyun gyi rgyun du bar mi gcad para nyams su blang ba'i thabs ni /
NK094(nge)001:10095: rdo rje theg pa'i yang gsang snying po'i lugs kyi
NK094(nge)001:10096: dngos po thams cad rang rig pa'i ye shes yin
NK094(nge)001:10097: pas / nam dang nyi ma'am nyin mtshan du snang ba'i dus kyang rdo rje ste /
NK094(nge)001:10098: de dag gi dus tshod la bsam pas yi ge'i
NK094(nge)001:10099: tshogsa bsgom pa las lhar bskyed cing yi ge'i 'phro
NK094(nge)001:10100: 'du la brten nas don du rdzogsa pa'ang de ltar
NK094(nge)001:10101: bsam pas ngang las mi 'da' bar sbyar bar bya'o
NK094(nge)001:10102: // de lta bu'i dkyil 'khor bsam pa la drangs
NK094(nge)001:10103: shing bstim ste brtan pa la mchod pa dang bzlas
NK094(nge)001:10104: brjod bsnyen pa dang bcas pa sbyar te las la
NK094(nge)001:10105: 'bad pa'ang bshad pa'i thabs tshogs kyi las gzhung bsrang
NK094(nge)001:10106: ba ji lta ba de bzhina du bya ba yin
NK094(nge)001:10107: // no // 'o na yi ge las lhar bskyed pa'i 'phro 'du bshad pa la'ang yod na /
NK094(nge)001:10108: 'di kho na la khyad par du gdags pa ci zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:10109: 'dir yi ge gtsor byed pa'i sgo nas mi 'gal te /
NK094(nge)001:10110: gzhan dag ni lha gtsor byed cing yi ge yan lag tu byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK094(nge)001:10115: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10116: yi ge tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor 'di ni dona dam
NK094(nge)001:10117: pa'i 'bras bu dang khyad par du nye ba'i lam
NK094(nge)001:10118: dam pa gyur pas 'di la 'bad na 'bras bu
NK094(nge)001:10119: bskrun pa myur bar 'grub pa'i don te /
NK094(nge)001:10120: lam kun la'ang 'bras bu la 'di nyid nye bas
NK094(nge)001:10121: de nyid myur du 'grub par 'gyur ba'i phyir ro
NK094(nge)001:10122: // de bas na 'dir ni yi ge rgyun gyi
NK094(nge)001:10123: ting nge 'dzin gyis rgyun du tshogsa kyi dkyil 'khor
NK094(nge)001:10124: bar ma gcad pa 'bad pa desa /
NK094(nge)001:10125: 'bras bu'i rig 'dzin las kyang khyad par du gyur
NK094(nge)001:10126: pas dama pa'i dama pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i
NK094(nge)001:10127: sangs rgyas kyi sa mchog mthar thug pa de nyid
NK094(nge)001:10128: du 'gyur pa la the tshom med pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:10129: 'di la yi ge'i phreng bas tshe sgrub pa zhes kyang gsungs so //
NK094(nge)001:10130: drug po rdo rje d+r+wa ba 'brel ba'i tshogs la gsum ste /
NK094(nge)001:10138: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10139: gzhan yang snga ma las mi mthun pa thabs dang
NK094(nge)001:10140: shes rab rdo rje d+r+wa ba'i dbyingsa su 'brel ba'i
NK094(nge)001:10141: tshogs yon tan dang dngos grub kyi 'byung gnas thugsa
NK094(nge)001:10142: kyi dgongs pas brnag pa'i gasnga chena gsang ba'i don
NK094(nge)001:10143: 'chad pa 'di ni bshad pa'i don nyid las 'grel
NK094(nge)001:10144: te / rdo rje brjod pa ni 'dir gsang ba'i rdo rje yina pasa na /
NK094(nge)001:10145: thabs kyi rdo rje gsang ba'i dbang po dang /
NK094(nge)001:10146: shes rab kyi pad+ma gsang ba'i yul gnyis dbyer med
NK094(nge)001:10147: par gyur te bde chen gyi ngang dang 'brel basa
NK094(nge)001:10149: de nyid las thun mong dang mchog gi dngos grub
NK094(nge)001:10150: thams cad 'byung zhing 'char bas dbyingsa zhes bya ba'i
NK094(nge)001:10151: ming gi nges tshig kyang 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK094(nge)001:10156: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10157: de dag kyang thabs shes kyi lha dngos gang zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:10158: yum rdo rje 'dzina ma dbyings phyug ma la sogs pa'i yum nyi shu rtsa lnga dang /
NK094(nge)001:10159: yab rdo rje 'dzina pa'i sems dpa' la sogsa pa
NK094(nge)001:10160: yab nyi shu rtsa lnga dang bcas te yi ge'i
NK094(nge)001:10161: tshogs kyi lha grangs ltar yab yum thabs dang shes
NK094(nge)001:10162: rab zung du 'khril nas don mnyam pa'i ngang du
NK094(nge)001:10163: bzhugs pa yang bshad pa de bzhin te /
NK094(nge)001:10164: de lta bu rnams kyi tshogs kyi dus su gzugsa
NK094(nge)001:10165: brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor dngos su bris pas bzhengs su
NK094(nge)001:10166: gsol / ting nge 'dzina gyi dkyil 'khor gsal bar bsgom /
NK094(nge)001:10167: rang bzhina gyi dkyil 'khor dbyings kyi gnas nas spyan
NK094(nge)001:10168: drangs te bstim pa sogs tshogs kun mthong ba'i gzhung
NK094(nge)001:10169: don ji ltar du las kyi rim pa bzhin sbyar
NK094(nge)001:10170: te sgrub par byas na 'bras bu nges par thob
NK094(nge)001:10175: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10176: de ltar sgrub pas rang gi las dang dngos grub
NK094(nge)001:10177: ji ltar 'dod cing bsam pa gang ltar mos pa
NK094(nge)001:10179: dper na nor bu rin po che'am /
NK094(nge)001:10180: 'doda pa'i khamsa kyi lha 'phrul dga' ltar du bdag
NK094(nge)001:10181: gi re ba ji snyed pa'ang 'byung bas lha dang
NK094(nge)001:10182: mnyam zhing sangs rgyas kyi yon tan ji lta bar
NK094(nge)001:10183: bdag gis kyang thob par 'gyur te gong 'phang mchog
NK094(nge)001:10184: nyid 'grub para bka' las gsungsa pa gang nyid 'khrul
NK094(nge)001:10186: bdun pa thabs shes rab 'brel ba'i tshogs la lnga ste /
NK094(nge)001:10187: skal ldan spro ba skyed pa /
NK094(nge)001:10189: gdul bya gang gi don du byung ba /
NK094(nge)001:10190: dkyil 'khor gyi ngo bo las rim dang bcas pa /
NK094(nge)001:10191: dbang dang dngos grub bsgrub pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:10196: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10197: gzhan yang bshad pa'i don nyid mi mthun pa'i bye brag ston pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:10198: gnas gang du thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med
NK094(nge)001:10199: par gang 'brel ba'i tshogs kyi don lta bas thag
NK094(nge)001:10200: bcad pa ltar gasnga chen gsang mchog dama pa'i dkyil
NK094(nge)001:10202: bsam gyis mi khyab cing tha dad du snang ba'i
NK094(nge)001:10203: chos rnams kun gyi ngo bo nyid sems nyid ji
NK094(nge)001:10204: bzhin pa'i rang bzhina gyi ngang 'di nyid du gcig
NK094(nge)001:10205: pas / lha yab yum du rol ba rtags su
NK094(nge)001:10206: bkod pa ltar don gyi ngo bor phana tshun d+r+wa
NK094(nge)001:10207: basa 'brel ba'i dbyer med mnyam pa nyid kyi ngo
NK094(nge)001:10208: bo la mtha' gnyis med pas stong nyid nam mkha'i
NK094(nge)001:10209: dbyings kyi rang bzhina nyid thams cad kyi gzhir gyur
NK094(nge)001:10210: pa'i ngang lasa sprul pa sna tshogs pa'i bkod pa
NK094(nge)001:10211: bye ba phrag mang ji snyed pa'i tshul du rig
NK094(nge)001:10213: ngo bo tha dad med par chos sku chen por
NK094(nge)001:10214: gcig pa ni thabs dang shes rab gnyis med chen
NK094(nge)001:10215: por mnyam pa'i tshul du 'brel ba'i rnam dbyer med
NK094(nge)001:10216: pa'i don te / dpe d+r+wa ba dang 'dra ba'i tshul du 'brel bar thag chod do //
NK094(nge)001:10217: de lta bu'i don ni rnal 'byor pa shes rab
NK094(nge)001:10218: chen po'i blo gros mchog dang ldan pa'i spyod yul
NK094(nge)001:10219: yin pas de nyid ji bzhin du rtogs par nus
NK094(nge)001:10220: pa'i shes rab kyi rtsal dang ldan pa'i slob ma
NK094(nge)001:10221: gsang sgo 'dir zhugs pa'i snod dang ldan pa 'di
NK094(nge)001:10222: la bla mas man ngag gsang ba'i sgo dbye ste
NK094(nge)001:10223: zab mo'i don rnams sbyin para bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:10224: skal pa can la byin na rtags ni gsang ba'i
NK094(nge)001:10225: sgo 'dira rigs nges par chud de mi ldog pa'i
NK094(nge)001:10226: bu rnams ni / shes rab kyi blo grosa chen
NK094(nge)001:10227: po dang man ngag gi thabsa dang ldan pasa na
NK094(nge)001:10228: rgyu de las theg pa mchog gi dgongs spyod zab
NK094(nge)001:10229: mo len par chas pa la mi skrag cing sngangs
NK094(nge)001:10230: pa med par slar dad cing mos pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:10231: dga' ba'i 'dun pa skyes te chos la bzod pa
NK094(nge)001:10232: thob nas ngo mtshar skye bar 'gyur ba ni dngos
NK094(nge)001:10233: su na sa bzhi pa lta bu'o //
NK094(nge)001:10238: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10239: gsang chen snying po'i lung dang 'bral ba'i lha grangs
NK094(nge)001:10240: sum cu rtsa bzhi'i dkyil 'khor gyi ngo bo gasnga
NK094(nge)001:10241: ba mchog tu gyur pa'i dkyil 'khora gyi don 'di
NK094(nge)001:10242: nyid nye bar gzung ba ni /
NK094(nge)001:10243: gtso bo rdo rje rgyal po rigs lnga dang rdo
NK094(nge)001:10244: rje rgyal mo yum lngar bcas pa'i thabs dang shes
NK094(nge)001:10245: rab lnga gnyis te bcu nyid zung du 'khril te
NK094(nge)001:10246: bzhugs pa ni // gtso bo g.yas nas yum g.yona
NK094(nge)001:10247: du bzhugs pas yab kyis 'khril zhing yum gyis 'khyud
NK094(nge)001:10248: de sbyor ba'i skyil krung du bzhugs pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:10249: yab rnams kyi gayasa nyid na thugs kyi byang chub mtshon pas mi bskyod pa'i rdo rje dang /
NK094(nge)001:10250: ranga ranga gi mtshan ma snang mdzad kyi 'khor lo dang /
NK094(nge)001:10251: rin chen 'byung ldan rin po che 'bar ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:10252: snang ba mtha' yas kyi pad+ma dang /
NK094(nge)001:10253: don yod grub pa ral gri rnams 'od 'bar ba bsnams pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:10254: kun kyang g.yona nyid na sgra brnyan gyi dril bu bsnams pa nyid dang /
NK094(nge)001:10255: yum rnams kyang chos kyi dbyings kyi rang rtagsa dril bu bsnams te /
NK094(nge)001:10256: de ltar thugs kyi rang rtags kyis phyag rgyas mdzesa
NK094(nge)001:10257: par brgyan te 'od du gasla ba yi sku de
NK094(nge)001:10258: dag gi tshul la yab rnams dbu g.yon du 'aphyo
NK094(nge)001:10259: zhing yum rnams g.yas su 'dud pa'i gzi madngas dang
NK094(nge)001:10260: ldana pasa / yab yum gcig la gcig chags pa
NK094(nge)001:10261: chen po'i rjes su chags shinga dgongs pa g.yo zhing
NK094(nge)001:10262: ldang ba'i tshul nyid kyis ni /
NK094(nge)001:10263: rdo rje'i rigs seng chen gyi gdan dang /
NK094(nge)001:10264: bde gshegs rigs khyu mchoga gi gdan /
NK094(nge)001:10265: la sogs pa zhes pas rin chen rigs rta'i gdan dang /
NK094(nge)001:10266: pad+ma'i rigs rma bya'am khyung gi gdan dang /
NK094(nge)001:10267: las kyi rigs shang shang te'u'i gdan la bzhugs te gdan re re'ang lnga brtseg go //
NK094(nge)001:10268: sems can gyi gdan rnams kyang byang chub semsa dapa'a
NK094(nge)001:10269: rnams damna pa'i lus su byung ste gus pas lus
NK094(nge)001:10270: khri la phul nas rna bas chos nyan par bshad
NK094(nge)001:10271: pa nyid do // de ltar gtso bo rnams kyi
NK094(nge)001:10272: bzhugs tshul rdzogsa pa'i skyil mo krung gi tshul gyis
NK094(nge)001:10273: 'gying bag dang bcas te bzhugs so //
NK094(nge)001:10274: 'od zer ni sku re re la'ang kha dog lnga
NK094(nge)001:10275: lnga yi 'oda 'abra ba nyid de ye shes rgya
NK094(nge)001:10276: ma chad par rdzogs pa'i don to //
NK094(nge)001:10277: de ltar dbu rgyan la sogs pa rgyan chas bcu gsum gyi cha lugsa kyis sgeg pa'i tshul /
NK094(nge)001:10278: sngar bshad pa bzhin te rnams zhes mang po'i sgras
NK094(nge)001:10279: sems dpa' dang sems ma sgo ba yab yum kyang
NK094(nge)001:10280: rgyun dang 'khril lugs dang 'dud 'byor rnams rjes su
NK094(nge)001:10281: mthun pa'o // bskyod pa'i tshul ni /
NK094(nge)001:10282: bdag nyid sa mtho dman dang /
NK094(nge)001:10283: sngar goms ma goms kyis rim gyis sam ni skad
NK094(nge)001:10284: cig gis cig char du bskyed de gang 'tshams pa
NK094(nge)001:10289: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10291: gang 'dira 'doda pa'i khamsa pa dag 'khrig pa la chagsa pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:10292: 'dod yon spyi la zhena cing gtong mi phod pa'i
NK094(nge)001:10293: 'gro ba rnams kyi shes rab kyi dabnga po'i rima
NK094(nge)001:10294: pa dang sbyar nas longs spyod lnga'i tshogs nyid rim
NK094(nge)001:10295: pa dang cig char du brtsam par bya ba yin
NK094(nge)001:10296: te / 'dod khams de mina par gzugs dang gzugs
NK094(nge)001:10297: med kyi khams pa'i ched du ni yab yum 'brel
NK094(nge)001:10298: ba'i dkyil 'khor yong ye mi dmigsa pas de ltar
NK094(nge)001:10304: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10305: de ltar yo ga phyi pa'i yul ma yin pas
NK094(nge)001:10306: shin tu gsang ba nyid kyi tshogsa kyi dkyil 'khora
NK094(nge)001:10307: gyi lha de dag rnams kyang /
NK094(nge)001:10308: gzhan zhig nas rang rgyud pa ma yin te /
NK094(nge)001:10309: bdag cag gi phung po lnga dang /
NK094(nge)001:10311: skye mched bcu gnyis kyi rtog pa'i tshogs kyi ngo
NK094(nge)001:10312: bo nyid ma bslad par bshad pa'i lha rnams kyi
NK094(nge)001:10313: rang bzhin du ye nas gnas pa nyid mngon du
NK094(nge)001:10314: 'gyur bar byas pa'i mtshan nyid gnyis su med pa
NK094(nge)001:10315: yi lhar gsal ba'i ye shes kyi rang bzhina gyis
NK094(nge)001:10316: sku phyag rgya nyid du bskyed pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:10317: dngos gtso bo rigs lnga rgyal po rgyal mo yab
NK094(nge)001:10318: yum dang bcas pa'i 'khor sems dpa' sems ma brgyad
NK094(nge)001:10319: phrag gnyis zung du bsgril te yab yum 'khri 'khyud
NK094(nge)001:10320: du sbyor ba gang zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:10322: nam mkha' yi snying po dang /
NK094(nge)001:10326: sgrib pa sel ba'i rdo rje dang /
NK094(nge)001:10329: nang dang phyi yi yo byad kyis mnyes par byed pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:10330: nang gi sems ma l+aa s+ye dang /
NK094(nge)001:10334: phyi'i sems ma d+hup+pe la sogs pa bzhi ste sems
NK094(nge)001:10335: ma bzhi phrag gnyis te brgyad po dag gisa mnyes
NK094(nge)001:10336: par sbyor te dgyes par 'khril bar bsgom pa'ang ji
NK094(nge)001:10337: ltar bsam bar bya ba la sogsa pa gtso bo
NK094(nge)001:10338: de bzhina du sgom pa bya ba yin no //
NK094(nge)001:10339: bdud dpung 'dul ba'i rdo rje sgo ba stobs chen dang /
NK094(nge)001:10342: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba bzhi dang bcas par ni /
NK094(nge)001:10343: rdo rje sgo ma bzhi dang dgyes par 'khril 'khyud
NK094(nge)001:10344: dang sbyor bar bsgom pa ni gasnga ba'i longs spyod
NK094(nge)001:10345: rdzogs pa'i lha'i tshogsa te de dag rnal 'byor skal
NK094(nge)001:10346: ldan mi'i tshogs nyid longsa spyod 'byor ba'i yo byad
NK094(nge)001:10347: kyi tshogs chen po dang ldan par byas te mchod
NK094(nge)001:10348: pa rgya cher sbyar basa sku gsung thugs dgyes pa
NK094(nge)001:10349: bskyed de mnyes par byas nas sgo gsum gyi sgrib
NK094(nge)001:10350: pa sbyangsa pa'i phyir mchod pa gsum go rim bzhina
NK094(nge)001:10356: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10357: gsang ba'i tshogs 'di dag gi dus su dbang la 'jug pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:10358: thabs shes rab kyis rol pa'i tshul dang la sogas
NK094(nge)001:10359: pa zhes bsdu ba'i don gyis bro brdungs pa dang
NK094(nge)001:10361: bza' btung gi tshogs la longs spyod pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:10362: rgyan dang byug pa bya ba dag dang /
NK094(nge)001:10363: sgrol ba bya ba dag dang /
NK094(nge)001:10364: de ltar bu yon tan gyi longs spyod par bya ba ril thams cad de /
NK094(nge)001:10365: de dag gi sgo nas gsang ba'i go 'phang mchog
NK094(nge)001:10366: dang thun mong dang bcas pa'i yon tan gyi dona
NK094(nge)001:10367: rnams mtha' dag bsgrub par bya ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:10368: gsum pa dkyil 'khor gyi don bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK094(nge)001:10369: 'khor gyis dkyil 'khor gyi don mthong ba gsol ba /
NK094(nge)001:10370: ston pas dkyil 'khor gyi don gsungs pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:10373: 'dus pa kun gyi zhes pa nas /
NK094(nge)001:10375: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10376: skyes bus sngar thos pa brjod de tshogs kyi rnam grangs bstan pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:10377: de'i tshe 'khor gyi 'dus pa kun gyis dkyil 'khor gyi dona mthonga ba nyid /
NK094(nge)001:10378: ston pa rdo rje 'dzina pa de la gsol pa /
NK094(nge)001:10379: semsa dapa'a chen po badga caga gisa 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams kun gyi ranga bzhina ni /
NK094(nge)001:10380: thabs shes rab re re'i sgo nas grub pa'am dbyer med pa sbyor ba'i tshul gyis 'grub pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:10381: thabsa kyi sbas tshogs nyid dang /
NK094(nge)001:10382: shes raba kyi sbas tshogs nyid du bkod pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:10383: dus bzhi kun nas mnyam pa'i tshogs dang /
NK094(nge)001:10384: thabs dang shes rab bcu drug cha yi nyi zla rgyas pa'i tshogs dang /
NK094(nge)001:10385: yi ge'i rgyun gyi tshogsa dang /
NK094(nge)001:10386: rdo rje d+r+wa ba 'byung ba'i dbyingsa su gcig pa'i tshogs dang /
NK094(nge)001:10387: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med par d+r+wa basa
NK094(nge)001:10388: 'brel ba'i tshogs la sogsa pas bsdu ba ni 'das
NK094(nge)001:10390: de'i skabs su rang bzhina gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK094(nge)001:10392: gzugsa brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor rnam pa gsum du snang ba bdag cag gis ngesa par mthonga lagas so //
NK094(nge)001:10393: zhes 'khor gyis rtogs pa phul ba de skad du gsol bas /
NK094(nge)001:10395: dkyil 'khor gsum gyi don gsungs tshul /
NK094(nge)001:10396: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi don gsungs tshul lo //
NK094(nge)001:10409: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10410: de nas ston pas lan gsungsa pa nyid don ma nor bar bstan pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:10411: 'chad pa'i skyes bu sems dpa' rdo rjes /
NK094(nge)001:10414: de ltar tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mang po de dag kun kyang /
NK094(nge)001:10415: khyed rnams kyis ji ltar mthong ba de nyid ltar du ma nor ba yina no //
NK094(nge)001:10417: de bas dkyil 'khor rnam pa gsum gyi ngo bo
NK094(nge)001:10418: yang ya gdod nas ma bcos ma bslad pa'i chos
NK094(nge)001:10419: nyid ji bzhina pa nyid du lhun gyis grub pa
NK094(nge)001:10420: ni rang bzhina gyi dkyil 'khora de kho na nyid
NK094(nge)001:10425: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10426: de'i don la mi dmigs pa nyid ltar dgongsa pa
NK094(nge)001:10427: dam para lhun gyis grub pa nyid du rang shar
NK094(nge)001:10428: la mi g.yo bar brtan pa ni ting nge 'dzina
NK094(nge)001:10429: gyi dkyil 'khora dam pa nyid yin no //
NK094(nge)001:10434: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10435: dkyil 'khor gnyis po de daga gi gazhi'am rtsa ba
NK094(nge)001:10436: yang sems nyid rang rig pa'i de kho na nyid
NK094(nge)001:10437: yin pasa 'gro ba rigs drug gi semsa can nyid
NK094(nge)001:10438: rten gzhi yin pa'i sgo nas gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil
NK094(nge)001:10440: lam pa'i ngor 'gro ba la dngos su gzugs brnyan mtshon par 'byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK094(nge)001:10445: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10446: de lta bas na rang bzhina dang ting nge 'dzina
NK094(nge)001:10447: dang gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gsum du thams cad
NK094(nge)001:10448: ril ye gdod ma nas rang bzhin du zhugsa zin
NK094(nge)001:10450: gzugs brnyan du rdzogsa zin pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:10453: dbang du bsgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK094(nge)001:10455: ras la ri mor bya ba /
NK094(nge)001:10456: khang bu la ri mor bya ba /
NK094(nge)001:10457: gser dngul lugs su bya ba /
NK094(nge)001:10458: shel rdo la 'bur du bya ba /
NK094(nge)001:10461: sa la rdul chon gyi dkyil 'khor bya ba /
NK094(nge)001:10462: gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor byas pa'i yon tan no //
NK094(nge)001:10467: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10468: gzhi de lta bu'i rang bzhin lasa skabs 'dir khyad
NK094(nge)001:10469: para du skal ldan mi yi tshogs rnams kyi dbang
NK094(nge)001:10470: po'i spyod yul du gyur pa nyid kyis gzugs brnyan
NK094(nge)001:10471: gyi dkyil 'khor gyi ming yang grub pa yin te
NK094(nge)001:10472: / de yang bri ba'i thabs kyi rnam grangs ni /
NK094(nge)001:10473: rasa dang dar 'ajama po khod snyomsa la rgyu gzhi
NK094(nge)001:10474: bzang ba la sogas pa la ri mor bris te
NK094(nge)001:10475: / kha doga lnga pa'am bye brag tu phye bas
NK094(nge)001:10476: nyi shu rtsa lngas ye shes lnga'am bye brag gis
NK094(nge)001:10477: lhag pa'i ye shes nyer lnga'i don ma mthong ba'i
NK094(nge)001:10478: rmongsa pa rnams la gzugs brnyan du bstan pa'i phyir
NK094(nge)001:10479: mtshon par byed pa'i rtags kyi dkyil 'khor te /
NK094(nge)001:10480: de dag kyang sku la sogs pa rnam par bkod
NK094(nge)001:10481: pa'i yan lag dang rgyan rnams ma nyamsa par rdzogs
NK094(nge)001:10482: par bris pa'i mtshan mas gdul bya slob bu de
NK094(nge)001:10483: sems rangsa shing tshim par 'gyur bas don 'grub par
NK094(nge)001:10484: yin te 'a di dag zag bcas kyi las so
NK094(nge)001:10489: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10490: gzhi brtan zhing ngos 'ajama pa'i khang bu bzang po'i logs la /
NK094(nge)001:10491: gong ltar kha doga 'abra basa gzugsa bris nas legs
NK094(nge)001:10492: par mtshon te sku phyag rgya rgyan dang bcas te
NK094(nge)001:10493: ma nyamsa shing mdzesa pa dang ldan pa'i gzugs brnyan
NK094(nge)001:10494: gyi grangs rdzogs par byas na des kyang mtshan ma'i
NK094(nge)001:10495: cho 'phrul ston para nus pas don grub bo //
NK094(nge)001:10500: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10501: gser dngul dang zangas lcagsa la sogsa pa rnams la
NK094(nge)001:10502: ganga lugs su blugsa pa'i rgyal ba'i sku gzugs byas
NK094(nge)001:10503: te phyag rgya ma nyamsa pa dang rab tu ldana
NK094(nge)001:10504: na / de yang gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi
NK094(nge)001:10505: matshana ma'i rten du nges par 'gyur bas don 'byung
NK094(nge)001:10510: zhes ba'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10511: rin po che shel rdo dang dung la sogas pa
NK094(nge)001:10512: la 'bur du brkos pa lasa rgyal ba'i sku gzugs
NK094(nge)001:10513: byas nas / gong ma de bzhina du yan lag
NK094(nge)001:10514: ma nyamsa par rgyan gyi mdzesa pa'i mtshan nyid kyi
NK094(nge)001:10516: dngos grub kyi mtshan ma 'byung ba'i rten du 'gyur ba yin no //
NK094(nge)001:10521: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10522: glag sha zhes pa'i byang chub kyi shing sogas la
NK094(nge)001:10523: makhasa par bzor bcug ste bzhogsa la gzugsa barnyan byas
NK094(nge)001:10524: te phyag rgya ma nyamsa par kun du rdzogas na
NK094(nge)001:10525: / 'di yanga matshana ma'i rten du 'gyur bas don grub bo //
NK094(nge)001:10526: shing 'di la dpe la lar blak+sha yang 'byung ste
NK094(nge)001:10527: rgya bal du skye ba'i shing gi bye brag zhig
NK094(nge)001:10528: yin par lung rjes su rnal 'byor gyi dpal 'bar
NK094(nge)001:10529: khro mo'i rgyud las lo ts+aa ba'i mchan du snang
NK094(nge)001:10534: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10535: sa la sogsa pa'i lder so la phyag rgyar byas te /
NK094(nge)001:10536: kha doga mdzesa pa dang ldan par byas na dngos grub kyi mtshan ma 'byung ba'i rten yina te /
NK094(nge)001:10537: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi mtshan mas 'khrul ba'i mtshan
NK094(nge)001:10538: ma rnam par grol ba ni rigsa shing 'thad pas
NK094(nge)001:10544: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10545: gang dag rdul tshon gyi sa lasa rgyal ba'i dkyil
NK094(nge)001:10546: 'khor gyi dbyibsa kun tu lham par byas pa la
NK094(nge)001:10547: / tshon rtsi lnga yisa mdzesa par bkod de gsal bar bzhengs na /
NK094(nge)001:10548: de yang rnam grol rig pa'i rten du 'gyur ba yin pas don dang ldan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:10553: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10554: gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor byas pas 'bras bu thob
NK094(nge)001:10555: pa'i gzhir 'gyur du btub pa'i don 'chad pa ni
NK094(nge)001:10556: / bshad pa ltar lha gang gi gzugsa brnyan gyi dngos po gang yina pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:10557: de yi rang bzhina gyi dkyil 'khor gyi lha gang
NK094(nge)001:10558: yang rung ba de gnyis ngo bo tha dad med
NK094(nge)001:10560: 'di gnyis la byang chub kyi sems ji bzhin pa
NK094(nge)001:10561: nyid yin pa la rang bzhin bzang ngan gyi khyad
NK094(nge)001:10562: para cung zad kyang med pa'i phyir gzugs brnyan dang
NK094(nge)001:10563: dngos gzhir 'brel ba yod pas 'di yisa rnam par
NK094(nge)001:10564: grol ba'i rig pa thob par 'gyur ba ni nges
NK094(nge)001:10565: pa'o // gnyis pa la lnga ste /
NK094(nge)001:10569: rgyan dgod cing las kyi rim pa /
NK094(nge)001:10570: mchod pa'i yon tan bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:10575: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10576: bder gshegas rgyal ba rigs lnga gang gi gtso bo
NK094(nge)001:10577: byas pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi pho branga gang yanga rung
NK094(nge)001:10578: ba'i gzhal yas khang rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor lhun
NK094(nge)001:10579: gyis grub pa'i tshul du bzhugs pa de nyid ji
NK094(nge)001:10580: lta bar gang zag lam bas rang bzhin ji 'dra
NK094(nge)001:10581: bar byed de gzugs brnyan du bzhengs su gsol ba'i
NK094(nge)001:10582: dus su lha yi tshogs bzhugs pa'i gnas 'di ltar
NK094(nge)001:10583: byed pa'o // gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la thig
NK094(nge)001:10584: gdab cing bri ba'i rim pa rgyas par las kyi
NK094(nge)001:10590: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10591: de nas gnas der stegs bu kun nas gru bzhi lham par tshad dang ldan pa brtsigs te /
NK094(nge)001:10592: shin tu ngos mnyam par mdzesa par byas la go ma ye yis legs par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:10593: de nas sngags mkhan chas gos lnga dang ldan par byas te /
NK094(nge)001:10594: thig g.yog grogs mo mtshan dang ldan par byas la /
NK094(nge)001:10595: dam tshig dang ye shes kyi skud pa rgyu so
NK094(nge)001:10596: so las legs par bsgril te rab gnas tshul bzhin
NK094(nge)001:10598: dam tshig gi thig gdab pa'ang /
NK094(nge)001:10599: dang por phyogs kyi 'grus bsnyams la /
NK094(nge)001:10600: phyogs mtshams kyi chas srad bu brgyad dang ldan pa'i
NK094(nge)001:10601: thig brgyad tshangs thig dang bcas pa gdab par byas
NK094(nge)001:10602: te / de'i mtha' ma bsdu ba'i las kyi thig
NK094(nge)001:10603: legs par gdab par bya bas mdzesa para bya ba
NK094(nge)001:10605: de nas 'gying phur nas bzung la ji ltar 'tshams
NK094(nge)001:10606: par srad bu thig gcig gisa lte ba zlum por
NK094(nge)001:10607: bskor ro // de ltar dbus mu khyud dang bcas
NK094(nge)001:10608: te dkyil 'khora gyi tshul lta bu nyid du gyur
NK094(nge)001:10609: bskor ro // pa dang / lte ba'i nang du
NK094(nge)001:10610: lham pa srad bu thig thung brgyad bsnol bar btab
NK094(nge)001:10611: pas pho brang le'u tshe lham pa dgur 'gyur te
NK094(nge)001:10612: thig thung zung re'i bar na ka ba re ste
NK094(nge)001:10614: de nas mu khyud kyi tha ma mtha'a zad kyi
NK094(nge)001:10615: sgo rgyan ma gtogs pa'i thig gsum gyi char btab
NK094(nge)001:10616: ste cha chen gsum du byas pa le'u tshe'i phyi
NK094(nge)001:10617: de rdo rje ra ba'i phyi la cha gsum mo
NK094(nge)001:10618: // de nas dkyil 'khor kun gyi re'u cha la
NK094(nge)001:10619: cha chen gsum gdab ste cha chen nang ma nyid
NK094(nge)001:10620: du yang srad bu thig phran gsum btab pas cha
NK094(nge)001:10622: de bzhin du cha chen phyi ma gnyis la'ang thig
NK094(nge)001:10623: phran gsum ste phra mo daga gisa mdzesa para brgyan
NK094(nge)001:10624: te cha chen gsum la cha phran dgu yi char
NK094(nge)001:10625: ni thig gis bgos pa lasa dgur 'gyur ro //
NK094(nge)001:10626: de yi nga ma gnyis gnyis la lha snam bya zhing phyi ma re re la sgo bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:10627: de'ang dang po'i cha chen gsum ni sgo sum brtsegs re re bya ba ste /
NK094(nge)001:10628: de'i cha phran gsum gsum po re re la'ang sgo
NK094(nge)001:10629: dang sgo khyud thig gis bsgos la bya ba'ang sgo
NK094(nge)001:10630: la sum gnyis dang khyud la cig char du bya'o
NK094(nge)001:10635: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10636: sgo'i g.yas g.yon nas ka ba zung ste brgyad kyis mdzesa par brgyan par byas la /
NK094(nge)001:10637: de lta bur rina chen mchog gi ka ba'i nanga
NK094(nge)001:10638: logas kyi dbus su rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangsa rgyas
NK094(nge)001:10639: kyi pho brang bum pa zlum po'i dbu rtser bya
NK094(nge)001:10640: ba'o // sgo sum brtseg gi don ni /
NK094(nge)001:10643: rnam par thar pa bzhi'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:10647: sgo phyi nang rim pa gsum gyis legs par mdzesa shing gsal ba la /
NK094(nge)001:10648: rta babsa bzhi dang them skas brgyad kyis kyang mdzes par brgyan cing spras pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:10649: des na thig chen bcu gcig /cha phran gyi thig phran bcu gsum /
NK094(nge)001:10650: thig thung brgyad ldab tu 'gyur bas phyogs chas rig par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:10651: de nas ye shes kyi thig grangs dang mthun par gdab bo //
NK094(nge)001:10653: dbus kyi pho brang rigs kyi gtso bo gang byed pas dbye ba ni /
NK094(nge)001:10654: las kyi rigs gtso bor byed na le'u tshera bya ba'am /
NK094(nge)001:10655: bde gshegs gtso bor bzhugs na 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad dang /
NK094(nge)001:10656: rdo rje'i rigs gtso bor byed na rdo rje'i dpal be'u bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:10657: pad+ma'i rigs gtso bor bzhugs na pad+ma 'dab brgyad du bya ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:10658: rin chen rigs gtso bo na rina chen zur brgyad du bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:10659: de dag la sogas pa las kyi skabs su ji
NK094(nge)001:10660: ltar rigas shing 'thad pa de bzhina du bri ba'ang
NK094(nge)001:10661: / tshon 'byor pa dang bstun la rab gnas bya ba des /
NK094(nge)001:10662: thig gi lha rnams be kra mas btegs la /
NK094(nge)001:10663: phyogs dang por pany+tsa re ka rdo rje rgyal pos sor bcu drug drangs la bkab ste /
NK094(nge)001:10664: sa bon tshul bzhin byas la nang par thig btegs pa la lag pa'i byin gyis brlabs la /
NK094(nge)001:10665: rdo rje rgyal po'i dgongs pas gzhal yas khang bri ba bzhin bskyed /
NK094(nge)001:10666: byan pos dbus nas lugs bzhin du bri ba'ang de ltar bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:10668: rina po che kha dog mdzes chen sna tshogsa kyi rgyan bri ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:10669: ye shes kyi rtsig pa rin po che sna lnga'i
NK094(nge)001:10670: rim par brtsigs pa'i tshul du pany+tsa re kha bris
NK094(nge)001:10671: pa'i steng du / chu srin gyi t+wa ra na dang /
NK094(nge)001:10672: seng thod kha nas rat+na'i mu tig gi phreng ba ha ras brgyan pa dang ni /
NK094(nge)001:10673: gzhal yas khang gi mgul bar d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa ba phyed pasa legs par brgyan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:10674: rta babs bzhis sgo brgyan tshul ni /
NK094(nge)001:10675: rin po che'i za ra tshag dang /
NK094(nge)001:10677: lce la dril bu g.yer kha'i the'u chung 'phyang ba'i sna 'phyang ngo //
NK094(nge)001:10678: steng du khyung mgo dang bcas pa de dag ni
NK094(nge)001:10679: sgo rgyan te spyi'i dbang du ni rta bab brgyad
NK094(nge)001:10680: du 'gyur ro // de ltar na thig kyang grangs 'phel bar bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:10681: 'dir ni dngos su smos pa tsam gyi phyir grangs 'grib pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:10682: d+r+wa ba'i phyi rol tu 'dod yon gyi lha snam bris te /
NK094(nge)001:10684: rol mo'i sgra sgrogsa pa sogs lha yi bu mo
NK094(nge)001:10685: mang posa phyi nang gi nam mkha'a d+r+wa mig 'phyang
NK094(nge)001:10686: ba'i bar de lasa mchod pa sna tshogsa 'bul bar
NK094(nge)001:10687: bsam zhing bri ba'i tshe 'dod snam du'o //
NK094(nge)001:10688: dbus su theg pa chen po'i gdung bzhis bsnol mar nam mkha' la raba tu brgyan te /
NK094(nge)001:10689: gdung ma ni rigs kyis dbye zhing snang nas ka ba brgyad kyis btegs pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:10690: rina chen gyis pha gu'i kha bad ni rtsig pa'i thog tu'o //
NK094(nge)001:10691: mchod rten gyi dbyibs ni gzhal yas khang gi phyi'i dbyibs te /
NK094(nge)001:10692: yang na sgo'i g.yas g.yon du'ang gsum pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:10693: rgyal mtshan ni dbu rtser rin po che las byas pa'am /
NK094(nge)001:10694: rtsa ba'i rgyud ltar gru bzhi nas brgyan par yang rigs so //
NK094(nge)001:10695: tog rina chen 'oda 'abra ba dang ldan pasa gzhal yas khang mdzesa para brgyan pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:10696: bkod pa phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK094(nge)001:10697: phyi rol du yang rin po'i che'i phung po dang /
NK094(nge)001:10699: phyogs skyong yang bri bar bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:10700: 'di dag tshom bur byed pa ni skabs dang sbyar
NK094(nge)001:10701: la le'u tshe gcig gi thog tu pho brang rdzogs
NK094(nge)001:10702: par bris te / mdor rang rang gang byed kyang
NK094(nge)001:10703: phyogs pho brang chung ngu lnga lngar bris te rang
NK094(nge)001:10704: rang gi sems dpa' dang sems ma 'god do //
NK094(nge)001:10705: mdor na 'og min chos kyi mtho ba'i gnas kyi
NK094(nge)001:10706: gzhal yas khang gi pho brang nyid ci 'dra ba
NK094(nge)001:10707: de dang 'dra bar de nyid mtshon par bri ba'o
NK094(nge)001:10712: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10713: de ltar 'og min dang 'dra ba'i gzhal yasa khanga
NK094(nge)001:10714: gi rgyal ba'i pho brang du gang bris pa de
NK094(nge)001:10715: nyid du gyur pa na bshad pa'i rgyan dang /
NK094(nge)001:10716: 'dir ma smos kyang 'og min la ji ltar bzhugs pa'i rgyan mtshon par bri'o //
NK094(nge)001:10717: de dag tsakli'am yi ge'am phyag rgya gang rung gdan thog tu bkod la bzhag go //
NK094(nge)001:10718: gzhan yang lhab lhub kyi rgyan la sogs pa kun
NK094(nge)001:10719: kyis kyang mdzesa pa dang legsa par brgyan te bskor
NK094(nge)001:10720: bar bya'o // de la mchod pa bla na yod pa phyi'i mchod pa thun mong lnga dang /
NK094(nge)001:10721: bla na med pa zab mo nang dang gsang ba'i mchod ba kun kyang /
NK094(nge)001:10722: dngos ji ltar 'byor pa dang ldan pa dang bsam
NK094(nge)001:10723: pas chud mi gsan par nana tan du byas la
NK094(nge)001:10724: dbul lo // de'ang rim gyis pa dang cig char ba gang yang rung bas /
NK094(nge)001:10725: rang nyid kyis las kyi dkyil 'khor bskyed de /
NK094(nge)001:10726: las rdzogs par bsrang mchod pa phul nas /
NK094(nge)001:10727: gzugs brnyan dang sa bon gang bkod pa las /
NK094(nge)001:10728: gzhal yas khang dang lhar bzhengs nas spyan drangs bstims brtan byas pa la dbul lo //
NK094(nge)001:10729: rab tu gnas par bya ba'i dkyil 'khor la tshogs kyi phyir rab gnas kyi mchod pa'ang /
NK094(nge)001:10730: phyi'i mchod pa sna tshogs dang /
NK094(nge)001:10731: rgyal srid rin chen sna bdun dang /
NK094(nge)001:10732: 'dod yon lnga'i longas spyod dang bcas pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:10733: de bzhin du glu bro gar dang rol mor bcas pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:10734: dug 'jomas pa'i sman dang bdud rtsi la sogs pa
NK094(nge)001:10735: rnams rgyal ba rgya mtsho ji snyed pa thams cad
NK094(nge)001:10737: gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi thig gdab pa las
NK094(nge)001:10738: kyi rigs kyi gzhung du bstan par gsungs te 'dir
NK094(nge)001:10739: mdor bsdus tsam las yi ges 'jigs kyang spros pas
NK094(nge)001:10743: rgyud byang rnam grol rig /ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10744: rab gnas byas pa'i dkyil 'khor du mchod cing zhugs pa'am /
NK094(nge)001:10745: lta ba ji bzhin du rtogs nas mnyam pa nyid
NK094(nge)001:10746: kyi mchoda pa yang dag par sbyar basa yon tan
NK094(nge)001:10747: gyis rang rgyud kyi sgrib pa kun byang zhing dag
NK094(nge)001:10748: nas 'khor 'das gnyis med mthong bas chos thamsa cad
NK094(nge)001:10749: chos nyid mnyam para rtogs te rgyal ba nyid du
NK094(nge)001:10750: 'gyur ba'o // ston pa sems dpa' rdo rjes de
NK094(nge)001:10751: skad ces smras pasa 'dus pa kun thamsa cad kyi
NK094(nge)001:10752: dkyil 'khor gyi don mthong bas rgyud byang nas rnam
NK094(nge)001:10753: grol gyi riga pa skyes so //
NK094(nge)001:10756: yongs su sbyang bar shes par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:10757: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10758: grogsa po daga /bshad pa de dag ni bkoda pa'i
NK094(nge)001:10759: bya bas gtso bor gzhan don gyi yongsa su sbyang
NK094(nge)001:10761: gnyis pa'i me'i bya bas sbyangs ba la gnyis te /
NK094(nge)001:10765: bstod pa nye bar bstan par /
NK094(nge)001:10766: bstod nas zhus pa dngos so //
NK094(nge)001:10770: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10771: grogsa po dag /ces skyes bus bos nas /
NK094(nge)001:10772: 'di la sbyong ba'i spyod pa gnyis pa me'i bya
NK094(nge)001:10773: basa yongsa su sbyong ba nye bar bstan pa gang
NK094(nge)001:10775: chos can thamsa cad chos nyid du sbyang ba'i phyir dgos ched dang ldan pas /
NK094(nge)001:10776: dngosa po thamsa cad ye shes kyi me'i ngo bo
NK094(nge)001:10777: nyid kyi rang bzhina du ston pas byin gyis brlabs
NK094(nge)001:10779: 'khor 'dus pa'i tshogas thamsa cad kyis chos thams cad
NK094(nge)001:10780: ye shes kyi me'i rang bzhina du rang snang bar
NK094(nge)001:10782: ston pa dang me la shina tu ngama nas gzhan
NK094(nge)001:10783: don du zhu ba'i phyir don la ngo mtshar du
NK094(nge)001:10784: gyur pas / don ston pa'i skyes bu dang me la bstod pa /
NK094(nge)001:10789: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10790: chos so cog ye shes kyi mer gsal ba'i don ston pa la e ma'o //
NK094(nge)001:10792: semsa dapa'a semsa dapa'a che zhes skyes bu la bos
NK094(nge)001:10793: nas don du ston pa dang me tha mi dad
NK094(nge)001:10794: pas yon tan chen po mnga' bar bstod pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:10795: yon tan de ltar bu mnga' ba'i skyes bu khyod ni /
NK094(nge)001:10796: sku gsung thugs kyi mthu'i cho 'phrul che ba'i che
NK094(nge)001:10797: ba mnga' ba'i byin rlabsa mchog tu che ba'i chen
NK094(nge)001:10799: de ltar dgongs pa'i byin rlabs kyi ting 'dzina chen
NK094(nge)001:10800: po bdag cag 'khor la sogs pa la snang bar
NK094(nge)001:10801: mdzad pa che'am chen po khyod sku gsung thugs kyi
NK094(nge)001:10802: cho 'phrul chen po ji snyed pa sna tshogsa kyi
NK094(nge)001:10803: che ba'i mdzad pa tha dad par bstan nas 'dul
NK094(nge)001:10805: de bas na gsang sngags kyi thabsa mchog d+r+wa ba'i
NK094(nge)001:10806: sprin phung dapaga gisa mi lang ba'i mnga' bdag lags
NK094(nge)001:10807: te / 'dir chos so cog kun me long lta
NK094(nge)001:10808: bu'i ye shes kyi me'i ngo bor 'od 'abra zhing
NK094(nge)001:10809: gsal bar snang bar mdzad pa de nyid rang byung
NK094(nge)001:10810: gi ye shes chen por gasla ba la mtha'i sel
NK094(nge)001:10812: de'i byin rlabs thams cad du snang ste 'abra zhing
NK094(nge)001:10813: 'phro la ma sgrib par gasla bar gyur pa'i mdzad
NK094(nge)001:10814: pas ni / ma rig pa'i mun pa basla zhing
NK094(nge)001:10815: mtha'i dngosa po thams cad bsregsa shing sbyongs te dag
NK094(nge)001:10816: pas ni / par mdzad do // chos sku bde
NK094(nge)001:10817: ba chena po'i dbyingsa su mnyam pa'i ngang du kun
NK094(nge)001:10818: nas lhun gyis rdzogsa shing sangs rgyas par mdzad pa'ang
NK094(nge)001:10819: pas ni / par mdzad do // / gdul dka'
NK094(nge)001:10820: 'dul ba'i dapa'a bo khyod kyis madzada pa rmad du
NK094(nge)001:10822: zhes par mchog tu bstod pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:10823: ngo bo ma nges pa nyid mdzad pa nges pa'i
NK094(nge)001:10824: tshul du mun pa gsal ba'i ye shes kyi me
NK094(nge)001:10825: klong 'abra ba chen po 'od du 'khyil bas mtha'
NK094(nge)001:10826: kun sel ba'i mkhyen rab kyi bdag po khyod nyid
NK094(nge)001:10827: a la la zhes dgyes par mdzod cig pa dang
NK094(nge)001:10828: / khyab pa'i gzi byin gyi zera 'phro ba'i thugs
NK094(nge)001:10829: rje kun tu snang ba'i bdag po a la la
NK094(nge)001:10830: zhes dgyes par mdzod cig dang /
NK094(nge)001:10831: mtha' yasa pa'i chos thams cad mnyam pa'i dbyingsa su
NK094(nge)001:10832: kun nas sdud pa'i chos nyid kyi me yang khyod
NK094(nge)001:10833: nyid yin te a la la /
NK094(nge)001:10834: zhes dgyes pa'i sgra kun rjes su mthun no //
NK094(nge)001:10835: mtha'i dngos po thamsa cad sreg par byed pa'i phrin
NK094(nge)001:10836: las kyi dpal dang ldan pa'i me yang khyod nyid
NK094(nge)001:10838: gdug pa can dang rtog sgrib thams cad za bar
NK094(nge)001:10839: byed pa'i klong chen po yang skyes bu khyod nyid
NK094(nge)001:10841: mtha' bzhi kun dang bral zhing dabus kyi tha snyad
NK094(nge)001:10842: du'ang gzung du med par mchog tu 'das pa'i dkyil
NK094(nge)001:10843: 'khor chen po'ang khyod nyid yin pas a la la
NK094(nge)001:10844: / thugsa rje zhi ba'i rang bzhin bas thams cad
NK094(nge)001:10845: bde ba mchog la 'god cing rgyas par mdzad pa'i
NK094(nge)001:10846: ngang yang khyod nyid yin no a la la /
NK094(nge)001:10847: lhun gyis grub pa'i dbang phyug bdud 'dul drag po'i
NK094(nge)001:10848: 'jigsa par byed pa'ang khyod nyid yin pas a la
NK094(nge)001:10849: la / zhes brgyad kyis kyang bstod pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:10850: de ltar bstod nas zhu ba dngos ni /
NK094(nge)001:10851: ston pa gsang ba mchog gi bdag po yon tan
NK094(nge)001:10852: rmad du byung ba'i khyad par mnga' ba'i byin rlabsa
NK094(nge)001:10853: kyis ye shes gsang ba'i me yi ranga bzhina chen
NK094(nge)001:10854: po daga gi rnam grangs 'chad pa rnams badga cag
NK094(nge)001:10855: 'dus pa'i 'khor tshogs rnams la legs par bashada du
NK094(nge)001:10856: gsol / zhes de skad 'dus pasa zhus shing gsola ba btab pa lasa /
NK094(nge)001:10864: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10865: de skad ces bstod pas ston pa skyes bu de nyid dgyes pasa /
NK094(nge)001:10869: rdo rje mi yi rang bzhina daga 'di ltar ngesa
NK094(nge)001:10870: para bashada kyis gus pasa legs par nyon cig ces
NK094(nge)001:10871: bka' stsal bar zhal gyis bzhes nas gdams pa mdzad
NK094(nge)001:10872: pa'o // gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK094(nge)001:10879: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10880: khyad para shin tu phul du gyur pa'i bla ma'i
NK094(nge)001:10881: dgongs pa dam pa'i lasa kyi bsreg rdzas kyi mchog
NK094(nge)001:10882: 'disa rnal 'byor pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi dgongs pa
NK094(nge)001:10883: me cir yang snang la mi g.yo ba'i thabsa su
NK094(nge)001:10884: bde ba chen por sbyor bar mdzad pasa /
NK094(nge)001:10885: tshul de yis rgyal ba thams cad kun mnyes par
NK094(nge)001:10886: byas te gnyis su med pa'i mchod pa phul nas
NK094(nge)001:10887: 'gro ba kun gyi rtog sgrib kun sreg cing sbyangsa
NK094(nge)001:10888: pas dag pa chen po ra mdzad pas /
NK094(nge)001:10889: dona rnam pa gnyis grub pa ni phrin lasa kyi mchog tu gyur pas sbyangsa pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:10890: zhes che ba'i sgo nas mos pa bskyed phyir bka' stsal pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:10895: rang bzhin gyi ting nge 'dzin dang shes rab kyi sbyin sreg thun mong du bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:10896: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi sbyin sreg bshad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:10901: zhes pa'i bar tshigs bcad bdun gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10902: de dag gi don re re nas rgyas par bstan pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:10903: rang bzhin gyi hom 'chad pa ste /
NK094(nge)001:10904: zab pa chos nyid ji bzhina pa yi hom khung gi thab tu /
NK094(nge)001:10905: rgya che ba chos so cog gi dngos po ji snyed pa yi yama shing la /
NK094(nge)001:10906: gnyis med de bzhina nyid kyi me byung bas /
NK094(nge)001:10907: de dag gdod nas rgyu thamsa cad dang 'bras bu
NK094(nge)001:10908: thamsa cad ngo bo gnyis par snang ba med de
NK094(nge)001:10909: / ye shes de bzhin nyid du byung thebs pas
NK094(nge)001:10910: mtha' las grol ba ni bsregsa sbyangsa thima pa ste
NK094(nge)001:10911: 'chad pa rnams kyang phyogs mthun par bstan te rnam
NK094(nge)001:10912: grangs rjes su sbyar bar bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:10914: shes rab skye med rnam par daga pa'i hom khung du /
NK094(nge)001:10915: skye ba rnam bzhi yama shing gi rdzas la /
NK094(nge)001:10916: ma skyes spros bral du rtogs pa'i me byung bas /
NK094(nge)001:10917: matshana ma'i bag chagsa thams cad bsregsa sbyangsa thima pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:10918: mtshan ma dang bral te bsam du med pa'i hom khung du /
NK094(nge)001:10919: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chos kyi yam shinga la /
NK094(nge)001:10920: 'od gsal dapaga tu meda pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi me 'byung basa /
NK094(nge)001:10921: mtha' yasa rdul snyed kyi gnyis snang kun bsregsa sbyangsa thim pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:10922: lta ba chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i hom khung du /
NK094(nge)001:10923: chos can sna tshogsa pa'i bsreg rdzas kyi yama shing la /
NK094(nge)001:10924: stong nyid ye shes gsal ba'i me 'abra bas /
NK094(nge)001:10925: 'khrul snang dngos po'i baga chagsa thams cad bsregsa sbyangsa thim pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:10926: rang rig lta ba'i semsa nyid rnam par dag pa'i hom khung du /
NK094(nge)001:10927: semsa can skye 'gro kun gyi yama shing la /
NK094(nge)001:10928: gnyis med rang byung ye shes kyi me 'abra bas /
NK094(nge)001:10929: las snang 'khora ba'i bag chagsa thams cad bsregsa sbyangsa thim pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:10930: gzhi dbyings kun gzhi b+ha ga'i hom khung du /
NK094(nge)001:10931: nyon mongas dug chen lnga yi yama shing la /
NK094(nge)001:10932: ma 'gag par rtogs pa'i 'bras bu ye shes lnga yi me byung basa /
NK094(nge)001:10933: gzung 'dzina rtog pa thams cad bsregsa sbyangsa thim pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:10934: mtshan ma'i ting 'dzin sgom pa snang srid nam mkha'i dbyings kyi hom khung du /
NK094(nge)001:10935: dngos por 'byung ba bzhi yi yama shing la /
NK094(nge)001:10936: lhar snang phyag rgya 'abra ba'i me byung basa /
NK094(nge)001:10937: snang zhing srid pa'i dngosa po thams cad bsregsa sbyangsa thim pa dang bdun ni rang bzhin te /
NK094(nge)001:10938: de dag ji 'dra bar rtogs nas bsgom pas spyod yul yongs su dag pa ste /
NK094(nge)001:10939: de ltar gyur pa ni ting nge 'dzin gyi hom
NK094(nge)001:10940: ste don gyi gnyis ka thun mong du 'gyur ro
NK094(nge)001:10943: las kyi rim pa bshad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:10951: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10952: gzugs brnyan gyi hom khung spyir 'grel pa ste /
NK094(nge)001:10953: 'chad pa'i hom gyi chos bcu gnyis la /
NK094(nge)001:10954: zhi ba sogs rnam pa bzhi yi las kyi hom khung du /
NK094(nge)001:10955: thab kyi sbyin sreg gi shing so sor phye ba
NK094(nge)001:10956: bzhi'am de la shing rnam pa bzhi yi yama shinga
NK094(nge)001:10957: gis gsos te me sbar ba de la rigsa bzhi
NK094(nge)001:10958: yi sprul pas las bzhi'i me lha bskyed pa dang
NK094(nge)001:10963: las bcol ba dag byas te 'abra ba'i me byung
NK094(nge)001:10964: basa 'phags pa mchod cing 'gro ba la sbyin pa'i
NK094(nge)001:10965: bsreg rdzas so sor bsregs pas bdag gzhan gyi sgrib
NK094(nge)001:10966: pa'i dngosa po bsregsa shing sbyangsa te lha'i zhal du
NK094(nge)001:10968: gzugs brnyan gyi hom 'di la yanga las bzhi so
NK094(nge)001:10969: so'i bye brag gi khyad par gyis kha lta phyogsa
NK094(nge)001:10972: rdzas rnams las kyi gzhung ganga ltar rigsa pa de ltar sbyar te mdzes par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:10977: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:10978: de nyid rgyas par bstan pa gang snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:10979: bye brag gsal bar bshad pa 'di dag ste /
NK094(nge)001:10980: 'di la phyogs ni zhi ba'i tshe na shar du lta'o //
NK094(nge)001:10981: rgyas pa'i tshe byang ngam lho ru'o //
NK094(nge)001:10983: drag po'i skabs lho'am byang du'o //
NK094(nge)001:10984: kha dog ni zhi ba la ril dkar po'o //
NK094(nge)001:10987: drag po la mthing ga nag po thal mdoga gsum po nyid sbyar ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:10988: dbyibs kyang me thab zlum po dang /
NK094(nge)001:10989: pad+ma dang le'u tshe bya ba zhi ba ste /
NK094(nge)001:10990: tshad ni zab dang gyen du khru phyed phyed de gang ngo //
NK094(nge)001:10991: chu dang zheng du'ang rjes su mthun te gzhan yang de bzhin no //
NK094(nge)001:10994: rin chen zur brgyad du bya ba ni rgyas pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:10997: gzhu brdung ba'i dbyibsa lta bu ni dabnga la bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:10999: b+ha ga'i mkha'a dang khro zhal lta bur bya ba ni mngona spyod drag po'o //
NK094(nge)001:11000: de dag kyang dbus bang rim sum brtseg /rgya dpang
NK094(nge)001:11001: re rer sor gsum gsum yod pa de kha dog
NK094(nge)001:11002: gi madngas dang so so'i phyag rgya legs par ri
NK094(nge)001:11003: mora mdzesa pa'i mtshan ma dgod par bya ste bang
NK094(nge)001:11004: rim gyi phyed la gtang ngo //
NK094(nge)001:11005: der lasa bzhi'i bye brag rnams kyi shing brtsig pa'ang bsreg shing thab dbyibs su brtsig la /
NK094(nge)001:11007: zhags pa la sogs pa yi rdzas kyis brgyan par bya ba yin no //
NK094(nge)001:11018: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11019: de dag gi las bya thabs gang snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:11020: 'di dag bya ba'ang ye shesa rdo rje lasa kyi
NK094(nge)001:11021: rgyud la shin tu mkhas pa dang ldana pas bya
NK094(nge)001:11022: ba ste / de yang las so sor bsko ba'i
NK094(nge)001:11023: ched du 'chad pa'i bla ma dgongs pa mdzad pa
NK094(nge)001:11024: ba ste / / las gzhung srong ba /
NK094(nge)001:11025: sbyin sreg byed pa gsum gyis thabsa mchog dang sbyar te bya ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:11027: rdo rje rgyal pos dgongs pa bya ba /
NK094(nge)001:11028: las sbyor bla mas las gzhung bsrang ba /
NK094(nge)001:11029: skabs sbyor bla mas sbyin sreg bya ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:11034: sdig sgrib ci byas pa thams cad dgongs pa'i 'phro
NK094(nge)001:11035: 'du daga par mdzad pa'i las kyi mtha'a 'dzina zhing
NK094(nge)001:11036: mi gtong bas tshogs gnyis par mdzad de rgyal ba
NK094(nge)001:11037: mnyes pa'i dgongs pa mchog gi mchod pa 'dzina pa
NK094(nge)001:11038: rdo rje rgyal po bla ma'i thabs so //
NK094(nge)001:11043: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11044: rdo rje gasnga ba'i las la sbyor ba'i bla mas
NK094(nge)001:11045: glu bro gara thabs dang bcas pas las gzhung phyi
NK094(nge)001:11047: bstod cing mchod pa desa pa'i 'byor tshogsa rnams kyang sbyar nas 'bul ba dag go //
NK094(nge)001:11048: de'ang rdo rje sngags kyi lasa sbyor mkhan gyis las
NK094(nge)001:11049: rnam pa bzhi po gang byed kyi gzhung srong ba
NK094(nge)001:11050: de ltar byin gyis brlabs pa'i sgrub pa tshul bzhin
NK094(nge)001:11052: sbyin sreg byed pa'i las mkhan skabs sbyor bla ma'i
NK094(nge)001:11053: las gzhung dang mthun par mdo chen po'i gasnga ba
NK094(nge)001:11054: lasa kyi rgyud gzhung gi bye brag dang ldan pasa
NK094(nge)001:11055: las gang byed kyi phreng ba gshar btab la /
NK094(nge)001:11056: zhi ba na zhi ba'i lha rgyud dang /
NK094(nge)001:11057: rgyas pa na rgyas pa'i lha rgyud dang /
NK094(nge)001:11058: de bzhin du dbang drag gi lha rgyud dag bshad
NK094(nge)001:11059: pa bzhin bsgom zhing las gzhung bsrang ba tshul bzhin
NK094(nge)001:11060: du gashara basa gsal btab nas so so'i lha bskyed
NK094(nge)001:11061: de bsgom zhing gsal ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:11062: sngagsa dang phyag rgya bzla zhing bca' ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:11063: de bzhina du me mchod nas so so'i bstod tshig
NK094(nge)001:11064: gi glu yi sgo nas mchod pa'ang rgyud dang mthun
NK094(nge)001:11065: par sbyar te rdzogs par bya ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:11070: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11071: rigs kyi gtso bo lnga so sor dbye ba'i rigsa
NK094(nge)001:11072: lnga'i rgyud du byung ba'i khyad par lnga ru snang
NK094(nge)001:11074: las bzhi so so'i skabs kyi rigs lnga'i cha yis
NK094(nge)001:11075: gtso bo gang gis byed pa'i lha de'i rigas su
NK094(nge)001:11076: kun gshar btab ste mchod pa'ang /
NK094(nge)001:11077: ye shes klong yangsa 'khyil ba'i hom khung chen po nyid du /
NK094(nge)001:11078: dama rdzasa nyid ye shes kyi bdud rtsi mchog gi 'od du 'abra ba yis mchod cing /
NK094(nge)001:11079: sdig sgrib sbyangsa pa dang dngos grub thob par bya
NK094(nge)001:11080: ba'i phyir bsreg byar sbyar te mchod par bya ba
NK094(nge)001:11082: de yang gang gi mchod cing bstod zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:11083: yon tan gyi mu mtha' dapaga tu med pa mnga'
NK094(nge)001:11084: ba'i rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rgya mtsho'i chu
NK094(nge)001:11085: ltar zab cing mang ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogsa
NK094(nge)001:11086: rnams kyi che ba sngagas pa'i yona tan tshad med
NK094(nge)001:11087: daga /rdo rje glu yisa bston pa'i tshig glu ru
NK094(nge)001:11088: blang zhing brjod nas kyang mtshan re rdzogs pa dang
NK094(nge)001:11089: / rtsa ba'i sngags la kh+aa hi dang /
NK094(nge)001:11092: p+aa shang ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK094(nge)001:11093: m+aa ra ya phatah ces las skabs dang sbyar la
NK094(nge)001:11094: mchod cing mnyes para bya ba'i las kyi sbyin sreg
NK094(nge)001:11095: gi thabsa chen po brtsamsa par byas te mjug tu
NK094(nge)001:11096: smon lam man chad bya ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:11098: me pra bzang ngan brtags pa /
NK094(nge)001:11099: ngan na sbyin sreg bskyar la bya ba /
NK094(nge)001:11100: bzang na dngos grub blang ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:11105: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11106: de dag zin pa dang me pra brtags pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:11107: bstod pa zin nas mnyes par bya ba'i lasa rnams rdzogsa pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:11108: ganga sgrib pa byang zhing dag pa dang ma byang
NK094(nge)001:11109: bas dag pa min pa'i dona chen po dang dman
NK094(nge)001:11111: dngos grub grub pa dang ma grub pa'i ltas kyi
NK094(nge)001:11112: rnam pa de rnams thams cad dag /rnal 'byor pa
NK094(nge)001:11113: me yi mtshan nyid la makhasa shing goms pasa brtagsa
NK094(nge)001:11115: me sgra snyan par 'bar ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:11116: mi snyan par 'bar ba gnyis dang /
NK094(nge)001:11117: kha doga sdug mi sdug dang gsal ba dang mi gsal ba gnyis dang /
NK094(nge)001:11118: 'abra ba'i tshul drag par 'bar ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:11120: me'i dbyibs kyang las bzhi'i dbyibs su 'bar ba rnam pa bzhi dang /
NK094(nge)001:11121: 'og gi yid du 'ong mi 'ong gnyis te rtsa ba drug gam /
NK094(nge)001:11122: rigs lnga yab yum gyi phyag mtshan drug gi dbyibsa rnam pa drug tu'ang gsungs te /
NK094(nge)001:11123: sku gdung chen po'i rgyud las /
NK094(nge)001:11126: dkar la me lce rwa bzhin 'byung //
NK094(nge)001:11127: rdo rje'i rigs kyi mchod rten thob //
NK094(nge)001:11129: 'khor lo snang mdzad chos sku'i gzugs //
NK094(nge)001:11130: me lce gcig la rtse rno ba //
NK094(nge)001:11131: kha dog lnga ka tshang ba de //
NK094(nge)001:11132: don grub mchod rten dngos grub thob //
NK094(nge)001:11133: me lce mang la ma gyes par //
NK094(nge)001:11134: me lce gsum dang ldan gyur na //
NK094(nge)001:11137: me la dri bsung ldan gyur na //
NK094(nge)001:11139: rin chen mchod rten 'grub pa'i rtags //
NK094(nge)001:11140: zhi rgyas dbang dang mngon spyod kyi //
NK094(nge)001:11141: me yi mdog kyang de 'drar brtags //
NK094(nge)001:11142: me lce med la mdog 'gyur na //
NK094(nge)001:11143: sgrib pa las tshan che ba yin //
NK094(nge)001:11144: me 'od chung la dmar nag na //
NK094(nge)001:11145: de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs rje yis //
NK094(nge)001:11146: sdig can de ni ma zin rtags //
NK094(nge)001:11148: bsod nams zhan te sdig chung rtags //
NK094(nge)001:11150: lha dag mi yi sgyu sogs 'dra //
NK094(nge)001:11151: zhi la dkar ba'i mdog dang ldan //
NK094(nge)001:11152: spyi ru me lce legs par 'dod //
NK094(nge)001:11153: me lce chad 'dod rlung che la //
NK094(nge)001:11155: da lta dngos su sdig zhang yod //
NK094(nge)001:11156: me lce zhi la dkar 'khyil ba //
NK094(nge)001:11157: mjug la'ang je zhan dkar zhan pa //
NK094(nge)001:11158: de ni byang chub sems dpa'i me //
NK094(nge)001:11159: me yi mtshan nyid gzhan yang brtags //
NK094(nge)001:11160: zhes gsungs pa'i don dang sbyar ro //
NK094(nge)001:11161: de lta bu daga la shin tu yongas su mkhas shing shes para bya ba nges par gces so //
NK094(nge)001:11166: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11167: de ltar yongs su shes nas tshul dang ldan pa'i las brtsam pa'i phyir /
