NK094(nge)001:11168: gal te de ltar sreg sbyong byas pas me'i matshana
NK094(nge)001:11169: ma rnams mi sdug cing mi legs par byung na
NK094(nge)001:11170: / 'bras bu yid du mi 'onga zhing mi 'dod par ltung ba'i rtagsa yina pasa /
NK094(nge)001:11171: slar yang sreg sbyong gis bshags pa chen po bya ba'am /
NK094(nge)001:11172: las la shin tu gdung zhing 'gyod pas sbyin sreg
NK094(nge)001:11173: rgyas par bya ba la nan tan du 'bad do
NK094(nge)001:11178: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11179: de nas me'i mtshan ma legs nas yida du 'ong zhing sdug par gyur na /
NK094(nge)001:11180: 'bras bu yid du 'ong zhing 'doda pa ltar 'byung ba nges par grub pa'i rtags yin pas /
NK094(nge)001:11181: me la dngos grub gang 'dod pa'i mtshan ma rnams
NK094(nge)001:11182: dang bstun te rab 'bring tha ma rnam pa gsum
NK094(nge)001:11183: gang ltar byung ba de ltar gang grub pa yi
NK094(nge)001:11184: dngos grub blang bar bya ste /
NK094(nge)001:11185: gang yod bdag tshe 'das pa zhig na /
NK094(nge)001:11187: des blang bar bsam par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:11191: bla ma so so'i las rim /
NK094(nge)001:11195: sbyong byed kyi mtshan ma dgod pa /
NK094(nge)001:11196: sbyang bya'i mtshan ma dgod pa /
NK094(nge)001:11202: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11203: de ltar bya ba la'ang ro bsreg pa'i las dngos gang snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:11204: 'dus pa chen po zhes skyes bu sems dpa' rdo
NK094(nge)001:11205: rjes bos nas gazhana yang gang las bzhi'i sbyin sreg
NK094(nge)001:11206: las dgar bar ro yi rdzas rnams bsreg sbyang bya
NK094(nge)001:11207: ba nyid na thabs 'di ltar brtsam par bya ste
NK094(nge)001:11208: / thog mar ro la chos nyid rnam par dag
NK094(nge)001:11209: pa'am yi ge brgya pa bzlas pa'i sngagas kyis btab
NK094(nge)001:11210: nas kyang shin tu dri zhima pa'i spos chu sna
NK094(nge)001:11211: tshogsa kyis ro la byug cing phyi'i khrus kyis bkru
NK094(nge)001:11212: zhing dag par bya ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:11213: nang gi khrus ni bdag med sgom pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:11218: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11219: de nas bdud rtsi zhun chen gyi khu ba yisa
NK094(nge)001:11220: rasa la byug pas ro dkris te gos dang rgyan
NK094(nge)001:11221: byas pas snang tshul du phyi'i gos rgyan byed do
NK094(nge)001:11222: // nang du gos ni tshul khrims dang /
NK094(nge)001:11223: rgyan ni ngo tsha shes pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:11224: de nas gnyen po dgod pa ni ro yi rtog
NK094(nge)001:11225: pa'i gansa nyi shu rtsa gnyis sam bzhi bcu zhe
NK094(nge)001:11226: gnyis la sogs pa rnams gang yin para rtog pa
NK094(nge)001:11227: lhar bskyed pa'i phyir lha rnams kyi las sngagsa kyi
NK094(nge)001:11228: sbyor ba byang bu'am shog bu la bris te gsang
NK094(nge)001:11229: gi phyag rgya kun ro la bkod pa ni rtog
NK094(nge)001:11230: pa las lhar bskyed pa'i rkyen no //
NK094(nge)001:11231: de nas gsung bkod pa'i lha rnams kyi thugs ye
NK094(nge)001:11232: shes kyi phyag rgya'i mtshan mas gadba par bya ba
NK094(nge)001:11233: mtshon byed sdong bu'i snying po rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khora
NK094(nge)001:11234: bkod pa gang gi lha'i grangs dang mnyam pa de
NK094(nge)001:11235: yi thugs mtshon pa'i phyag rgya rnams ras la byas
NK094(nge)001:11236: te gsung gi snying po gang du bkod pa de
NK094(nge)001:11237: nyid du rasa kyi sdong bu'i snying po'i grangsa kyang
NK094(nge)001:11238: de ltar du bya zhing gdags te rtog pa sbyong
NK094(nge)001:11239: ba'i phyir ro // de ltar rtogs pa lhar bskyed
NK094(nge)001:11240: pa'i snying po daga la lha so so yi rgyu
NK094(nge)001:11241: ma nor ba rtsa ba'i yiga 'abru re re ba
NK094(nge)001:11242: m+aum h'u t+r+aam la sogs pa'am /
NK094(nge)001:11243: ta tha la sogs pa dag rasa sama shing ngam
NK094(nge)001:11244: shog bu la bris te dgoda par byed pa ni
NK094(nge)001:11245: sa bon gyi snying po bskyed gazhi'o //
NK094(nge)001:11250: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11251: de ltar ro yi sbyor ba rdzogsa zin pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:11252: de nas ro yi phyi ras kyi steng khyab pa'i
NK094(nge)001:11253: lus kyi mgo 'jug thamsa cad du 'khor ba sreg
NK094(nge)001:11254: pa'i phyir mi mthun pa'i rnam par nyon mongsa pa
NK094(nge)001:11255: dang 'khora ba rgyu 'bras kun bkod par byed de
NK094(nge)001:11257: rgyu ni ras sam shing shun ganga dag la /
NK094(nge)001:11258: 'khora ba'i sa bona drug gi yi ge a n+ri la sogs pa thamsa cad dgod pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:11259: de drug gi las nyon mongas pa lnga yi ming dang 'khor ba'i rgyu gzhan dag kun dang /
NK094(nge)001:11260: nyon mongs pa dug gsum dang bacasa pa yang bris la gdags so //
NK094(nge)001:11261: mjug la de dag dag par gyur cig ces bya ba'ang bri'o //
NK094(nge)001:11262: de bzhin du skye ba'i gnas bzhi dang lam rgyud
NK094(nge)001:11263: lnga rgyu drug gi 'gro ba rigs drug rnams dang
NK094(nge)001:11264: bcas te ming yig bri ba dang ngam yang na
NK094(nge)001:11266: gti mug phag gi gzugs dang /
NK094(nge)001:11267: zhe sdang sbrul gyi gzugs dang ma rig pa rgan
NK094(nge)001:11268: mo long ba la sogs pa so so'i gzugsa su
NK094(nge)001:11269: byas nas ni / gnas drug dang gnas lnga la sogs pa daga tu dgod par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:11270: gzhan yang sa bona drug dang 'du mched bcu gnyis dang /
NK094(nge)001:11271: phung po'i dngos po lnga dang /
NK094(nge)001:11272: gzunga ba dang 'dzina pa'i ming du bcas pa rnams kyang yi ge mas klog gam /
NK094(nge)001:11273: rgyal khams sde gzhan gyi yi ger bris shing /
NK094(nge)001:11274: me dang 'dam dang mun pa dang khur dang mdud
NK094(nge)001:11275: pa dang ri bo la sogs pa mtshon byed brda
NK094(nge)001:11276: yi tshul du ro yi gnas rnams kun tu bkoda
NK094(nge)001:11277: nas ni / ro rnams rdzogs par khyab para dgoda par bya ste /
NK094(nge)001:11278: de dag bsreg pa dang sbyong ba'i dngos po yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK094(nge)001:11283: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11284: de nasa ro yi phung po bcas zin pa de nyid /
NK094(nge)001:11285: rten pas drangs nas glegsa ma brtsigs pa'i stegsa bu yi steng du makhasa pasa bzhag ste /
NK094(nge)001:11288: sgrib pa dral ba dag brtsam par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:11291: bsreg khang rtsig cing rdzas dgod pa /
NK094(nge)001:11293: gzugs thag bla ma'i phyag tu 'bul ba /
NK094(nge)001:11296: thab kyi cho ga /zhes pa nas /
NK094(nge)001:11298: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11299: de nas las gang byed kyi me thab kyi cho ga ltar brtsigs par bya ba yanga /
NK094(nge)001:11300: man+dal lam dkyil 'khor che chung gi 'khora yug khru
NK094(nge)001:11301: gang la sogs pa rana pa tsam du byas la
NK094(nge)001:11304: lham pa'i gzugs ni gang yin pa //
NK094(nge)001:11305: zhes bzhugs te gzhan la mi 'dug go //
NK094(nge)001:11306: mar zab su brko zhing bru ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:11307: yar kha khyer rtsig pa'ang khru phyed phyed tsam du rgyud kyi lugsa bzhin brtsams la legs par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:11308: der phyag rgya bzhugs te lha dgod pa'i gnas su
NK094(nge)001:11309: dbus kyi pho brang daga kyang thiga gisa phye ste
NK094(nge)001:11310: / las gang byed pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi sgo yan
NK094(nge)001:11311: chad yul bcad de legs par bri zhing gru chad
NK094(nge)001:11312: man chad mnyam par bri ba'ang tshul bzhin du so
NK094(nge)001:11318: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11319: de yi steng du bsreg shing brtsig nas /
NK094(nge)001:11320: bsreg khang gi dbyibsa ni rigsa so so'i las bzhi
NK094(nge)001:11321: gang byed pa'i tshul du gru bzhir gtamsa pa la
NK094(nge)001:11322: / grwa zur ka bas brtan par brten te /
NK094(nge)001:11323: sum brtseg gi rnam par yanga thog par khanga dang bcas par bya zhing /
NK094(nge)001:11324: tha ma yam shing bardzangasa pasa gtamsa par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:11325: de nas bar khang dag gi glegsa ma la ro
NK094(nge)001:11326: de gzhug pa yi bzhina gyi kha lta phyogsa ni
NK094(nge)001:11327: ro bsregs pa'i las kyi gzhung bzhin te /
NK094(nge)001:11328: zhi ba na shar du bstan pa la sogs pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:11329: yang na rtsa ba'i rgyud las /
NK094(nge)001:11330: ro yi bzhin phyogs shar du bstan //
NK094(nge)001:11331: zhes pa ltar shar nyid du bstan to //
NK094(nge)001:11336: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11337: ro yi steng khang gi yanga thog tu ras sam
NK094(nge)001:11338: gro shog la sogsa pa la bris pa yi zhi
NK094(nge)001:11339: ba rdo rje dbyings kyi phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor gasla
NK094(nge)001:11340: bar dgod de dbub nas lding du gzhug pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:11345: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11346: ro khang gi glo skar phyogs bzhir bzhi phye la
NK094(nge)001:11347: rdo rje gzungsa kyi rgyun thaga bzhi phung po'i phyogs
NK094(nge)001:11348: bzhir btagsa nasa phyogs bzhi'i bla ma'i phyag tu dbul
NK094(nge)001:11349: lo // de yang gzungs thag gi grangs ni glo skar dang mnyam par rnam pa bzhir sbyar te /
NK094(nge)001:11352: dbang la drug /drag po la gsum mam /
NK094(nge)001:11353: yang na kun la bzhi ste bla ma'i grangs kyang rjes su mthun no //
NK094(nge)001:11354: de dag shing gi brtsigs lugs kyi dbyibs kyis phye ba ste /
NK094(nge)001:11355: tshul de yi bya ba kun rdzogsa pa dang legs par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:11360: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11361: shing de yi phyi mtha'i bar gyi man+dala gyi stegsa bu la dkyil 'khor bris te /
NK094(nge)001:11362: der rnam bzhi lasa kyi lha rnams dgod pa yang dbus su gtso bo /
NK094(nge)001:11364: phyi mthar tshangs pa la sogs pa yang gsungs pas so so'i tsaka li dgod par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:11372: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11373: de ltar shing dang stegsa bu bkod pa'i bya ba
NK094(nge)001:11374: thams cad rdzogsa para gyur te legs par zin pa
NK094(nge)001:11375: dang / rdo rje lasa kyi bla ma rnams rang
NK094(nge)001:11376: rang gi las la sgos gadba pa'i tshul bstan pa
NK094(nge)001:11377: dang / ni / gnyis pa la drug ste /
NK094(nge)001:11378: rdo rje rgyal pos 'dzab bya ba /
NK094(nge)001:11379: las sbyor bla mas gzhung bsrang ba /
NK094(nge)001:11380: rdo rje rgyal theb kyis sdig pa bshags pa /
NK094(nge)001:11381: skabs sbyor bla mas sbyin sreg bya ba /
NK094(nge)001:11382: dge ba'i ltang 'dzin gyis dkar byang bla ma la dbul ba /
NK094(nge)001:11383: sdig pa'i nag byang thab tu bsreg pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:11388: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11389: rang nyid kyi 'khor ba bsregs zin pa'i rdo rje
NK094(nge)001:11390: rgyal po bla ma dam pa la tshe 'das kyi
NK094(nge)001:11391: 'khora ba bsreg para mang'a gsol te /
NK094(nge)001:11393: ro la bkod pa'i lha rnams gsal bar byas la /
NK094(nge)001:11394: dgongs pa chos nyid las mi g.yo bar thams cad
NK094(nge)001:11395: der sbyangs pa'i ye shes kyi me chen po'i ngang
NK094(nge)001:11396: du rtse gcig par gnas pasa /
NK094(nge)001:11397: tshe 'das kyi rtog sgrib sreg pa'i rdo rje sngags
NK094(nge)001:11398: kyi me yi 'adu 'phro bya zhing gzungs thag nas
NK094(nge)001:11399: bzung la dgongs pa rgyun du bya zhing bar mi
NK094(nge)001:11404: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11405: de nas rdo rje sngagsa kyi las sbyor mkhan la
NK094(nge)001:11406: las rnam pa bzhi gang byed pa'i phrin lasa kyi
NK094(nge)001:11408: byang du las bzhi gang rung gi phrin lasa kyi
NK094(nge)001:11409: phreng ba rdzogas para bya ste zhi khro gzhung bsrang
NK094(nge)001:11410: 'dzab dus su dkyil 'khor gnyis su phye la bstims
NK094(nge)001:11416: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11417: bla ma rdo rje rgyal theb tu gyur pa'i dam
NK094(nge)001:11418: pa zhig gis ro yisa tshe rabs su byas pa'i
NK094(nge)001:11419: sdig sgrib kyi nyes pa'i mtha'a bzung nas da lta'i
NK094(nge)001:11420: bar gyi lasa kyi basgas pa bsngo bgrang bya zhing
NK094(nge)001:11421: nub phyogs nas bshagsa pa'i thabs zab mo bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:11426: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11427: skabsa sbyor byed pa'i rdo rje bla ma yisa /
NK094(nge)001:11428: lho yi phyogs nas bla na meda pa'i me yi mchod pa dang sbyin bsreg rgyun du bya ste /
NK094(nge)001:11429: de'ang dang po thab gang yin pa las /
NK094(nge)001:11431: zhes me'i sa bon btags pa brjod la thabs dang mthun par 'byams klas par bskyed /
NK094(nge)001:11432: de 'og rdo rje'i brag thab dang dbyibs mthun pa'i steng du de las ra skyes bskyed /
NK094(nge)001:11433: de'i sga gong du rigs bzhi'i sa bon gang rung las /
NK094(nge)001:11434: las bzhi'i me lha las dang mthun pa'i kha dog la tri shu la dang /
NK094(nge)001:11438: g.yon bgrang phreng can bsams la /
NK094(nge)001:11440: ye shes kyi me lha spyan drangs /
NK094(nge)001:11441: de yang da ru na zhes bya ba'i me lha dang /
NK094(nge)001:11442: stobs sbyin zhes bya ba'i me lha dang /
NK094(nge)001:11443: 'dod pa skyes zhes bya ba'i me lha dang /
NK094(nge)001:11444: khro bo zhes bya ba'i me lha dang bzhi'am /
NK094(nge)001:11445: de dang cha mthun pa'i ye shes kyi me lha'o //
NK094(nge)001:11446: de dam tshig gi me lha la bstim /
NK094(nge)001:11447: brtan par byas la mchod pa rnams phul te bstod la /
NK094(nge)001:11449: de'i lto snying du tshe 'das kyi rtog tshogs lha'i dkyil 'khor du gsal bar bskyed la /
NK094(nge)001:11450: spyan drangs pa dang bstim brtan byas la /
NK094(nge)001:11451: bro gar dang glu tshig snyan pa'i stabsa chen gyis
NK094(nge)001:11452: mchod pa'i khyad par kun sbyar ba dang rola mo
NK094(nge)001:11453: sna tshogsa pa dbul la bstod pa rdzogs ma thag
NK094(nge)001:11454: tu / h'u badz+ra d+h+rika m+aum da du shwa ri kh+aa hi sh+aan+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK094(nge)001:11456: bzlas pa stong rdzogs nas rnam lnga 'bul ba stong tshigs kyi mchod pa zer ro //
NK094(nge)001:11457: skabs su rdo rje las kyi smon lam las mthun du gadba ste /
NK094(nge)001:11458: mchod pa'i skabsa dug gsum mchod pa'ang bya zhing lasa
NK094(nge)001:11459: kyi mjug tu rdzogs pa'i bar mthar chags su bya'o
NK094(nge)001:11464: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11465: rdo rje lasa kyi ltang 'dzina pa'i dam pasa /
NK094(nge)001:11466: tshe 'das kyi tshe snga phyi'i dge ba ci bsags pa'am /
NK094(nge)001:11467: ma shi tsam na dge rtsa ji ltar byas pa
NK094(nge)001:11468: thams cad shog bu'am ras la bris nas dakara byang
NK094(nge)001:11470: legsa mtha' rnams bla ma dama pa rnams kyi phyag la 'bul bar bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:11475: zhes pa'i bar gyiis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11476: ro yi nyes mtha' gang yin rnams 'dzina pasa tshe
NK094(nge)001:11477: 'das kyi tshe rabs su sdig pa ci byas pa'am
NK094(nge)001:11478: / tshe 'dir bsags pa thams cad ras sam shog bu la bris pa'i nag byang bklags la /
NK094(nge)001:11479: mtshan ma nag po'i bud shing de dag ye shes
NK094(nge)001:11480: me'i klong du bsrega ste tshig tu'ang lha la bskul
NK094(nge)001:11483: gsang chen nang pa'i lugs kyis me lha logs na med pas /
NK094(nge)001:11485: tshul de ltar lta ba bskul ba dang rjes su
NK094(nge)001:11486: mthun par snang ba mtha' yas yab yum me lha
NK094(nge)001:11487: dang dbyer med par byas te /
NK094(nge)001:11488: me sbyor me la gnas pa'i lha //
NK094(nge)001:11489: me yi sangsa rgyas 'od dapaga meda //
NK094(nge)001:11490: me yi lha mo gosa dakara mo //
NK094(nge)001:11491: rgyal ba kun gyi 'od yina te //
NK094(nge)001:11492: 'byung ba me la dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK094(nge)001:11493: thamsa cad kun gyi drod bdag yin //
NK094(nge)001:11494: srid gsum sreg par zhal gyis 'ches //
NK094(nge)001:11495: dngos po bsreg pa'i phrin las ni //
NK094(nge)001:11496: thugsa dam dbang gis yong mi 'da' //zhes dbyangs su brjod la /
NK094(nge)001:11497: dang por sdig sgrib bsreg par thugs dam du bcas pa lags pas /
NK094(nge)001:11498: tshe 'das gang gi sdig sgrib bag chags dang bcas
NK094(nge)001:11499: pa sreg pa'i thabs dam pa de nyid mkhyen par
NK094(nge)001:11500: mdzod la bsreg par gyis shig par bskul lo //
NK094(nge)001:11501: de ltar nag byang bsreg par byed de /
NK094(nge)001:11502: me sbyor me la gnas pa'i lha //
NK094(nge)001:11503: zhes pa sogs 'di nag byang la 'byar ba ni
NK094(nge)001:11504: gzhung gi dgongs pa dngos yin pas 'grel pas kyang
NK094(nge)001:11505: de ltar bshad la kun 'dus dang yang mthun no
NK094(nge)001:11507: mjug gi las dngos bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:11508: zhor la gdung gi rim pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:11510: me pra brtag cing bzang ngan gyi bya thabs /
NK094(nge)001:11511: thal ba phyag rgyar bzhengs pa /
NK094(nge)001:11512: gdung byung na mchod ga nas su dbul ba /
NK094(nge)001:11518: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11519: de nas ro yi rnam shes kyi sdig sgrib byang
NK094(nge)001:11520: ma byang ngam dag ma dag gi khyad par me
NK094(nge)001:11521: la makhasa pasa bshad pa de bzhina du me lce
NK094(nge)001:11522: la brtag go // gal te mi sdug pa'i tshul
NK094(nge)001:11523: byung nas ma legs na slar yang bsreg sbyang rgyas
NK094(nge)001:11524: par bya zhing bshags pa mang du bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:11525: gal te me lce sdug cing legsa par byung na
NK094(nge)001:11526: de nyid la sgrib pa sregs shig par brjod la
NK094(nge)001:11527: ye shes kyi mes sbyangs par bsam nas tshe 'das
NK094(nge)001:11528: la me dabnga bskur zhing dngos grub blang bar bya'o
NK094(nge)001:11533: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11534: thal ba la phyi nas sku gdung mchod rten dang
NK094(nge)001:11535: ring bsrel dang ldan pa'i sku brnyan gyi gdung dang
NK094(nge)001:11536: / phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor la sogsa pa bzhengs su gsol la rab gnas tshul bzhin du bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:11541: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11542: tshe 'das de nyid gal te rnal 'byor dam pa mchog tu gyur pa zhig yin na /
NK094(nge)001:11543: de la sku gdung byung ma byung yi ge brgya
NK094(nge)001:11544: pas bshags pa'i sngags kyi then tshar la brtagsa te
NK094(nge)001:11545: / byung na bla ma'i mchod gnas dam pa'i rten
NK094(nge)001:11546: du rdo rje rgyal po la dbul bar bya ba'am
NK094(nge)001:11547: / / rnal 'byor tshul bzhin byed pa gang yang rung ba la dbul bar bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:11548: 'di ltar byed pa ni sgo gsum gyi las kyi
NK094(nge)001:11549: sbyor ba kun gyi mchog tu gyur ba yin no
NK094(nge)001:11550: // de skad ces gsang ba'i mnga' bdag semsa dapa'a
NK094(nge)001:11551: rdo rje ston pa mchog desa smras te bka' stsal
NK094(nge)001:11552: // par mdzad do // zhes gsang ba pas gsungs so //
NK094(nge)001:11556: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11557: grogsa po dag /bstan pa de dag ni me'i bya
NK094(nge)001:11558: bas yongsa su sbyang ba yin par shes para bya'o
NK094(nge)001:11559: // zhes spyod pa'i ngo bo bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:11561: dang po ji ltar byung ba'i khungs kyi rim pa /
NK094(nge)001:11562: gdung bsgrub pa'i thabs bshad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:11564: gang la sa byung ba'i tshul don byed tshul dang bcas pa /
NK094(nge)001:11565: byin rlabs dang yon tan bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:11566: rig 'dzin dang byang chub sems dpa' dag pa la snang ba /
NK094(nge)001:11567: gdung gi khyad par bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:11568: phebs pa'i yon tan bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:11573: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11574: gdung gi lo rgyus bstan pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:11575: rdo rje gsang ba'i theg pa chen po bsgrub pa'i
NK094(nge)001:11576: chos kyi spun zung du gyur pa dag la bos
NK094(nge)001:11577: nas gang zhig 'das par bshad pa de bzhin du
NK094(nge)001:11578: lnga phung me yi bya basa sbyangs pa yi rkyen
NK094(nge)001:11579: lasa byung ba gdung zhesa gragsa pa sha ri rama
NK094(nge)001:11580: nyid ji ltar 'byung ba'i tshul yang /
NK094(nge)001:11581: bskal pa dpag tu med pa ji srid pa'i sngon
NK094(nge)001:11582: rol yi dus dag nas grangsa med pa'i sprul pa'i
NK094(nge)001:11583: sku'i rgyal ba mang po dag mya ngan las 'adsa
NK094(nge)001:11584: para gyur nas spur sbyangs par byas pa'i phyi na
NK094(nge)001:11585: / dgongs pa mtha' dang bral ba'i spros med ye
NK094(nge)001:11586: shes chen po'i byin rlabs dam pa lasa byung ba'i
NK094(nge)001:11587: sku gdung zhes su grags pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:11588: sku yi gdung dngos sam sha ri ram dang ring
NK094(nge)001:11589: bsrel zhes grags pa gdul bya la snang nas 'gro
NK094(nge)001:11590: ba'i bsoda namsa kyi rten du kun la gragsa shing
NK094(nge)001:11591: snang ba'o // 'o na rgyal ba la dngos po zhig yod do zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:11592: rgyal ba rnams kyi ngo bo ni dngosa po yod
NK094(nge)001:11593: stong gi mtha' dang bral ba'i spros mtshan gang yang
NK094(nge)001:11594: med pas chos sku gdal khyab chen po la /
NK094(nge)001:11595: sku gdung dang ring bsrel gyi dngos po rang rgyud
NK094(nge)001:11596: par mi dmigs pas nges pa'i mtshan ma can du
NK094(nge)001:11598: gdul bya semsa can rnams la phan gdags te drang ba'i dgos ched kyi don du /
NK094(nge)001:11599: gsang ba'i dbyings dngos med rang bzhin lhun gyis grub
NK094(nge)001:11600: pa'i ngang lasa thugsa rje'i cho 'phrul du bzhag pas
NK094(nge)001:11601: skal ldan kun la snang ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:11602: de bzhina du 'jig rten gyi khams ganga du rgyal
NK094(nge)001:11603: ba'i sku gang la'ang gdung byung ba'i tshul de ltar
NK094(nge)001:11604: / da lta mi mjed kyi zhing khams gang 'dira
NK094(nge)001:11605: snang ba'i sgron ma sprul pa'i sku thub pa'i dbang
NK094(nge)001:11606: po dag mya ngan 'adsa pa'i sku gdung yanga sha
NK094(nge)001:11607: ri ram zhes su gragsa para 'gyur pa nyid de
NK094(nge)001:11608: / / gdung de yi bsod nams kyi rten nam
NK094(nge)001:11609: mos pa'am dad pa skyed nas 'gro ba sems can
NK094(nge)001:11610: 'dren pa'i don mdzad pa'i phrin las kyang bshad pa
NK094(nge)001:11611: de dag ji lta ba de bzhina no //
NK094(nge)001:11616: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11617: de la sogsa pa'i snyegs sdud kyi rgyal ba rnams
NK094(nge)001:11618: ni thub pa'i dbang po yan chad dang ma 'ongs
NK094(nge)001:11619: pa ste snga mar ranga byung ba'i 'od srung la
NK094(nge)001:11620: sogs pa dang / rjes thog tu da lta gansa pa rdzogs nas 'byung ba'i byams pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:11621: de nas seng ge la sogs pa dang bcas pa
NK094(nge)001:11622: rnams kun gyi sku gdung ni tshul mthun zhing gcig
NK094(nge)001:11623: para gyur pa yi sha ri ram du snang bas
NK094(nge)001:11625: de mi yul du ji ltar 'phel ba ni /
NK094(nge)001:11626: sku gdung de'i sa bon gyi byin rlabsa kyis /
NK094(nge)001:11627: gdung gi yona tan gyi cha lasa bdud rtsir 'phel
NK094(nge)001:11628: ba ni lho'i 'dzam bu'i gling gi sa khamsa kun
NK094(nge)001:11629: tu khyab para snang ste rgyu gdung gi byin rlabs
NK094(nge)001:11630: las byung ba'i phyir na ngo bo sra zhing mkhregsa
NK094(nge)001:11631: la dbyibs zlum po nyid de /
NK094(nge)001:11632: ming du tha skar rdo rjera rab tu gragsa shing
NK094(nge)001:11633: dbyibs dang che chung dang kha dog gi tshul yang
NK094(nge)001:11634: lgang bu zur gsum til gyi lgang bu dang 'dra
NK094(nge)001:11635: la / smin lugs gzhon pa'i tshe mar ram 'o mara snang la /
NK094(nge)001:11636: nar son par smin pa'i rtagsa sra zhing mkhregsa par 'gyur te /
NK094(nge)001:11637: tshad tsa na ka yi 'abru bzhina du dkar la
NK094(nge)001:11638: tsan tsam damra bas kha dog gsal zhing bzang ba'o
NK094(nge)001:11639: // de nyid bsgrubs nas zosa pa'i yona tan bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'byung ste /
NK094(nge)001:11640: lus sra ba sogs bdud rtsi sman gyi mchog tu gragsa shing grub pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:11645: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11646: rgyal ba'i rjes su 'tshob pa la'ang snang ba'i phyir
NK094(nge)001:11647: bshad pa de bzhina du rigs 'dzina rnams dang byang
NK094(nge)001:11649: mi yi lus su sprul pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:11650: gang zaga sa ba chos mig ldan pa'i shes rab kyi spyan can dang /
NK094(nge)001:11651: bsod namsa bsags pa'i dpal gyis zhing dag par gyur pa dag kyang /
NK094(nge)001:11652: sku 'das pa'i tshe sdong bu snying pora bcas te
NK094(nge)001:11653: phung po lnga zhugs la legs par sbyangsa pa'i phyi
NK094(nge)001:11654: na 'byung zhing skal ba can la snang ba ni
NK094(nge)001:11655: / la la dag la gdung sha ri rama dang /
NK094(nge)001:11656: la la dag la ringa bsrel dang sku la sogs pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:11657: de dag rnyed par dka' ba'i phyir skal ba ngana
NK094(nge)001:11658: pa phyogs gcig dag la snang zhing mthong bar mi
NK094(nge)001:11659: 'gyur ro // gal te la la zhig las dag
NK094(nge)001:11660: nas snang bar gyur na yanga 'phral du sgo gsum
NK094(nge)001:11661: gyi sbyor ba dag na spyod yul du'ang yun ci
NK094(nge)001:11662: tsam du bzhag par rtag tu sdod la /
NK094(nge)001:11663: 'phral spyod ma daga na nub cing gzhan du 'bros te mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
NK094(nge)001:11664: de nyid ji lta ba'i dbang las gyur zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:11665: rnal 'byor pa de la yida du 'onga ba dang
NK094(nge)001:11666: mi 'onga ba'i skyon yon 'byung ba'i ltas ni so
NK094(nge)001:11667: sor ston pa'i snga ltas kyi dbang ste dbyibs dang
NK094(nge)001:11669: snang mi snang du 'gyur bar byed do //
NK094(nge)001:11670: 'on kyang sku gdung ni chos nyid rtogs pa'i byin rlabs kyi rtags yin pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:11672: snod na 'dug pa'i yod pa rtag pa theg zug ma yina la /
NK094(nge)001:11673: meda la ngo bo chad pasa gtan du brlag par
NK094(nge)001:11674: yang yong ye mi 'gyur bas rnal 'byor pas lasa
NK094(nge)001:11675: dang sbyor ba rnams dag na mang du 'phel la
NK094(nge)001:11676: brtan pa dang / ma dag na nyung zhing 'grib
NK094(nge)001:11677: pa'i tshul la sbyor te de ltar shes pa'i rtags
NK094(nge)001:11678: yin pas dag na spel la ma dag na sbyong
NK094(nge)001:11679: brtan pa dang / ngo // bzhi pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:11682: lcags kyi gtun gyis yang mi tshigs //
NK094(nge)001:11683: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11684: des na dag pa las 'byung ba'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:11685: gdung de yanga snga mar bsod namsa dri ma med
NK094(nge)001:11686: par bsags te bsgom pa las byung ba'i dngos pos
NK094(nge)001:11687: dag pa yisa / skyes bu gang dag theg pa
NK094(nge)001:11688: chen po'i lam zab cing rgya cher mosa shing dad
NK094(nge)001:11689: dag pa yisa / pa dang / rnal 'byor gyi
NK094(nge)001:11690: don la rtse gcig tu dmigsa pa btud pa'i ting
NK094(nge)001:11692: rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rjesa ngang dang
NK094(nge)001:11693: mi phyed par sbrel ba dang lasa dang 'bras bu
NK094(nge)001:11695: zhen pa gnyis kyi rgyud rnams yongsa su dag pa la yang gdung 'abba cing 'byung ngo //
NK094(nge)001:11696: grangs dang tshad bstan pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:11697: de yanga rgyal ba dang rig 'dzin gyi khyad para
NK094(nge)001:11698: rima pasa bstan te gang zag gi cha yis dbye
NK094(nge)001:11699: ba ni / rgyal ba'i sku gdung sha ri rama nyid /
NK094(nge)001:11700: zhing khamsa kun tu khyab par 'byung ba ni /
NK094(nge)001:11701: dper na mgar ba dang bzos ni dbyibs zlumsa par byas pa bzhina du /
NK094(nge)001:11702: don la byas pa med pa lasa snang ba dag kyang /
NK094(nge)001:11703: kha dog dkar 'tsher mdoga gasla zhing 'od 'adzaga pa
NK094(nge)001:11704: 'dra ba tsan dmar gyi mdangsa su gasla ba yi
NK094(nge)001:11705: rnam par snang nas nam mkha'a ganga ba char bzhina
NK094(nge)001:11706: du 'abba bo // gzhan rigas 'dzina semsa dapa'a sprul pa'i gdung ni /
NK094(nge)001:11707: mdog dkar gsal grangs 'ag'a tsam du 'byung la /
NK094(nge)001:11708: ganga zaga sa pa'i rtagsa chen po ni /
NK094(nge)001:11709: mdog snga ma dang mnyam la grangs ni gcig gam
NK094(nge)001:11710: gsum mam gnyis sam gsum dang gcig ni bzhi yin
NK094(nge)001:11711: la / la lara lnga'am kha cig la bcu 'byung zhing /
NK094(nge)001:11712: gdung gi yon tan de ni bshad pa de ltar dang tshul 'di ltar 'gyur ro //
NK094(nge)001:11713: de yang sra zhing mkhregsa pa rdo rje dang 'dra
NK094(nge)001:11714: bar lcagsa kyi gtun gyis yang mi tshigsa pa nyid
NK094(nge)001:11719: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11721: de ltar gdung dang ring bsrel 'di dag phebsa shing
NK094(nge)001:11722: 'phel ba'i yon tan gyis gzhan la phan pa yang
NK094(nge)001:11723: gang dang gang du babsa pa yi /
NK094(nge)001:11724: yul khamsa de dag thamsa cad du nad dang mi
NK094(nge)001:11725: nges pa dang bgegsa rnams zhi zhing gnod sbyin dang
NK094(nge)001:11726: srina po sogs ma rungsa pa dang 'jigs byed drag
NK094(nge)001:11727: po gtum po'ang lhan nera zhi bar 'gyur la /
NK094(nge)001:11728: rgyal po 'khrugsa pa dang 'byung khams 'khrugsa pa dang yul khamsa 'khrugsa pa'ang zhi bar 'gyur zhing /
NK094(nge)001:11729: 'bras bu lo tog 'phel ba dang smin cing yid du 'onga ba thamsa cad 'byung ngo //
NK094(nge)001:11730: yula de'i damngas rnams dang rgyal po yi yang sa
NK094(nge)001:11731: bona thamsa cad khye'u'am bu phor 'phel bar 'gyur te
NK094(nge)001:11732: / bder zhes bde bar btsas shing mtshan dang ldan
NK094(nge)001:11733: la rigsa mthor zhes mtho bar ni gyur pa'i bu
NK094(nge)001:11735: gdung bcangs pa'am rgyud la yod pa'am byung ba'i yon tan yang /
NK094(nge)001:11736: 'di dag su la 'chang ba rnams rigsa 'dzina gyi sa dang skal pa mnyam zhing /
NK094(nge)001:11738: 'khora los bsgyur rgyal dag dang mnyam ste de yi
NK094(nge)001:11739: dgos pa phun sum tshogs pa'i dgongas pa'i don bzang
NK094(nge)001:11741: tshe ring ba dang dgos 'dod skongsa pa dang las rnams 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK094(nge)001:11742: de nas phyin chad bla na med pa'i byang chub
NK094(nge)001:11743: kyi sa la rega pa'i rtagsa chen po'ang yina no
NK094(nge)001:11744: // gazhana yang yona tan bsam gyis mi khyab pa
NK094(nge)001:11745: de lta bu'i tshul dag 'byung ste gdung dang ring
NK094(nge)001:11746: bsrel rang gi rang bzhin du gnas pa'i yona tan
NK094(nge)001:11755: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11756: de nyid sgrub pa gang snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:11757: spyir gdung bsgrubsa na bsgrub pa'i yona tan bsam gyis mi khyab cing tshad med pas bsgrub pa'ang /
NK094(nge)001:11758: 'gro drug gi semsa can gyi rnam pa thams cad la'ang /
NK094(nge)001:11759: byang chub snying po 'bras bu'i ngo bor gnas pa de nyid yoda pasa /
NK094(nge)001:11760: de nyid rtsol ba tsam gyi rgyu yin te /
NK094(nge)001:11761: de'i phyir bshad pa bzhin du me yi las kyi
NK094(nge)001:11762: bya ba yisa lnga phung gang sbyangsa na yang gdung
NK094(nge)001:11763: re re med cing mi 'byung ba mi srid do
NK094(nge)001:11764: // des na lha rje zur chung gis rgya bor
NK094(nge)001:11765: bye'u shi ba blug mer bsregs pas byang chub snying
NK094(nge)001:11766: por grub pa'i rtags mang du byung skad do //
NK094(nge)001:11769: nye ba'i bsnyen pa dang sgrub pa thun mong du bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:11771: bsgrub pa chen por dngos grub blang ba /
NK094(nge)001:11772: mchod pa yon tan dang bcas pa /
NK094(nge)001:11773: de nyid bsgrub rdzas su bcangs pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:11777: ga'u'i nang du btsa' //zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11778: de ltar gang byung ba de la brten te 'di dag bsgrub para bya ba yang /
NK094(nge)001:11779: shel snod kyi za ma tog gi nang du bsdus
NK094(nge)001:11780: nas legs par bcugs te rdo rje rgya gram gyi
NK094(nge)001:11781: phyag rgya'i dngos su rgyas btab la kha bcad nas
NK094(nge)001:11782: bzhag go // gdung gcig po de yang de ltar
NK094(nge)001:11783: shel gyi ga'u'i nang du btsa' la stegs bu la
NK094(nge)001:11784: bzhag go // bzhag pa'o // gnyis pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:11788: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11789: de nas bsgrub pa pos 'dun pasa de la gang
NK094(nge)001:11790: 'dod pa'i smon lam gadba pa dang sgrib pa sbyong
NK094(nge)001:11792: 'dod pa'i don la gsola ba gdab pa byas la
NK094(nge)001:11793: de nas ting nge 'dzin gyi ngang nas bzlas pa'i
NK094(nge)001:11794: 'phro 'adu bya'o // de'ang bdag rigs kyi skur gsal
NK094(nge)001:11795: bas 'phro 'adu bya ba'i cho ga yang sngags bzlas
NK094(nge)001:11796: tsam na gdung gi 'od zer gyis nam mkha'a gang
NK094(nge)001:11797: ba'i sha ri rama mang po zhing khamas rab 'byams
NK094(nge)001:11798: gang ba'i phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba ji snyed pa lasa
NK094(nge)001:11799: byung ba'i gdung bsdus la char gyi rgyun bzhin du
NK094(nge)001:11800: ga'u de la dabba par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:11801: de tshe rtse gcig tu bzlas pa gsung gi gdung sngags rgyun du bzla ba ni /
NK094(nge)001:11802: ma ha sha ri ram gi li h'u /
NK094(nge)001:11804: dang po lnga pa'i tha ma bzhag /de 'og bdun pa'i bzhi pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:11805: de 'og bdun pa'i dang po ste /
NK094(nge)001:11806: de 'og dbyangs kyi bdun pa bzhag /de 'og k+aa li drug gnyis pa //
NK094(nge)001:11807: lnga pa'i tha ma sbyar ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:11808: de 'og k+aa li gsum pa la //
NK094(nge)001:11809: dbyangs kyi gsum pas steng nas brgyan //
NK094(nge)001:11810: de 'og dbyangs kyi dgu pa bzhag /tha ma thugs dang ldan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:11811: grangs med bar chad med par bzlas //
NK094(nge)001:11813: sngags 'di la dpe rnying la la dang spar ma na /
NK094(nge)001:11814: ma h+aa sha ri ram gyi li h'u /
NK094(nge)001:11816: de ltar grangsa ni tshad med par rtags thon thon
NK094(nge)001:11817: du bzlas zhing 'phro 'du bar chad pa med par
NK094(nge)001:11818: bzlas par bya'o // gsum pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:11822: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11823: rtags ji lta bu 'byung snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:11824: gdung phyi rol nas mchog tu gsal zhing 'tsher bar mthong ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:11825: 'od kyi zer phreng nyi zer bzhin du za zi
NK094(nge)001:11826: dang brang breng du snang bar 'gyur bar za ma
NK094(nge)001:11827: tog gi phyi rola nas kyang gsal bar mngon par
NK094(nge)001:11829: de bzhin du gdung 'gul zhing dang po gcig las grangs mang por 'pheela ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:11830: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK094(nge)001:11831: byang chub semsa dpa' dang riga 'dzin rnams kyi sku'i
NK094(nge)001:11832: gzugsa brnyan shel gyi za ma tog dang gdung gi
NK094(nge)001:11833: snod bcud de gnyis lasa ni gsal bar snang zhing
NK094(nge)001:11834: bdag la zhal ston par 'gyur ro //
NK094(nge)001:11835: rtags dang po rab gwa'u'i snod de khengas pa yina la /
NK094(nge)001:11836: gnyis pa 'bring snod phyed tsam khengs pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:11838: tha ma'ang grangsa 'agsa 'phel bar 'gyur pa ni nges pa 'byung ngo //
NK094(nge)001:11843: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11844: de daga ni grub pa'i rtagsa chen po nyid de /
NK094(nge)001:11845: de yi tshe 'od de bdag gi thugs la bsdus la dngosa grub blang bar bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:11846: dngos grub thob pa'i yon tan gang snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:11847: thob pa'i yon tan ni bsam gyis mi khyab ste /
NK094(nge)001:11848: tshe 'dira rig pa 'dzina pa'i sa la gnas shing
NK094(nge)001:11849: rim gyis rgyal ba dag dang mnyam para 'gyur la
NK094(nge)001:11850: / zhar lasa byung ba'i yon tan yang /
NK094(nge)001:11851: 'gro ba sems can kun gyi dona spyod pa'i mdzad
NK094(nge)001:11852: pa byang chub semsa dapa'a che rnams dang mtshungs ba
NK094(nge)001:11858: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11859: dam tshig nyams ma nyams brtags shing bskang ba'i phyir
NK094(nge)001:11860: rgyun du de ltar grub pa'i gdung de la mchod
NK094(nge)001:11862: mchod na yona tan dam pa mang po 'byung bas so //
NK094(nge)001:11863: ji ltar mchod para bya ba'i thabs kyi cho ga
NK094(nge)001:11864: yang sngon du sgrib pa sbyangsa shing bshags pa dang
NK094(nge)001:11865: bsod namsa kyi dpung bskyed de /
NK094(nge)001:11866: rang gi rgyud dag para byas nasa ni /
NK094(nge)001:11867: zla ba'i dus ni thamsa cada kyi yang tshes bcu
NK094(nge)001:11868: drug gi cha la bab ste zla ba yongs su
NK094(nge)001:11870: bdag nyid gciga pu semsa dmigs pa'i yul la rtse gcig tu gyur par byas nas mchod pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:11871: za ma tog gdung dang bcas pa daga rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mora btagsa par byas te /
NK094(nge)001:11872: mchod pa sna tshogs pas mchod cing ji ltar 'doda par smon lam gadba par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:11873: de ltar mchod pa des ni 'doda pa thamsa cad skongsa shing don kun 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK094(nge)001:11878: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11879: de ltar gdung de ni rnal 'byor pa skal ldan gyi /
NK094(nge)001:11880: dpe yida bzhina gyi nor bu rin po che lta
NK094(nge)001:11881: bur rnal 'byor sgrub pa'i dam rdzasa kyi mchog tu
NK094(nge)001:11882: spyod cing legs par bcangs na 'dod pa thams cad
NK094(nge)001:11883: 'byung ba'i phyir dgos pa khyad par du 'phags pa'i
NK094(nge)001:11884: ming gisa gdung re med du mi rung ba lta
NK094(nge)001:11885: bur snang ngo // gsum pa thabs kyi spyod pa'i mjug sdud ni /
NK094(nge)001:11886: ji ltar ro dag /ces pa nas /
NK094(nge)001:11888: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11889: spyod pa'i grangs ni bshad pa ltar /
NK094(nge)001:11890: ji ltar ro langs dag gser du 'gyur bar bsgrub pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:11892: go mtshon du bsgrub pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:11893: de bzhin du lnga phung me yis bsregsa sbyangsa la
NK094(nge)001:11894: sogs pa bzhina du dngosa por spyod pa ji snyed
NK094(nge)001:11896: de kho na nyid kyi dam tshig dam pa yin
NK094(nge)001:11897: pa lasa mi g.yo bas ji ltar spyad kyang skyon
NK094(nge)001:11898: med de / des na de la sogsa pa mtha' yasa pa'i spyod pa mchog kun gyis shig pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:11900: shi ba slong ba rtog pa'i zug rngu sbyong ba /
NK094(nge)001:11901: mtshan ma'i rgyud sbyong ba bzhi'am /
NK094(nge)001:11902: bshad pa'i 'khor ba'i dngosa po bzhi la gnas shing spyod la mi 'dzin pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:11903: rdo rje semsa dpa'i de kho na nyid rgyal ba'i
NK094(nge)001:11904: thugs kyi chos nyid dam pa yin pa'i phyir de
NK094(nge)001:11905: ltar spyod pa nyid ni rmad du byung ba'i spyod
NK094(nge)001:11906: pa dam pa'i phul du gyur pa yang dag pa'o
NK094(nge)001:11907: // gsum pa gces par gdams pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:11911: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11912: la spyod pas dor ba'i dpe gang zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:11913: dpe ji ltar na glang po chen po chur 'jug pa na /
NK094(nge)001:11914: tsham tshom gyi chagsa thogsa dang 'jigsa pa yong ye
NK094(nge)001:11915: med para tshad pas gdung bas chur dag'a ba'i 'jug
NK094(nge)001:11916: cing longsa spyod pa la brod pa'i tshul gyis tshur
NK094(nge)001:11917: la mi ldog par chu'i pha rol tu phyin pa
NK094(nge)001:11919: rnal 'byor dam pas gsang ba zab mo'i spyod pa'i
NK094(nge)001:11920: bslab rim la ngesa para spyod pa yang mnyam nyid
NK094(nge)001:11921: gsang ba'i brtul zhugsa kyi rgya mtsho'i chur 'jug pa
NK094(nge)001:11922: la rtogs pa'i shes rab kyi rtsal chen po sbyong
NK094(nge)001:11923: ba'i phyir don gyi bogs 'don la brod pa'i tshul
NK094(nge)001:11924: gyis thogsa chagsa gang yang med par la dora bar
NK094(nge)001:11925: byed pa'o // des na bslab pa'i mtha' dam pa
NK094(nge)001:11926: spyod pa barlanga po la don phul du byung bar
NK094(nge)001:11927: spyad par bya ba'i thabsa 'di la gomsa pa klung
NK094(nge)001:11928: du gyur bar byed pa ni shin tu gces pa
NK094(nge)001:11929: byed pa'o // nyid do // zhes gdams par mdzad do //
NK094(nge)001:11934: grogsa po dag /bshad pa de dag ni /
NK094(nge)001:11935: spyod pas la dor bar bslab pa'i tshul ma nor bar bgros par shes par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:11936: zhes bka' stsal pa nyid do //
NK094(nge)001:11938: sangsa rgyas kun gyi dgongsa pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po lasa /
NK094(nge)001:11939: rnal 'byor dam pa'i rjes su spyod pas la dor
NK094(nge)001:11940: te 'jug thabs mchog gi bslab pa bstan pa'i le'u
NK094(nge)001:11941: zhes bya ste bdun cu rtsa gciga pa nyid rnam
NK094(nge)001:11942: par 'grel te bshad pa'o ////bdun pa thag lta bas
NK094(nge)001:11943: gcad par khyung chen po nam mkha' la lding ba
NK094(nge)001:11944: ltar bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK094(nge)001:11953: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11955: thag lta bas bcad pa gang snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:11956: de nas yang ston pa gsang ba pa'i badga pos /
NK094(nge)001:11957: spyod pa mi 'ching ba'i lta ba rjes thogs su bstan pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:11958: grogs kyi sems dpa' lus damna pa can gyi dama pa rnams la smras pa /
NK094(nge)001:11959: kye grogsa po daga /ces bos nas /
NK094(nge)001:11960: gang dri ma thams cad dang bral ba'i sa yi
NK094(nge)001:11961: rtse mor phyin par byed pa'i thabs kyi snying po
NK094(nge)001:11962: lta bas thag bcad par bya ba ni /
NK094(nge)001:11963: nye bar bstan pa 'di lta ste /
NK094(nge)001:11964: lta ba'i ngo bo gang yin pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:11965: dgongas pa dam pa sems kyi chos nyid ji bzhin
NK094(nge)001:11966: pa'i de kho na nyid mthong ba'i shes rab kyi
NK094(nge)001:11969: de kho na nyid la thams cad 'dus par thag bcad pa /
NK094(nge)001:11970: de ltar gcig chod du rtogs pa'i yon tan bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:11971: rim gyis pa la ma nges pa'i 'jigs skyon yod tshul bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:11972: gzhi ji bzhin du thag chod pa rang gi ngo bo bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:11974: de kho na nyid la bslab pa kun 'dus par dam bca' ba /
NK094(nge)001:11975: de nyid gtan tshigs kyis nges tshul bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:11980: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:11981: de'i yon tan gyi gtan tshigs kyis mchog tu bstan pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:11982: de ltar dam bca' bar byed pa de ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:11984: dgongas pa dam pa ma nor ma bcos mi 'gyur
NK094(nge)001:11985: ba'i de kho na nyid gcig la bslab pa 'di
NK094(nge)001:11986: ni thams cad kyi rtsa bar gyur pasa /
NK094(nge)001:11988: brjod bya ngo bo dang rnam grangs bsam gyis mi khyab /
NK094(nge)001:11989: rjod byed theg pa rim dgus chos tshul bsam gyis mi khyab /
NK094(nge)001:11990: gang des don mtshon pa'i sgo yang bsam gyis mi
NK094(nge)001:11991: khyab par gyur pa'i chos thams cad la bslab pa
NK094(nge)001:11992: nyid las bya ba gzhan med pas na rim pa
NK094(nge)001:11993: dbang gis bgrod pa'ang 'di la 'dus pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:11995: dgongs pa de kho na nyid gcig po 'di la makhasa shing 'di'i don ji lta bar rig na /
NK094(nge)001:11996: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chos kyi rnam pa spyi
NK094(nge)001:11997: dang rang gi mtshan nyid thams cad ma 'dres par
NK094(nge)001:11998: lhun rdzogs su gsal te don kun la makhasa pas
NK094(nge)001:11999: na / de las phul du dbyung du med pa'i
NK094(nge)001:12000: phyir phul du mkhas pas dbyung ba'ang 'di la 'dus
NK094(nge)001:12001: na / pa'o // sgom lam lta bur /
NK094(nge)001:12002: dgongs pa de kho na nyid ma nor ba'i ngang de la gomsa par byas na /
NK094(nge)001:12003: sgom pa gzhan thams cad 'di'i yan lag yin pas /
NK094(nge)001:12004: 'di'i don la goms pa kho nas /
NK094(nge)001:12005: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chos kyi don kun la
NK094(nge)001:12006: goms pa nyid las gzhan zhig la gomsa par byar
NK094(nge)001:12007: med pas nyams su ting nge 'dzin gyis blang ba'ang
NK094(nge)001:12009: de kho na nyid du rig pa klong gdal ba
NK094(nge)001:12010: de lasa ma 'adsa na nyams pa ka nas dag
NK094(nge)001:12011: pas bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dama pa bsrungsa pa'ang
NK094(nge)001:12012: de las 'dar med pas gzhi dam tshig gis gzung
NK094(nge)001:12014: de kho na nyid gnyis su med pa de la
NK094(nge)001:12015: blo 'jug pa med par zhugsa na thams cad dang
NK094(nge)001:12016: rig pa tha mi dad cing 'jug sgo kun gyi
NK094(nge)001:12017: rtsa bar gyur pas bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chos
NK094(nge)001:12018: kyi sgor zhugsa pa'ang de las med pas don man
NK094(nge)001:12019: ngag gis bsgrub pa'ang 'di la 'dus pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:12020: de kho na nyid de la rig pa gnyis med du rol bas spyod na /
NK094(nge)001:12021: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i yo byad la spyad do
NK094(nge)001:12022: cog thams cad chos nyid kyi mdzad pa 'ching grol
NK094(nge)001:12023: med pa'i don du 'gyur bas la spyod pas dor
NK094(nge)001:12025: mthar lam lta bur de kho na nyid bzhin du
NK094(nge)001:12026: rig pa son bar gyur te mngona du byas na
NK094(nge)001:12027: / bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i lasa rgya mtsho snyed
NK094(nge)001:12028: kyi bsgrub par bya ba dang byas pa thams cad
NK094(nge)001:12029: kyi mchog tu gyur cing gzhan btsal rgyu med pas
NK094(nge)001:12030: mdo don gcig tu bsdu ba'ang 'di nyid du 'dus
NK094(nge)001:12031: / pa'o // de kho na nyid chos nyid ji
NK094(nge)001:12032: bzhin pa'i don de nyid ma nor bar gzhan la
NK094(nge)001:12033: / pa'o // bstan na / chos kyi sgo mo
NK094(nge)001:12034: dapaga tu med pa kun gyi grub mtha'i don yin
NK094(nge)001:12035: pas thams cad kun bstan pa nyid de /
NK094(nge)001:12036: de las bstan bya gzhan med pas sgo kun nas bsdur ba'ang 'di la 'dus pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:12038: de kho na nyid kyi don de nyid ma nor
NK094(nge)001:12039: ma bslad de phyin ci ma loga para thos na
NK094(nge)001:12040: / de las bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chos kyi
NK094(nge)001:12041: sgo thos par bya ba'i don lhag ma gzhan med
NK094(nge)001:12042: pas rgyud thos pa dgrol ba'ang 'di la 'dus pa'o
NK094(nge)001:12043: / // mthar lam rdzogs pa lta bur /
NK094(nge)001:12044: de kho na nyid de shes rab kyis spyan gyis
NK094(nge)001:12045: cir yang ma mthong bar mthong ste mngona du gyur
NK094(nge)001:12046: na / dapaga tu med pa'i rgyal ba ril gyi
NK094(nge)001:12047: dngos gzhi yin pas kun gyi zhal mthong ba'i mchog
NK094(nge)001:12048: tu nges pas thag lta bas gcad pa'ang 'di la
NK094(nge)001:12054: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:12055: de gtan tshigs ci'i phyir te /
NK094(nge)001:12056: de dag gi don la yid ches par gang gis bya zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:12057: de ltar yon tan lnga gnyis de dag thamsa cad kyi bcud du bya ba'i rtsa ba'am /
NK094(nge)001:12058: 'bras bu'i snying por bya ba ni de kho na nyid lhun gyis grub pa nyid de /
NK094(nge)001:12059: de lasa gzhan med pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:12060: gzhan ni yan lag dang rgyu tsam yin pas /
NK094(nge)001:12061: 'di las lhag pa'i don rgyal bas kyang mi rnyed pa'i don gyis gsal te /
NK094(nge)001:12063: so so'i theg pa'i sgo rnams la //
NK094(nge)001:12064: 'jug pa la sogs ma sbyangs kyang //
NK094(nge)001:12065: kun gyi rtsa ba 'dir bcad pas //
NK094(nge)001:12066: gcig ste tha dad yongs kyis med //
NK094(nge)001:12068: rang bzhin med par kun gcig pa'i //
NK094(nge)001:12069: bdag med phyogs bral lhun gyis grub //
NK094(nge)001:12070: gcig las rnam grangs ngang gis med //
NK094(nge)001:12071: tha snyad dag par yongs chud na //
NK094(nge)001:12072: nges pa'i don chen de nyid do //
NK094(nge)001:12074: bdag dang gzhan du mi gnyis pas //
NK094(nge)001:12075: bdag nyid bdag gi rang bzhin te //
NK094(nge)001:12076: sangs rgyas zhes bya gzhan na med //
NK094(nge)001:12077: bdag nyid lhun grub dbang phyug che //
NK094(nge)001:12078: zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK094(nge)001:12082: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:12085: dam bca' dang gtan tshigs de basa na 'di ltar
NK094(nge)001:12086: bshad pa'i yon tan gyi tshul de bzhin du yod
NK094(nge)001:12087: pas na / mthong lam thob nas lhun gyis grub
NK094(nge)001:12088: pa'i de bzhina nyid kyi dona mthong ste mngon sum
NK094(nge)001:12089: du rtogs na theg pa 'og ma ltar lta ba
NK094(nge)001:12090: gzhan gyis mthong ba thamsa cad bde ba chen po
NK094(nge)001:12091: ma yin par snang ba sgyu ma lta bur shar
NK094(nge)001:12092: bar yina pas bri ta tsam du bstan pa dang
NK094(nge)001:12093: pas na / / de nas sgom lam gyi dus
NK094(nge)001:12094: su lhun grub de bzhina nyid kyi ngang du rig
NK094(nge)001:12095: pa de nyid brten pa med par gansa na /
NK094(nge)001:12096: sa lam gyi rim pa rnams dang gansa yul thamsa
NK094(nge)001:12097: cad rang snang sgyu ma de bzhin nyid yina pa
NK094(nge)001:12098: dang / de nas mthar lam du zin te rtogs
NK094(nge)001:12099: pa de nyid mthar thug pa'i go 'phang dam pa
NK094(nge)001:12100: ma bslad pa'i don du rig pa'i rtsal 'phang rnyed
NK094(nge)001:12101: de mchog tu 'aphagas par gyur na /
NK094(nge)001:12102: rgyu'i theg pa'i grub pa bla na meda pa'i mtho btsun chos kyi sku man chad dang /
NK094(nge)001:12103: 'jig rten pa'i mchog ril mtha'a dag thams cad rdzun
NK094(nge)001:12104: pa sgyu ma ltar mi bden ba yin par rtogs
NK094(nge)001:12105: pa'o // de nas rig pa de bzhin nyid du
NK094(nge)001:12106: lhun gyis grub pa 'di la spyod yul dag par
NK094(nge)001:12107: rtogs pa'i yon tan 'byung ba'i gtan tshigs bstan te
NK094(nge)001:12108: pa'o // / rang gi rig pa ji bzhin pa
NK094(nge)001:12109: las de bzhina nyid du nges pa'i gdengs tshud de
NK094(nge)001:12110: mi 'gyur bar blo gros la brtan pa thob phana
NK094(nge)001:12111: pa'o // / chad / gang zag damna pa'i lus
NK094(nge)001:12112: can yin yang che chung ma dmigs pas spa bkong
NK094(nge)001:12113: zhing zhum pa meda pa de rnams kyang gsang don
NK094(nge)001:12114: zab mo'i bden pa mthong ba'i yon tan no //
NK094(nge)001:12115: de kho na nyid ji bzhina pa'i chos nyid rdzogs
NK094(nge)001:12116: par rtogs pas skyed du bya ba med par thag
NK094(nge)001:12118: 'khor ba ma spang bral bas 'jiga rten gyi lus
NK094(nge)001:12119: na gnas pa nyid kyang mtha' kun grol bas chos
NK094(nge)001:12120: kyi sku chen po nyid du rang gsal ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:12121: de'i phyir bdag gi blo ji bzhin par gnad chud
NK094(nge)001:12122: pas dam para ngesa kyang ched du bya ba med
NK094(nge)001:12123: par shes nas rtsol sgrub dang bral bzhin 'gro don
NK094(nge)001:12124: mi 'dor te 'jiga rten pa'i spyod yul du'ang 'jug
NK094(nge)001:12125: cing / byas pa la bya ba dang ngal dub
NK094(nge)001:12126: med pas 'khor ba'i srid pa mtha'a med la skyo
NK094(nge)001:12127: ba med la yid mi 'byung ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:12128: ji snyed pa'i las tshul mu mtha'a yasa pa thams
NK094(nge)001:12129: cad kun kyang don de bzhin nyid gcig tu rdzogsa
NK094(nge)001:12130: par rtogs pa'o // lta ba'i nyams rtags ni /
NK094(nge)001:12131: rang gi sems kyi dkyil 'khor 'od gsal ba'i ngang du rtogs pa'i skyes bu la ni /
NK094(nge)001:12132: ma bsgoms kyang bdud dang srin po'i gnas kyi khamas
NK094(nge)001:12133: la yang nyam mi nga bas 'jigs pa med cing
NK094(nge)001:12134: / mi bzad dmyal ba'i khamas la yang bag mi
NK094(nge)001:12135: tsha bas 'jig rten la yang gang yang med pa'o
NK094(nge)001:12136: / // des 'doda pa'i yon tan gyi dngosa po gang la spyad kyang /
NK094(nge)001:12137: spyad pa thams cad dbyingsa su sbyor te zin chags kyi nad med pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:12138: de bas na brgyud nas mi shes pa gcig shes
NK094(nge)001:12139: par bya ba dang bral ba'i gsang sngags cig char
NK094(nge)001:12140: du ngesa pa'i don bshad pa bzhin du mthong zhing
NK094(nge)001:12141: rtogs na / dbu ma sogs tha snyad kyi bya
NK094(nge)001:12142: bas rimas kyis sbyong ba'i grub pa'i mtha' rtogs pa
NK094(nge)001:12143: rtogs na / dag ni / bri ta bas baslu
NK094(nge)001:12144: brid mkhan dang 'dra ba lta bu'i phyir rtogs pa
NK094(nge)001:12145: mchog tu che bar bsnyad do //
NK094(nge)001:12146: de lta bu'i don de ma rtogs kyang mos pa'i yon tan ni /
NK094(nge)001:12147: de kho na nyid cig char ba'i don de la gdeng ma rnyed kyang /
NK094(nge)001:12148: rgyun du mosa pa tsam gyis kyang de ma thag par 'phrad pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12149: khamas gsum gyi sa bon rnams ldang mi nus par
NK094(nge)001:12150: zil gyis gnon para 'gyur ba'i phyir yon tan mchog
NK094(nge)001:12152: de bas na dus gsum du klung du gyur te
NK094(nge)001:12153: lta ba rnam par dag pa'i don dang ma bral
NK094(nge)001:12154: ba ni smos ci dgos te rnam rtog dang lta
NK094(nge)001:12155: ngan zil gyis gnon pa'i lta bas khyad par du
NK094(nge)001:12157: de nyid dpe yis mtshon pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:12158: dper na seng ge'i phrug gu dang khyung gi sgong nga daga /snga ma mig ma bye zhing /
NK094(nge)001:12159: phyi ma nam makhara rang rtsal blangsa te ma lding kyang /
NK094(nge)001:12160: seng phrug mngal dang bral ma thag gcan gzan kun skrag pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12161: sgong nga'ang shun dang bral ma thag mkha' la thogs pa med par 'gro ba ltar /
NK094(nge)001:12162: rnal 'byor pa de kho na nyid ngesa te yang
NK094(nge)001:12163: dag para rtogs pas gang shar rang grol du gyur
NK094(nge)001:12164: pa de dag dman pa'i lus dang ma bral bar
NK094(nge)001:12166: go 'aphanga dama pa mchog gi ngang rtogs pa de
NK094(nge)001:12167: nyid du brtan pa las mi 'gyur bar rigs ngesa
NK094(nge)001:12168: pasa 'khor ba'i g.yang sa ci la'ang bag mi tsha
NK094(nge)001:12169: ba kho na'o // gsum pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:12173: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:12174: rim gyis pa'i lta ba dag gol ba'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:12175: de ltar rtogs par mi nus par blo dman pa'i
NK094(nge)001:12176: mi'i mtshan nyid can gang dag don la mdongs te
NK094(nge)001:12177: cig char mthong ba'i mig dang mi ldan par rimas
NK094(nge)001:12178: kyis 'jug pa nyan thos rnams yul sems so sor
NK094(nge)001:12179: snang ba kun rdzob rdul tsam dang /
NK094(nge)001:12180: don dam shes pa skad cig ma re rer yod
NK094(nge)001:12181: par 'dod pa'i mtshan mara lta ba la spyod pa
NK094(nge)001:12182: can dang / rang rgyal ba yul rdzun pa sgyu ma tsam las med par 'dod pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12183: rnam rig pa yul nyid dmigsa pa'i shes pa rang snang bar 'dod pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12184: dbu ma pas kun rdzob sgyu ma tsam du yul
NK094(nge)001:12185: sems so sor snang yang dam par mi dmigas par
NK094(nge)001:12186: lta ba dang / byang chub don du gnyer te
NK094(nge)001:12187: ched du bsgrub pa dang sa'i rim par bgrod para
NK094(nge)001:12188: byed pa'i kri yog pa yi grub mtha' la gnas
NK094(nge)001:12189: pa de daga /gsang ba chen po'i man ngag gi
NK094(nge)001:12190: bye braga ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi gsang gnad yang
NK094(nge)001:12193: rtogs pa'i lta ba gnyis la brten nas don chen
NK094(nge)001:12194: po'i gdeng med para stong rtog des don la dmigs
NK094(nge)001:12195: nas 'jug pa yi don mchog ma mthong ba'i blun
NK094(nge)001:12196: po de dag 'bras bu chen po med pas stongsa
NK094(nge)001:12197: pa ste rgyal ba'i go 'phang dngos su thob pa'i
NK094(nge)001:12198: thabs dama par ngesa pa ga la yina te ma
NK094(nge)001:12199: yin pas rnam grol bla na med pa mi thob
NK094(nge)001:12200: pa ni dper na gacana gazana tha ma'i phru gu
NK094(nge)001:12202: wa ni ma yang 'jigs skrag dang bcas la bu
NK094(nge)001:12203: yang skrag cing dangngas pa'i ranga bzhina yin pa ji
NK094(nge)001:12209: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:12210: rtogs tshad rang gi ngo bo ni /
NK094(nge)001:12211: mtha' yasa shing ji snyed par snang ba'i 'khor 'das
NK094(nge)001:12212: kyis bsdus pa'i chos rnams kun gyi de kho na
NK094(nge)001:12213: nyid kyi ranga bzhina ji ltar gansa pa bzhina du
NK094(nge)001:12214: ma bcos ma bslad par phyin ci ma log par
NK094(nge)001:12215: rtogs pa'i thabs chen po dang ldan pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:12216: dper na ri bo chen po'i kha nas lhung na ltung bar mi bya snyam yang ltung ba ltar /
NK094(nge)001:12217: thabs chen pos grol bar mi bya snyam yang grol bar 'gyur te /
NK094(nge)001:12218: grol du med par thams cad de bzhina nyid du
NK094(nge)001:12219: shes pa nyid 'ching ba dang bral bas thag chod
NK094(nge)001:12225: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:12226: thag lta bas bcad pa gces par gdams pa'i dpe nye bar mtshon pa yang /
NK094(nge)001:12227: ji ltar na khyung chen po nam mkha'a la lding ba nyid /
NK094(nge)001:12228: 'adba gshog gi rtsal gyis gnam 'aphanga gcod pas /
NK094(nge)001:12229: ri brag dang chu klung mtha' yasa pa yod kyang /
NK094(nge)001:12230: gshog rtsal gyis 'phur ba'i rlabsa 'oga tu kun nas chud pa ltar /
NK094(nge)001:12231: don yang rnal 'byor pa chos nyid mnyam pa nyid
NK094(nge)001:12232: kyi nam mkha'a la lta ba'i rtsal gyis 'gro ba
NK094(nge)001:12233: nyid / theg pa'i spyod sgo mtha'a yasa pa ji snyed du snang ba kun kyang /
NK094(nge)001:12234: ji bzhina ma bcos pa'i dona du nges par rtogs pa nyid kyis na /
NK094(nge)001:12235: mthar 'bras dam pa'i go 'aphanga ji lta bar rtogs pa'i rlabsa kyis thag gcad pa nyid de /
NK094(nge)001:12236: 'di ni re ba dang dogas pa yi d+r+wa bar
NK094(nge)001:12237: chud pa'i the tshom gyi 'phyang mo nyug gzhi med
NK094(nge)001:12238: du gcod pa'i nges pa dam pa ste /
NK094(nge)001:12239: 'di lta bu'i gnas lugs dama pa nyid la ma
NK094(nge)001:12240: nor bar lta ba yi snying po'i go 'aphanga gcod
NK094(nge)001:12241: pa ni mchog tu ngesa para gces pa kho na
NK094(nge)001:12245: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:12246: grogsa po dag bshad pa de dag ni /
NK094(nge)001:12247: sa yi rtse mor bgrod pa'i lta bas thag yongsa
NK094(nge)001:12248: su gcod pa nyid phyin ci ma log par legs
NK094(nge)001:12249: par bgrosa pa yin para shes par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:12252: damna pa dam pa rnams re dogas med para lta
NK094(nge)001:12253: bas thag chod pa'i go 'aphanga dam pa mthar thug
NK094(nge)001:12254: pa legs par thoba par gyur to //
NK094(nge)001:12255: 'di la kun mkhyen dam pa rin po ches /
NK094(nge)001:12256: 'o na lta ba la le'u zhe drug par skol
NK094(nge)001:12257: mdo bcu gnyis kyi skabs su lta ba gcig byung
NK094(nge)001:12258: / le'u re gsum pa'i sngags kyi gzhi bcu'i skabs su lta ba gcig byung /
NK094(nge)001:12259: bslab pa'i mtha' bcu'i le'u don gnyis pa thag lta
NK094(nge)001:12260: bas gcad pa'i skabs 'dir yang lta ba gcig byung
NK094(nge)001:12261: bas bldabs sa ma snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:12262: ngo bo gcig la mtshon tshul ma 'dres te /
NK094(nge)001:12263: skol mdo bcu gnyis kyi skabs kyi lta ba ni /
NK094(nge)001:12264: sngags kyi theg pa gong 'og shan dbye ba'i lta ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:12265: gzhi bcu'i lta ba de lta ba rtogs nas 'bras
NK094(nge)001:12266: bu thob pa'i gzhi yin pa'i ngos nas bstan pa'o
NK094(nge)001:12267: // bslab pa'i mtha' bcu'i lta ba 'di lam pa'i bslab bya'i ngos nas bzhag pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:12268: zhes bka' stsal bar mdzad do //
NK094(nge)001:12270: sangsa rgyas kun gyi dgongsa pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po lasa /
NK094(nge)001:12271: lta ba'i gdeng nges te re dogs dang yin min
NK094(nge)001:12272: gyi the tshom yongsa su gcod pa'i le'u zhes bya
NK094(nge)001:12273: ste / bdun cu rtsa gnyis pa nyid gsal bar
NK094(nge)001:12274: bshad pa'o ////brgyad pa nyams su ting nge 'dzin gyis
NK094(nge)001:12275: blangs pa tshong dpon mkhas pas rgya mtsho'i nor bu
NK094(nge)001:12276: lon pa ltar bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK094(nge)001:12285: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:12286: le'u 'dis drang don dang nges don gnyis ka ston kyang nges don gtso che'o //
NK094(nge)001:12287: lta ba'i don las su rung bas yang dag pa'i sa la sbyar ba'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:12288: rjes thog de nasa yang ston pa gsang ba pa'i bdag posa /
NK094(nge)001:12289: grogs kyi 'khor dman pa dam pa rnams la smras pa /
NK094(nge)001:12290: kye grogsa po dag ces bos nas /
NK094(nge)001:12291: ganga nyams su ting nge 'dzin gyis blangs te dgongs
NK094(nge)001:12292: pa'i nyamsa rnyed par bya ba ni nye bar bstan
NK094(nge)001:12295: ting nge 'dzin gyi dgos ched bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:12296: cig char ba'i mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzin bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:12298: mtshan bcas kyi ting nge 'dzin bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:12299: mdo sems su 'dus par bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:12301: don du gnyer ba'i dgos ched /
NK094(nge)001:12302: gzhan sel ba'i dgos ched do //
NK094(nge)001:12307: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:12308: sgom pa'i dgos ched 'chad pa ste /
NK094(nge)001:12309: rgyal ba thams cad kyi dgongsa pa'i zhe phugs su
NK094(nge)001:12310: gyur pa'i rtogs pa dam pa mthar thug pa kun
NK094(nge)001:12311: 'dus pa'i lhun gyis grub pa'i don 'di la mi
NK094(nge)001:12312: gnyis par 'jug pa'i las dang thabs kyi mchog gam
NK094(nge)001:12313: gtsor gyur pa ni bsam gtan zab mo'i ting nge
NK094(nge)001:12315: de yang dper na 'khora losa sgyur ba'i rgyal po'i dpung bzhi'i tshogs thams cad la /
NK094(nge)001:12316: 'khor los dbang sgyur bar 'gro ba ji ltar ba bzhina du /
NK094(nge)001:12317: rgyu dang 'bras bu'i chos so cog kun ji lta
NK094(nge)001:12318: bar thag chod pa'i don la ma yengs par gnas
NK094(nge)001:12319: pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis dbang sgyur nas 'thob pa
NK094(nge)001:12320: las thabs gzhan nye ba'i rgyu ba yin pa'i phyir
NK094(nge)001:12321: bsam gtan nyid bsgom dgos pa yin te /
NK094(nge)001:12322: bslab pa bcu'i yang gtso bo bsam gtan yin la /
NK094(nge)001:12323: gzhan dgu ni 'khor lta bur gyur pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:12324: de bas na sgom pa'i yon tan ni 'di lta ste /
NK094(nge)001:12325: chos thams cad ril rnal ma ye ji bzhin pa'i
NK094(nge)001:12326: ngang du mi gnyis pa'i don 'byor bar shar ba'i
NK094(nge)001:12327: skyes bu ni gnas pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12328: byed pa gnyis ka bsam gtan gyi yon tan te /
NK094(nge)001:12329: ji bzhin pa'i ngo bo nyid yul dang bral ba
NK094(nge)001:12330: las ngang gis mi g.yo bar ma bcos pa'i rjes
NK094(nge)001:12331: su mthun pa'i bsam pa yang rtog rgyun ma 'gag
NK094(nge)001:12332: la g.yo ba med pa ni lhag par chen po
NK094(nge)001:12333: zhes pa'i ming thob pas don 'di nyid mchog tu
NK094(nge)001:12335: de lta bus sgrib pa ma spang bral ba ni /
NK094(nge)001:12336: dper na dug dang mun pa dang zangs lcags ma
NK094(nge)001:12337: bsal bar sman dang mar me dang gsera 'gyur rtsis
NK094(nge)001:12338: de nyid du byed pa bzhina /
NK094(nge)001:12339: sgo gsum gyi sgrib pa phra rags thamsa cad ma
NK094(nge)001:12340: bsal bar de nyid ye shes chen po'i 'bras bur
NK094(nge)001:12341: rang dabnga bsgyur te 'char bar byed pa'i las ni
NK094(nge)001:12342: bsam gtan gyi byed pa yin pas zang zing phyi
NK094(nge)001:12343: nang spang du med pa'i sems kyis bor la /
NK094(nge)001:12344: don chen po dang ldan pa desa na dgongs pa
NK094(nge)001:12345: dam pa'i bsam gtan bya ba la shin tu 'bad
NK094(nge)001:12346: par rigs so // gnyis pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:12350: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:12351: 'o na ma bsgom pa'i skyon ga nga snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:12352: snyoms las can dag gis tshig la khungs phyungs te
NK094(nge)001:12353: gal te don chen po'i bsam gtan 'di nyid ma
NK094(nge)001:12354: bsgoms te rtogs don brtan pa'i gdengs med pa ni
NK094(nge)001:12355: / dper na rgya mtsho'i 'jinga ngam gting gi pha
NK094(nge)001:12356: bong nyid rlan dang ma bral na yang snying po
NK094(nge)001:12357: skam par gnas pa ltar du /
NK094(nge)001:12358: rtsol bas rnam par dkar ba'i las rgya mtsho lta
NK094(nge)001:12359: bu dapaga tu med pa'i sgo la spyad de 'bad
NK094(nge)001:12360: pas zhugs kyang 'jig rten pa'i bde ba tsam las
NK094(nge)001:12361: sgrub pa'i 'bras bu bla na med pa'i go 'phang
NK094(nge)001:12362: mchog gi dona med cing snying po byang chub kyi
NK094(nge)001:12363: myu gu skamsa pa yin pas dpe dang tshul mtshungs
NK094(nge)001:12364: pa'o // 'on kyang rgyu tsam du mi 'dod pa ni ma yin no //
NK094(nge)001:12366: ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:12367: de la ting nge 'dzin gsum rdzogs par bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:12368: ting nge 'dzin de'i rang bzhin bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:12369: gol sgrib thun mong ba'i skyon bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:12370: de dag bcos thabs kyi nges pa bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:12371: rim gyis dang cig char ba'i khyad par bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:12372: ting nge 'dzin de'i khyad par gyi skyon bcos thabs thun mong du bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:12373: zhor la yon tan gyi nges 'byed bshad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:12378: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:12379: de lta ba'i don chen po la sbyor ba'i ting
NK094(nge)001:12380: nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo nyid gang snyam pa la
NK094(nge)001:12381: / ji bzhin pa'i ngang la rnal du 'byor te
NK094(nge)001:12382: 'du shes gang du'ang ma zhugs pa'i khyad par gyis
NK094(nge)001:12384: de lta bu'i bsam gtan de'i ngo bo nyid ni /
NK094(nge)001:12385: chos rnams kyi chos nyid ji bzhina pa yi de
NK094(nge)001:12386: kho na nyid ma bslad ma bsgyur ba'i gsang don
NK094(nge)001:12387: mtha' dang ye bral bas de nyid du'ang brjod du
NK094(nge)001:12388: med pa'i don la rang rig pas de ltar rtogs
NK094(nge)001:12389: te ji bzhin pa de nyid du thag chod pa'i
NK094(nge)001:12390: rgyus / don de kho na bar rang rig pa
NK094(nge)001:12391: snang ba la 'du shes cir yang ma skyes pas
NK094(nge)001:12392: rgyus / / rang snang ma bcos pa yi ngang
NK094(nge)001:12393: de la rang gi bsam pas gang yang bzhag pa
NK094(nge)001:12394: med par blo bzhag ste rang gsal du gnas pa
NK094(nge)001:12395: las ma yengsa par sa ler dwangs pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:12396: de bas na ji tsam du rtsol dpyod dmigs pa
NK094(nge)001:12397: ni don la ma reg pas yengs pa zhes bya
NK094(nge)001:12398: bar nga smra'o // zhes gnubs chen gyis gdams so //
NK094(nge)001:12399: de lta bu'i ngang la mngon du byed pa dang
NK094(nge)001:12400: gsal du re ba'i sems pa med pa ni mthar
NK094(nge)001:12401: 'dzin gyi skye 'agga gis ma bslad pas yang dag
NK094(nge)001:12402: pa'i shes rab skyon med pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:12403: de bas na 'gre ldog spyi'i tshugs gar 'gres kyang
NK094(nge)001:12404: snying po byang chub pa nyid pas so la nyams
NK094(nge)001:12406: rtog rgyun byung du dogs pa'ang med pas dus phyed
NK094(nge)001:12407: par ngang gis g.yeng rmugs med cing rig pa'i don
NK094(nge)001:12408: la dmigs pa dang mi mthun pa 'gog pa'ang med
NK094(nge)001:12409: de don mtha' gnyis bral bar rang gsal ba nyid
NK094(nge)001:12410: do // ting nge 'dzin gyi rtsa ba nye bar bstan pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:12411: sgom pa'i ngo bo ting nge 'dzin gyi mchog rnal
NK094(nge)001:12412: 'byor dam pa ji bzhina pa yi de kho na
NK094(nge)001:12414: semsa kyi chos nyid rang rig pa'i dkyil 'khor 'od
NK094(nge)001:12415: gsal ba de nyid kho nar gyur pas ting nge
NK094(nge)001:12416: 'dzin gyi sgo 'bum phrag kyang 'di las shar ba
NK094(nge)001:12422: bskyed pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams la bsgoom pa rnam
NK094(nge)001:12423: pa gsum brjod pa'i don rang la rdzogs pa gang
NK094(nge)001:12424: snyam pa la / thog mar de bzhina nyid kyi
NK094(nge)001:12425: ting nge 'dzin zhes bya ba cir yang mi dmigas
NK094(nge)001:12426: pa'am mi rtog pa bsgom pa'ang gzhan ma yin te
NK094(nge)001:12427: snyam pa la / / dngos po gnyis kyi gzhi
NK094(nge)001:12428: dang rtsa ba'i rnam par shes pa kun gzhi ni
NK094(nge)001:12429: byang chub kyi sems nyid do //
NK094(nge)001:12430: de ci yi phyir te gtan tshigs gang gis yid ches par bya zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:12431: rgyu rkyen med pas ma byas pa /
NK094(nge)001:12432: mkhan po dang bral bas ma bcos pa /
NK094(nge)001:12433: rang bzhin ma 'gag par shar basa ranga byung ba
NK094(nge)001:12434: dang gsum gyis spros pa dang bral ba'i de bzhina
NK094(nge)001:12435: nyid ces pa'i ming 'grub pas bsam pa po dang
NK094(nge)001:12436: rjes su mthun par bshad de bka' stsal to //
NK094(nge)001:12438: kun gzhi dmigs pa dang rnam pa ma chad pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12439: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin yang chos thams
NK094(nge)001:12440: cad la khyab cing rnam pa rgya ma chad pas
NK094(nge)001:12441: so // de bas na ngo bo nyid bstan pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12442: tshol ba'i zhen pa dgag pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12443: dngos po la gnas pa'i don du 'grel te 'chad pa'ang rjes su sbyar ro //
NK094(nge)001:12444: chos thamsa cad kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin rdzogs pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:12445: yul kun la 'jug par byed pa'i yid kyi rnam
NK094(nge)001:12446: par shes pa skad cig yud tsam du myur bar
NK094(nge)001:12448: de ci yi phyir te gtan tshigs gang zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:12449: yid kyi rnam shes ni thun mong dang khyad par
NK094(nge)001:12450: gyi yul kun tu phyi nang gi snang ba thams
NK094(nge)001:12452: spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid kyi phyi nang kun
NK094(nge)001:12453: tu snang ba'i yid nyid ye shes chen po'i ngo
NK094(nge)001:12454: bor gsal ba'i phyir thugs rje chen pos khyab par
NK094(nge)001:12455: shar ba'o // zhes bshad cing bka' stsal to //
NK094(nge)001:12456: chos mthun brtsi ba'ang yid sna tshogs te nyon yid
NK094(nge)001:12457: dang sgo lnga'i rjes su'ang 'gro ba bzhin kun ting
NK094(nge)001:12458: yang sna tshogs snang ba dang de ting gi yang
NK094(nge)001:12460: rgyu yi ting nge 'dzin gyi rnam par bkoda pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:12461: rang yul la 'ajug pa'i rnam par shes pa sgo lnga nyid do //
NK094(nge)001:12463: sgo lngas yul ganga bcad pa'i bag chags ni /
NK094(nge)001:12464: kun gzhi'i bag chags gsog pa gang gi yang ming
NK094(nge)001:12465: thogs par byed pa'i rgyur yang bkod pa yin pas
NK094(nge)001:12466: phyi nang mtho dman thamsa cad kun 'byung ba'i rgyu
NK094(nge)001:12467: zhes su'ang bashada cing bka' stsal ba'i phyir ro //
NK094(nge)001:12468: de bas na chos mthun pa'ang /
NK094(nge)001:12469: de nyid yi ge'i rnam par sgom pa po la gsal ba ni /
NK094(nge)001:12470: sgom pa po'i rig pa nyid yi ger byung ba
NK094(nge)001:12471: yang shes pa po'i yul du bag chags nyid snang
NK094(nge)001:12472: ba'o // shes pa gsum kho nar nges pa gzhag pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:12473: bshad pa'i don gsum dang chos mthun pas bsnyad kyi rgya chad par 'dod pa ni ma yin no //
NK094(nge)001:12478: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:12479: ting nge 'dzin gyi rang bzhin gang snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:12480: theg mchog chen po gang gi ting nge 'dzin dgongsa
NK094(nge)001:12481: pa dam pa khyad par can gyi rang bzhin ni
NK094(nge)001:12482: / rig pa ji bzhin pa nam mkha'i 'od bzhin
NK094(nge)001:12483: stong pa ma yina par ril rang gsal ba nyid
NK094(nge)001:12484: de thams cad du kun tu gsal ba yin la
NK094(nge)001:12485: / / ngo bo dmigs su med pas ther zug
NK094(nge)001:12486: pa'ang min te rtag chad las 'das pa kho na'o
NK094(nge)001:12487: / / // de ltar de gnyis kyi mtha' med pas dbu mar yang kun tu mi dmigas pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:12488: de bas na bsam du med pa de nyid kyang
NK094(nge)001:12489: ma yin gzhan pa'ang ma yin pa'i sems nyid mi
NK094(nge)001:12490: rtog pa chen por ma 'dres rdzogs par kun riga
NK094(nge)001:12491: cing gasla ba'i phyir 'od gsal rdzogs pa chen po
NK094(nge)001:12492: nyid de / rtag chad dang bral ba'i phyir yod pa dang med pa las kyang grol la /
NK094(nge)001:12493: yod mina med min lasa kyang 'adsa te /
NK094(nge)001:12494: ci yang gzung du med pa'i rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir te /
NK094(nge)001:12495: 'di gnyis las ma 'das na de'i skye mched du ltung ngo //
NK094(nge)001:12497: skye bo dang rgyu'i theg par gol ba /
NK094(nge)001:12498: mu stegs dang gzugs med du gol ba /
NK094(nge)001:12499: gzugs khams dang nyan thos su gol ba /
NK094(nge)001:12500: gol bas ma rtogs kyang chos nyid med par mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:12504: phyal pa dmigs pa gcig /ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:12505: de ltar ji bzhin du bsgom pa la gnod pa'i skyon dang sgrib pa gang snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:12506: 'di dag kyang lhan cig skyes pa'i skyon dang /
NK094(nge)001:12507: rkyen gyis bslad pa'i skyon dang /
NK094(nge)001:12508: ched du byas pa'i skyon du 'grel te gol sa bcu gnyis su'ang gsungs so //
NK094(nge)001:12509: de la sgom pa'i skabs gang 'dira rnal 'byor pa su yang rung ba zhig la /
NK094(nge)001:12510: byung tshor gyi rtog pa phra rags dang /
NK094(nge)001:12514: myur bul du byung nas g.yengs pa'i rjes su 'gro
NK094(nge)001:12515: ba ni skye bo mara basa 'jig rten tha mal
NK094(nge)001:12517: gang byung tshor de dag skyon du bltas te 'gog
NK094(nge)001:12518: par byed pa ni nyan rang byis pa'i spyod yul
NK094(nge)001:12519: du gol bas 'dzin chags kyi dbang gis 'gog par
NK094(nge)001:12520: 'gyur te don la shed ma bye ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:12521: 'dir gang bying rmugs kyis dran pa nyamsa pa'i dbang
NK094(nge)001:12522: gis 'thibs par gyur ba 'ben thim pa'i mda' lta
NK094(nge)001:12523: bu ni loga sred can rgyang 'phen dang phyal bar
NK094(nge)001:12524: gol ba'o // sems yan par btang nas yal bar 'jog pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12525: phyal ba don med pa ni 'jig rten rang ka
NK094(nge)001:12526: mar gol te phyal ba'i dbang gis med par 'gyur
NK094(nge)001:12527: ba'o // dmigsa pa rtse gcig tu 'dzin pa ni mtshan ma rtse gcig tu gol ba ste /
NK094(nge)001:12528: 'jig rten rang gi mtshan ma rtse gcig pa'am /
NK094(nge)001:12529: spyir dmigs pa gcig la rtse gcig tu byed pa'am /
NK094(nge)001:12530: ther zug gi dbang gis rtag par yang 'gyur ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:12535: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:12536: gang 'dira rnal 'byor chen po'i sgor zhugs kyang don
NK094(nge)001:12537: chen po las gol te log par lta basa sgrib
NK094(nge)001:12538: pa'i long ba lta bur don la mdongas pa dag
NK094(nge)001:12539: ni / badga tu 'dzin pa dang ma bral ba'i gzhi la brten nas grub mtha' sgrub ste /
NK094(nge)001:12540: ther zug rtag par 'dod pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12541: yang tshe snga phyi la sogs pa yang meda par
NK094(nge)001:12542: 'dod pa'i lta ngan gyi shes pa nyams bzhin des
NK094(nge)001:12543: 'bras bu thob bo bar rtog pa ni mu stegs
NK094(nge)001:12544: su gol ba ste ngan song gi rgyu'o //
NK094(nge)001:12545: yang 'di dag ni gzugs med par gol ba'ang yin
NK094(nge)001:12546: te bdag 'dzin la brten nas 'jig rten gyi grub
NK094(nge)001:12547: mtha' sgrub ste 'di la rtog pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:12548: chos so cog mkhan po la rag las par lta
NK094(nge)001:12549: zhing 'du shes de nyid kyis skrag cing skyo nas
NK094(nge)001:12550: ci'ang med pa la dga' ste med do snyam pa
NK094(nge)001:12551: la mos pa'i don de bsam gtan du sgrubs par
NK094(nge)001:12552: byas nas khams der 'gro bar 'gyur bas gzugs med
NK094(nge)001:12554: de nas bskal pa'i grangs tshang ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:12555: mya ngan las 'das pa bya ba'ang med do snyam
NK094(nge)001:12556: pa'i bardzu ba'i 'du shes g.yos nas thal byung de
NK094(nge)001:12557: ma thag tu ting nge 'dzin gyi lus zhig ste
NK094(nge)001:12558: skad cig la dmyal bar ltung ste ngana 'gror 'gro
NK094(nge)001:12564: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:12565: gzugs khams su gol ba gang snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:12566: mos pa chung ngu nyan thos kyi gang zag thamsa cad ni /
NK094(nge)001:12567: bsgom pa'i rnam grangs mang mod kyi /
NK094(nge)001:12568: gzhi gang zag la badga med pa'i lta ba la
NK094(nge)001:12569: rten nas 'dus byas thams cad la spyi'i mtshan nyid
NK094(nge)001:12570: rang bzhina mi rtag pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12573: bdag med par mthong nas yul drug po gang bkag
NK094(nge)001:12574: pa'i 'gog pa la zhugs nas rtog dpyod gnyis ka
NK094(nge)001:12575: yod pa'am / dpyod pa yod la rtog pa med pa 'di ni bsam gtan dang po kho na'o //
NK094(nge)001:12576: phyi nang gi chos thams cad kun stong par byas
NK094(nge)001:12577: nas 'du shes sbom po la mi ldang bar phra
NK094(nge)001:12578: ba'i stong pa la gnas pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:12579: rtog pa med la dpyod pa tsam gyi bsam gtan gnyis pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:12580: 'di la rang sa'i dran pa phra mo'i rjes su
NK094(nge)001:12581: dpyod pa tsam yod kyang sa 'og mi'i rtog dpyod
NK094(nge)001:12583: stong pa nyid la bsgom pa klong du gyur pa'i ngesa pa bzhag ste /
NK094(nge)001:12584: bdag gi gzengs bdag gis bstod nas /
NK094(nge)001:12585: da ni skye ba zad do //
NK094(nge)001:12587: khur bor ba'o snyam du yid la byed de /
NK094(nge)001:12588: dpyod pa med la dag'a ba skyed pa yod pa ni bsam gtan gsum pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:12589: de nas badga nyid kyi tshor ba dag gam /
NK094(nge)001:12590: gazhana rgyal ba'i byin gyis rlabs sam /
NK094(nge)001:12591: dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyi mthus chos bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:12592: rtog dpyod dang dga' ba gsum char bor nas skyon
NK094(nge)001:12593: med par stong pa mi g.yo ba la gnas pa
NK094(nge)001:12594: ni btang snyoms can te bsam gtan bzhi pa yin
NK094(nge)001:12595: no // des dgra bcom pa'i 'bras bu thob par lta ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:12596: 'di ni nyan thos dang 'jig rten pa thun mong
NK094(nge)001:12597: du 'grel te de dag tu lta na don chen
NK094(nge)001:12603: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:12604: su zhig yang dag pa'i shes rab yod na mthar gsang sngags rtogs par 'gyur ba srid kyi /
NK094(nge)001:12605: shes rab med na rtogs pa'i gzhi med pas mthar gsang sngags rtogs par mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:12606: gzhan du na ganga yod par 'dzin pa'i gang zag la ni /
NK094(nge)001:12607: de nyid kyi rgyus med pa'i mthar yang shugs kyis 'gyur ba 'ong srid kyi /
NK094(nge)001:12608: gang dam pa dag yod par 'dzin pa med par
NK094(nge)001:12609: 'du shes dang bral te lta ba dang rtogs pa'i
NK094(nge)001:12610: gansa med pa la ni de la ltos pa'i med
NK094(nge)001:12611: pa'i mthar ram mtha' med par mi 'gyur te /
NK094(nge)001:12612: mtha' la mi gnas par 'gyur bas gsang sngags kyi de kho na nyid kyang rtogs par 'gyur ro //
NK094(nge)001:12613: de la gsang sngags kyi de kho na nyid ces
NK094(nge)001:12614: bya ba nyid ye med pa zhig go bar dogs
NK094(nge)001:12615: pa la / bshad pa de dag ltar gang zhig
NK094(nge)001:12616: mtha' la zhen pa desa ma rig pa'i dbang gis
NK094(nge)001:12617: de kho na nyid gsal bar mi mthong la yang
NK094(nge)001:12618: dag par mi shes par nges pas don ji bzhin
NK094(nge)001:12620: de'i don la sha thang bar 'bad de btsal par
NK094(nge)001:12621: byas pas kyang ngo bo 'di 'dra bar rnyed par
NK094(nge)001:12623: sems kyi de kho na nyid med cing rlag par mi 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:12624: chos nyid gdal khyab chen po de la rgyu 'bras
NK094(nge)001:12625: kyi ngo bo dbyer med lhun rdzogs chen po yin
NK094(nge)001:12626: no // de basa na la la dag rgyu 'bras yod par lta ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:12627: rgyu 'bras med par zhen pa dag gis ma mthong ma rnyed par gyur kyang /
NK094(nge)001:12628: ji bzhin pa'i dona chen po med pa nyid min te /
NK094(nge)001:12629: ngo bo la 'gyur ba med pa nyid do //
NK094(nge)001:12630: de'i mthun pa'i chos nye bar bzung ba'i dpe ni
NK094(nge)001:12631: dper na lcagsa bsregsa pa la tsha ba'i dbal med
NK094(nge)001:12633: 'byung ba chen po bzhi med de stong par gyur na yang /
NK094(nge)001:12634: lcags de dang nam mkha' ni meda pa mina par yod pa ji bzhin du /
NK094(nge)001:12635: dmigs lta can gyis ma rnyed kyang /
NK094(nge)001:12636: de kho na nyid kyi klong ni cis kyang mi
NK094(nge)001:12637: rlag mi shigs pa'i ngo bo bas nam yang med
NK094(nge)001:12640: rang byung rang zhir bcos pa /
NK094(nge)001:12641: dgag sgrub med par bcos pa /
NK094(nge)001:12642: zung du 'brel bar rtogs te bcos su med par bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:12643: ma bcos par bzhag pas nyams rnyed par bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:12648: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:12649: rtog pa'i skyon rnams shes na ji ltar shes par bya snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:12650: bsgom pa'i tshe gzugs mthong sgra thos la sogs pa
NK094(nge)001:12651: rnam par shes pa tshogs drug gi rtog pa'i spyod
NK094(nge)001:12652: yul shar ba ni matshana ma nyid yin te /
NK094(nge)001:12653: de ltar matshana ma'i dngosa por ci byung cir snang yang /
NK094(nge)001:12654: rang bzhin la rtogs pa'i mtshan ma nyid chu'i rlabs
NK094(nge)001:12655: ltar de kho na nyid du rang snang bas na
NK094(nge)001:12656: mi mthun pa'i skyon du bsnyad du med pa'i phyir
NK094(nge)001:12657: / rtog pa nyid ma bkag par rang ci dagra
NK094(nge)001:12658: bazhaga pas chog gi de bzlog cing spong ba min
NK094(nge)001:12659: / no // de ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:12660: rtog pa ka nas ma grub pas mtshan ma'i dngos
NK094(nge)001:12661: po de nyid ye nas ma skyes pa'i stong pa
NK094(nge)001:12662: chen po'i chos nyid yin pas de la spang zhing
NK094(nge)001:12663: bzlog tu med pa'i phyir ro //
NK094(nge)001:12664: des na de ltar shes nas rang byung rang zhir
NK094(nge)001:12665: rtogs pa'i so las ma 'das par bya ba nyid
NK094(nge)001:12670: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:12671: des na bshad pa bzhin du mtshan ma thamsa cad
NK094(nge)001:12672: semsa kyi chos nyid du gsal bar tshig tsam min
NK094(nge)001:12673: par shes shing lta bas thag chod de gnad du
NK094(nge)001:12674: chud pa na rtogs pa skyes kyang rtog par mthong
NK094(nge)001:12675: ba med pas / ma bcos pa'i ngang la rtog pa mi 'chos /
NK094(nge)001:12676: klong chen po'i dbyings la yengs pa'i yul nyid bral bas rtag tu ma yengsa par gnas /
NK094(nge)001:12677: gal te yengas kyang chos nyid du grol bar lam
NK094(nge)001:12678: du khyer thub pas yengs pa'i tha snyad kyang med
NK094(nge)001:12679: par / sems la sgrib pa'ang med de ngang gir
NK094(nge)001:12680: rang gsal ba ni snyomsa par 'jug pa chen po
NK094(nge)001:12681: par / zhes bya'o // de bas na rtog rgyun
NK094(nge)001:12682: ma bkag la mthong thos med par shes pa'i skyes
NK094(nge)001:12683: par / zhes bya'o // bu la / chu yis
NK094(nge)001:12684: rlan mi tshol ba ltar rtsol sgrub kyis chos nyid
NK094(nge)001:12686: gsal zhing thob tu re ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:12687: ltung gol gyi dogsa pa dang bral bas rtsol sgrub
NK094(nge)001:12688: dang re dogs kyis 'ching ba ga la yod de
NK094(nge)001:12689: med pas na / nam du'ang mi mthun par snang
NK094(nge)001:12690: ba la gnyen po brten par mi byed cing sgom
NK094(nge)001:12691: yang mi dgos par rtogs par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:12692: gal te rtogs pa gnad du ma chud par tshul chos pa dag ni /
NK094(nge)001:12693: sbal bus nam mkha' la lding pa ltar tshi chad par 'gyur ro //
NK094(nge)001:12694: de bas na spang bya mi spong ste rtog pas 'chings pa'i phyir ro //
NK094(nge)001:12699: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:12700: de bas na bsam gtan gyi skyon dang yoona tan la spong ba dang lena par byed pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12701: bying rgod la sogs pa rnams ril skabs gang 'dira ma 'gags la /
