NK094(nge)001:12702: ngo bo dbyer med pas ris su chad pa'ang med de /
NK094(nge)001:12703: ji bzhin pa'i ngo bor zung du 'brel bar gsal
NK094(nge)001:12704: ba na byung tshor ma bkag la mi g.yo bas
NK094(nge)001:12705: zhi gansa dang lhag mthong 'brel bar gyur te /
NK094(nge)001:12706: de nyid kyang rang rig pa'i semsa kyi chos nyid lasa rang byung bar shar ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:12707: de bas na ma bcos pa'i nyams rnyed de rang byung rang zhir ma rtogs na /
NK094(nge)001:12708: dper na dngos po zhig pasa kyang nam mkha' med par brlag par mi 'gyur pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12709: bskal par 'khor bar 'khyamsa pas kyang byang chub kyi
NK094(nge)001:12710: semsa mi stor ba ltar du rtog pa rnams spong
NK094(nge)001:12716: 'du shes las ni de mi thar //
NK094(nge)001:12718: des na sgrib pa mtha' yasa pa thams cad sems
NK094(nge)001:12719: kyi chos nyid du ma shes na sbyang zhing bkrus
NK094(nge)001:12721: rtsol sbyong nyid lta ba'i sgrib pa chen po'o //
NK094(nge)001:12722: de bas na mtha' bzhi rang grol gyi stong nyid
NK094(nge)001:12723: zab mo chos nyid gsang ba'i dbyingsa su shes par
NK094(nge)001:12724: bya'o // 'o na thabs dam pa nyid gang zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:12725: gang stong pa dngos po zhig pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12726: yod pa dngos po'i snang ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:12727: chad pa dang rtag par 'dzina pa la sogs pa'i
NK094(nge)001:12728: mtha' rnams ngang gis dag pa'i tshul ni ji lta
NK094(nge)001:12729: bu yin na / mtha' snang thamsa cad ril chos
NK094(nge)001:12730: nyid dbyings kyi ye shes chen po'i klong du gsal
NK094(nge)001:12731: bar rig pasa nyi tshe ba'i stong pa ma yin
NK094(nge)001:12732: bu yin na / zhing / de nyid la ngo
NK094(nge)001:12733: bo'i dngosa po 'di 'drar med pas rtag pa yod
NK094(nge)001:12734: pa'i chos kyang ma yin te mtha' kun las 'das
NK094(nge)001:12735: bu yin na / zhing / pa'o // de ltar
NK094(nge)001:12736: na ther zug gi dngos po med pas rtag pa
NK094(nge)001:12737: bu yin na / zhing / pa'o // ma yin
NK094(nge)001:12738: / 'bras bu'i bdag nyid yin pas chad pa'ang ma
NK094(nge)001:12739: bu yin na / zhing / pa'o // ma yin
NK094(nge)001:12740: / yin te / ngo bo nyid gang yang ma
NK094(nge)001:12741: bkol ba nyid la dbyibs dang kha dog mtshan ma
NK094(nge)001:12742: dang tha snyad 'di 'drar gzung ba ci yanga med
NK094(nge)001:12743: pas sgrib pa dang bag chags sbyang du yang med
NK094(nge)001:12744: bu yin na / zhing / pa'o // ma yin
NK094(nge)001:12745: / yin te / pa nyid do // 'di ni
NK094(nge)001:12746: gol sa bcad pa'i gnad chen po'ang yin no //
NK094(nge)001:12751: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:12753: las su bya ba thamsa cad yongsa su btang nas
NK094(nge)001:12754: gang yang rig pa las gzhan du med pas mi
NK094(nge)001:12755: len mi spyod par ye gdod nas ma bcos ma
NK094(nge)001:12756: bslad pa'i chos nyid kyi ngang du /
NK094(nge)001:12757: rang rig pa cir yang bzhag tu med par shes
NK094(nge)001:12758: pa nyid bdera zhes bde ba chen por rang bab
NK094(nge)001:12759: tu bazhaga pa yin pas na /
NK094(nge)001:12760: de ltar gnad du chud na de la chos kyi
NK094(nge)001:12761: dbyings su 'du shes pa de yang med pas na
NK094(nge)001:12762: sgrib ba de yang med pa'am /
NK094(nge)001:12763: sems de nyid med pas na sems las byung ba
NK094(nge)001:12764: dang kun tu rtog pa de yanga med par nges
NK094(nge)001:12765: pa'i phyir btsal yang mi rnyed pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:12766: de ltar ma nor bar rtogs pa ni dama pa'i
NK094(nge)001:12767: nyamsa kyi dgongs pa'i gdengs rnyed pa ste bden pa
NK094(nge)001:12773: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:12774: de lta bu dman pa'i yul ma yin par bstan pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:12775: 'o na blo chen po cig char ba rnams kyi
NK094(nge)001:12776: dgongs pa dam pa de nyid blo chung rim gyis
NK094(nge)001:12777: pa la'ang nges par bstan par bya'am zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:12779: skabs 'di ni gsang sngags theg pa chen po'i don
NK094(nge)001:12780: mchog dam pa yi snying po cig char ba'i dgongs
NK094(nge)001:12782: rgyu'i theg pa rim gyis 'jug pa ba rang gi
NK094(nge)001:12783: rtsol mtha'i nad chen gyi rimsa kyis sgribs nas don
NK094(nge)001:12784: chen po thob pa ma yin pas yang dag par
NK094(nge)001:12786: de bas na rim gyis pa yi tshogs drug g.yeng
NK094(nge)001:12787: ba'i rgyur bzhag pa'i bying rgoda can du bstan pa
NK094(nge)001:12788: nyid ni / blo mchog cig char 'char ba'i skabs
NK094(nge)001:12789: su de nyid ji bzhin pa de kho na nyid
NK094(nge)001:12790: lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i chos nyid du shar bas ma
NK094(nge)001:12791: bkag la mi g.yo ba nyid du gsal ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:12792: des na zhes pas snyegs pa ni 'jug sgo gnyis gcig gi nang du gcig gyur pas /
NK094(nge)001:12793: blo chung ba rim gyis 'jug pa ganga dang blo
NK094(nge)001:12794: che ba cig char du 'jug pa gang dag gi
NK094(nge)001:12795: gdul bya'i dngos po rnams kyis bab col du mi
NK094(nge)001:12796: 'jug par 'jug rims de dag gis tshul du rim
NK094(nge)001:12797: cig char gyis rang gi blos ji ltar go ba'i
NK094(nge)001:12798: rtogs tshad dang mos pa ji lta ba de bzhin
NK094(nge)001:12799: du bstan pa chos kyi sgo mo rims par bstan
NK094(nge)001:12800: pa gang dang cig char du rtogs thabs bstan pa
NK094(nge)001:12801: gang dag la so sora yid brten pa'i yul du
NK094(nge)001:12802: 'bad nas chud mi za bar bya ba'i don to
NK094(nge)001:12803: // de bas na so sor nges pa'i gtan tshigs yang /
NK094(nge)001:12804: de ltar sgo so so bar spyad dgos pa'i don
NK094(nge)001:12805: gyis sgron ma bkod pa'i rgyal ba dpag tu med
NK094(nge)001:12807: zhing so sor bka' stsal pa'i dama pa'i chos kyi sgo dam pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12808: thabs sna tshogs pa ji snyed cig tu gsungsa pa rnams /
NK094(nge)001:12809: gdul bya'i blo rims dang bstun pas gcig tu sa
NK094(nge)001:12810: zin med par phyogs su ma chad cing nges pa
NK094(nge)001:12811: can du gsungs par gzung du med de /
NK094(nge)001:12812: rang rang gang la ji ltar mos pa 'byung ba
NK094(nge)001:12813: de ltar gsungs pa yin pas de kho na ltar
NK094(nge)001:12814: bden par ngesa pa nyid du 'gyur ro //
NK094(nge)001:12816: bar du gcod pa'i skyon bcos pa /
NK094(nge)001:12817: dug lnga la sogs nyon mongs pa bcos pa /
NK094(nge)001:12818: ched du byas pa'i skyon bcos pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:12822: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:12823: bsgom pa'i tshe bar du gcod pa'i skyon bstan pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:12824: ma nor ba'i don 'di la gang 'jug ste sgom
NK094(nge)001:12825: pa'i bsam pa las su mi rung bar byed pa'i
NK094(nge)001:12826: bar du gcod pa bgegs kyi rnam grangs ni /
NK094(nge)001:12827: le lo gnyis byed pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12828: sgo gsum gyi bya ba mang ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:12830: blo g.yenga ba drug gi dbang du gyur ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:12831: don mi gsal bar sems rmugsa pas bying dbang du song ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:12832: don gcig gsal bar 'doda pa'am 'dod pa che ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:12834: rtags dang mtshan ma la re ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:12836: rtog pa skyes su dogsa pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12837: nges pa'i don la the tshom za ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:12838: sems nang du 'du ba'am dmigs pas nang du sdud pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12839: sems phyi rol du 'phro ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:12840: chos spyod kyi g.yeng ba la mos pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12841: bsgom pa'i don la yid 'byung skyes pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12842: ting nge 'dzin gyi ro dag'a bde la chags pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12843: ca co la dga' ba ste dngos bstan bco lnga'o //
NK094(nge)001:12844: 'o na de dag dgag gam ji ltar bya zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:12845: bcos pa'i thabs dam pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:12846: de yanga bar du gcod pa'i bdud rnams kyi rang bzhina skyes bdo tsam nyid na /
NK094(nge)001:12847: mtha' ril las 'das pa'i de kho na nyid ma
NK094(nge)001:12848: bcos pa'i de bzhina nyid sems kyi dkyil 'khor 'od
NK094(nge)001:12849: gsal ba'i rang bzhin las skyon rdul phran tsam yang
NK094(nge)001:12850: med pa'i phyir / skyes ma thag pa tshor ba
NK094(nge)001:12851: tsam gyis rkun po tshor ba ltar de kho na
NK094(nge)001:12852: nyid du rang gsal ba dgag dang spang du med
NK094(nge)001:12853: med pa'i phyir / pa'o // 'o na tshor ba zhen pa'i dngos po zhig brten no zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:12854: de ni bsten pa med de /
NK094(nge)001:12855: cir yang ma tshor ba nyid tshor ba chen po bas tshor ba gcig ces kyang bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:12856: tshor ba nyid yid la bya ba med pa nyid kyis dag go //
NK094(nge)001:12861: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:12862: bsgom pa'i tshe nyon mongs skyes na ji ltar bya zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:12864: kun mkhyen dam pa rin po ches /
NK094(nge)001:12865: de la skyon ni rnam pa drug /glo bur 'dod chags ldang ba dang //
NK094(nge)001:12866: zhe sdang chen po skyes pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:12867: nga rgyal phrag dog 'khrug pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:12868: lta ba snyems dang de drug go //
NK094(nge)001:12870: dug chen lnga yi chags sdang skyes pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12871: la sogas pa zhes gzhan bsdu ba ni /
NK094(nge)001:12873: sgrib pa bcu dang lnga dag ste /
NK094(nge)001:12874: nyon mongs pa'i rtog tshogs kun tu 'byung ba rnams te /
NK094(nge)001:12875: de nyid ji ltar zhes par bya ba ni /
NK094(nge)001:12876: de dag nyid de kho na nyid dang nyi ma
NK094(nge)001:12877: dang 'od zer lta bu bas ma spangs par ranga
NK094(nge)001:12878: byung ba nyid rig pa'i ngang du ranga zhi ba
NK094(nge)001:12879: ni rang rig de bzhin nyid du rang grol ba
NK094(nge)001:12880: ste bcos thabs dam par 'gyur ba rjes su mthun
NK094(nge)001:12885: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:12886: de kho na nyid dama pa'i dona mchog sgom pa
NK094(nge)001:12887: la ganga sgrib par byed pa ni rnam grangs bcu
NK094(nge)001:12888: ste / sems mi g.yo ba la dga' ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:12890: bde ba thob par 'dod pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12892: yang na bde ba'i ro la chags pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12893: las su ma rung du dogs pas rtsol ba'i sdug bsngal dang /
NK094(nge)001:12894: rtog pa'i rkun bu mang po skye ba'am drod rtags skye bar 'dod pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12895: mngon shes gasla bar 'dod pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12896: mtshan ma'i rdzu 'phrul 'byin par 'dod pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12897: don la zhen pas ngesa par 'dzin pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12898: gzhan gyi lta ba khyad du gsod pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12899: rang gi lta bas snyemsa pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:12900: de dag ji ltar bcos na /
NK094(nge)001:12901: rang byung rang zhi chen po nyid gsal bar bzhag go //
NK094(nge)001:12902: de lta bu rang byung rang zhi ched du bsten pa'ang med pa nyid bzhag par smra'o //
NK094(nge)001:12903: 'di gsum gyi skyon dang po gnyis ni tshogs lam gyi rnal 'byor la bar du gcod la /
NK094(nge)001:12904: gsum pas ni sbyor lam dang mthong lam la nye ba na'ang bar du gcod do //
NK094(nge)001:12907: bdud kyi spyod yul bco brgyad rtags dang skyon du ji ltar 'gyur ba /
NK094(nge)001:12908: mtshan ma rang grol zhing gang la'ang dga' 'gyod med na tshad du phyin pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:12913: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:12914: de ltar 'bad de bsgom pa'i yon tan nyams brtan pa'i tshad bstan pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:12915: ji bzhin pa'i bsam gtan chen por gdeng du chud
NK094(nge)001:12916: de ngesa par goms pa'i yon tan gyi rtags nyid
NK094(nge)001:12918: spyod lam bzhi po kun tu legs nyes ji spyad kyang rtogs pa'i don las mi nyamsa pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12919: rtags dang 'bras bu la re ba med pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12920: khams gsum 'khor ba'i g.yang du lhung bar dogsa pa med pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12921: gnas gcig las ma g.yos par zhing khams thams cad
NK094(nge)001:12922: du skyu ru ra rlon pa lag mthil du bzhag
NK094(nge)001:12923: pa bzhin mngon du gyur bar mthong yang dang zhing
NK094(nge)001:12924: dga' ba mi skye ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:12925: srin po 'bar ba mthong yang 'jigs pa'i sems mi g.yo ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:12926: lha'i bu mo 'ongs kyang chags pa'i 'du shes mi skye bar kun tu mi chagsa pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12927: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chos kyi dbyings la gnas kyang 'dus byas chos spyod rgyun mi gcad pa'am /
NK094(nge)001:12928: ci spyad ci byed ril bdag gi mdzad spyod dam pa bas dge ba rgyun mi 'chad pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12929: 'dod pa lnga la spyad kyang gang la'ang dang du
NK094(nge)001:12930: lena pa med pas legs nyes kyi 'bras bu mi
NK094(nge)001:12931: 'byin pa dang / phung po la gzhan gyis gtses pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:12932: ngag mi snyan pa ji ltar brjod kyang yid sems
NK094(nge)001:12933: 'khrug pa med na de ni chos nyid ji bzhin
NK094(nge)001:12934: pa'i rang bzhin rig pa de bzhin nyid du gsal
NK094(nge)001:12935: ba'i yon tan snang ste nang rtags phyi ru 'byung
NK094(nge)001:12940: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:12941: bdud kyi spyod yul bco brgyad brjod pa gang zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:12942: don las su rung ba'i rnal 'byor pa la skye
NK094(nge)001:12943: ba'i bdud kyi spyod yul du'ang 'gyur bas cho 'phrul
NK094(nge)001:12944: gyi rtags ni bco brgyad yod de /
NK094(nge)001:12945: de la 'dzin na gnyis med kyi bdud du 'chad par byed do //
NK094(nge)001:12946: de'ang dngos su sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'
NK094(nge)001:12947: dama pa mang po bdag gi mdun du 'khod par
NK094(nge)001:12948: gyur te bdag nyid 'dun pas de dag las chos
NK094(nge)001:12949: nyan par mthong ba dang gcig /bdag nyid chos kyi
NK094(nge)001:12950: rgyal po rnam snang lta bur ston par gyur nas
NK094(nge)001:12951: byang chub sems dpa' mang po la chos dama para
NK094(nge)001:12952: smra zhing ston pa mthong ba dang gnyis /
NK094(nge)001:12953: bdag nyid las skad cig la sangs rgyas kyi sprul
NK094(nge)001:12954: pa grangsa med pa 'gyed pa mthong ba dang gsum
NK094(nge)001:12955: / rgyal ba dam pasa gsungs shing smras pa'i chos
NK094(nge)001:12956: kyi sgo dpag tu med pa'i bstan pa kun bdag
NK094(nge)001:12957: gi gasla bar mthonga zhing rtogs pa snyam byed pa
NK094(nge)001:12958: / dang ni / dus bzhi'am tshe rabs snga phyi
NK094(nge)001:12959: kun shes te yid la sa ler gasla zhing mthong
NK094(nge)001:12961: 'gro ba rgyu drug gi lam la gnas pa srid
NK094(nge)001:12962: pa bar ma kun srin bu yan chad gang du
NK094(nge)001:12963: skye ba drung na 'khod pa bzhin yid la snang
NK094(nge)001:12964: ba dang drug /de dag las nyam thag pa rnams
NK094(nge)001:12965: la gdung ba'i snying rje chen po rang dbang med
NK094(nge)001:12966: par byin rlabs kyi shugsa kyis 'byung ba dang bdun
NK094(nge)001:12967: / nyin dang mtshan mo med par kun tu snang
NK094(nge)001:12968: zhing gasla ba'i 'od chen po rab tu 'bar bar
NK094(nge)001:12971: sa rdo ri brag me chu rtsig pa sogs ci
NK094(nge)001:12972: la'ang mi rdugs par thogsa pa med par 'gro bar
NK094(nge)001:12974: nam mkha' la sa la bya ba bzhina 'gro 'dug
NK094(nge)001:12975: dang nyal ba sogs byed par nus pa dang bcu
NK094(nge)001:12976: / phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba dama pa rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK094(nge)001:12977: rgyas thams cad kyis phyag gser gyi mdog can brkyangsa
NK094(nge)001:12978: nas bdag gi spyi bor bzhag nas lung ston par
NK094(nge)001:12980: 'gro ba sems can kun gyi skad dang mthun pa
NK094(nge)001:12981: nyid du chos ston cing smra bar nus so snyam
NK094(nge)001:12982: du shes pa dang bcu gnyis /
NK094(nge)001:12983: snod bcud kyi dngosa po bartan g.yo kun gyis bdag
NK094(nge)001:12984: la bsti gnas su bkur te 'dud phyag dang bkur
NK094(nge)001:12985: sti byed par mthong ba dang bcu gsum /
NK094(nge)001:12986: stong gsum 'jig rten gyi khams thamsa cad lag mthil
NK094(nge)001:12987: ltar mnyam par bkod pa mthong ba dang bcu bzhi
NK094(nge)001:12988: / bdag gi sems kyi chos nyid de kho na
NK094(nge)001:12989: nyid thogs pa med par chos thams cad kyi rang
NK094(nge)001:12990: bzhina du gsal bar snang bar rtogs snyam byed par
NK094(nge)001:12991: / dang bco lnga / nga ni ting nge 'dzin
NK094(nge)001:12992: lasa su rung bas ci la'ang thogsa pa med par
NK094(nge)001:12993: sems can gyi don nus snyam byed pa dang bcu
NK094(nge)001:12994: drug /sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' dama pa
NK094(nge)001:12995: mang po snang basa rigs kyi bu khyod 'jig rten
NK094(nge)001:12996: gyi khams su sems can gyi dona la 'gro zhing
NK094(nge)001:12998: zhes bdag la bsgo bar mthong ba dang bcu bdun /
NK094(nge)001:12999: tshangs pa dang brgya byin la sogs pa 'jiga rten
NK094(nge)001:13000: gyi gtso bo lha klu mthu bo che mang posa
NK094(nge)001:13001: bdag la mchod pa 'bul bar mthong ba dang bco
NK094(nge)001:13002: brgyad do // de ltar bco brgyad po 'di dag
NK094(nge)001:13003: ji ltar snang yang sems nyid ranga bzhin gyi 'od
NK094(nge)001:13004: gsal ba'i don du shes shing rtogs nas mi 'dzin
NK094(nge)001:13005: cing dga' bar mi byed na dama pa'i rtagsa bco
NK094(nge)001:13006: brgyad du 'gyur te snang stong gi zhen pa gang
NK094(nge)001:13007: brgyad do // yang med do // ganga gis de
NK094(nge)001:13008: ltar chos nyid du mi shes par mtshan mar bzung
NK094(nge)001:13009: ste dngos por zhen pas dga' bar byed pa ni
NK094(nge)001:13010: de kho na nyid mthong du mi ster bar loga
NK094(nge)001:13011: pa'i bdud chen po yin pas bdud kyi spyod yul
NK094(nge)001:13012: du khas blangs pa'i don bshad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:13013: de bas na rtags dang bdud ni thun mong par bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:13014: 'di dag bsam gtan nyams kyi sgron ma dang yang
NK094(nge)001:13015: go rims cung zad mi 'dra ba tsam las don
NK094(nge)001:13016: la khyad par med de tshig kyang gcig go //
NK094(nge)001:13021: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:13022: sems bcos pa'i rjes su bstan pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:13023: dbang po'i sgo drug gi shes pas rang bzhin la
NK094(nge)001:13024: rtog pa'i matshana ma sna tshogs ci zhig skyes kyang
NK094(nge)001:13025: de kho na nyid du rang byung bas dgag tu'ang
NK094(nge)001:13026: med par rang zhi yin la /
NK094(nge)001:13027: mthong zhing thos pa la sogs pa ci dagra bzhag
NK094(nge)001:13028: pa nyid ma skyes pa'i chos nyid du rtogs pasa
NK094(nge)001:13029: na de la spong rgyu dang bzlog tu'nga meda do
NK094(nge)001:13031: de yanga rtog pa de dag gi ngo bo'i de
NK094(nge)001:13032: bzhina nyid la 'di 'drar mi zin pas dgag bya
NK094(nge)001:13033: ngang gis bral ba ni ma bcos ma bslad pa'i
NK094(nge)001:13034: chos nyid ma nor ba'i de kho na nyid do
NK094(nge)001:13035: // 'adsa dang ma 'ongas da ltar gyis bsdus pa'i
NK094(nge)001:13036: dus gsum gyi las dang 'bras bu nyes pa dang
NK094(nge)001:13037: legsa pa'i bzang ngan gyi dngos por gyur ba gang
NK094(nge)001:13038: ci la yang legs shing bzang ba la dag'a ba
NK094(nge)001:13039: dang ngan pa mi bzang ba la mi dga' zhing
NK094(nge)001:13040: 'gyod pa'i gnyis rtog byed pa gang yang med par
NK094(nge)001:13041: gyur pa nyid tshad du phyin pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:13042: de'ang bshad pa ltar ranga byung ranga zhi ste de
NK094(nge)001:13043: nyid de bzhin nyid du rlom sems pa'ang bral ba'i
NK094(nge)001:13044: thabs chen por gyur pa kho na yina no //
NK094(nge)001:13045: 'on kyang skyon ni sgo gnyis dang thun mong yang bcos thabs 'di dag ni /
NK094(nge)001:13046: cig char ba'i dbang du bka' stsal pa ste /
NK094(nge)001:13047: rim gyis pa'i skyon dang dgag thabs ni ci rigs
NK094(nge)001:13048: su bsnyad du yod na'ang rgyud nyid kyi bka' lung
NK094(nge)001:13050: sgra yis 'jigs pa ma bsnyad do //
NK094(nge)001:13061: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:13062: de ltar bsgom ste nyams su blangs pa'i 'bras bu
NK094(nge)001:13063: la sbyor ba'i snga ltas kyi dpe gang snyam pa
NK094(nge)001:13064: la / de yang gnas skabs 'dira ni rgyu yi
NK094(nge)001:13065: dus na lta ba'i ngo bo dama para gang gis
NK094(nge)001:13066: ngesa pa rnyed nas don la nye ba'i rnal 'byor
NK094(nge)001:13067: gyi matshana ma'i snga ltas lnga 'byung ba ni /
NK094(nge)001:13068: dper na chu dang rlung dang me dang gser rnams
NK094(nge)001:13069: 'byung ba ga na bar de dag gi snga ltas
NK094(nge)001:13070: chu yod na rlabs dang spabs dang srog chags skyar
NK094(nge)001:13072: rlung 'byung ba'i snga ltas sprin rgyug la dum bur 'chad cing 'phro ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13073: me yi ltas du ba 'byung ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13074: rtsi mtshal lo ma gang du yod pa na gser yod par ngesa pa bzhina /
NK094(nge)001:13075: blo ma nor bas lta ba dang ting nge 'dzin
NK094(nge)001:13076: gyi don dam para ngesa nas don la phebs shing
NK094(nge)001:13077: goms na / blo dang lus dang rdzas dang rmi
NK094(nge)001:13078: lam dang 'dun pa lnga yi ltas kyi drod rtags
NK094(nge)001:13080: gal te ltas byung yang rig pa dama para gdeng
NK094(nge)001:13081: du chud de lta ba ma ngesa pas dngos por
NK094(nge)001:13082: zhen pa 'byung na ni thamsa cad bdud du 'gro
NK094(nge)001:13083: bar 'gyur ro // lta ba dang ting nge 'dzin
NK094(nge)001:13084: gyi gdeng dama para tshud de don du ngesa pa
NK094(nge)001:13085: na ltas chung ngu tsam gang zhig byung ba yan
NK094(nge)001:13086: chad 'bras bu dam pa 'byung ba'i snga ltas su
NK094(nge)001:13087: shes par bya ste blo rtsal gyis bden pa mthong
NK094(nge)001:13090: blo rtsal gyi khyad par bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:13091: snang ba lus kyi snga ltas /
NK094(nge)001:13092: ngo mtshar rdzas rnyed kyi tshul rtags /
NK094(nge)001:13094: mtshan ma pra'i snga ltas bshad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:13096: bden pa mthong ba'i ltas bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:13097: drod rtags gsal ba'i rtsal bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:13098: ngag bden grub pa'i ltas bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:13103: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:13104: bden pa mthong ba'i rtags blo rtsal gyi khyad par gang snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:13105: rnal 'byor pa gang gis chos nyid mchog tu gsang
NK094(nge)001:13106: ba'i don zab mo dam pa nyid thos pa na
NK094(nge)001:13107: yang mi skrag cing mi dangngas par dag'a ba skye
NK094(nge)001:13108: ba ni dngos su sa bzhi pa la sogs par
NK094(nge)001:13109: thob pa dang / gang zhig rig pa phyin ci
NK094(nge)001:13110: ma log pas gdal khyab mnyam pa chen po'i rang
NK094(nge)001:13111: rig dama pa gsang ba'i chos nyid du yang dag
NK094(nge)001:13112: par lta ba la brten nas spyod yul gyi dngos
NK094(nge)001:13113: po thamsa cad de kho na nyid dam pa 'gag
NK094(nge)001:13114: pa med pa'i rang snang nyid du mthong ba dang
NK094(nge)001:13115: thob pa dang / / dama pa'i snang yul thams
NK094(nge)001:13116: cad nges pa'i klong du ganga shar rang grol du
NK094(nge)001:13117: gyur pa nyid kyis tshig gi rnam grangsa manga po
NK094(nge)001:13118: rnams kyang ma nor ba'i don dama pa yang dag
NK094(nge)001:13120: lta ba dama pasa don ngesa par mthonga ste gnas pa na /
NK094(nge)001:13121: tshig lam gyi rjesa su de nyid mi 'gro bas tshig la dga' ba mi skye ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13122: de ltar mthong bas thams cad ril chos nyid dama para gasla ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:13123: de bas na chos nyid snang ba meda pa'i dam par chos ci yang ma mthong ba ni /
NK094(nge)001:13124: gnyis su snang ba med para yang dag pa'i chos nyid kyi bden pa mthonga bar bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:13125: nyams drod kyang thob par 'gyur ba yin no //
NK094(nge)001:13126: 'chad pa'i cho 'phrul rnams rgyu gang las 'byung snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:13127: ji lta ba de kho na nyid gting phyin par rtogs pa de nyid ni /
NK094(nge)001:13128: gang yang ma bkol zhing ril gyi dngos gzhir gyur bas kun gyi rgyu yang yina te /
NK094(nge)001:13129: 'chad pa'i cho 'phrul gyi rgyu ba thamsa cad 'byung ba'i yang rgyu'o //
NK094(nge)001:13130: de skad du rtsa ba'i rgyud las /
NK094(nge)001:13131: blo rtsal las kyi khyad par gyis //
NK094(nge)001:13133: yang dag bden pa'i don bstan na //
NK094(nge)001:13134: mi skrag mi sngang dga' ba skye //
NK094(nge)001:13135: yang dag don la nges bltas na //
NK094(nge)001:13136: 'khor ba'i chos la skyo ba skye //
NK094(nge)001:13137: yang dag don la 'dris pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13138: rnam grangs chos la dad mi 'gyur //
NK094(nge)001:13139: yang dag don nyid mthong ba na //
NK094(nge)001:13140: tshig la dga' ba mi skye zhing //
NK094(nge)001:13141: don nyid nye bar 'dzin par byed //
NK094(nge)001:13142: don mthong ba dang ye shes skye //
NK094(nge)001:13143: ye shes skyes par gyur ba dang //
NK094(nge)001:13144: dngos por snang ba thams cad kun //
NK094(nge)001:13145: sgyu ma bzhin du shes par 'gyur //
NK094(nge)001:13146: sgyu ma tsam du shes ba la //
NK094(nge)001:13147: brten nas chos nyid don bltas na //
NK094(nge)001:13148: snang ba med pa'i don nyid ni //
NK094(nge)001:13149: snang ba med par mthong bar 'gyur //
NK094(nge)001:13150: snang med srid pa mthong ba'i tshe //
NK094(nge)001:13152: de ni bden pa'i snga ltas so //
NK094(nge)001:13158: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:13159: drod rtags kyi rnam grangs dang dpe gang snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:13160: drug gam brgyad du ston te /
NK094(nge)001:13161: rtogs pa'i drod rtogs g.yo ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13162: drod rnam pa gsum byung ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13163: de nas drod thob pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13165: ting nge 'dzin gsal ba'i drod dam g.yo rtags dang /
NK094(nge)001:13166: rtagsa thob cing brtan par gyur ba rnams ni 'di ltar /
NK094(nge)001:13167: nyi zer gyi rdul phran lta bur mthong ba'i don ni g.yo ba'i rtags so //
NK094(nge)001:13168: smig rgyu lta bu'i don ni dang po'i drod do //
NK094(nge)001:13169: mtsho rlabsa lta bu ni drood par pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:13170: lus sems rlung ltar yangs pa ni tha ma'i drod de 'di dag drod g.yo ba'i rnam grangs te /
NK094(nge)001:13171: drug tu byed na rtags g.yo ba dang drod gnyis su brtsi la /
NK094(nge)001:13172: brgyad du byed na drod g.yo ba dang byung ba gsum mo //
NK094(nge)001:13173: de nas yig 'bru'i 'phro 'du char gyi rgyun 'bab ba ltar 'byung ba ni drod thob pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:13174: lus nam mkha' la sprin bzhin lding ba ni drod brtan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:13175: lus t+aa la ganga tsam du nam mkha' la 'aphara
NK094(nge)001:13176: te 'gro ba ni ting nge 'dzin gsal ba'i drod
NK094(nge)001:13178: spyod yul kun sa g.yo ba ltar yom yom mer
NK094(nge)001:13179: mer du gyur na rtags chen dang po thob pa'o
NK094(nge)001:13180: // de bzhin du me rlung sa chu'i 'byung ba'i
NK094(nge)001:13181: skye mched gang ltar sgom bar snang du btub pa
NK094(nge)001:13183: 'di dag mi 'gyur bar yod pa ni brtan pa nyid do //
NK094(nge)001:13184: snga ma'i le'u gsum pa las gsal bar 'byung ste /
NK094(nge)001:13185: de nas nyi ma'i 'od zer gyi //
NK094(nge)001:13187: de ni g.yo ba'i snga ltas so //
NK094(nge)001:13188: de nas smig rgyu lta bur 'byung //
NK094(nge)001:13189: dang po'i drod ces bya bar bshad //
NK094(nge)001:13190: de nas mtsho yi rlabs ltar 'byung //
NK094(nge)001:13191: bar gyi drod ces bya bar bshad //
NK094(nge)001:13192: de nas rlung chen lta bur yang //
NK094(nge)001:13194: tha ma'i drod ces bya bar bshad //
NK094(nge)001:13195: de nas yig 'bru'i drod spros pas //
NK094(nge)001:13197: de ni thob pa'i drod ces bshad //
NK094(nge)001:13198: de nas mkha' la sprin lding bzhin //
NK094(nge)001:13200: de ni shin tu brtan pa'i drod //
NK094(nge)001:13201: de nas t+aa la gcig tsam du //
NK094(nge)001:13202: bdag gi lus ni dbang med par //
NK094(nge)001:13204: 'di ni shin tu gsal ba'i drod //
NK094(nge)001:13205: de nas sa chen g.yo ba ltar //
NK094(nge)001:13206: shin tu yam yom mar mer 'byung //
NK094(nge)001:13207: 'di ni dang po'i rtags zhes bya //
NK094(nge)001:13208: de nas ting 'dzin rtsal sbyangs nas //
NK094(nge)001:13209: ji ltar dmigs pa der 'grub ste //
NK094(nge)001:13210: me yi skye mched der bsgom na //
NK094(nge)001:13211: me yi rang bzhin nyid du 'gyur //
NK094(nge)001:13212: chu yi skye mched der sgoms na //
NK094(nge)001:13213: chu yi skye mched nyid du gyur //
NK094(nge)001:13214: rlung gi skye mched der sgoms na //
NK094(nge)001:13215: rlung gi skye mched nyid du 'gyur //
NK094(nge)001:13216: yig 'bru'i skye mched der sgoms na //
NK094(nge)001:13218: de ltar rdzas kyi skye mched du //
NK094(nge)001:13219: gang ltar sgom pa de ltar 'gyur //
NK094(nge)001:13220: de ni rtags chen thob pa yin //
NK094(nge)001:13221: zhes gsungs pas yid ches par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:13226: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:13227: blo'i rtsal rdzogs nas gang gis las gang snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:13228: me phung dang chu rlung gnon pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13229: rlung chen 'byung ba rnams kyi rgyun dang nad kyi
NK094(nge)001:13230: zug rngu la sogas pa dag la yang gang gisa
NK094(nge)001:13231: yongsa su zhi bar gyur cig ces brjod pas zhi
NK094(nge)001:13232: ba dang / nad pa'i tshogs la gang na bar
NK094(nge)001:13233: se gol gtogs shing sos shig par brjod pas nad
NK094(nge)001:13234: zhi bar 'gyur ba'i ngag gi rtsal gyis bden pa'i
NK094(nge)001:13237: blo yi ting 'dzin rtsal rdzogs na //
NK094(nge)001:13238: ngag gi bden pa'i rtsal 'byung ste //
NK094(nge)001:13239: srid pa'i me chen mthong ba na //
NK094(nge)001:13240: zhi bar gyur cig byas pa yis //
NK094(nge)001:13241: de nyid du ni zhi bar 'gyur //
NK094(nge)001:13242: chu rlung gnod pa'i rgyun byung na //
NK094(nge)001:13243: chad par gyur cig brjod pa yis //
NK094(nge)001:13244: de nyid du ni chad par 'gyur //
NK094(nge)001:13245: rlung chen gnod pa'i rgyun byung na //
NK094(nge)001:13246: zhi bar gyur cig brjod pa yis //
NK094(nge)001:13247: de nyid du ni chad par 'gyur //
NK094(nge)001:13248: nad pa'i tshogs ni mthong ba na //
NK094(nge)001:13249: gang na na ba'i dmigs der ni //
NK094(nge)001:13250: se gol gtogs pa tsam gyis nas //
NK094(nge)001:13251: nad rnams zhi bar 'gyur zhes brjod //
NK094(nge)001:13252: nad kyi tshogs rnams zhi bar 'gyur //
NK094(nge)001:13253: de bzhin ngag gis brjod byas pas //
NK094(nge)001:13260: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:13261: lus kyi rtsal gang zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:13262: muna pa'i skye mched kyi gnyid chom pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13263: lus kyi bzoda pa thob pas /
NK094(nge)001:13264: tsha grang lci yang snyoms te bzod pa ni dang po'i drod do //
NK094(nge)001:13265: khams kyi zas bral yang mdangs dang dbang po gsal ba drod gnyis pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:13266: shing bal lta bur yang ba dang khams bde mi
NK094(nge)001:13267: bde med pas nad dang bral zhing bde ba ni
NK094(nge)001:13268: drod brtan pa dang gsum mo //
NK094(nge)001:13269: lus kyi rtags drod gnyis pa 'di ni ting nge 'dzin gyi ro tshor ba'i rtags so //
NK094(nge)001:13270: skyil krung gi khru gang tsam du 'phar ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13271: t+aa la gang tsam du 'gro ba rtags thob pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:13272: nam mkha' la gom pas 'gro ba dang chu la
NK094(nge)001:13273: mi bying sa la 'dzul ba dang mes mi 'tshig
NK094(nge)001:13274: rlung 'ching bar nus pa sogs 'byung ba kun la
NK094(nge)001:13275: thogs pa med par bde blag tu 'dod pa ji
NK094(nge)001:13276: bzhina du bsam rgu kun 'grub pa ni rtags brtan
NK094(nge)001:13277: pa'o // mthu'i rtsal gang zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:13278: gang min pa'i dngos po sa rdo bye ma las
NK094(nge)001:13279: gser dngul la sogs pa dngos po gzhan gang du
NK094(nge)001:13280: bsgyur ba dang / gang med pa lasa dngos po
NK094(nge)001:13281: ganga 'byin pa skam sa las chur 'byin pa dang
NK094(nge)001:13282: bsgyur ba dang / / sol ba las ljon shing skyed pa la sogs pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:13286: ngo mtshar rdzas rnyed kyi tshul rtags ni gang snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:13287: nor bu la sogs pa yida du 'onga ba'i nor rnyed pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13288: sems la 'doda rgu thams cad grub cing 'byung ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13289: rdzas mchog ngo mtshar can rnyed par 'gyur ba ste /
NK094(nge)001:13291: spyod pa'i mthu dang rtsal rdzogs na //
NK094(nge)001:13295: rdzas kyi mchog tu gyur pa yi //
NK094(nge)001:13296: ngo mtshar can yang rnyed par 'gyur //
NK094(nge)001:13297: de dag rung ba'i snga ltas so //
NK094(nge)001:13303: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:13304: 'gro gang 'dun pa'i snga ltas bstan pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:13305: 'gro ba kun bdag la dag'a bar sems pas kun gyis bdag khur zhing gus pas 'dud pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13306: bdag kun gyis yida du 'ong zhing 'thad pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13307: bdag gis kun la ji ltar 'dul ba ltar dabnga
NK094(nge)001:13308: bsgyur ba'i gtso bo mchog grub pa'i ltas kyang 'byung
NK094(nge)001:13309: ba'o // de dag las rtags ni /
NK094(nge)001:13310: lha la dmigs pa las dang po pa la'ang 'byung zhing /
NK094(nge)001:13311: mi rtog pa la dmigs pa las ni sa bzhi pa yan chad du 'byung la /
NK094(nge)001:13312: ngag gi rtsal dang mthu ni /
NK094(nge)001:13313: lam gyi rim pa las 'dun pa nas sar nye ba na yang 'byung ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:13314: skabs su mtshan ma so sor sgrubs pas grub pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:13315: sa bzhi pa nas yar 'byung ngo //
NK094(nge)001:13316: 'dun pa la ni rgya che chung sbyar te /
NK094(nge)001:13317: ngo mtshar rdzas ni drod rtags thob nas 'byung ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:13319: bag chags byang ba'i ltas brgyad /
NK094(nge)001:13320: 'jigs pa dang bral ba'i ltas brgyad //
NK094(nge)001:13323: sangs rgyas kyi sras kyi ltas brgyad /
NK094(nge)001:13324: chos la dbang thob pa'i ltas bco lnga /
NK094(nge)001:13325: bden pa mthong ba'i ltas brgyad /
NK094(nge)001:13331: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:13332: mtshan ma pra'i rmi ltas gang zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:13333: bag chags 'byong ba'i ltas thog mar 'chad de /
NK094(nge)001:13334: yul la dngos por kun tu brtags pa'i bag chags
NK094(nge)001:13335: kyi yul rnams 'byang ba lasa rtags sngona du byung
NK094(nge)001:13336: ba'i ltas ni / rtag pa sgren mor 'byung ba rmi ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13337: rtag par chus 'akhru zhing khrus byed par rmi ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13338: dri ma rnam par daga par rmi ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13339: chu bo chen po 'bogas te brgal ba'i bar 'gyur ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13340: mtsho chu la rkyal ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13343: me dpung gis bsregsa pa daga rlung chen pos g.yenga bar byed pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13344: de yis rnam para 'thor bar bya ba rmi ba
NK094(nge)001:13345: dang bcu po 'di dag gang rnams ni so so'i
NK094(nge)001:13346: bag chags rnams sbyong ba nyid rnam par daga cing
NK094(nge)001:13347: 'byang ba'i ltas te sa bcu'i rim par skye'o //
NK094(nge)001:13350: rnam grangs brgyad kyi sgren mor 'byung bas dang po
NK094(nge)001:13351: dang gnyis par sbyar te rkyen gyis 'gyur ba las
NK094(nge)001:13352: kyi bag chags dag pa'i ltas dang /
NK094(nge)001:13353: khrus byed pa sa gsum pa dang sa bzhi par
NK094(nge)001:13354: sbyar te mngon du rgyu ba'i bag chags rags pa
NK094(nge)001:13356: rnam par dag pa sa lnga pa dang sbyar te
NK094(nge)001:13357: mngon du rgyu ba'i bag chags cha phra ba dag
NK094(nge)001:13358: pa'i rtags dang / chu bo 'bogs rkyal sa drug
NK094(nge)001:13359: pa dang sbyar te kun tu 'gro ba'i bag chags
NK094(nge)001:13361: char rgyun gyis 'khru ba sa bdun pa dang sbyar
NK094(nge)001:13362: te lhan cig skyes pa'i bag chags dag pa'i rtags
NK094(nge)001:13363: dang / bum chu 'byung ba sa brgyad pa dang
NK094(nge)001:13364: sbyar te bag la nyal gyi bag chags rags pa
NK094(nge)001:13366: me dpung gis bsregs pa sa dgu pa dang sbyar zhing /
NK094(nge)001:13367: rlung chen pos g.yeng 'thor sa bcu pa dang sbyar
NK094(nge)001:13368: te bag la nyal ba cha phra ba shin tu
NK094(nge)001:13369: rnam par dag pa'i rtags so //
NK094(nge)001:13372: mtshan ma pra yi rmi ltas kyang //
NK094(nge)001:13373: shin tu rgya cher 'byung ba ste //
NK094(nge)001:13374: rnal 'byor can gyis shes par gyis //
NK094(nge)001:13375: bag chags sbyang ba'i snga ltas kyang //
NK094(nge)001:13376: rtag pa gcer bur 'byung ba dang //
NK094(nge)001:13377: khrus chen rtag tu byed pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13378: dri ma'i tshogs rnams dag pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13379: chu bo dag la rgal ba dang //
NK094(nge)001:13380: mtsho chu dag la rkyal ba dang //
NK094(nge)001:13381: char gyi rgyun gyis 'khru ba dang //
NK094(nge)001:13382: gzhan gyis bum pa gang ba'i chus //
NK094(nge)001:13383: bdag gi lus la ldugs pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13384: me dpung chen pos bsregs pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13385: shin tu mthon po'i rtse dag las //
NK094(nge)001:13386: rlung gis shin tu g.yeng zhing 'thor //
NK094(nge)001:13387: 'di dag bag chags sbyong ba'i ltas //
NK094(nge)001:13389: dgu po sa dgu man chad dang sbyar bar gsungs so //
NK094(nge)001:13394: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:13395: gang 'dira 'jigas pa dang bral ba'i snga ltas bstan pa yanga /
NK094(nge)001:13396: g.yul 'gyed pa zhi nas slar log pa rmi ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13397: nad kyi zug rngu byang zhing sos pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13398: btson ra la tha mar thar ba'am thag pa grol ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13399: gsheda ma'i lag nas shor te de lasa thar ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13400: gcan gzan gdug pa'i tshogsa kyi nang nas 'bros te bral ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13401: dug nad sos nas zhi ba rmi ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13402: bcingsa pa las grola ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13403: thag pa bcad pa rmi ba rnams 'jigs pa dang
NK094(nge)001:13404: bral ba'i ltas bazanga po yin te sa brgyad dang
NK094(nge)001:13406: yang na dang po gsum sa lnga pa'i bar du sbyar te /
NK094(nge)001:13407: g.yul zhi ba dang po dang gnyis par ngan 'gro ba'i 'jig pa chen po las thar ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13408: zug rngu byang ba gsum pa dang bzhi par 'bring las thar ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13409: btson las grol ba lnga par chung ngu las kyang grol ba'i ltas so //
NK094(nge)001:13410: gshed ma las thar ba 'khor ba'i 'jigs pa chen po las thar ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:13411: gdug pa'i tshogs bral ba mthong lam gyi 'du byed chung ngu dang bral ba sa bdun pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:13412: dug nad zhi ba brgyad par mi g.yo ba thob pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:13413: bcings pa grol ba dgu par ye shes mngon du byed pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:13414: thag pa bcad pa bcu par bag la nyal gyi bzhi rtsa bcad pa ste /
NK094(nge)001:13415: chos rje'i phyag mchan ltar ro //
NK094(nge)001:13420: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:13421: khyad para dam pa thob pa'i sngon du byung ba'i ltas bstan pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:13423: shinga phal pa'i skas la 'dzegs dang /
NK094(nge)001:13427: ri bo'i rtse la 'dzegs pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13429: nam mkha'i skas la 'dzegs pa dang brgyad de /
NK094(nge)001:13431: sa rnams thob pa'i snga ltas ni //
NK094(nge)001:13432: khri rkang dag la 'dzegs pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13433: phal pa'i skas la 'dzegs pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13434: ljon shing dag la 'dzegs pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13435: gyen du shin tu 'gro ba dang //
NK094(nge)001:13436: ri bo'i rtse la 'dzegs pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13437: rin chen skas la 'dzegs pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13438: mchod rten dag la 'dzegs pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13439: nam mkha'i skas la 'dzegs pa rnams //
NK094(nge)001:13440: 'di dag don gyi snga ltas yin //
NK094(nge)001:13441: zhes ltas brgyad sa brgyad dang sbyar bar gsungs so //
NK094(nge)001:13442: chos rje'i phyag mchan sogs las /
NK094(nge)001:13443: shing dang ljon shing gcig tu byas nas bdun du
NK094(nge)001:13444: bgrang ste rigs chen 'byed pa nas 'byung bas sa
NK094(nge)001:13445: bzhi pa yan chad kyi ltas su bzhed de sa
NK094(nge)001:13446: gong nas gong du 'aphara ba'i ltas dam par 'gyur
NK094(nge)001:13451: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:13452: sa gang la gansa pa dang sa gang de nyid nona pa'i rtags bstan pa yanga /
NK094(nge)001:13453: khri mthona po'i steng la 'dug pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13456: khyung chen mkha' la lding ba'i 'dab chagsa zhon pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13457: machada rten gyi rtse la phyin pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13458: ri bo'i rtse'i spo la 'dug pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13459: nam mkha'i dbyingsa na 'dug pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13460: lus lasa sprin dpung 'byung ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13461: nyi ma dang zla ba'i steng la 'dug pa dang dagu'o //
NK094(nge)001:13462: 'di dag 'gyur dbang ma nges pa'i sa ma gtogs
NK094(nge)001:13463: pa dgu gang 'thob par yas nas go rims su
NK094(nge)001:13464: sbyar te bshad pa dang 'chad pa la'ang sbyar ro
NK094(nge)001:13465: // kha cig ni 'di dag spyir sa non pa'i
NK094(nge)001:13466: ltas te go rims mi sbyar zhes kyang 'chad pa
NK094(nge)001:13468: chos rje'i phyag mchan sogs na /
NK094(nge)001:13469: lus las sprin 'byung ba dang nyi zla la 'dug
NK094(nge)001:13470: cing zhon pa rnams gcig gi dbang du mdzad de
NK094(nge)001:13471: grangs brgyad du byas nas sa dang po nas brgyad
NK094(nge)001:13472: pa man chad du sbyar ro //
NK094(nge)001:13474: sa rnams non pa'i snga ltas kyang //
NK094(nge)001:13475: khri mthon steng na 'dug pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13476: glang po che la zhon pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13477: seng ge dag la zhon pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13478: khyung chen lding la zhon pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13479: mchod rten kha la phyin pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13480: ri bo'i rtse la 'dug pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13481: nam mkha'i dbyings na 'dug pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13482: lus las sprin phung 'byung ba dang //
NK094(nge)001:13483: zla ba'i steng na 'dug pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13484: nyi ma'i steng na 'dug pa rnams //
NK094(nge)001:13485: rnal 'byor sa la gnas pa'i rtags //
NK094(nge)001:13486: zhes gsungs pas snga ltas bcu po sa bcu re re la sbyar bar bshad do //
NK094(nge)001:13487: ltas de dag gang la byung ba ni sa'i rim pa non te gnas pa'i rtagsa so //
NK094(nge)001:13492: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:13493: dama pa'i rigas kyi sngon du byung ba'i sangs rgyas kyi sras kyi snga ltas bstan pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:13494: rgyal pos bka' la btagsa pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13495: bka'i dbang po'am rgyal po'i blon po dbang can du bskos pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13496: gzhan la dbang bsgyur bar byed pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13497: 'jig rten pa skos la 'debas pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13498: gzhan gyi sde pa dabnga du sdud pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13499: g.yul 'thab pa las rgyal ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13500: bdag nyid rgyal pora gyur pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13501: mgo la me tog gi thod skyes pa'am bcings pa dang brgyad de /
NK094(nge)001:13503: sangs rgyas sras kyi snga ltas ni //
NK094(nge)001:13504: rgyal pos bka' la btags pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13505: bka' yi dbang por bskos pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13506: gzhan la dbang sgyur byed pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13508: gzhan gyi sde pa dbang sdud dang //
NK094(nge)001:13509: g.yul chen dag las rgyal ba dang //
NK094(nge)001:13510: bdag nyid rgyal por gyur pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13511: mgo la me tog skyed pa rnams //
NK094(nge)001:13512: rgyal ba'i sras su gyur pa'i ltas //
NK094(nge)001:13513: zhes gsungs te mchan rnying du sa brgyad pa man chad dang sbyar bar bshad kyang /
NK094(nge)001:13514: chos rje'i phyag mchan du sa gsum pa yan chad
NK094(nge)001:13515: la sbyar bar gsungs pa nyid legs sam snyam ste
NK094(nge)001:13521: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:13522: chos kyi dngos po gang la dbang thob cing mnga'
NK094(nge)001:13523: dabnga sgyur ba'i sngona du byung ba yi ltas bco
NK094(nge)001:13524: lnga ni / glegsa bam zab mo rnyed pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13525: de 'bri zhing de la lta bar byed pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13526: de la bsam dpyod byed pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13527: gazhana la 'chad cing ston pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13529: me longa la lta ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13530: shel gyi bum pa ganga ba la lta rtog byed cing brtags te 'thung ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13531: rin po che nora bu thu ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13532: 'khora lo lag tu baba pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13534: ri raba klad la bskor ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13535: nam mkha' ganga la rnga dung dril bu sogs rol
NK094(nge)001:13536: mo'i sgra rgyas te stong gsum gang ba thos pa
NK094(nge)001:13537: dang / dngosa po mtha'a daga yi ger mthong ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13538: de nyid klagsa pasa ngo mtshar chen po kun la skyed pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13539: nam mkha'a lasa me tog gi char mgo la 'bebas pa dang bco lnga'ang rim par sbyar ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:13540: de'ang chos rje'i phyag mchan las /
NK094(nge)001:13541: glegs bam rnyed pa sa dang po /
NK094(nge)001:13543: gzhan la ston pa gsum pa /
NK094(nge)001:13545: me long la lta ba lnga pa /
NK094(nge)001:13547: nor bu thu ba bdun pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13549: nyi zla zin pa dgu pa /
NK094(nge)001:13550: ri rab bskor ba man chad sa bcu pa dang sbyar ro zhes gsungs /
NK094(nge)001:13552: chos la dbang thob snga ltas ni //
NK094(nge)001:13553: glegs bam zab mo rnyed pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13554: de bzhin 'bri ba mang po dang //
NK094(nge)001:13555: de dag la ni dpyod pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13556: gzhan la 'chad cing ston pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13557: don nyid gtan la 'bebs pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13558: me long dag la lta ba dang //
NK094(nge)001:13559: shel gyi bum pa gang ba la //
NK094(nge)001:13560: lta zhing brtags te 'thung ba dang //
NK094(nge)001:13561: rin chen nor bu thu ba dang //
NK094(nge)001:13563: nyi zla lag pas zin pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13564: ri rab klad la skor ba rnams //
NK094(nge)001:13565: chos la dbang thob snga ltas so //
NK094(nge)001:13567: rig 'dzin lnga'i rnal 'byor bcu gcig la sbyar bar gsungs so //
NK094(nge)001:13572: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:13573: bden pa dama pa mthonga ba'i snga ltas su sngona du byung ba yi rtags ni /
NK094(nge)001:13574: sngona ma mthonga ba'i yul mthonga ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13575: stong gsum rgya cher mthonga ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13576: gling rnams gzhan du bgrod de mthong ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13577: ri raba kyi rtser ram kha la phyin nas thamsa cad mthonga ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13578: nam mkha'a mtha'a yasa pa nyid rgya cher mthonga ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13579: rgya mtsho'i gting du phyin pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13580: lag na sgron me thogsa pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13581: snang srid kun la dpyod pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13582: nyi ma'i snying po lta ba dang dagu'o //
NK094(nge)001:13583: de'ang chos rje'i phyag mchan sogs su /
NK094(nge)001:13584: sgron me thogs pa dang snang srid dpyod pa gnyis
NK094(nge)001:13585: gcig tu byas nas rnam grangs brgyad du mdzad de
NK094(nge)001:13586: / nam mkha' mtha' med mthong ba'i bar sa gnyis pa nas drug pa'i bar dang /
NK094(nge)001:13587: de nas rgya mtsho'i gting du phyin pa chos nyid
NK094(nge)001:13588: kyi dgongs pa zab mo rtogs pa'i ltas te sa
NK094(nge)001:13589: bdun pa / sgron me thogs te snang srid dpyod pas brgyad pa dang dgu pa /
NK094(nge)001:13590: nyi ma'i snying por lta ba rang byung ye shes
NK094(nge)001:13591: rtogs pa'i ltas te sa bcu pa dang sbyar bar
NK094(nge)001:13592: mdzad do // rtsa rgyud las ni /
NK094(nge)001:13593: bden pa mthong ba'i snga ltas kyang //
NK094(nge)001:13594: sngon ma mthong gi yul mthong dang //
NK094(nge)001:13595: stong gsum rgya cher mthong ba dang //
NK094(nge)001:13596: gling rnams gzhan du phyin pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13597: ri rab kha la phyin pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13598: nam mkha' rgya cher mthong ba dang //
NK094(nge)001:13599: rgya mtsho'i gting du phyin pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13600: lag na sgron ma thogs pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13601: nyi ma'i snying po lta ba dang //
NK094(nge)001:13602: snang srid dpyod par byed pa rnams //
NK094(nge)001:13603: chos la dbang thob ltas chen yin //
NK094(nge)001:13604: zhes gsungs te sa dgu pa man chad kyi byang chub kyi sems dang sbyar bar mdzad do //
NK094(nge)001:13609: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:13610: lung bstan pa chen po thob pa'i snga ltas sngon du byung ba ni /
NK094(nge)001:13611: rola mo rnams kyi sgra thos pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13613: seng ge'i nga ro grags pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13614: chos kyi bgro bar byed pa'i gtam thos pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13615: gzugs brnyan gyi sku zhal 'dzum zhing 'oda 'abyung ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13616: rnam 'dren sangs rgyas dam pa'i gsung thos shing sku mi mthong ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13617: lha mo rnams glu dbyangs sgrogs pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13618: gazhala yasa khang dag las chos sgra 'byung ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13619: gcig la gcig grogsa po dam pa zhes 'bod pa
NK094(nge)001:13620: 'byung zhing chos kyi de nyid bgro bar byed pa
NK094(nge)001:13621: dang dgu ste rtsa ba brgyad dang yan lag bcu
NK094(nge)001:13623: de'ang lung bstan pa 'di dag chos rje'i phyag mchan las /
NK094(nge)001:13624: sa gnyis pa nas rim par sa drug pa la
NK094(nge)001:13625: gzugs brnyan zhal 'dzum pa dang 'od 'byung ba gnyis
NK094(nge)001:13626: dang gzhan rnams re rer sbyar nas gsungs so //
NK094(nge)001:13627: dgu'i dbang ltar rtsa rgyud las kyang /
NK094(nge)001:13628: lung bstan thob pa'i snga ltas ni //
NK094(nge)001:13629: rol mo'i sgra rnams thos pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13630: 'brug gi sgra ni grags pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13631: seng ge'i nga ro grags pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13632: chos kyi bgro ba'i gtam thos dang //
NK094(nge)001:13633: gzugs brnyan zhal ni 'dzum pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13634: sangs rgyas gsung thos sku mi mthong //
NK094(nge)001:13635: lha mo glu dbyangs sgrogs pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13636: gzhal yas dag las sgra 'byung dang //
NK094(nge)001:13637: grogs po grogs po zhes brjod cing //
NK094(nge)001:13638: chos kyi bgro ba byed pa rnams //
NK094(nge)001:13639: lung bstan 'byung ba'i snga ltas so //
NK094(nge)001:13641: las dang po pa'i skabs lam du zhugs te rnal
NK094(nge)001:13642: 'byor spyod pa'i tshe na rmi ltas la sogs pa
NK094(nge)001:13643: de dag byung na ji ltar shes par bya ba
NK094(nge)001:13645: de la sogs pa'i mtshan ma rnams //
NK094(nge)001:13646: ltas chen kun tu snang ba dang //
NK094(nge)001:13647: gang zag las kyi dang po rnams //
NK094(nge)001:13648: rig 'dzin so so'i sa bar ni //
NK094(nge)001:13649: 'gyur ba'i snga ltas bshad pa yin //
NK094(nge)001:13650: rnal 'byor las kyi dang po la //
NK094(nge)001:13653: don la rtogs shing sa rnams sbyong //
NK094(nge)001:13654: des ni don la reg par 'gyur //
NK094(nge)001:13655: zhes pa'i don gyis ltas skye ba'i dus ni /
NK094(nge)001:13656: 'dun pa'i rnal 'byor las dang po pa la gnas pa'i tshe skye bar gsungs te /
NK094(nge)001:13657: de yang skabs kyis gnyis su 'gyur te /
NK094(nge)001:13658: gzhi las dang po pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13659: skabs kyi las dang po pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:13660: de la 'dun pa'i rnal 'byor gzhi'i las dang po'i
NK094(nge)001:13661: dbang du ni snga mar sbyangs pa'i rgyus da ltar
NK094(nge)001:13662: skad cig la gzhi bar snang ba'i yang ltas dang
NK094(nge)001:13663: sbyar nas ltas dang mthun pa'i sa gong ma gang
NK094(nge)001:13665: gzhi nas brtsam mi dgos so //
NK094(nge)001:13666: ltas kun kyang da ltar sa gar 'byung ba de skabs 'dir skye ba mi 'gal lo //
NK094(nge)001:13667: de bas na rtsa ba'i rgyud las /
NK094(nge)001:13668: nges pa'i snga ltas rnam pa lnga //
NK094(nge)001:13669: rgyu yi dus na 'byung ba ni //
NK094(nge)001:13671: so so'i sa par zhes sngar drangs pa'i sgras ltas rnams kyang 'phags pa dkon mchog brtsegs pa las /
NK094(nge)001:13672: rmi lam brgya rtsa brgyad gsungs pa'i rtsa ba las /
NK094(nge)001:13673: yan lag bye ba rnams mtho dman dang sbyar ba'i
NK094(nge)001:13674: ltas su gsungs pa mtshungs par 'dir yang mi rigs
NK094(nge)001:13676: rtsa ba brgyad kyi dbang du ni bag chags 'byang ba'i ltas byung na /
NK094(nge)001:13678: sa thob pa dang chos la dbang thob pa'i ltas byung na /
NK094(nge)001:13682: bden pa mthong ba'i snga ltas byung na /
NK094(nge)001:13684: lung bstan thob pa'i snga ltas byung na /
NK094(nge)001:13685: lung chen thob pa'i rnal 'byor du 'gyur ro //
NK094(nge)001:13686: sangs rgyas sras kyi snga ltas byung na /
NK094(nge)001:13687: rtsa chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor du 'gyur ro //
NK094(nge)001:13688: des na rtags dang po'i sa gcig nas de dag
NK094(nge)001:13689: re re'ang so so bar 'gyur ba'i ltas yin pas
NK094(nge)001:13690: / mthun par 'du 'dzi bsal la 'bad par bya ba'i don ni /
NK094(nge)001:13691: yan lag gi bshad pa'i dbang du sngar bstan pa
NK094(nge)001:13692: ltar go rims su sa bcu dang sbyar la 'bad
NK094(nge)001:13693: do // de ni rmi lam la khyad par yod
NK094(nge)001:13694: pa'i phyir re re'i yan lag kyang sa rnams dang
NK094(nge)001:13696: de'i phyir cho 'phrul sgrub pa'i ting nge 'dzin brgyad dang /
NK094(nge)001:13697: tshogs la sogs pa gang 'dod pa'i rgyu de la /
NK094(nge)001:13698: las dang po lha'i rnal 'byor brtan ma thag sbyar bas cig char tshul du'ang 'gyur ro //
NK094(nge)001:13699: skabs kyi las dang po pa'i dbang du ni /
NK094(nge)001:13700: sa 'og ma nas gong mar 'thob ma thag pa ni rang gi las dang po pa ste /
NK094(nge)001:13701: des na rmi ltas kyang gcig tu mi skye ste /
NK094(nge)001:13702: 'og ma la gnas tsam na gong mar 'thob pa'i
NK094(nge)001:13703: ltas 'byung bas skabs lnga dang bcu gar skye zhes
NK094(nge)001:13704: 'chad do // de la ltas rnams gcig tu skye'o zhe na'ang /
NK094(nge)001:13705: las dang por shin tu mtho ba'i ltas 'char ba'i rgyur mi rung ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13706: gal te 'char du rung yang 'og nas ma bgrod par ltas dang sbyar te /
NK094(nge)001:13707: gong ma'i yang gong mar bgrod du btub na /
NK094(nge)001:13708: lam rim par bzhag pa la'ang dgos pa med la /
NK094(nge)001:13709: de ste min na rim gyis pa dang cig char ba'ang bye brag med par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:13710: de ltar bden na'ang ltas rim pa skye ba kho nar nges na /
NK094(nge)001:13712: las dang po pa kho nar skye bar gsungs pa'ang 'gal bar 'gyur ba /
NK094(nge)001:13713: gong du bshad pa'i don gyi khong nyid kyi 'grel te /
NK094(nge)001:13714: lam gnyis ni shes rab la khyad par yod pas
NK094(nge)001:13715: ltas kyi mtshan mas sgrub ste 'phar ba'ang mnyam pa
NK094(nge)001:13716: ma yin no // gnyis pa la bzhi ste /
NK094(nge)001:13725: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:13726: de ltar sa bgrod pas rig 'dzin thob nas mthu'i rtsal ji lta bu 'byung snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:13727: de ltar rig 'dzina dam pa'i sa bcu la rtsal
NK094(nge)001:13728: dang sbyar te ltas shar nas bgrod de rtsal chen
NK094(nge)001:13729: rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin
NK094(nge)001:13730: thob pa'i skabs su byin rlabsa mthu yi cho 'phrul
NK094(nge)001:13731: 'byung ba yang / rnam grangs bzhi las /
NK094(nge)001:13732: dang po rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:13733: nyi ma dang zla ba zhona te 'gro ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13734: ri bo mchog rab sked nas gsora ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13735: 'jiga rten gyi khams rgyang mar 'phena pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13736: bsrega pa'i bskal pa gzhila ba la sogas pa'i mthu
NK094(nge)001:13737: yi cho 'phrul nyi shu thob pa thamsa cad kun
NK094(nge)001:13738: rdzu 'phrul gyi khyad para la gnas pa'i rtsal gyis
NK094(nge)001:13739: stobs las ston para nus pa yin te /
NK094(nge)001:13741: rig 'dzin sa la gnas pa dang //
NK094(nge)001:13742: sa la rtsal chen sbyong ba'i tshe //
NK094(nge)001:13744: nyi zla zhon nas 'gro ba dang //
NK094(nge)001:13745: ri rab sked nas gsor ba dang //
NK094(nge)001:13747: sreg pa'i bskal pa gzhil ba la //
NK094(nge)001:13748: sogs pa'i cho 'phrul thams cad kun //
NK094(nge)001:13749: khyad par rtsal gyis ston par nus //
NK094(nge)001:13750: de la sogs pa'i rdzu 'phrul rnams //
NK094(nge)001:13757: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:13758: gang 'dul ba'i snod du rung ba'i gdul bya'i 'gro ba thamsa cad kun la /
NK094(nge)001:13759: rang rang so so'i skad dang chos mthun para ji
NK094(nge)001:13760: ltar 'dul ba'i thabs kyi sgo ni sna tshogsa pa
NK094(nge)001:13761: rnams su gang la gang gis ji ltar 'dul ba
NK094(nge)001:13762: de ltar ston par nus pa ni gsung rjes su
NK094(nge)001:13765: rjes su bstan pa'i cho 'phrul ni //
NK094(nge)001:13767: so so'i skad du chos mthun par //
NK094(nge)001:13768: 'dul ba'i sgo ni sna tshogs su //
NK094(nge)001:13769: so so'i skad du ston par nus //
NK094(nge)001:13770: de dag rjes su bstan pa yin //
NK094(nge)001:13776: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:13777: rnal 'byor mchog gi rtogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK094(nge)001:13778: rtsal gyi khyad para la brten pa'i thabs kyis stong
NK094(nge)001:13779: chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khamas kun gyi phyi nang
NK094(nge)001:13780: thams cad rab tu g.yosa nas kyang gdul bya ma
NK094(nge)001:13781: lus pa thamsa cada mchog tu ngo mtshar cher skyes
NK094(nge)001:13782: par gyur te dag'a magu dang rangsa pa'i ro myong
NK094(nge)001:13783: bar 'gyur pa ni chos snang ba'i cho 'phrul nyid
NK094(nge)001:13785: chos kyi sgo rnams snang ba yi //
NK094(nge)001:13786: nges pa'i cho 'phrul bstan pa ni //
NK094(nge)001:13787: ting 'dzin rtsal gyi khyad par gyis //
NK094(nge)001:13788: 'jig rten khams kun g.yos nas kyang //
NK094(nge)001:13789: thams cad ngo mtshar skye gyur te //
NK094(nge)001:13790: sems kyi bsam pa rangs byas nas //
NK094(nge)001:13791: so so dga' ba'i ro myong 'gyur //
NK094(nge)001:13792: chos snang ba yi cho 'phrul yin //
NK094(nge)001:13798: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:13799: gsang ba'i yi ge sna tshogs kyi phreng ba lasa /
NK094(nge)001:13800: rdzu 'phrul chos kyi sgra dbyangs rgya mtsho rnam par
NK094(nge)001:13801: bsgragsa pasa yod mthong snang gragsa kyi chos rnams kun
NK094(nge)001:13802: kyang gsang sngagsa mtshon pa'i sgor snang ste zab gsang
NK094(nge)001:13803: ston pa'i sngagsa su ma gyur pa'i brjod pa gang
NK094(nge)001:13804: yang med pa ni kun brjod pa'i cho 'phrul te
NK094(nge)001:13806: kun nas kun tu brjod pa ni //
NK094(nge)001:13807: gsang ba'i yi ge'i phreng ba las //
NK094(nge)001:13808: rdzu 'phrul chos kyi sgra sgrogs pas //
NK094(nge)001:13809: mthong yod snang grags chos rnams kun //
NK094(nge)001:13810: kun kyang sngags kyi sgra grags pas //
NK094(nge)001:13811: sngags su ma gyur gang yang med //
NK094(nge)001:13812: des na rtsal gyi khyad par la //
NK094(nge)001:13813: sogs pa'i yon tan thams cad 'byung //
NK094(nge)001:13815: bzhi pa mtshan bcas kyi ting nge 'dzin lha bsgom pa la gnyis te /
NK094(nge)001:13822: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:13823: rnal 'byor pas kun brjod pa la sogs pa bzhi
NK094(nge)001:13824: yi rgyu bzlas pa'i 'phro 'du la sogs pa rnams
NK094(nge)001:13825: / lam pa'i shes rab che chung gi rim pa'i khyad par las byung ba dag ni /
NK094(nge)001:13826: mi rtog pa'i shes rab la sbyangs pas blo gros
NK094(nge)001:13827: kyi rtsal gyi khyad par dag lasa byung ste las
NK094(nge)001:13828: dang so so'i mtshan ma grub pa yin pas snang
NK094(nge)001:13829: ba la rima gyis 'jug pa'i sa yi rim pa
NK094(nge)001:13830: dang / blo mchog cig char du 'jug pa'i khyad par gnyis su bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:13834: cho 'phrul sgrub pa'i ting nge 'dzin bshad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:13843: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:13844: de la rim gyis pa dang cig char ba'i sa
NK094(nge)001:13845: bcu nyid kyi khyad par gyi tshul bstan pa gang
NK094(nge)001:13846: snyam pa la / 'dun pa'i rnal 'byor pas dbugsa kyi yul tsam dang /
NK094(nge)001:13847: las dang po'i rnal 'byor gyis sna yis dri tshor ba tshun chad dang /
NK094(nge)001:13848: rigs chen pas rna bas sgra thos pa tsam dang /
NK094(nge)001:13849: mtshan ma rtags kyi rnal 'byor pas mig gis gzugs mthong ba tsam dang /
NK094(nge)001:13850: la sogsa te zhes pas bsdu ba spyod pa rgyun
NK094(nge)001:13851: gyi rnal 'byor pas gling gcig gang ba tsam dang
NK094(nge)001:13852: / dbugs chen pas khor yug chen pos khyab pa tsam dang /
NK094(nge)001:13853: lung chen pas stong gsum gyi khams gang ba tsam dang /
NK094(nge)001:13854: rtsal chen pas semsa kyi yul dang /
NK094(nge)001:13855: bde ba chen pos nam mkha'i dbyingsa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13856: lhun gyis grub pas chos kyi dbyingsa kyi mtha' klas
NK094(nge)001:13857: para khyab pa'i bar gsal ba man chad kyi go
NK094(nge)001:13859: de nyid sgom pa'i tshul gang zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:13860: bdag gi sgo gsum la ranga bzhina lhun grub tu
NK094(nge)001:13861: yod pa'i yi ge a ma skyes pa de las
NK094(nge)001:13862: ting nge 'dzin gyi dbang bsgyur te yi ge so
NK094(nge)001:13863: sor gsal nas sems nyid yan lag gi yi ge
NK094(nge)001:13864: ka kha la sogs pa lha so so yi rtsa
NK094(nge)001:13865: ba'i snying por gyur pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13866: la sogas pa zhes dngos po gzhan bsdu ba'i don
NK094(nge)001:13867: gyis bskyed pa'i snying po dang bzlas pa'i bsnyen sngags
NK094(nge)001:13869: rgyu'i yi ge'am rtsa ba'i snying po'i yig 'bru thugs
NK094(nge)001:13870: kar gdan gyi dkyil du gzhi gcig tu bzhag pa
NK094(nge)001:13871: la bzlas sngags phreng ba dang bcas pas bskor ba'o
NK094(nge)001:13872: // de dag bsgom pa'i tshul gong 'og gi khyad par ni /
NK094(nge)001:13873: de nas 'phro 'du'i tshad ring thung dang /
NK094(nge)001:13874: sku phyag rgya'i khyon che chung dang /
NK094(nge)001:13875: lha mang po blos mi 'phyogs pa dang 'phyogs pas
NK094(nge)001:13876: tshom bu'i grangsa mang nyung du sgom pa nyid kyang
NK094(nge)001:13877: de bzhina te rim pa yod pa yin no //
NK094(nge)001:13878: de bas na sngar tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor pa'i skabs
NK094(nge)001:13879: shig tu bshad pa'ang gtsor spyod pa'i dbang tsam ste
NK094(nge)001:13881: de ltar bshad pa 'di ni las dang po'i rnal
NK094(nge)001:13882: 'byor pa yi ge'i phyag rgya la 'jug pa'i blo
NK094(nge)001:13883: rimas kyi dbang du bstan par nges te /
NK094(nge)001:13884: de ltar mathara gyis 'dris shing gomsa par byed pa nyid du bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:13885: ltas shar nas mthu'i rtsal cho 'phrul bshad pa rnams kyi khyad par gyi rgyu mdor bstan pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:13886: yi ge kun rig pa'i ye shes kyi ngo bor
NK094(nge)001:13887: gsal ba lasa phyag rgya'i lhar bskrun te yi ge'i
NK094(nge)001:13888: gzugs su rang shar bar bsgom pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:13890: des bdag gzhan gyi dona byed pa nyid kyi phyir
NK094(nge)001:13891: yang de las 'phro 'du dang bcas pa'i sku phyag
NK094(nge)001:13892: rgyar bskyed de sgom pa 'byung ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:13894: sa dang po'i ting nge 'dzin bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:13895: sa gnyis pa'i ting nge 'dzin bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:13896: sa gsum pa dang bzhi pa'i ting nge 'dzin thun mong du bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:13897: sa lnga pa yan chad kyi ting nge 'dzin bshad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:13903: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:13905: desa na zhes tshul snga ma la snyegs pa ni gtan tshigs su bzhag pa ste /
NK094(nge)001:13906: don gyi gtso bo ting nge 'dzina gyi khyad para yanga /
NK094(nge)001:13907: lha de nyid dam de kho na nyid don gyi ngo bo gciga la bsgom par byed moda kyi /
NK094(nge)001:13908: don kyang mi mthun pa'i don gyis rnal 'byor pasa
NK094(nge)001:13909: ting nge 'dzin gyi rtsal 'phangs che chung dang mtho
NK094(nge)001:13910: dman gyi khyad par can du snang ba ni mi
NK094(nge)001:13911: gcig bar bsam pa'i yul ni sna tshogsa su rang
NK094(nge)001:13912: blo dang 'tshams par sgom pa'i don te /
NK094(nge)001:13913: de nyid gsal bar bstan pa gang snyam ba la /
NK094(nge)001:13914: khas blangs pa'i thun mong ma yin pa'i gsang ba'i lam 'ba' zhig tu 'chad pa'i don nyid de /
NK094(nge)001:13915: dang po 'gyur dbang ma nges pa'i sa la gnas
NK094(nge)001:13916: pa yi 'bad rtsol lhur len pa'i brtsamsa pa lasa
NK094(nge)001:13919: la sogsa pa zhes bcos ma'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK094(nge)001:13920: phra men spyod pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK094(nge)001:13923: dge bar 'dun pa'i rnal 'byor dang rnam grangs drug po dag gi skabs su /
NK094(nge)001:13924: dngos po lha'i dkyil 'khor du snang ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:13925: de nyid rang sems snang ba'i don yid la byed
NK094(nge)001:13926: pa tsam gyi lta ba yin pas shes raba kyi
NK094(nge)001:13927: rtsal gyi 'phangsa damsa pa'am dma' basa na /
NK094(nge)001:13928: ting nge 'dzina gyi rtsal yanga chung ba ste /
NK094(nge)001:13929: de kho na nyid rang gi mtshan nyid mthonga bar mi 'gyur basa na /
NK094(nge)001:13930: ranga gi bsam pas mosa shing dad pa yi rtog pa'i lha gang la dmigsa pa na'ang /
NK094(nge)001:13931: lha de yi sa bona h'u la sogs pa'i rtsa
NK094(nge)001:13932: ba'i yi ge gang yina pa las rigs kyi kha
NK094(nge)001:13933: doga dang dbyibsa kyis rnam par phye nasa ni /
NK094(nge)001:13934: 'phro 'du byed pa'i thabs kyang sna yi dbugsa la
NK094(nge)001:13935: rgyu ba dang yig 'bru mthun par byas te 'phro
NK094(nge)001:13936: ba yang phyi rol du dbugs de yi phyin pas
NK094(nge)001:13937: yul du gyur pa tshun chad kyi tshad tsam du
NK094(nge)001:13938: yab yum gyi yi ge zung sgril du 'oda zer
NK094(nge)001:13939: 'abra zhing 'phro ba gsal bar byas pa lasa 'phro
NK094(nge)001:13940: 'adu dang bcas pas don rdzogs pa dang slar rang
NK094(nge)001:13941: gnas su 'dus nas nang du tsit+ta'i dkyil du rtsa
NK094(nge)001:13942: ba'i yi ge la bstims nas byin rlabs gsal bar
NK094(nge)001:13943: bskyed par bya'o // sku yang rang gi rnam par
NK094(nge)001:13944: smin pa'i lus kyi chag tshad dang sbyar te khru
NK094(nge)001:13946: lha gcig gi sku yi khyon yanga de tsam zhig 'phyogs par bsam zhing sgom mo //
NK094(nge)001:13951: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:13952: sa gnyis par gyur pa'i rten pa gzhi yi sa la gnas pa yi rnal 'byor pas /
NK094(nge)001:13953: bka'a sdod las kyi rnala 'byor dang /
NK094(nge)001:13954: la sogas pa zhes dang po las kyi rnal 'byor dang /
NK094(nge)001:13955: bslab par sbyor ba'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK094(nge)001:13956: nges pa'i rnal 'byor dang rnam pa bzhi po rnams
NK094(nge)001:13957: kyi ting nge 'dzina gyi rtsal gyi khyad par ni
NK094(nge)001:13958: / rigs kyi sa bona gang yin pa'i ranga bzhina
NK094(nge)001:13959: gyi yi ge sgom pa la'ang 'od zer 'abra zhing
NK094(nge)001:13960: 'phro bar bacasa te sgom pa de yi 'phro 'du
NK094(nge)001:13961: yang dri 'byung ba'i sgo dri ma bsnams pa'i sna'i
NK094(nge)001:13962: yul ni tshun chad tsam du gsal te 'phro 'adu
NK094(nge)001:13963: gasla bar bskyed pa lasa sku yang ranga gi chag
NK094(nge)001:13964: tshad gnyis 'gyur du bsgyur ba'i khru brgyad tsam du
NK094(nge)001:13965: lha yab yum gnyis yan lag dang bcas pa'i sku
NK094(nge)001:13966: yi khyon yanga de tsam du gsal zhing sgom mo
NK094(nge)001:13971: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:13972: 'dir sa gsum pa dang bzhi pa'i ngo bo bstan pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:13973: lo ts+aa bas rtsa ba dang bshad rgyud gnyis ka las bka' chags pa'i don te /
NK094(nge)001:13974: des na gsum par gyur pa'i gal chen sbyong ba'i sa la gansa pa yi rnal 'byor pa la /
NK094(nge)001:13975: rigs chen 'byed pa gcig sgom zhing //
NK094(nge)001:13977: rigs chen 'byed pa'i rnal 'byor gcig las med pas /
NK094(nge)001:13978: lha'i sa bon rtsa ba'i yi ge yang chu dang
NK094(nge)001:13979: chab rom ltar rang rig pa nyid yi ger gsal
NK094(nge)001:13980: bas sku'i khyon chag tshad bzhi 'gyur tsam du bskyed
NK094(nge)001:13981: nas 'od zer dang bcas pa'i 'phro 'du sgra thos
NK094(nge)001:13982: pa'i yul tshun chad du gsal ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:13983: bzhi pa'i sa la gnas pa yi //
NK094(nge)001:13985: sa bzhi pa bslab pa rgyun gyi sa yi rnal
NK094(nge)001:13986: 'byor pas gsang sgo mtshon pa'i lung gi bka'a yi
NK094(nge)001:13987: sgo la rten pa'i rnal 'byor drod rtags g.yo ba
NK094(nge)001:13988: dang / la sogsa pa'i don gyis bsdu ba /
NK094(nge)001:13989: spyod pa rgyun gyi rnal 'byor drod rtags thob pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:13990: mtshan ma rtags kyi rnal 'byor drod rtags shin tu brtan pa dang gsum ste /
NK094(nge)001:13991: rnal 'byor rnam pa gsuma po rnams su dmigas pa'i ting nge 'dzina sgom pa 'di ltar 'doda de /
NK094(nge)001:13992: lha yi sa bona gang yina pa yang rigs kyi
NK094(nge)001:13993: rang bzhina gyi yi ger bsgyur bar byas te 'oda
NK094(nge)001:13994: zer 'bar ba dang bcas te gsal bar sgom pa
NK094(nge)001:13996: thos pa'i yul ni tshun chad du //
NK094(nge)001:13997: zhes pa sa gsum pa'i 'phro 'du yin pas /
NK094(nge)001:13999: gzugs mthong tshad kyi mthong ba'i yul tshun chad du 'phro 'adu gsal bar byas pa lasa /
NK094(nge)001:14001: ranga gi chag tshad bzhi 'gyur tsam gyi rigs gcig 'khor dang bcas pa sgom pa yin zhing /
NK094(nge)001:14003: rigs gsum 'khor dang bcas pa yi lha rnams chag
NK094(nge)001:14004: tshad brgyad 'gyur tsam du bskyed de sku yi khyon
NK094(nge)001:14005: yanga de tsam nyid du gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK094(nge)001:14006: 'on kyang rnal 'byor gsum nyid la'ang de gsal mi
NK094(nge)001:14007: gsal gyi cha yod de bshad pa dang 'chad par
NK094(nge)001:14012: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14013: de bzhina du sa lnga pa la sogs rnal 'byor
NK094(nge)001:14014: gyi rim pa bzhina du lha yi khyad para gang
NK094(nge)001:14015: yina pa yang yi ge'i rim pa bzhina du sbyar
NK094(nge)001:14016: nas 'phro 'du'i tshad kyang de bzhina du sgom pa
NK094(nge)001:14017: yin te sa lnga pa bsod nams gter gyi sa
NK094(nge)001:14018: la spyod pa rgyun gyi rnal 'byor pas lha'i sku
NK094(nge)001:14019: chag tshad bcu drug 'gyur du sgoms nas 'phro 'du
NK094(nge)001:14020: rgyang grags gcig tshun tshad do //
NK094(nge)001:14021: 'o na de bas 'og gi mthong thos ring ngo zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:14022: de ni mtho sa dang sgra chen po'i dbang ma yin te rnal ma'i dbang du brjod pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:14023: sa drug pa rten pas khyad par du 'gro ba'i sa la /
NK094(nge)001:14026: mnyam rdzogs chen po'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK094(nge)001:14027: nges par spyod pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK094(nge)001:14028: rtsal chen sbyor ba'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK094(nge)001:14030: rig par sbyor ba'i rnal 'byor dang bdun ni /
NK094(nge)001:14031: sku'i chag tshad sum cu rtsa gnyis 'gyur du gsal la /
NK094(nge)001:14032: 'phro 'du dpag tshad gcig tshun du gsal ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:14033: sa bdun pa dmigs pas 'bras bu skye ba'i sa la /
NK094(nge)001:14036: nges par 'byung ba'i rnal 'byor dang gsum gyis 'phro 'du gling gcig tshun chad du'o //
NK094(nge)001:14037: khyon chag tshad drug cu rtsa bzhi 'gyur du gsal ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:14038: brgyad pa gnas pa mi 'gyur ba'i sa la /
NK094(nge)001:14039: rmad byung rol pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK094(nge)001:14041: rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor dang gsum gyis 'phro
NK094(nge)001:14042: 'du sems kyis lcogs tshad dam 'khor yug gcig tshun
NK094(nge)001:14044: khyon ni chag tshad kyang sems kyi yul tshun chad
NK094(nge)001:14045: du'am brgya nyi shu rtsa brgyad 'gyur du gsal lo
NK094(nge)001:14046: // sa dgu pa gdal ba chos nyid kyi sa la /
NK094(nge)001:14047: rol pa rgyan gyi rnal 'byor dang /
NK094(nge)001:14048: bde ba chen po'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK094(nge)001:14049: thig ler rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor dang gsum gyis 'phro 'du byed pa'i ring thung yang /
NK094(nge)001:14050: nam mkha'i khams gang ba tshun chad de /
NK094(nge)001:14051: stong gsum gcig dang brgya stong bye ba la sogs
NK094(nge)001:14052: pa mtha' tshad med pa ma chad par gsal lo
NK094(nge)001:14053: // sku'i khyon yang nam mkha'i khams sku yis gang ba'i ngo bo nyid du sgoms te /
NK094(nge)001:14054: sa 'dir spyod yul ye she sgyu ma'i ngo bor gsal ba'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:14056: sgyu ma'ang sgyu ma yin spyod pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:14058: sa bcu pa rdzogs pa spyir chibs kyi sa la bdag nyid chen po'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK094(nge)001:14059: lhun gyis grub pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK094(nge)001:14060: klong yangs chub pa'i rnal 'byor dang gsum gyis ni /
NK094(nge)001:14061: sems kyi dbyings khyon tshad med pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:14062: sku yi khyon gyi khyad par yang //
NK094(nge)001:14063: chos kyi dbyings kyi mtha' klas par //
NK094(nge)001:14064: sku yi khyon gyis gang bar bsgom //
NK094(nge)001:14065: zhes pa 'phro 'du dang khyon gnyis ka sa dgu
NK094(nge)001:14066: par sbyangs pa'i stobs las byung ba'i tshad dang bral
NK094(nge)001:14067: ba'o // des na nam mkha'i khongs su chos nyid ma 'dus pa'i khyad par yod pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:14068: bshad pa de ltar rim pa bzhina du sbyar nas
NK094(nge)001:14069: kyang so so'i 'phro 'adu gasla bar gyur ba dang
NK094(nge)001:14070: / semsa kyi yul ni ji tsam du khyab par
NK094(nge)001:14071: spro zhing sku yi khyon gyi khyad para yanga de
NK094(nge)001:14072: ltar gsal te mthar chos kyi dbyingsa kyi mtha' klas
NK094(nge)001:14073: par gdal ba'i bar du sku yi khyon gyisa ganga
NK094(nge)001:14074: bar bsgom par byed de mthar phyin pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:14075: 'o na 'dir sa bcu bskyed pa'i rim pa la
NK094(nge)001:14076: 'di kho na ltar brgyud pa ni shin tu'ang lam
NK094(nge)001:14077: ring bas / rgyu'i theg pa dang bye brag med par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:14080: 'di ltar rims kyis slob pa yang rgya gar gyi 'phong slob pa dang mtshungs te /
NK094(nge)001:14081: 'dir sa dang po brtan par bya ba'i stobs kyis
NK094(nge)001:14082: gnyis pa yan chad du sbyangs dgos kyang bying rgod
NK094(nge)001:14083: bral bas dka' ba med par gyur pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:14084: rgyu la gnas pa ltar bsod nams la re ba
NK094(nge)001:14085: med pas bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin 'bras bu la
NK094(nge)001:14086: lam du byas pa nyid kyis /
NK094(nge)001:14087: tshe 'di nyid la nges par 'byung bas the tshom med pa dag go //
NK094(nge)001:14092: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14093: rim gyis pas 'grub tu btub pa'i tshul gang snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:14094: mthun pa'i dpe nye bar bzung ste ji ltar gsera
NK094(nge)001:14095: sbyangsa shing dri ma dag pa na kha dog gsal
NK094(nge)001:14097: de ltar rim par rig pa'i semsa nyid rtsal sbyangsa
NK094(nge)001:14098: pasa sgrib pa'i dri ma rags pa nas rim par
NK094(nge)001:14099: dag pas ting nge 'dzin de nyid gasla zhing 'phro
NK094(nge)001:14100: 'adu sbyor ba'i ting nge 'dzina 'di ltar sgoms te
NK094(nge)001:14101: rimsa kyis sbyongsa nas goms pa lasa mjug tu ciga
NK094(nge)001:14102: char du gsal ba'i drod thob par 'gyur ba la
NK094(nge)001:14104: shing thog ma le ka'i 'bru dang 'dra'o //
NK094(nge)001:14112: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14113: cig char 'jug pa'i rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin gang snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:14114: ston pa gsang bdag skyes bus sdud pa po lang ka'i bdag po la bos te /
NK094(nge)001:14115: cig char ba'i mtshan bcas kyi rnal 'byor nye bar bstan pa 'di lta ste /
NK094(nge)001:14116: blo che ba la don dang 'du 'bral med pas
NK094(nge)001:14117: chos rgyun chen po'i ting nge 'dzina gyi ngo bo
NK094(nge)001:14118: 'di ni thog mar gsang bdag nyid la ston pa
NK094(nge)001:14119: semsa dapa'a rdo rje'am rdo rje sems dpa' dam pasa
NK094(nge)001:14120: bshad cing bka' stsal bar mdzad de /
NK094(nge)001:14121: don 'di rgyun du 'bral bar med pa ni rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin chen po'o //
NK094(nge)001:14122: des na ting nge 'dzin 'di kun cig char ba la res mos su bstan du med de /
NK094(nge)001:14123: lhun gyis grub pa'i klong du rig pa 'phro 'du'i
NK094(nge)001:14124: thag chod pas rgyun gyi dus gcig tu mi g.yo
NK094(nge)001:14127: brtan par rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin /
NK094(nge)001:14128: bdud rtsi rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin /
NK094(nge)001:14129: mchod pa rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin /
NK094(nge)001:14130: sangs rgyas rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin /
NK094(nge)001:14131: bzlas pa rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin /
NK094(nge)001:14132: sbyor ba rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin /
NK094(nge)001:14133: sgrol ba rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin /
NK094(nge)001:14134: dkyil 'khor rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin no //
NK094(nge)001:14139: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14140: chos thams cad ril sems nyid 'od gsal ba'i ngo bor gyur pas /
NK094(nge)001:14141: nam mkha'a dona gyi glegsa bam la sna tshogsa riga
NK094(nge)001:14142: pasa yi ge rang gsal du bris te 'byung ba
NK094(nge)001:14143: chen po bzhi yi sgra bsgragsa pasa sgra ril gsang
NK094(nge)001:14144: ba mchog gi rang sgra ste theg chen gsang sngags
NK094(nge)001:14145: kyi sgra dbyangs rgyun mi 'chad pa nyid de blo
NK094(nge)001:14146: che ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang dngos po'i gnas thabs
NK094(nge)001:14151: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14152: 'khor 'das kyi chos so cog gi ranga bzhina ni /
NK094(nge)001:14153: byang chub sems kyi chos nyid de bzhina nyid lasa
NK094(nge)001:14154: ma g.yos pasa rtag chad kyi 'jigs pa thamsa cad
NK094(nge)001:14155: sel ba'i sems nyid skye shi'i mtha' las 'das pa'i
NK094(nge)001:14156: bdud rtsi ra sa yana du nges pas ranga byung
NK094(nge)001:14157: don gyi bdud rtsi chen po rgyun mi 'chad pa
NK094(nge)001:14162: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14163: 'khora ba rgya mtsho'i yo byad ma lus pa rnams kyang /
NK094(nge)001:14164: mnyes byed mchod pa rgya mtsho'i rang bzhina du bkod pa yin te /
NK094(nge)001:14165: srid pa rgya mtsho mtha' yasa pa kun tu snang
NK094(nge)001:14166: ba nyid ji bzhin pa'i gnas su stobs pa las
NK094(nge)001:14167: spyod yul yongs su dag pa nyid kyi phyir /
NK094(nge)001:14168: kun tu bzang po'i mchod sprin rgyun mi 'chad pa kho na'o //
NK094(nge)001:14173: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14174: chos so cog kun gyi rang bzhin de kho na
NK094(nge)001:14175: nyid kyi chos nyid de bzhina nyid kyi dbyingsa su
NK094(nge)001:14176: nges pa'i phyir / ngang las shar ba'i 'gro ba
NK094(nge)001:14177: rigs drug gi semsa can thams cad mtha' gnyis ngang
NK094(nge)001:14178: gis bral ba'i phyir sangsa rgyas kyi snying po chos
NK094(nge)001:14179: sku chen pora sus kyang ma byas byas pa med
NK094(nge)001:14180: par rang shar ba la 'gro ba gang zhig bsam
NK094(nge)001:14181: gyis mi khyab pa kun kyang rang byung don gyi
NK094(nge)001:14182: sangsa rgyas sgom pa rgyun gyi ting 'dzin dam par
NK094(nge)001:14183: dus gsum du rgyun mi 'chad pa nyid du mjal
NK094(nge)001:14184: nges pa'i phyir / ba'o // lnga pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:14188: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14189: dngosa po snod bcud du snang ba'i brtan g.yo thams cad dang /
NK094(nge)001:14190: la sogas pa zhes de las gyur pa ril rang
NK094(nge)001:14191: byung rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor du gnas pa'i phyir sgra
NK094(nge)001:14192: skad bsam gyis mi khyab par ji ltar grags pa
NK094(nge)001:14193: kun kyang gsang sngagsa gasnga ba dam pa'i tshig tu
NK094(nge)001:14194: shar bar rtogs pas bzlas pa dang brjod pa rgya
NK094(nge)001:14195: mtsho rgyun mi 'chad par gsal ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:14200: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14201: snod du gyur pa de dang bcud du snang ba
NK094(nge)001:14202: de yi ngo bo ril nyid dbyingsa mu mtha' med
NK094(nge)001:14203: pa nyid la / rang gi rig pa'ang de kho
NK094(nge)001:14204: na nyid yin pas dngos po gang dang de nyid
NK094(nge)001:14205: rtogs par byed pa gang gi thabsa gzhan sbyor ba
NK094(nge)001:14206: pa nyid la / med de / de nyid ye
NK094(nge)001:14207: nas yin par thag chod de zhan du mi tshol
NK094(nge)001:14208: bas shes rab rang rig mu mtha' bral ba las
NK094(nge)001:14209: pa nyid la / med de / / thabs de
NK094(nge)001:14210: nyid ye shes su ma 'gags par rang gsal ba
NK094(nge)001:14211: nyid 'adu 'abral med par rtogs pas na dus gsum
NK094(nge)001:14212: du gnyis su med pas sbyor ba chen po rgyun
NK094(nge)001:14218: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14219: srid pa khams gsum po nyid bsgral ba'i zhing du
NK094(nge)001:14220: gyur pa yin te mnyam pa nyid dang 'gal ba'i
NK094(nge)001:14221: rtag chad kyi 'khrul mtha' 'dzin pa yin pas 'di
NK094(nge)001:14222: daga thams cad stong pa nyid du ji lta bar
NK094(nge)001:14223: rtogs pa'i shes rab mchog ni de dag skad cig
NK094(nge)001:14224: gis mi gnas par byed pas mtshon cha'i rgyal po
NK094(nge)001:14225: rab tu rnon po yin pas /
NK094(nge)001:14226: rtogs pa de yisa 'jig rten gsum po thams cad
NK094(nge)001:14227: dngosa po med para bsad de 'bras bu'i las mthar
NK094(nge)001:14228: phyin pa'am mtha' las 'das pa'i ye shes su byung
NK094(nge)001:14229: thebs pasa na / ye nas sgrol bya sgrol byed
NK094(nge)001:14230: med par mnyam pa'i dbyings su sgrol ba chen po
NK094(nge)001:14231: rgyun mi 'chad de de'i ngang las 'da' ma myong
NK094(nge)001:14232: thebs pasa na / ba'o // brgyad pa la gnyis te /
NK094(nge)001:14233: gzhal yas khang gi ting nge 'dzin /
NK094(nge)001:14234: sku gdung rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin no //
NK094(nge)001:14236: gzhan yas khang gi ngo bo bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:14237: de yi don rdzogs lugs bshad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:14242: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14243: dkyil 'khor gyi ngo bo snang srid rnam par dag
NK094(nge)001:14244: pa'i gazhala yasa khang gi gnas su gzhi don gyi
NK094(nge)001:14245: kun gzhi dapala gyi man+dal la /
NK094(nge)001:14246: rnam shes tshogs brgyad kyis thig chen po'i srad bu brgyad du gsal ba nyid /
NK094(nge)001:14247: ye shes kyi tshogs brgyad du ma spangs rang shar
NK094(nge)001:14248: bar rtogs te thag chod pas rang rig cir yang
NK094(nge)001:14249: gsal bar ye nas btab pa'i dkyil 'khora chen po
NK094(nge)001:14250: rgyun mi 'chad par mjal ba nyid do //
NK094(nge)001:14256: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14257: bzhugs gnas gyi rmang gzhi'i ngo bo de bzhina nyid
NK094(nge)001:14258: kyi sa gzhi de kho na nyid du ye nas
NK094(nge)001:14259: gnas pa la / kun gzhi ma bcos pa'i bzhugs
NK094(nge)001:14260: gnas ji bzhina pa yi gazhala yasa khanga tshad dang
NK094(nge)001:14261: bral ba'i ngo bo nyid du rang snang ba'i rmang
NK094(nge)001:14262: ni yang dag pa'i don ma nor ma bcos pa'i
NK094(nge)001:14263: rang bzhin mi 'gyur ba'i chos nyid du rang snang
NK094(nge)001:14264: ba'i rmang chen gyis brten pa la /
