NK094(nge)001:14266: byang chub kyi semsa bcu'i rim pa bshad pa bzhin gyi rtsig pa chen pos gtamsa pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:14267: skar mthong ni rang byung gi ye shes chen po
NK094(nge)001:14268: la ye shes lnga yi ngo bo tha dad med
NK094(nge)001:14269: par shar ba nyid kyi don te phyogs bzhi nas
NK094(nge)001:14270: dbus dang lngar snang ba'i skar mthonga du gsal ba'o
NK094(nge)001:14272: bsdu ba'i dngos po rnam pa bzhi dang /
NK094(nge)001:14274: rnam par thar pa bzhi'i sgo bzhi bsnol ma rim gsum du shar ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:14275: dran pa nye bar bzhag pa bzhi dang yang dag
NK094(nge)001:14276: par spong ba bzhi lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i phyir phyi
NK094(nge)001:14277: nang gi them skas brgyad do //
NK094(nge)001:14278: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi'i phyir rta babas rnam bzhi dag gisa brgyan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:14279: mi 'jigsa pa bzhi lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i phyir steng
NK094(nge)001:14280: gi rig pa'i gdung chen bzhi bsnol ma'i don la
NK094(nge)001:14281: / yanga dag pa'i rtogs la sogs pa 'phags pa'i
NK094(nge)001:14282: lam yan lag brgyad kyis 'bras bur 'degs pas brgyad
NK094(nge)001:14283: kyi ka basa mdzesa par gdung sna nas btegs pa'i
NK094(nge)001:14284: / don to // rgyu rkyen las ma byas pa'i
NK094(nge)001:14285: ranga byung gi ye shesa chen po'i ngo bo nyid
NK094(nge)001:14286: ril 'dus pa'i dabu rtser 'aphagas te blar gyur pa
NK094(nge)001:14287: / don to // nyid do // don dam dang
NK094(nge)001:14288: kun rdzob kyi bdena pa gnyis lhun gyis rdzogs pas
NK094(nge)001:14289: bar khyamsa gnyis kyis ngesa para mdzesa pa'i don to
NK094(nge)001:14290: / don to // nyid do // // rang byung
NK094(nge)001:14291: gi ye shesa 'byung 'jug med pa'i ngo ba thugsa
NK094(nge)001:14292: rje'i kun la snyoms pas cir yang snang ba'i yona
NK094(nge)001:14293: tan g.yo ba med pa lasa byin rlabsa kyi snang
NK094(nge)001:14294: ba phrin las bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i rgyan gyis
NK094(nge)001:14295: mdzesa para brgyan pa'i don dang /
NK094(nge)001:14296: chos nyid kyi ngo bo mu mtha' med par gdal
NK094(nge)001:14297: ba'i byin rlabsa kyi bla rera bresa pa'i don to
NK094(nge)001:14298: // dril bu dang g.yer kha la sogs pa sil
NK094(nge)001:14299: snyan gyi sgra sgrogsa pa gsung lnga lhun gyis rdzogs
NK094(nge)001:14300: pa'i byin rlabs kyis gsang ba'i theg pa ston pa'i
NK094(nge)001:14301: theg chen sngagsa kyi rang sgrar 'char ba'i don to
NK094(nge)001:14302: // // de ltar gdul bya'i bsam pa la snang
NK094(nge)001:14303: ba'i don ma bral bar dus kun tu gsal ba'ang
NK094(nge)001:14304: rgyun gyi bsam pa ste dngos don rgyu 'bras kyi
NK094(nge)001:14305: chos de dag lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i ngo bor gsal
NK094(nge)001:14306: ba'i rig pa nyid rgyal ba'i bzhugs gnas dam par
NK094(nge)001:14307: gyur pas rgyun gyi bsam pa chen por 'char te
NK094(nge)001:14308: // // / gnas lugs ji bzhina ba ye ma
NK094(nge)001:14309: bslad par lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i chos kyi dbyings de
NK094(nge)001:14311: rgyal ba'i bzhugs gnas pho brang gi don te /
NK094(nge)001:14312: bzhugs gnas 'dira ni rgyal ba rnams bzhugs pa nye
NK094(nge)001:14313: bar bzung ba'i rim pa'i don de ltar ngo bo'i
NK094(nge)001:14314: tshul 'di ltar bzhugs par rigs te /
NK094(nge)001:14315: ngo bo nyid kyi dbyings ni mtha'i dri ma dang
NK094(nge)001:14316: bral bas spyod yul yongs su dag pas kun tu
NK094(nge)001:14317: bzang po byang chub semas kyi ngo bo'i chos nyid
NK094(nge)001:14318: ma bcos ma bslad pa nyid ril gyi bzhugs gnas
NK094(nge)001:14320: kun gzhi byang chub kyi sems yon tan rgyu dang
NK094(nge)001:14321: 'bras bu'i chos ji snyed par ma 'dres so sor
NK094(nge)001:14322: gsal ba la / ngo bo 'di 'drar mi zin
NK094(nge)001:14323: pas yongsa rdzogsa thig le nyag gcig tu gyur pa
NK094(nge)001:14324: ni gcig dang du ma'i mtha' las grol ba'i chos
NK094(nge)001:14325: chen po gsang sngags bla na med pa'i theg pa
NK094(nge)001:14327: don de 'du byed sems pa la sogs pa lnga
NK094(nge)001:14328: bcu rtsa gnyis kyi semsa dpa' mchog gi 'khor dang
NK094(nge)001:14329: mtshungs par ldan pa'i yid kyi rnam par shes pa
NK094(nge)001:14330: ma spangs bral ba'i yid yang dag pa'i ye shes
NK094(nge)001:14331: kyis yud tsam gyi yun la don mthong ba nyid
NK094(nge)001:14332: kyis rna ba la brten nas sgra yang ngesa par
NK094(nge)001:14333: chod de thos pasa na bstan pa rgya mtsho lta
NK094(nge)001:14334: bu'i chos kyi mchog yang gsang nges pa'i snying po
NK094(nge)001:14335: yin pas don ji lta ba bzhin mjal ba nyid
NK094(nge)001:14336: rgyun mi 'chad la bral ba'ang med pa ni bshad
NK094(nge)001:14337: pa ltar rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin chen po'o //
NK094(nge)001:14339: khams gsum mchod rten du bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:14340: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten mchod rten du bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:14341: nang bcud kyi sems can mchod rten du bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:14347: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14348: 'doda pa'i khamas kyi rmang gi ri raba kyi gzhi la /
NK094(nge)001:14349: gzugsa kyi khamsa rnams banga rim khri 'phang du brtan cing /
NK094(nge)001:14350: gzugsa med khams kyi bum rten bum para bcas pa'i
NK094(nge)001:14351: khams gsum gyi snod bcud gnyis ka'i rim pa ma
NK094(nge)001:14352: spangs bral bas ye shes kyi khams gsum nyid gdung
NK094(nge)001:14353: chen chos kyi skur ma 'gag par gsal ba nyid
NK094(nge)001:14354: dus gsum rgyun mi 'chad pa'i rang snang du mjal
NK094(nge)001:14359: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14360: phyi snod kyi gnas 'byung ba chen po nam mkha'a
NK094(nge)001:14361: dang me chu sa rlung lnga po rnams las grub
NK094(nge)001:14362: pa'i rmang gi gling bzhi ni ri raba kyi rten
NK094(nge)001:14363: du snang la / bang rima gyi rnam pa can
NK094(nge)001:14364: gyi gser gyi ri bdun dang bcas pa rnams kyi
NK094(nge)001:14365: ri rab de nyid kyi 'og gi bang rima dang
NK094(nge)001:14366: khri 'aphanga dang brtan par gnas la ri bo mchog
NK094(nge)001:14367: rab chen po yar 'phags pa ni bum rten dang
NK094(nge)001:14368: bum para bcas pa nyid de /
NK094(nge)001:14369: de ltar snang ba nyid ye dag pa'i ye shes
NK094(nge)001:14370: kyi skur gsal ba'i don ji lta bar mjal ba
NK094(nge)001:14371: 'di yang gdung chen po'i chos sku rgyun mi 'chad
NK094(nge)001:14375: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14376: nang bcud kyi dbang du byas te /
NK094(nge)001:14377: 'dzugs par byed pa'i rkang lag gi yan lag bzhi ni rmang rten dang /
NK094(nge)001:14378: 'khor lo rim par rten pa'i rgal tshigs kyi tshogsa chen po nyid khri 'phang du brtan la /
NK094(nge)001:14379: yan lag gi dang po mgo bo nyid dbang po
NK094(nge)001:14380: dang ldan pa'i bum rten bum pa dang bcas te
NK094(nge)001:14381: / skra'i lcang lo cod pan gyi phreng basa klubsa
NK094(nge)001:14382: pa'i dngos po'i lus nyid ye ma spangs dag pa
NK094(nge)001:14383: ye shes kyi lus su byung ba nyid sku gdung
NK094(nge)001:14393: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14394: de'ang cho 'phrul tha dad la ting nge 'dzin du bsgom pas rtsal sbyang ba 'grub pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:14395: rgya mtsho rkang pas gnona pa'i ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK094(nge)001:14396: bshad pa ltar rnam gsum rim par bskyed pa'i rgyu las lhar gsal bas /
NK094(nge)001:14397: rgya mtsho rdo rje gtams par sgoms te /
NK094(nge)001:14398: de gsal ba stobs can du gyur ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:14399: rgya mtsho rkang pas bgrod de /
NK094(nge)001:14400: de la gnas pa'i 'gro ba rnams 'od zer du
NK094(nge)001:14401: sprul pas sgo gsum sbyangs te thar pa la bskyal
NK094(nge)001:14403: nam mkha'i skas la 'dzegs pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:14404: lhar gsal ba las nam mkha' la h'u las rdo
NK094(nge)001:14405: rje'i skas dang sa gzhi goms pas stobs can du
NK094(nge)001:14406: gyur ba dang / phan tshun 'gro ba'i tshul gyis
NK094(nge)001:14407: bgrod nas snang srid lta zhing bshad pa ltar de
NK094(nge)001:14408: na gnas pa'i 'gro don bya ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:14410: nam mkha'i gzhi la a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK094(nge)001:14411: bskyed pa'i dbus su bdag gnas te bsgom pa shin
NK094(nge)001:14413: zla ba'i 'og nas ye shes kyi rlung gis btegs
NK094(nge)001:14414: te shin tu rlung mgyogs pa'i shugs kyis rgyal ba'i
NK094(nge)001:14415: zhing kun tu bgrod pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:14416: nam mkha'i gtos rdo rje gtams par sgoms te rlung gis bsgul mi nus par bya ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:14417: chu bo chen po'i rgyun bzlog pa'i ting nge 'dzin ni rjes su mthun par sbyar ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:14418: bsrega pa'i bskal pa gzhila ba ni /
NK094(nge)001:14419: bskal pa'i me gzhil ba dang dmyal ba'i me gzhil ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:14420: bskal pa'i me gzhil ba ni /
NK094(nge)001:14421: lhar gsal ba'i sdigs mdzub kyi rtse mo la /
NK094(nge)001:14422: a las zla ba bsam pa shin tu brtan pa las chu rgyun phab la gzhil ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:14423: dmyal ba'i me gzhil ba ni /
NK094(nge)001:14424: rnal 'byor pa'i lag mthil du 'khor lo bsam pa'i lte ba la /
NK094(nge)001:14425: a las zla ba'i steng du kham sngon po bsam
NK094(nge)001:14426: pa las bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun phab la dmyal ba'i
NK094(nge)001:14429: nam mkha'i gzhi nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor ma'i sa bon
NK094(nge)001:14430: las bskyed pa'i dbus su bdag gnas par bsgom pa
NK094(nge)001:14431: brtas pa dang de las nyi ma 'bum gyi 'od
NK094(nge)001:14432: bkye nas mun pa bsal ba ste zla ba'ang ji
NK094(nge)001:14433: ltar rigs par sbyar ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:14435: rnal 'byor pa'i lag mthil du stong gi 'jig rten sgoms pa de shin tu brtan pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:14436: nam mkha'i khams su 'phangs te sa nas sar 'phar bar bya ste 'og nas 'chad par 'gyur ro //
NK094(nge)001:14437: gzhan yang sa dang lus mi dmigs pa'i stobs kyis sa la byi ba ltar 'dzul ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:14439: stong gsum yungsa 'brur ram de tsam du 'jug cing tshud pa'i tshul du bya ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:14440: pha rol gyi dpung gzhig cing gzhil ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:14442: la sogsa pa zhes dngos po gzhan bsdu ba ni /
NK094(nge)001:14443: gso gsad pham rgyal dang dgug bcing dgrol ba la sogs pa'i las mtha' yas pa rnams te /
NK094(nge)001:14444: bsam bya bsam gyis mi khyab pa sna tshogs ting
NK094(nge)001:14445: nge 'dzin la gomas pa las su rung ba yi
NK094(nge)001:14446: skabs na 'grub pas rnal 'byor pa rig pa 'dzin
NK094(nge)001:14447: pa'i sa la ting nge 'dzin gyi rtsal chen po
NK094(nge)001:14448: sbyong ba'i phyir bsam bya de dag bsgom para zada
NK094(nge)001:14449: do // cho 'phrul 'di dag yi ge'i rnal 'byor
NK094(nge)001:14450: pas lha dgu nyid dang bcu la goms nas 'grub
NK094(nge)001:14451: do // la / mtshan med pas zag med ma thob bar du mi 'grub ste /
NK094(nge)001:14452: phyi'i mngon rtags shas che bas so //
NK094(nge)001:14453: zhes kun mkhyen kahthoga pa chen pos gsungs /
NK094(nge)001:14454: des na dper 'jig rten gyi bya ba bsgrub pa dang 'dra ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:14455: de dag gi rgyu dang khyad par thun mong du bstan pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:14456: bzlas pa mathara phyin te tshad du phyin par grub pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:14457: phyag rgya bcinga zhing sgom pa yongas su rdzogas pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:14458: ting nge 'dzin gyi bsam pa las su runga ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:14459: lta bas sems kyi dona mthonga zhing rtogs pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:14460: ngag gi bden pa'i tshig grub pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:14461: 'gro don bya ba'i lus kyi spyod pa yongsa su
NK094(nge)001:14462: dag pa dag la bshad pa'i rtsal rnams 'byung ba'ang
NK094(nge)001:14463: gzhi dona bsam bya gcig gi yul la goms pa
NK094(nge)001:14464: dang ma goms pa'i blo'i stobs kyis sa'i khyad par
NK094(nge)001:14465: gong 'og so sor snang bar 'byung ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:14467: nam mkha'i skas bgrod pa'i ting nge 'dzin /
NK094(nge)001:14468: rgya mtsho gnon pa'i ting nge 'dzin /
NK094(nge)001:14469: rlung bcing ba dang zla ba zhon pa'i ting nge 'dzin /
NK094(nge)001:14470: nyi ma zhon pa'i ting nge 'dzin /
NK094(nge)001:14471: chu rgyun bzlog pa'i ting nge 'dzin /
NK094(nge)001:14472: sreg pa'i bskal pa gzhil ba'i ting nge 'dzin /
NK094(nge)001:14478: zhes pa'i bar yis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14479: ltas dang sbyor bas cho 'phrul dang sa gong ma sgrubs pas rgyal bar bstan pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:14480: mi dmigs pa'i ngang las nam mkha' la h'u las
NK094(nge)001:14481: rdo rje'i them pa dang skas bsgom nas brtan pa
NK094(nge)001:14482: dang / nam mkha'i skas der bgrod nas bdag nam
NK094(nge)001:14483: mkha'i dbyingsa kyi dbus su 'dug cing gansa par gyur
NK094(nge)001:14484: nas snang srid mtha' yas thug pa med pa la
NK094(nge)001:14485: blta bar byas pa desa ni rnal 'byor pa de
NK094(nge)001:14486: yis sems kyi yul yangas shing rgya che bar 'gyur
NK094(nge)001:14487: dang / ro // de ni bshad pa bzhin nam mkhar bgrod pa'i ting 'dzin no //
NK094(nge)001:14492: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14493: rkang pa'i zhabs su rgya mtsho la rdo rje rgya
NK094(nge)001:14494: gram bsam pas gtamsa pa dang sdigs mdzub la h+aum
NK094(nge)001:14495: las rdo rje bsam pas gtams pa gnyis byas te
NK094(nge)001:14496: / mtsho de la gnas pa'i semsa can rnams la /
NK094(nge)001:14497: dpal rdo rje semas dapa'a nyid kyis byin gyis brlabs pa brtan par byas te /
NK094(nge)001:14498: gdul bya thamsa cad dam pa'i rdo rjera bya zhing don byed pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:14503: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14504: bdag nyid nam mkha'a dbyingsa kyi ling ga la zla
NK094(nge)001:14505: ba'i dkyil 'khora kyi dbus su gnas para sgom pa
NK094(nge)001:14506: nyid / myur mgyogsa ye shes kyi rlung zla'i 'pheena
NK094(nge)001:14507: shugsa kyis zhing khamas rnam kun tu bgrod de gdul
NK094(nge)001:14508: bya'i don sgrub para bya ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:14509: nam mkha'i gtos rdo rjes gtams pas rlung mi 'gul ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:14514: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14515: nam makhasa kun tu dwangs pa'i dbyingsa kyi ling ga
NK094(nge)001:14516: la mun pa gsal ba'i nyi ma'i dkyil 'khora bsam
NK094(nge)001:14517: nas de'i dbus su rnal 'byor pa gnas par byas
NK094(nge)001:14518: te / nyid la nyid shina tu gsal zhing ngesa para gyur pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:14519: phyi nang gi mun pa rnam par dag pa'i gansa rnams thams cad snang zhing gsal bar byed pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:14525: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14526: rnal 'abyor pas phyag gi sdigsa pa'i mdzub mo la
NK094(nge)001:14527: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor 'od 'abra ba re bsam pa
NK094(nge)001:14528: lasa / de'i zer lasa nyi ma 'bum phrag mang po 'phros pasa /
NK094(nge)001:14529: phyi bskal pa'i mun pa dang nang ma rig pa'i
NK094(nge)001:14530: mun pa thamsa cad basla nas 'byung ba'i chu bo'i
NK094(nge)001:14531: rgyun dang 'khor ba'i chu rgyun zlog ste don mchog
NK094(nge)001:14534: nang gi sreg pa gzhil ba /
NK094(nge)001:14540: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14541: rnal 'byor pas lag gi dkyil 'khora gyi mthil du 'khor lo bsam pa lasa /
NK094(nge)001:14542: de'i lte bar a las chu zla'i dkyil 'khora rab tu gsal ba la kham sngon po bsam pas /
NK094(nge)001:14543: de las bdud rtsi'i chu bo chen po'i rgyun byung
NK094(nge)001:14544: bas sreg cing 'bar ba dmyal ba'i me chen po
NK094(nge)001:14545: gasda de rab tu zhi bar byed pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:14551: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14552: rnal 'abyor pas sdigsa 'dzub kyi rtse mo la a
NK094(nge)001:14553: las zla ba'i dkyil 'khora 'od 'abra ba gsal te
NK094(nge)001:14554: shin tu brtan par gyur pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:14555: de las chu rgyun phab ba desa 'jig rten sreg pa'i me yi bskal pa gzhila bar byed pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:14560: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14561: rnal 'byor pas lag gi dkyil 'khora gyi mthil du
NK094(nge)001:14562: stong gsum gyi 'jiga rten 'khora yuga dang bcas pa
NK094(nge)001:14563: sgom te shin tu brtan pa na nam mkha'i khams
NK094(nge)001:14564: su rgyang mar 'aphangas nas ni de yi yon tan
NK094(nge)001:14565: gyis / de na gnas pa'i sems can rnams kyang
NK094(nge)001:14566: rang rang gi skal ba bzhin sa nas sar ni
NK094(nge)001:14568: de ltar bshad pa dang mdo rgyas kyi dbang du
NK094(nge)001:14569: bka' stsal kyang bsam pa la mi 'dra ba med
NK094(nge)001:14570: pas sbyar te shes par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:14571: lnga pa mdo sems su 'dus par bstan pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:14575: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14576: gazhana yanga langa ka'i bdag po /
NK094(nge)001:14578: ting nge 'dzina mi mthun pa'i don kun gyi mdo
NK094(nge)001:14579: gang du 'dus pa nges par gzung nas nye bar
NK094(nge)001:14580: bstan pa ni / 'di kho nara 'dus par gsungsa pasa /
NK094(nge)001:14581: ston par 'gyur pa 'di kho na ltar shes par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:14582: ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo ji snyed cig tu bstan
NK094(nge)001:14583: pa'i rtsa ba semsa kyi dkyil 'khor 'od gsal ba'i
NK094(nge)001:14585: mtshan nyid cir yang snang la gcig tu ma nges
NK094(nge)001:14586: par gyur pas sgyu ma'i ranga bzhina dang chos mthun
NK094(nge)001:14588: de bas na rig pas ji ltar brtagsa shing bsgom
NK094(nge)001:14589: pa de ltar chos sna tshogs pa rnams su snang
NK094(nge)001:14590: ba'i phyir rtsa ba'i mdo sems su nges pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:14591: bsgom pa'i don sna tshogs pa ji lta bur 'byung zhing shar ba'i chos rnams kun /
NK094(nge)001:14592: bsam pa tsam gyis skad cig de ma thaga bar mngon du ma gyur kyang /
NK094(nge)001:14593: bsgom bya de kho na nyid la dngos po ji
NK094(nge)001:14594: ltar bsam zhing gang ltar brtagsa pa de ltar mthu
NK094(nge)001:14595: brtas shing goms pa'i dbang gis cir yang snang du
NK094(nge)001:14598: 'gro ba'i skye bo brtags par zhen pas gdosa bcas
NK094(nge)001:14599: kyi spyod yul can la bems po ther zug tu
NK094(nge)001:14600: snang bas na ting 'dzin gyi 'bras bu mngon shes
NK094(nge)001:14601: med pa'i mthong yul du mi snang yanga /
NK094(nge)001:14602: mi mthun pa ston pa'i don ni yid kyi gzugsa
NK094(nge)001:14603: can mngona shesa yod pa'i sde brgyad kyis mthong zhing
NK094(nge)001:14604: / kun mkhyen rgyal ba dang mngon shes can gyi
NK094(nge)001:14605: dam pa dag la snang ba'i cha yod pas kyang
NK094(nge)001:14607: de ltar gsal por yun bsrings te /
NK094(nge)001:14608: bsgom bya'i dngos po gang la yang nas yang du
NK094(nge)001:14609: brtagsa shing goms pas de ltar ting nge 'dzin de
NK094(nge)001:14610: yi mthu brtas par gyur na /
NK094(nge)001:14611: mjug tu rig pa'i mngon sum du byas pa de
NK094(nge)001:14612: nyid dbang po'i mngona sum du gasla por reda de
NK094(nge)001:14613: snang bar 'gyur ba nges par 'byung bas the tshom
NK094(nge)001:14614: mi za bar bsgom par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:14615: yang na mi mthun pa ston pa'i don ni ma nor ba'i lam pa la snang btub pa ste /
NK094(nge)001:14616: 'gro bas brtags pa'i rtog yul ril rang rgyud pa
NK094(nge)001:14617: gzhi nas med de rang rig pa nyid snang bas
NK094(nge)001:14618: snang ba ril rang rig pa'i sku'i ngo bor gsal
NK094(nge)001:14619: bas tha dad med cing 'brel ba can pas mngon
NK094(nge)001:14620: sum bzhi kar gsal zhing rig pa'ang rig pa nyid
NK094(nge)001:14621: snang ba ste / rig pa ril gyi dngos gzhi
NK094(nge)001:14622: bas gang ltar bsam pa snang zhing de la 'dris
NK094(nge)001:14623: shing goms pa brtan pa dang mjug mngon shes dang
NK094(nge)001:14624: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa 'byung bar 'gyur ro
NK094(nge)001:14625: snang ba ste / // de'i phyir yod med dang
NK094(nge)001:14626: legsa nyes la sogs pa mtha' gnyis pa'i chos so
NK094(nge)001:14627: cog gi ranga bzhina rnams rang rgyud pa med par
NK094(nge)001:14628: brtags pa tsam brda yis snang ba las ngo bo
NK094(nge)001:14630: dper na chu khamas kyi rgyun brtas pa nyid 'gro
NK094(nge)001:14631: bar btub pa dang grang reg gis chab rom du
NK094(nge)001:14632: 'gyur ba lta bur nges par zad de /
NK094(nge)001:14633: 'khor 'das cir yang snang ba thamsa cad ril sems
NK094(nge)001:14634: nyid 'di yisa dbang du bsgyur bar byed nas snang
NK094(nge)001:14636: desa na rtsa ba ting nge 'dzina gyi semas nyid
NK094(nge)001:14637: la rag las pa yin pas 'bras bu'i gtso bo'i
NK094(nge)001:14638: rgyu kho nar gzhag ste bstan par mdzad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:14643: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14644: dpera na rgya mtshor phyin te nor bu lena pa'i mi dag ni /
NK094(nge)001:14645: sbrul dang chu srin dang sbrang ma la sogsa pa
NK094(nge)001:14646: shin tu gdug pa'i sdug bsngal kun khyad du bsad
NK094(nge)001:14647: de dka' bas nyamsa su blangsa pas don 'grub pa
NK094(nge)001:14648: nyid de / 'di ni ting nge 'dzin gyi chos mthun pa ste dka' bas 'bad par byed pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:14649: dpe de bzhina du mtshon par bya ba'i don ni /
NK094(nge)001:14650: rnal 'byor dam pa bde ba chen po'i ye shes
NK094(nge)001:14651: rab tu gsang ba nyid yang dag par tshol bar
NK094(nge)001:14653: rnam par rtog pa bying rmugsa dang 'aphyar g.yeng la
NK094(nge)001:14654: sogs pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dgra gzhom par dka'
NK094(nge)001:14655: ba'i byed las can 'di daga gzhom ste don la
NK094(nge)001:14656: mkhas pas nyamsa su blangsa na ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK094(nge)001:14657: bde ba dam pa thob cing rnyed nas yon tan
NK094(nge)001:14658: rgya mtsho lta bu'i gter mdzod du 'gyur ro //
NK094(nge)001:14659: ji skad bstan pa 'di ni ting nge 'dzina dam
NK094(nge)001:14660: pa yi snying po rab tu gsal ba nyid tshul
NK094(nge)001:14661: bzhin du nyams su blangsa pa'i bslab pa phul du
NK094(nge)001:14662: byung ba ste / de ltar semsa nyid kyis snying
NK094(nge)001:14663: po'i don la gomsa para bya ba'i lasa la brtson
NK094(nge)001:14664: pas 'bad de 'dris para bya ba nyid rab tu
NK094(nge)001:14670: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14672: bshad pa'i don bstan pa de dag ni nyams su
NK094(nge)001:14673: ting nge 'dzin gyis blangs pas dgongs pa'i nyamsa rnyed
NK094(nge)001:14674: pa nyid du shes par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:14675: zhes ston pa gsang bdag chen pos de skad ces smras te don bstan pas /
NK094(nge)001:14676: rig 'dzin 'gro ba'i lus can gyi dman pa dam
NK094(nge)001:14677: pa de rnams gang gi dgongsa pa de kho na
NK094(nge)001:14678: nyid dama pa'i nyamsa drod drug rnyed para gyur te
NK094(nge)001:14679: mthar thug gi rtogs pa'i gdeng thob par gyur to
NK094(nge)001:14681: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongsa pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po lasa /
NK094(nge)001:14682: rnal 'abyor pas lta ba rtogs pa'i ngang las sems
NK094(nge)001:14683: las su rung ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyis dbang bsgyur
NK094(nge)001:14684: nas don gyi rtsal sbyangs pas 'bras bu mngon par
NK094(nge)001:14685: 'grub pa'i tshul bstan pa'i le'u zhes bya ste bdun
NK094(nge)001:14686: cu rtsa gsum pa nyid gsal bar bkrol te bshad
NK094(nge)001:14687: pa'o ////dgu pa don man ngag gis sgrub pa gser
NK094(nge)001:14688: 'gyur gyi rtsi ltar bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK094(nge)001:14697: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14699: de yang spyir man ngag la lnga ste /
NK094(nge)001:14700: sbyangs pa'i stobs kyi man ngag sbyang stobs che chung
NK094(nge)001:14701: dang sbyar bar snod dang bstun te 'jug pa dang
NK094(nge)001:14702: / 'jug pa sgo'i man ngag rang rang gi blos
NK094(nge)001:14703: gdams pa'i mtshon thabs gang mos su 'jug pa dang
NK094(nge)001:14704: / / 'grub byed thabs kyi man ngag don dang yi ge'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK094(nge)001:14705: grub pa 'bras bu'i man ngag rang snang gi sangs rgyas mngon du byas pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:14706: la bzla ba'i man ngag le'u 'di nyid kyi bstan pa'i don no //
NK094(nge)001:14707: de la nyams su ting nge 'dzin gyis blang pa'ang don che la /
NK094(nge)001:14708: de nyid tshegs chung bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:14709: de nas yanga ston pa gsang ba ba'i badga po 'chad pa'i skyes bu chen po desa /
NK094(nge)001:14710: dman pa'i lus kyi byang chub semsa dapa'a rnams la 'di skad ces rjes su bstan te bgros so //
NK094(nge)001:14711: gtan tshigs byung khungs kyi gleng gzhi'i dbang du grogs po dag ces bos nas /
NK094(nge)001:14712: gang 'di la tshegsa byang chub bar bya ba don
NK094(nge)001:14713: man ngag gis sgrub pa nye bar bstan pa gang
NK094(nge)001:14715: gang bsgom bya'i dngos po ci la yang bsgom pa'i
NK094(nge)001:14716: tshe sems kyis ched du thob par bya ba'i phyir
NK094(nge)001:14717: 'bad pa dang dmigs su meda pa'i thabs khyad par
NK094(nge)001:14718: can las gzhan pa ma yin pa nyid de /
NK094(nge)001:14719: de yang ganga la sems kyis ched du 'bad cing
NK094(nge)001:14720: dmigs pa'i bya ba med pa de nyid gang zhe
NK094(nge)001:14721: na / ngo bo nyid bstan pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK094(nge)001:14722: de bzhin nyid rtogs te de kho na nyid ji
NK094(nge)001:14723: lta bar thag chod pa'i thabs dam pa nyid do
NK094(nge)001:14724: // des na sems lung chen po las /
NK094(nge)001:14725: don rnams ji bzhin mi bskyod de //
NK094(nge)001:14726: chos nyid nam mkha' lta bu'i dngos //
NK094(nge)001:14727: skyon rnams ma lus dag pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:14728: bya ba'i yul rnams ngang gis stong //
NK094(nge)001:14729: bya ba med pas rang bzhin grol //
NK094(nge)001:14732: don man ngag gis zin pa'i yo na tan bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:14733: de ltar man ngag gis ma zin pa'i skyon bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:14734: la bzla ba'i don gyi man ngag gi ngo bo bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:14735: de blo chung ba'i yul ma yin par bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:14738: zhes pa la sogs yon tan drug gi sgo nas bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14739: de yang zhib tu bstan na /
NK094(nge)001:14740: lta ba'i nges gsang gis zin pa'i thabs kyi yon tan /
NK094(nge)001:14741: sgom pas yongs grol du 'jug pa'i thabs kyi yon tan /
NK094(nge)001:14742: spyod pas don chen por bogs dbyung ba'i thabs kyi yon tan /
NK094(nge)001:14743: rtogs pa'i rtsal gyis tshegs dang bral ba'i thabs kyi yon tan /
NK094(nge)001:14744: blo gros dam pa'i thabs dang ldan pa'i man ngag gi yon tan /
NK094(nge)001:14745: de'i phyir man ngag dag gi babs la mkhas na
NK094(nge)001:14746: don mchog kun ma btsal lhun grub tu 'byung ba'i
NK094(nge)001:14747: yon tan no // dang po ni /
NK094(nge)001:14751: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14753: gtan tshigs kyis yid ches par bya ba ni /
NK094(nge)001:14755: dper na dug ha la nag po yang sngagsa kyis
NK094(nge)001:14756: yongsa su zin pa'i thabs kyis spyad na dug gi
NK094(nge)001:14757: nad kyis gang la yang gnod par byed mi nus
NK094(nge)001:14758: pa ltar / de kho na nyid ji bzhin par
NK094(nge)001:14759: gdeng chud pa'i de bzhina nyid kyis rtogs pas zin
NK094(nge)001:14760: pa yi lta ba can la /
NK094(nge)001:14761: nyon mongs pa 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug gi
NK094(nge)001:14762: dug gsuma mam nga rgyal phrag dog dang bcas pa
NK094(nge)001:14763: 'i dug chen lngasa mi tshugs pas gnod par mi
NK094(nge)001:14764: 'gyur te de nyid ye shes chen po'i klong du
NK094(nge)001:14765: gsal bas slar la lam du 'gyur ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:14766: de bas na thag chod pas gang la'ang spang blang
NK094(nge)001:14767: med pa de nyid kyang mi len mi 'dor bas
NK094(nge)001:14768: rtog rgyun ril de bzhin nyid kyi ngang la rtog
NK094(nge)001:14769: pa skyes kyang mi 'gegs shing zhe sdang bar yang
NK094(nge)001:14770: mi byed la / mthong thos kyi rjes su 'brang
NK094(nge)001:14771: bar bya ba'ang med par rtogs pa'i thabs khyad par
NK094(nge)001:14772: can ni shin tu gces pa'i phyir 'chad pa ltar
NK094(nge)001:14773: dang du blang bar bya ste /
NK094(nge)001:14774: kun tu bzang po che ba rang la gnas pa'i rgyud las /
NK094(nge)001:14775: thabs kyi rgyal por gang shes pa //
NK094(nge)001:14776: de nyid don rdzogs thabs kyi sku //
NK094(nge)001:14777: ma skyes shes rab don shes pas //
NK094(nge)001:14778: de nyid bcos med man ngag tshang //
NK094(nge)001:14780: skyon gyi rgyu las ma gtogs pa'i //
NK094(nge)001:14781: sangs rgyas gzhan nas yongs med de //
NK094(nge)001:14782: sman mchog bdud rtsi 'byung ba yang //
NK094(nge)001:14783: dug yod pa las sman du 'byung //
NK094(nge)001:14784: dug la sman gyi rgyu med na //
NK094(nge)001:14785: thams cad sman la sman ming med //
NK094(nge)001:14786: legs pa thams cad 'byung ba yang //
NK094(nge)001:14787: skyon gyis legs par 'byung bar byed //
NK094(nge)001:14789: skyon gyi rgyu 'di ma rig pa //
NK094(nge)001:14790: ma rig pa ni dbyings kyi mdzod //
NK094(nge)001:14791: de yi gong na che ba med //
NK094(nge)001:14792: skyon gyi rgyun ni 'dzin rtog gnyis //
NK094(nge)001:14793: 'dzin rtog thabs dang shes rab na //
NK094(nge)001:14794: skyon gyi rgyu las che ba med //
NK094(nge)001:14795: skyon gyi rgyu ni nyon mongs lnga //
NK094(nge)001:14796: nyon mongs ye shes lngar snang na //
NK094(nge)001:14797: skyon gyi rgyu las che ba med //
NK094(nge)001:14798: ces sogs shin tu mang ngo //
NK094(nge)001:14804: zhes pa'i bar rkang pa gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14806: ji bzhin pa'i ngo bor thag chod pa'i de bzhina
NK094(nge)001:14807: nyid kyis chos so cog kun la khyab pas thams
NK094(nge)001:14808: cad ril de nyid kyi don du gnas para ganga
NK094(nge)001:14809: su zhig gis shes sam rtogs pa na nyon mongsa
NK094(nge)001:14810: pa'i 'ching ba lnga gsum la sogs pa nyid rnam
NK094(nge)001:14811: par grol ba'i ye shes su shar bar 'gyur ba
NK094(nge)001:14812: ni yang dag par rtogs pa'i yon tan te /
NK094(nge)001:14813: sems lung chen po'i mdo las /
NK094(nge)001:14814: 'gro ba zhi ba chen po'i ngang //
NK094(nge)001:14815: de phyir rang bzhin grol ba ste //
NK094(nge)001:14817: rang byung ye shes btsal med pas //
NK094(nge)001:14818: btsal med dam pa zhi ba yin //
NK094(nge)001:14819: grol nas grol ba'i lam yang ston //
NK094(nge)001:14820: snang phyir grol ba chen po ste //
NK094(nge)001:14821: grol dang ma grol gnyis med do //
NK094(nge)001:14823: gnyis su sgro btags yod ma yin //
NK094(nge)001:14824: de lta bur ni sus mthong ba //
NK094(nge)001:14825: mtshan ma'i g.yul las rgyal ba yin //
NK094(nge)001:14826: de lta bu ni sus 'dzin pa //
NK094(nge)001:14827: sangs rgyas yin te rgyal ba'i sras //
NK094(nge)001:14834: zhes pa'i bar tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14835: man ngag dang ldan pa'i yon tan ni /
NK094(nge)001:14836: rnal 'byor gang zhig man ngag dam pa'i de nyid
NK094(nge)001:14837: la mkhas pa'i skyes bu blo dang ldan pas 'ching
NK094(nge)001:14838: ba'i chos nyon mongas pa'i rtog tshogs rnams la thabs
NK094(nge)001:14839: kyis zin pasa ganga ltar spyad kyang spyod la ma
NK094(nge)001:14840: 'gags spyod rgyus mi 'ching bar ma zad de /
NK094(nge)001:14841: de la ni las grol du ma gyur pas ci
NK094(nge)001:14842: spyod tshogs su gyur pas rnam grol chen po ranga
NK094(nge)001:14843: byung gi mya ngana las 'adsa pa yang gzhan nas
NK094(nge)001:14844: tshol ba'i sems bral bas tshegsa meda pa'i thabs spyod
NK094(nge)001:14845: gyin 'ad'a tsam gyis kyang spyod yul rgyal ba'i zhing
NK094(nge)001:14846: khams yang dag pa'i sa mchog ma bgrod par non
NK094(nge)001:14847: pas dona po che'am don chen po bla na med
NK094(nge)001:14848: pa'o // 'o na man ngag gi spyod pa zin
NK094(nge)001:14849: byed kyi lta ba yin pas bslab pa'ang dgur 'gyur
NK094(nge)001:14850: pa'o // ro zhe na / 'dir rtogs na 'bad
NK094(nge)001:14851: pa'ang byar med pa'i thabs khyad par can la ngo
NK094(nge)001:14852: bo nges par bzung bas thag lta bas bcad pa
NK094(nge)001:14853: dang 'dre bar mi 'gyur te bslab pa ni bcu
NK094(nge)001:14854: pa'o // ro zhe na / nyid do // bzhi pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:14859: zhes pa'i bar rkang pa bzhis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14860: chos thamsa cad stong pa chen por yang dag par
NK094(nge)001:14861: gdengs su chud de ma nor bar shes pa yi
NK094(nge)001:14862: skyes bu dam pa spyod yul dag par rtogs pa'i
NK094(nge)001:14863: blo can ni ril da lta nyid du mya ngana
NK094(nge)001:14864: las 'adsa pa nyid du gsal ba ste /
NK094(nge)001:14865: don du gnyer ba'i tshol sems kyis bya ba'i lasa
NK094(nge)001:14866: la sha thang ba'i 'bad pa drag pos tshegsa chen
NK094(nge)001:14867: gyis dka' ba'i las dang bral te bya rtsol mang
NK094(nge)001:14868: po'i las kyi kun spyod nyid mi dgos pas man
NK094(nge)001:14869: ngag can gyi bla ma la lus srog gis blu
NK094(nge)001:14870: bar byed pa ni nges par rigs shing 'os pa'o
NK094(nge)001:14876: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14877: bshad pa ltar dama pa'i man ngag blo dang ldan par bya ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:14878: gros kyis chod par bya ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:14879: thabsa kyis zin par bya ba'i 'phrul gyi nges gsang
NK094(nge)001:14880: don gyi snying po 'di gsum 'chang ste gnad kyi
NK094(nge)001:14881: man ngag yod na 'jig rten 'khor ba dman pa'i
NK094(nge)001:14882: gnas kyi dngosa po 'khrul pa'i snang ba yang yongs
NK094(nge)001:14883: su rdzogs par mnyam pa'i chos dbyings rang bzhin med
NK094(nge)001:14884: pa'i ngang du rtogs pa'i skyes bu dam pa ni
NK094(nge)001:14885: 'bras bu chen por ma byas par rang shar rang
NK094(nge)001:14886: grol du gsal ba'i dpal dang ldan par 'gyur te
NK094(nge)001:14887: / rnam grol dag pa chen po'i ngo bo ni ranga byung gi ye shes yin gyi /
NK094(nge)001:14888: rgyu rkyen dang ngo bo gzhan gyis byas pa las byung ba mina te /
NK094(nge)001:14889: sems lung chen po'i mdo las /
NK094(nge)001:14890: 'khor ba thams cad byang chub ste //
NK094(nge)001:14892: sa chu me rlung nam mkha' che //
NK094(nge)001:14893: don nyid ye nas sangs rgyas te //
NK094(nge)001:14894: snang ba nyid na dag pa yin //
NK094(nge)001:14895: sems can thams cad rang bzhin grol //
NK094(nge)001:14896: de phyir chos nyid grol ba yin //
NK094(nge)001:14897: 'gro ba kun la rang bzhin gnas //
NK094(nge)001:14898: mi shes pas su bslad mi nus //
NK094(nge)001:14900: phyin ci log gi rjes mi 'brang //
NK094(nge)001:14901: phyin ci log tu rnam bslad kyang //
NK094(nge)001:14902: grol ba rang bzhin gzhan las min //
NK094(nge)001:14903: yang dag ye shes dag pa ste //
NK094(nge)001:14904: chos rnams thams cad ngang gis stong //
NK094(nge)001:14905: de phyir rang bzhin bcom ldan 'das //
NK094(nge)001:14912: zhes pa'i bar tshigs bcad bzhi yis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14913: de phyir zhes snyegs pas snga ma gtan tshigs su gyur pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:14914: mtha' gang la'ang mi gnas pas bya ba med pa'i don bstan pa la snyegs pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:14915: 'on kyang man ngag gi blo gros thabsa gsum 'chang zhing legs par ldan na /
NK094(nge)001:14916: 'bad rtsol gyis sgrub pa'i brtson 'grus kyis don du gnyer ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:14917: phyi nang gi yo byad la brten pa kho na
NK094(nge)001:14918: gtsor ma gsungsa pas brten mi dgos te de la
NK094(nge)001:14920: 'o na skyon du dgag go zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:14921: gal te rtsol sgrub dang yo byad la brten par
NK094(nge)001:14922: byas na'ang 'gag pa med de rol pa la dgag
NK094(nge)001:14924: brten par ma byas na'ang de ltar de kho na nyid du ngesa pas thag ring ba med pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:14925: bshad pa de ltar blo gros thabsa gsum gyi man
NK094(nge)001:14926: ngag gi don dang ldana na mtshamsa med lnga yi
NK094(nge)001:14927: las byed pa dang bsgral ba'i zhing bcur gyur pa'i
NK094(nge)001:14928: semsa can kun byang chub kyi sems snying rje chen
NK094(nge)001:14929: po dang / don dam chos nyid rtogs pa'i rdo
NK094(nge)001:14930: rje'i mtshon rnam pa gnyis kyis dngosa por spyod pa
NK094(nge)001:14931: yan chad du gasda cing bsgral na thugs rje dpag
NK094(nge)001:14932: tu med pa'i dger zhes dge bar 'gyur la /
NK094(nge)001:14933: gal te thugs rje dang bral bas ma basda na
NK094(nge)001:14934: de ltar min par gnyis ka ltung ba'i skyon no
NK094(nge)001:14935: // ji bzhin pa'i don rtogs dka' bar bstan pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:14936: lam rim kun gyis dona du gnyer zhing ched du bya ba'i rtogs bya'i dngos po dam pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:14937: gang zhig tu nges na rang gi kun gzhi byang
NK094(nge)001:14938: chub semsa kyi ngo bo mu mtha' las 'das pa'i
NK094(nge)001:14939: dbyingsa kyi chos nyid ril gyi 'byung gnas mtshan gzhi
NK094(nge)001:14941: rnal 'byor pa dmigs lta can gang zhig gis bskal
NK094(nge)001:14942: pa grangs med dpag tu med pa nyid du srid
NK094(nge)001:14943: pa gsum po g.yengs bshigs rmal bar byas te dkrugsa
NK094(nge)001:14944: pasa bsal bar byas nas yang /
NK094(nge)001:14945: dee nyid kyi ngo bo lhan pa med pa'i don te rega cing rtogs par 'gyur ba mina no //
NK094(nge)001:14946: 'o na gtan nas rtogs par bya ba'i thabs med do bar dogs pa la /
NK094(nge)001:14947: zab mo gsang ba'i sgo ji bzhin du nges pa 'dira ni /
NK094(nge)001:14948: rnal 'byor pa blo gros thabsa gsum gyi man ngag dang ldan pa zhig tu gyur pasa /
NK094(nge)001:14949: don yang dag pa nyid du rtogs na /
NK094(nge)001:14950: de la ni dper na chu yis rlan mi tshol ba ltar /
NK094(nge)001:14951: bdag nyid de kho na nyid kyi bdag nyid pas
NK094(nge)001:14952: ji bzhin pas ji bzhin pa gsang ba'i don nyid
NK094(nge)001:14953: btsal ba'i bya byed dang bral te bya ba med
NK094(nge)001:14955: yal bar 'dug pa'ang gyin 'ad'a ba'i btang snyoms chen po ste /
NK094(nge)001:14956: de ltar ranga riga pa gting nas mjal basa dona
NK094(nge)001:14957: chen po ma sgrub pa grub cing ma yengs par
NK094(nge)001:14958: rnal du 'byor te 'bad pa med par thob pa'i
NK094(nge)001:14959: thabs chen po nyal mo btsun du chos kyi dbyings
NK094(nge)001:14960: dang 'du 'bral med par ma btsal bar 'bras bu
NK094(nge)001:14961: lhun gyis grub pa'i thabs mchog dam pa bla na
NK094(nge)001:14962: med par gyur pa yina no //
NK094(nge)001:14963: de ltar yang kun tu bzang po che ba rang la gnas pa'i rgyud las /
NK094(nge)001:14964: byang chub sems nyid bde chen po //
NK094(nge)001:14965: rgyu nyid dag pa 'bras bu ste //
NK094(nge)001:14966: tshig dang yi ge las 'das pa //
NK094(nge)001:14967: btsal med lhun grub rang gnas pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:14969: rdzogs chen 'di la gang spyod pa //
NK094(nge)001:14970: ye shes kun bzang nyid yin pas //
NK094(nge)001:14971: bzang ngan gtsang sme gnyis su med //
NK094(nge)001:14972: man ngag don dang ldan pa'i gding //
NK094(nge)001:14973: sems las ma yengs dgongs pa'i klong //
NK094(nge)001:14975: sangs rgyas nyid du rang gnas pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:14976: zhes sogs shin tu mang ngo //
NK094(nge)001:14978: de bzhin nyid kyis ma zin sogs skyon bzhi'i sgo nas bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14979: de yang rnam grangs ngos bzung na /
NK094(nge)001:14980: man ngag gi thabs kyis ma zin pa'i rnam par
NK094(nge)001:14981: dkar ba'i las kyis kyang go 'phang dam par mi
NK094(nge)001:14982: 'gyur ba'i tshul / thabs kyi man ngag med na
NK094(nge)001:14983: yang dag pa'i spyod pa la 'bad kyang rang gi
NK094(nge)001:14985: man ngag gi thabs kyis don mthong ba med par
NK094(nge)001:14986: 'ching ba'i las la spyad na slar 'khor bar ltung
NK094(nge)001:14987: ba las thar pa med tshul /
NK094(nge)001:14988: de bas na thabs dang mi ldan pa 'ching bar
NK094(nge)001:14989: 'gyur gyi thabs dang ldan na de ltar mi 'gyur
NK094(nge)001:14993: de bzhin nyid kyis ma zin /
NK094(nge)001:14996: zhes pa'i bar tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:14997: gal te don gyi man ngag dang ldan pa'i dmigs
NK094(nge)001:14998: med pas chos nyid de bzhina nyid rtogs pa'i thabs
NK094(nge)001:14999: kyi dgongs pa'i rtsi mchog nyid kyis ma zin na
NK094(nge)001:15000: / rnam par dkar ba'i lasa kyi phyogsa bzang po rnams la kun tu 'bad par spyad kyang /
NK094(nge)001:15001: bde 'gro lha mi'i go 'phang tsam du ngesa par 'byung ba'i thabs su rung gi /
NK094(nge)001:15002: mthar thug gi 'bras bu rgyal ba'i go 'aphanga dama
NK094(nge)001:15003: pa thob para ga la 'gyur te mi 'gyur ro
NK094(nge)001:15009: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:15010: rnal 'byor pa ganga su zhig gis nyon mongs pa
NK094(nge)001:15011: de nyid chos nyid kyis zina nas rang grol bar
NK094(nge)001:15012: ma shes pa de kho na nyid mthong ba'i bya
NK094(nge)001:15013: ba med pa'i thabs dang ma ldan na /
NK094(nge)001:15014: yang dag dama pa'i spyod pa sgo gsum dag pa'i
NK094(nge)001:15015: lasa rnams la 'bad par byas yang dar gyi srin
NK094(nge)001:15016: bu bzhin du rang gi ched du byas pa'i rtog
NK094(nge)001:15017: pa des bcings nas thar pa dam pa'i go 'phang
NK094(nge)001:15018: du rnam par grol bar mi 'gyur te /
NK094(nge)001:15019: kun tu bzang po che ba rang la gnas pa las /
NK094(nge)001:15020: tshi chad las la grub pa med //
NK094(nge)001:15021: gzhan du rnal 'byor ma tshol cig /don med sgra tshig sgra phyir 'brangs //
NK094(nge)001:15022: theg pa nges med sa ma zin //
NK094(nge)001:15023: nges pa'i man ngag rtog par gol //
NK094(nge)001:15025: zhes gsungs pa ltar man ngag zab mo'i gol sar ltung ba srid pa yin no //
NK094(nge)001:15031: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:15032: gsang ba zab mo blo dman pa'i yul ma yin pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:15033: gang su zhig gis zab mo gsang ba'i sgo 'dira
NK094(nge)001:15034: de bzhin nyid mthong ba'i blo gros kyi mig dang
NK094(nge)001:15035: mi ldana pasa / spyod pa blo gros kyi spyan
NK094(nge)001:15036: dang ldan pa'i tshul du 'chos te bya ba med
NK094(nge)001:15038: gang 'ching ba'i las la spyod par byed pa dag ni /
NK094(nge)001:15039: don mchog dama pa'i go 'phang du rnam para grol bar mi 'agyur gyi /
NK094(nge)001:15040: slar yang srid par 'ching ba kho na las med
NK094(nge)001:15041: pas 'dod pa'i gnas kyi tha mar ngan song gsum
NK094(nge)001:15042: du ltung zhing 'khor ba'i dngos por 'gyur gyi /
NK094(nge)001:15043: thar zhing grol bar mi 'gyur ro //
NK094(nge)001:15044: de bas na rim slob tshad du phyin pa dang
NK094(nge)001:15045: cig char ba'i yul du gyur pas gang zag gnyis
NK094(nge)001:15046: ka'i bslab par brgyud pa dang mngon sum pa'i sgo
NK094(nge)001:15052: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:15053: gal te thabs dang ldan kyang 'ching ba la spyad
NK094(nge)001:15054: na grol bar mi 'gyur ro snyam du dogs pa
NK094(nge)001:15055: la / bshad pa ltar dama pa'i blo dang ldan par bya ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:15056: gros kyis chod par bya ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:15057: thabsa kyis zin par bya ba'i man ngag dam pa
NK094(nge)001:15058: gsum dang mi ldan par med par gyur na dman
NK094(nge)001:15059: spyad kyis slar yang 'ching ba yin gyi /
NK094(nge)001:15060: gzhan du na zag med mngon du byas pa'i byang
NK094(nge)001:15061: chub sems dpa' dama pa'i skyes bu sgom lam pa
NK094(nge)001:15062: rnams kyang ni / snying rje chen pos gdul bya
NK094(nge)001:15063: 'dul ba'i thabs mkhas kyis don mdzad pa'i dabnga gisa
NK094(nge)001:15064: skye ba rang dbang can du bzhes nas sems can
NK094(nge)001:15065: dman pa'i lus shan pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:15066: smad 'tshong la sogs pa lta bu'i tshul du sten
NK094(nge)001:15067: pa'am ston para byed pa'ang ltung bar 'gyur rigs na
NK094(nge)001:15068: yang mi ltung bas gsal lo //
NK094(nge)001:15069: de bas na thabs de dag mi ldan na de nyid kyang ltung ngo //
NK094(nge)001:15075: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:15076: 'o na grol ba kho na'o zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:15077: grol bar 'dzin pa dang ma grola bar 'dzin zhing
NK094(nge)001:15078: rtog pa dang la sogsa pa zhes dngos po gzhan
NK094(nge)001:15079: bsdu ba ni / bcing ba dang thar ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:15080: mthong ba dang ma mthong ba la sogs pa gnyis su rtog par bsnyad pa ril thamsa cad de /
NK094(nge)001:15081: gang phyogs gcig tu bsam pa nges pa kun mtha'a la thug pa zhes bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:15082: de bas na rnam pa thams cad kun mkhyen pa'i ye shes mnga' ba rnams ni /
NK094(nge)001:15083: grol ba la grol bar 'dzin pa'ang bral bas bcings
NK094(nge)001:15084: pa smos su med pa'i phyir dbu ma zhig tu
NK094(nge)001:15085: 'dzin pa'i 'du shes pa'ang mi mnga' bas yang dag
NK094(nge)001:15086: pa'i don gyi dbus la'nga gnas pa min te /
NK094(nge)001:15087: de ltar rtogs te rang gsal ye nas ma bcos
NK094(nge)001:15088: pa'i ngang la ni ye nas grol ba mngon du
NK094(nge)001:15089: byas pa las gsar du grol bar 'dod pa'ang med
NK094(nge)001:15090: pa nyid de de nyid thug pa med pa'i grol
NK094(nge)001:15091: ba chen po'o // des na sems lung chen po las /
NK094(nge)001:15092: mnyam nyid chos dbyings kun tu bzang //
NK094(nge)001:15093: phyogs bral chos nyid yongs rdzogs phyir //
NK094(nge)001:15094: dus gsum rnam pa zhi ba'i tshul //
NK094(nge)001:15095: mnyam pas rim par bkod pa med //
NK094(nge)001:15096: gcig pas phyogs su bsngo dang bral //
NK094(nge)001:15097: dri med rang bzhin dag pa'i tshul //
NK094(nge)001:15099: gleng bral 'di la gnas pa yis //
NK094(nge)001:15101: chos nyid gter ldan nam mkha'i tshul //
NK094(nge)001:15102: rnal 'byor chos nyid yin pa'i phyir //
NK094(nge)001:15103: bdag dang gzhan dag med pa'i phyir //
NK094(nge)001:15104: bdag dang gzhan don mi byed pas //
NK094(nge)001:15105: sgyu ma lhun grub yul la rol //
NK094(nge)001:15106: mi gnas dbyings las cir snang yang //
NK094(nge)001:15107: snang ba sgyu ma chen po ste //
NK094(nge)001:15108: yul la rol pas lhun gyis grub //
NK094(nge)001:15110: des na grol bar 'dod pa nyid ni 'ching ba
NK094(nge)001:15111: chen po yin pas mchog gsang rin po che snang
NK094(nge)001:15112: ba'i thabs kyi man ngag mthar thug pa la mkhas
NK094(nge)001:15113: par bya ste / ye shes rdzogs pa las /
NK094(nge)001:15114: ye shes rdzogs pa bde ba che //
NK094(nge)001:15115: mtha' yas 'gro ba kun la ldan //
NK094(nge)001:15116: rig pa dbyer med kun tu bzang //
NK094(nge)001:15117: gang yang ma yin rig par gsal //
NK094(nge)001:15118: rtsol ba'i sems bral mngon sangs rgyas //
NK094(nge)001:15120: rnam byang shes pa rang gnas pa //
NK094(nge)001:15121: byed pa nyid kyis mthong bar gyis //
NK094(nge)001:15122: zhes gsungs pa ltar man ngag gi gnad khyad par can la brten pa gal che'o //
NK094(nge)001:15127: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:15128: man ngag snying po'i don 'di nyid btsa' ba'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:15129: de ltar mtha' ril ma spangs ka nas dag pa'i
NK094(nge)001:15130: don mchog zab mo 'di ni blo chung gi spyod
NK094(nge)001:15131: yul du ma gyur pa'i gsang sngags gasnga ba dam
NK094(nge)001:15132: pa'i dgongs don bla med mchog tu gyur pa ste
NK094(nge)001:15133: / des na thabs kyi khyad par 'di ltar du ma rtogsa pa'i skye bo dang /
NK094(nge)001:15134: mu stegs kyi ris kun dang /
NK094(nge)001:15135: nyan thos nas yo ga phyi pa'i bar gyi blo
NK094(nge)001:15136: chung ba de dag kun la mi bstan par rab
NK094(nge)001:15138: 'o na bstan mi bzod pa'i ngan pa zhig go zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:15139: gsang don zab mo ni skyon yoda pa'i nyes pas
NK094(nge)001:15140: bstan du mi rung bar snyad can du gyur pa
NK094(nge)001:15141: ma yina te bshad pa ltar don du mi 'gyur
NK094(nge)001:15142: ba'i bzhi'i phyir mchog tu gzhan don du mi 'gyur
NK094(nge)001:15143: bas na mi bstan par bka' rgyas btab pa ste
NK094(nge)001:15144: / blo chung rnams la brgyud nas phana gdags pa'i phyir ro //
NK094(nge)001:15149: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:15150: dpe ji ltar na mun pa dang dug dang lcags
NK094(nge)001:15151: la sogs pa'i rdzas rnams sman dang snang ba dang
NK094(nge)001:15152: gsera du gyur ba na yang /
NK094(nge)001:15153: thabs med na 'grub tu mi btub ba'i dpe ste /
NK094(nge)001:15154: gong ma gsum gyi 'gyur rdzas sam gser 'gyur gyi
NK094(nge)001:15155: rtsi la mkhas pa'i man ngaga gi gnad med pa'i
NK094(nge)001:15156: misa dka' ba'i lasa chena sna tshogsa pa byas te
NK094(nge)001:15157: sdug bsngal mang po spyad kyang mi 'grub ste /
NK094(nge)001:15158: de gsum gyi 'gyur rdzas sam khyad par du'ang gser
NK094(nge)001:15159: 'gyur gyi rtsi 'chang ba dang mi 'chang ba'i tshul
NK094(nge)001:15160: ji lta ba'o // des na mkhas pa su zhig
NK094(nge)001:15161: 'gyur rtsi gsum gyi man ngaga da nga ldan pa'i
NK094(nge)001:15162: ji lta ba'o // misa ni / tshegsa chen po
NK094(nge)001:15163: med cing dka' ba sna tshogs mi dgos par sgron
NK094(nge)001:15164: ji lta ba'o // misa ni / ma dang / sngags sam rtsi sbyor dang /
NK094(nge)001:15165: gser 'gyur byed pa'i rtsi yis thabs chen po gyin
NK094(nge)001:15166: 'ad'i tshul gyis na de gsum bsgyur basa dug sman
NK094(nge)001:15167: dang mun pa snang ba dang rdzas rnams gser du
NK094(nge)001:15168: 'gyur ba'i dpe ltar de bzhin du mtshon par bya
NK094(nge)001:15169: ba'i don yang / rnal 'byor chena po gang gis
NK094(nge)001:15170: 'bras bu bla na med pa'i dona mchog gsang ba
NK094(nge)001:15171: yang dag par grub pa yang /
NK094(nge)001:15172: de nyid mthong ba'i blo dang grosa dang thabas dag
NK094(nge)001:15173: dang ganga daga yang dag par mi ldan pa daga
NK094(nge)001:15174: gisa ni daka'a ba sna tshogs pa spyad de bya
NK094(nge)001:15175: rtsol gyis 'bad kyang nges pa'i don grub pa mina
NK094(nge)001:15176: no // gang zhig semas kyi rang bzhin shin tu
NK094(nge)001:15177: rig cing shes par dka' ba'i gasnga ba mchog gi
NK094(nge)001:15178: don 'di dam pa sus rtogs shing mthong ba de
NK094(nge)001:15179: no // ni / blo gros thabas kyi man ngag gsum dang ldan pa ste /
NK094(nge)001:15180: de yis gang 'doda pa'i dona mchog gi 'bras bu dam pa gang yina pa de yang /
NK094(nge)001:15181: de daga gis tshegsa chen po med par thabs kyi
NK094(nge)001:15182: man ngag gi gyin 'adsa kyang nges par 'grub pa
NK094(nge)001:15183: yin no // khas blangs pa ltar gces par gdams pa'i don te /
NK094(nge)001:15184: de ltar bsgrub pa'i 'bras bu'i dona rnams yang dag
NK094(nge)001:15185: par grub par dam pa gang gis byed de mngon
NK094(nge)001:15186: du gyur pa ni man ngag gi gsang ba zab
NK094(nge)001:15187: mo blo gros thabsa gsum gyis nges par 'grub par
NK094(nge)001:15188: 'gyur ba'i phyir / gtan tshigs tshad mar 'byung ba'i
NK094(nge)001:15189: dgos pa de bas na snying po'i dona mchog gsang
NK094(nge)001:15190: ba zab mo rnams man ngag gi thabs khyad par
NK094(nge)001:15191: can gyis grub para 'gyur pa yi bslab pa 'di
NK094(nge)001:15192: dag snying nor du byed pa raba tu gces pa
NK094(nge)001:15193: 'gyur ba'i phyir / yin no // zhes gdams par mdzad de /
NK094(nge)001:15194: kun tu bzang po che ba rang la gnas pa'i rgyud las /
NK094(nge)001:15195: rang byung rgyal po sems can la //
NK094(nge)001:15196: rig pa'i rgyal po rnam shes shar //
NK094(nge)001:15197: phung po'i thig le chen po la //
NK094(nge)001:15198: rnam par dag pa'i thig le shar //
NK094(nge)001:15199: skye mched ting 'dzin gsal ba la //
NK094(nge)001:15201: gang la dpes bstan de bzhin du //
NK094(nge)001:15202: de bzhin sems can dpe bstan par //
NK094(nge)001:15203: bde ba chen po'i man ngag 'byung //
NK094(nge)001:15204: dag pas brtags kyang kun kyang gtsang //
NK094(nge)001:15205: rtogs pas bsam pas gang yang 'grub //
NK094(nge)001:15207: des na man ngag gi gnad la brten nas don
NK094(nge)001:15208: ma nor bar rtogs pa ni mchog tu gal che
NK094(nge)001:15210: mkhas pa mi gtso rtogs pa gtso //
NK094(nge)001:15211: mkhas pa'i tshig gi than yin no //
NK094(nge)001:15212: rtogs pas chos nyid klong na 'phyo //
NK094(nge)001:15213: bshad pa mi gtso bsgom pa gtso //
NK094(nge)001:15214: bshad pa tshig gi bshad ra yin //
NK094(nge)001:15215: bsgoms pas lha dang gnyis su med //
NK094(nge)001:15216: bsgrub pa bas kyang rtogs pa gtso //
NK094(nge)001:15217: rtogs pa gdeng du ma chud na //
NK094(nge)001:15218: bsgrub pa rtog pa'i rgyun la bsgrub //
NK094(nge)001:15219: bsgom pa mtshan ma'i ngang la bsgom //
NK094(nge)001:15220: rtsol ba nyon mongs zhen pa tshol //
NK094(nge)001:15221: rtogs pa ye nas che ba ni //
NK094(nge)001:15222: snang srid rtogs pas ye shes che //
NK094(nge)001:15223: phyi nang rtogs pas thig le che //
NK094(nge)001:15224: che chung rtogs pas mnyam nyid che //
NK094(nge)001:15225: yang dag rtogs pas ye shes che //
NK094(nge)001:15226: bzang ngan rtogs pas bde chen che //
NK094(nge)001:15227: bya btsal rtogs pas bde chen che //
NK094(nge)001:15228: bde chen rtogs pas byang chub che //
NK094(nge)001:15229: rtogs pa'i glang chen phyogs ris med //
NK094(nge)001:15230: yang dag don ldan bsnyen bsring med //
NK094(nge)001:15232: rang byung rang shar bya btsal med //
NK094(nge)001:15233: thar pa'i gnas ris spang len med //
NK094(nge)001:15234: dbyings kyi bde gdal phyogs ris med //
NK094(nge)001:15235: rtogs na bcos med snying po rtogs //
NK094(nge)001:15236: ston na rang byung 'bras bu ston //
NK094(nge)001:15237: thob na rnam dag bcos med thob //
NK094(nge)001:15238: nyi ma shar bas mun pa sangs //
NK094(nge)001:15239: zhes pa la sogs shin tu mang ngo //
NK094(nge)001:15243: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:15245: ji skad bgros pa de dag ni tshegas chung la
NK094(nge)001:15246: dona che ba man ngag gi ngo bo nyid du
NK094(nge)001:15247: yang dag par shes shing rig par bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:15248: de skad ces ston pa gsang bdag chen pos smras te bka' stsal pasa /
NK094(nge)001:15249: damna pa dam pa rnams rtogs pa'i blo dang ldana /
NK094(nge)001:15250: shes bya gros kyis chod de /
NK094(nge)001:15251: man ngag gi thabsa kyis zin te go zhing rtogs pa'i yon tan dang ldan para gyur to //
NK094(nge)001:15253: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongsa pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po las /
NK094(nge)001:15254: rtogs pa'i man ngag gis 'bras bu'i dona chena po
NK094(nge)001:15255: nges par sgrub pa zhes bya ba'i le'u ste bdun
NK094(nge)001:15256: cu rtsa bzhi pa nyid rnam par bshad de legs
NK094(nge)001:15257: par bkrol ba'o ////bcu pa mdo don gcig tu bsdu
NK094(nge)001:15258: ba la bslab pa tshong pa khe spogs sdud pa
NK094(nge)001:15259: ltar bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK094(nge)001:15262: bslab pa gces par gdams pa /
NK094(nge)001:15268: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:15270: de nasa yanga skyes bu chen po gasnga ba pa'i badga po desa /
NK094(nge)001:15271: lang ka'i bdag po la sogas pa damna pa'i lus
NK094(nge)001:15272: kyi byang chub semsa dapa'a sems dpa' chen po'i 'khor
NK094(nge)001:15273: rnams la sku shina tu rngamas brjid kyi tshul du
NK094(nge)001:15275: kye grogsa po dam pa dag mdo don gcig tu
NK094(nge)001:15276: 'dus pa'i bslab pa chen po bcu pa'i ngo bo
NK094(nge)001:15277: nye bar bstan pa ni gang zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:15281: sku lnga'i dgongs pa gcig tu bsdus te bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:15282: rigs lnga'i dgongs pa gcig tu bsdus te bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:15283: zhing khams lnga bcu rtsa brgyad kyi sgron ma'i dgongs pa gcig tu bsdus te bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:15284: zhing khams bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i sgron ma'i dgongs pa gcig bsdus te bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:15285: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi dgongs pa bya
NK094(nge)001:15286: ba med pa ye nas sangs rgyas par bsdus te
NK094(nge)001:15290: rgyun gyi 'byung ba ngo bo nyid dag pas de skad ces gsungs so //
NK094(nge)001:15291: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:15292: lung bstan brgyud pa'i gleng gzhi'i dbang du 'di skad badga gisa thos pa'i dus gcig na /
NK094(nge)001:15293: zhes gsang bdag chen po nyid kyis sku gsum mam
NK094(nge)001:15294: bzhi dang ngo bo nyid kyi sku las thos pa
NK094(nge)001:15295: nyid 'chad pa ste de dag bshad pa bzhin 'grel
NK094(nge)001:15296: to // de yang rgyal ba re re'i dgongs pa'i
NK094(nge)001:15297: mdo don bsdus pas mtshan nges par 'grub pa ni
NK094(nge)001:15298: to // / de kho na nyid lhun gyis grub
NK094(nge)001:15299: pa'i lam dang 'bras bu ril gyi dngos gzhi bas
NK094(nge)001:15300: der 'dus pa thun mong du bstan pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:15301: de bzhin gshegas pa sku lnga thamsa cad kyi dgongs
NK094(nge)001:15302: pa'i gsang ba dkyil 'khor gsum dbyer med par chos
NK094(nge)001:15303: nyid rang snang du mngon par gyur pas bcom ldana
NK094(nge)001:15304: 'adsa ngo bo nyid dag pa'i chos nyid kyi sku
NK094(nge)001:15305: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs dag pa gnyis ldan gyi gsang
NK094(nge)001:15306: sngags ji bzhin pa ni rgyal ba'i spyi myes dam
NK094(nge)001:15307: para gyur pas / dbyings rnam par dag pa chen
NK094(nge)001:15308: po de nyid du phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhina
NK094(nge)001:15309: gshegsa thamsa cad kun gyi dgongs pa'i dngos gzhi rab
NK094(nge)001:15310: tu gsang ba ma lus pa kun 'dus shing rdzogs
NK094(nge)001:15311: la mtha' ril ngag gis dag pa'i ngo bor gcig
NK094(nge)001:15312: dang du ma las 'das para gyur pa'i klong chen
NK094(nge)001:15313: para gyur pas / po nas / rgyud dag pa'i
NK094(nge)001:15314: de bzhina gshegas pa rgyal ba skyob pa'i dbang phyug
NK094(nge)001:15315: thamsa cad kyis kyang dgongs pa de kho na nyid
NK094(nge)001:15316: kyi ngang der son par gyur te /
NK094(nge)001:15317: rgyal ba de dag ril gyis /
NK094(nge)001:15318: de bzhina gshegas pa thamsa cad kyi dgongsa pa chos
NK094(nge)001:15319: rnams kyi de kho na gcig tu 'dus para gyur
NK094(nge)001:15320: pa'i don mchog rab tu gsang ba nyid ji ltar
NK094(nge)001:15321: bka' stsal pa bzhin du ma nor bar bashada par
NK094(nge)001:15322: mdzad pa ni / rang bzhin gyi gtan tshigs la
NK094(nge)001:15323: brten nas dngos po rnams kyi chos nyid de kho
NK094(nge)001:15324: na nyid rang rig pa nyid ni mtha' kun las
NK094(nge)001:15325: grol ba'i rnam par dag pa yin pasa na chos
NK094(nge)001:15326: can thams cad kun kyang de ltar rang bzhina rnam
NK094(nge)001:15327: para dag pa yin te chu gsher ba yin pas
NK094(nge)001:15328: rlan dang chab rom yang gsher ba lta bu'o //
NK094(nge)001:15329: don de ni rgyal ba de bzhin gshegsa pa thamsa
NK094(nge)001:15330: cad kyi thugsa dama mthar thug gi dbyingsa mchog dgongs
NK094(nge)001:15331: pa'i zhe phugs raba dang khyad par du gyur pa
NK094(nge)001:15332: nyid do // zhes bcom ldan 'das ngo bo nyid
NK094(nge)001:15333: kyi sku shin tu rnam par dag pa lasa rang
NK094(nge)001:15334: bzhin mnyam pa chen po'i dgongs pa de skad ces
NK094(nge)001:15335: nyid do // 'byung ba'o // de ltar na yanga 'di lta ste /
NK094(nge)001:15336: dbyings dang ye shes dus gsum du rang gi ngo
NK094(nge)001:15337: bos dbyer mi phyed pa rdo rje lta bur 'du
NK094(nge)001:15338: 'bral med pa'i dam tshig chen po ni /
NK094(nge)001:15339: snang stong gnyis su med pa'i rdo rje gsang ba'i
NK094(nge)001:15340: de bzhina nyid kyi ngang lasa rang byung rang shar
NK094(nge)001:15341: ba'i de nyid yin pas rgyu 'bras med pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:15342: de yang rang gi sems kyi chos nyid mi phyed
NK094(nge)001:15343: rdo rje'i dama tshig tu nges nas dgongs pa de
NK094(nge)001:15344: nyid ji lta bar ni mngon du gyur te rang
NK094(nge)001:15345: rig 'dus ma byas pa'i ngang du lhun gyis grub
NK094(nge)001:15346: par rtogs na 'pho 'gyur med pas nam yang 'dus
NK094(nge)001:15347: byas ltar 'jiga pa'i dus med pa nyid do //
NK094(nge)001:15348: grogsa po dag /bcom ldan 'adsa chos kyi sku rnam
NK094(nge)001:15349: par dag pa'i ngo bo nyid lasa chos nyid 'gyur
NK094(nge)001:15350: ba med pa'i dgongs pa de skad ces gsungas so
NK094(nge)001:15351: // grogsa po dag /de nasa yanga 'di lta ste /
NK094(nge)001:15352: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba kun gyi dgongs pa'i thugsa dam chen po ni /
NK094(nge)001:15353: 'khor 'das kyi dngos po gnyis kyi longs spyod thamsa
NK094(nge)001:15354: cad sems kyi chos nyid kyi rang snang dam pa
NK094(nge)001:15355: de kho na nyid lasa rang shar zhing de nyid
NK094(nge)001:15356: du rdzogs pas thams cad sems kyi dbyings las mi
NK094(nge)001:15357: gazhana te sems nyid las gazhana du gyur pa'i chos
NK094(nge)001:15358: don la med pas btsal yang rnyed pa yoda pa
NK094(nge)001:15359: ma yina no // de lta bu'i gnyis med yul
NK094(nge)001:15360: dang bral ba'i rol pa de lasa ganga du yang
NK094(nge)001:15361: 'ad'a bar mi 'gyur bar rang snang bde ba chen
NK094(nge)001:15362: ma yina no // por gsal ba'o // zhes bcom
NK094(nge)001:15363: ldan 'adsa rdzogsa longsa spyod pa ngo bo nyid dag
NK094(nge)001:15364: pasa rang snang sbyong yul phral ba'i dgongs pa de
NK094(nge)001:15368: rgyal ba'i dbang po dama pa rnams kyis bka' stsal te gsungs pa'i tshig ni gang zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:15369: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje mi phyed cing mi
NK094(nge)001:15370: 'jig pa'i ngo bo las mi g.yo bar don mdzad
NK094(nge)001:15371: pa'i go cha chen po'i thugs dama bcas pa yi
NK094(nge)001:15372: shin tu dama pa'i rgyal ba'i tha tshig 'di ltar
NK094(nge)001:15373: ni lam pas kyang gal te ma spyad par 'adsa
NK094(nge)001:15374: na ltung zhing bsreg ste 'tshig par 'gyur ba kho
NK094(nge)001:15375: na'o // zhes bcom ldan 'adsa gasnga ba'i sku nga
NK094(nge)001:15376: bo nyid dag pasa gsang don 'da' bar dka' ba'i
NK094(nge)001:15377: dgongs pa de skad ces gsungsa te 'di ni rdo
NK094(nge)001:15378: rje'i sku'i dgongs pa yang cha mthun par gsungs so
NK094(nge)001:15381: theg pa chen po mnyam pa'i dam tshig ni rgyal ba rnams kyi thugs dam dam pa ste /
NK094(nge)001:15382: mnyam pa'i dam tshig 'di las ma nyams par bsrungsa
NK094(nge)001:15383: pasa theg pa chen po'i sgo so sor grags pa
NK094(nge)001:15384: kun gyi 'dul ba'i sdom pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:15385: dam tshig dam pa mtha'a yasa pa kun thamsa cad
NK094(nge)001:15386: nas thamsa cad du bsrungsa shing dag par gyur pa
NK094(nge)001:15387: ste / de ltar bsrung ba 'di yi don dang
NK094(nge)001:15388: 'phrad cing nges par rtogs pa ni shin tu rnyed
NK094(nge)001:15389: ste / bar daka'a ba'o // zhes bcom ldan 'adsa
NK094(nge)001:15390: sprul pa'i sku rgyun gyi 'abyung ba ngo bo nyid
NK094(nge)001:15391: dag pasa dam tshig chen po'i dgongs mdo de skad
NK094(nge)001:15392: ste / bar daka'a ba'o // ces gsungsa so //
NK094(nge)001:15393: de dag ni rgyal ba sku lngas mnyam pa chen
NK094(nge)001:15396: kye grogs po dag /ces pa nas /
NK094(nge)001:15397: yon tan gyi 'byung gnas ngo bo nyid dag pas de skad ces gsungs so //
NK094(nge)001:15398: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:15399: kye grogsa po dag ces bos nas yanga 'di lta
NK094(nge)001:15400: ste mi spangs pa'i dam tshig 'dus pa gang zhe
NK094(nge)001:15401: na / rdo rje sems dpa'i dgongs pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:15402: zhe sdang ril gyi ngo bo gsang ba'i dbyings las
NK094(nge)001:15403: tha dada pa ma yin te rang rig pa mtha'
NK094(nge)001:15404: las bral ba'i byang chub kyi semsa su mnyam pasa
NK094(nge)001:15405: na chos nyid de bzhina nyid lasa gzhan pa'i rang
NK094(nge)001:15406: rgyud pa ma yina pas don la gnyis su med
NK094(nge)001:15407: pa'o // dgongs pa de lta bur rtogs te zhe
NK094(nge)001:15408: sdang ma spangsa bral bas mnar sems kyi dngos po
NK094(nge)001:15409: bcom nas rang rig pa'i ngang du rnam par dag
NK094(nge)001:15410: pa ni rdo rje gsang ba'i dama tshig chen po
NK094(nge)001:15412: zhes bcom ldana 'adsa rdo rje semsa dapa'a ngo bo nyid dag pasa de skad ces gsungsa so //
NK094(nge)001:15414: 'od mtha' yas kyi dgongs pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:15415: 'doda chags kyi shes pa dang chagsa pa'i yul gyi ngo bo nyid na /
NK094(nge)001:15416: rang bzhin ye nas ma bcos pa'i chos nyid du ka nas dag pa gang yin pa ste /
NK094(nge)001:15417: don la gnyis su med pa'i de bzhina nyid byang chub kyi sems su rtogs pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:15418: 'dod pa'i longsa spyod la ro myong ba dang tshor
NK094(nge)001:15419: ba'i ngo bo ma spangs bral te rnam par dag
NK094(nge)001:15420: pas spyod la ma chagsa pa'i ye shes dang ldan
NK094(nge)001:15421: nas zin chags kyi skyon med pa nyid rdo rje
NK094(nge)001:15422: gsang ba'i dama tshig dam pa de kho na nyid
NK094(nge)001:15423: do // zhes bcom ldan 'das 'od mtha' yasa ngo
NK094(nge)001:15424: bo nyid rnam par dag pasa de skad ces gsungsa
NK094(nge)001:15426: rnam par snang mdzad kyi dgongs pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:15427: tha snyad thamsa cad ril byang chub kyi sems de
NK094(nge)001:15428: bzhina nyid dera mtshungsa shing ngo bo de kho na
NK094(nge)001:15429: nyid du gcig pasa khyad para so so'i bye brag
NK094(nge)001:15430: gi ris su 'byed pa dang bral bas dbyer med
NK094(nge)001:15431: chen po mtshan nyid so sor mi phyed pa'i rdo
NK094(nge)001:15432: rje gsang ba'i nam mkha'a gnyis su med par 'oda
NK094(nge)001:15433: gasla ba'i ye shes yang dag pa'i gti mug rnam
NK094(nge)001:15434: par dag pasa rmongsa pa'i mun nag rnam para gasla
NK094(nge)001:15435: te ma rig pa ma spangs bral ba nyid du
NK094(nge)001:15436: bstan pa'o // bcom ldan 'adsa snang khyab madzada ngo bo nyid daga pasa de skad ces gsungsa so //
NK094(nge)001:15437: yanga don yod grub pa'i dgongs pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK094(nge)001:15438: sems kyi de kho na nyid spros pa dang bral
NK094(nge)001:15439: bas rnam par dag pa la phyogs ris su thug
NK094(nge)001:15440: pa'i mtha'a yi mu med cing rgya khyon dang bral
NK094(nge)001:15441: basa klong yangs pa la phrag doga dang de nyid
NK094(nge)001:15442: spangs par brjod pa'i tshig gi lam gyi brjod pa
NK094(nge)001:15443: dang yang bral te spyod yul dag pas kun tu
NK094(nge)001:15444: bazanga po la gang yang ma bkol bar yangas pa'i
NK094(nge)001:15445: de bzhin nyid kyi ngang rtogs pa'i lam du thams
NK094(nge)001:15446: cad byang chub kyi sems su gcig pas phrag dog
NK094(nge)001:15447: ma spangs bral te bde ba chena po'i klong yangas
NK094(nge)001:15448: par dag par spangs pa chen po ste /
NK094(nge)001:15449: de nyid rdo rje gsang ba'i theg pa chen po'i thabs kyi dama tshig dam pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:15450: zhes bcom ldana 'adsa thamsa cad grub pa ngo bo nyid dag pasa de skad ces gsungsa so //
NK094(nge)001:15451: yang rin chen 'byung ldan gyi dgongs pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK094(nge)001:15452: dngos po gnyis pa ril mnyam pa'i de bzhina nyid
NK094(nge)001:15453: du byung thebs te byang chub sems kyi ngang las
NK094(nge)001:15454: med pasa na nga yi ltar yina dang ma yina
NK094(nge)001:15455: bya ba'i bden rdzun gyi nga rgyal gnyis lasa 'adsa
NK094(nge)001:15456: te ngang gis bral ba la nga badga gi ngo
NK094(nge)001:15457: bo meda par rtogs nas rtog pas ma zin pa
NK094(nge)001:15458: ni / mi phyed pa'i rdo rje gsang ba'i ngo
NK094(nge)001:15459: bo ma bcos ma bslad pa'i de bzhina nyid yin
NK094(nge)001:15460: pas de la khengs dregs kyi nga bdag tu 'dzin
NK094(nge)001:15461: pa med pas ngo bo mi 'gyur ba ni nga
NK094(nge)001:15462: rgyal chen po'i rdo rje thabs kyi dama tshig go
NK094(nge)001:15463: ni / // zhes bcom ldan 'adsa yona tan kun
NK094(nge)001:15464: gyi 'byung gansa ngo bo nyid daga pasa de skad
NK094(nge)001:15465: ni / // ces gsungsa so // 'o na rigs
NK094(nge)001:15466: kyi sku lnga po de dag bstan pa gcig tu
NK094(nge)001:15468: sku lngar phye ba la dgos pa med do zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:15469: 'khor so so la rigs so sos 'dul ba'i dbang gis bstan par zad kyi /
NK094(nge)001:15470: don so sor mi gnas pas 'gal ba med do //
NK094(nge)001:15472: 'di dag gzhi dam tshig gis gzung bar bslab pa'i mdo 'dus par yang 'grel to //
NK094(nge)001:15473: gsum pa zhing khams lnga bcu rtsa brgyad kyi sgron ma'i dgongs pa la gsum ste /
NK094(nge)001:15474: sems nyid dkyil 'khor gsum du bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:15475: sems nyid gleng gzhir bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:15476: sems nyid mtshan nyid gsum du bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:15483: dri med sgra ngo bo nyid dag pas de skad ces gsungs so //
NK094(nge)001:15484: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:15485: grogsa po dag /gazhana yanga dri med sgra'i dgongs pa gang zhe na 'di lta ste /
NK094(nge)001:15486: dbang po drug dang yul drug la sogs pa yod
NK094(nge)001:15487: mthonga snang gragsa kyi chos 'khrul pa la snang zhing
NK094(nge)001:15488: grags so cog gi chos can rnams la brtags pas
NK094(nge)001:15489: rang bzhin lhun grub kyi rol pa la ngo bo
NK094(nge)001:15490: tha dada mi mthun pa sna tshogsa mtha'a yasa ji
NK094(nge)001:15491: snyed pa mang por snang kyang /
NK094(nge)001:15492: ril gyi ranga bzhin ye ji bzhin pa'i ngang du
NK094(nge)001:15493: 'phral du ma bcos ma byas par ye nas dag
NK094(nge)001:15494: pa'i de kho na nyid gsang ba'i chos nyid kyi
NK094(nge)001:15495: dbyings de bzhina nyid du dri mas ma sgrib par
NK094(nge)001:15496: gnyis su med pa'i byang chub sems su 'od gasla
NK094(nge)001:15497: bar gyur pas rang snang rnam par dag pa'i rgyal
NK094(nge)001:15498: ba'i zhing khams kyi bkod pa'ang de ltar dkyil 'khor
NK094(nge)001:15499: gsum gyi de bzhin nyid du dag pa gang yin
NK094(nge)001:15500: pa'o // zhes bcom ldan 'adsa dri med sgra ngo bo nyid dag pasa de skad ces gsungsa so //
NK094(nge)001:15502: rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK094(nge)001:15504: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK094(nge)001:15508: dkon mchog sprin ngo bo nyid dag pas de skad ces gsungs so //
NK094(nge)001:15509: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:15510: de bzhina du rgyal ba dkon mchog sprin gyi dgongs pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK094(nge)001:15511: sna tshogs pa'i dngos po kun tu ma 'gags par
NK094(nge)001:15512: rang shar zhing snang ba'i ye shes 'di ni sus
NK094(nge)001:15513: kyang ma byas bar ranga byung ye shes chen po
NK094(nge)001:15514: ste / thams cad de nyid du 'dus so //
NK094(nge)001:15515: des na ye shes chen po ni chos thamsa cad
NK094(nge)001:15516: kyi 'byung ba'i gnas kyi rtsa ba yin pas na
NK094(nge)001:15517: / chos so cog thams cad rang rig pa byang
NK094(nge)001:15518: chub kyi sems lasa rang byung ba'i ye shes nyid
NK094(nge)001:15519: du gnyis su med par rang 'char ba ni snying
NK094(nge)001:15520: po dang chos thams cad dang 'dus pas dkyil 'khora
NK094(nge)001:15521: chen por rdzogsa pa'i rtsa ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:15522: zhes bcom ldan 'adsa dkona mchog sprin ngo bo nyid dag pasa de skad ces gsungas so //
NK094(nge)001:15526: bkod pa'i 'byung gnas ngo bo nyid dag pas de skad ces gsungs so //
NK094(nge)001:15527: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:15528: gazhana yang bkod pa'i 'byung gnas kyi dgongsa pa rnam par bshad pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK094(nge)001:15529: de bzhin nyid ni ye nas ma bcos pas byed
NK094(nge)001:15530: pa por med pa la rang bzhin ma bslad pas
NK094(nge)001:15531: ji bzhina pa snang zhing grags pa'i chos so cog
NK094(nge)001:15532: kun gyi yang gsang gi rtsa ba'i snying po dam
NK094(nge)001:15533: pa ste / de'i mtshan nyid ni ngo bo bstan
NK094(nge)001:15534: du med pa lasa rang rtsal du byung ba'i chos
NK094(nge)001:15535: sna tshogsa cir yang snang la /
NK094(nge)001:15536: de nyid la'ang ngo bo la snang ba med pas
NK094(nge)001:15537: thams cad ma bsgos pa ni ye ji bzhin pa
NK094(nge)001:15538: de bzhina nyid kyi dkyil 'khora rdzogsa pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:15539: zhes bcom ldan 'adsa bkoda pa'i 'byung gansa ngo bo nyid daga pasa de skad ces gsungsa so //
NK094(nge)001:15543: seng ge sgra ngo bo nyid dag pas de skad ces gsungs so //
NK094(nge)001:15544: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:15545: gazhana yang seng ge'i sgra'i dgongs pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK094(nge)001:15546: dus gsum du 'gag pa med par ranga byung zhing
NK094(nge)001:15547: rang gi ngo bo riga par gsal ba'i semsa nyid
NK094(nge)001:15548: kyis ma bcos ma bslad par chos nyid chen po
NK094(nge)001:15549: gsang ba'i dbyingsa kyi dona nyid tha dad pa med
NK094(nge)001:15550: par gnyis med du lhun gyis grub pa'i ye shes
NK094(nge)001:15551: ni dbyings dang ye shes thabsa dang she sa raba
NK094(nge)001:15552: gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin kho na ste /
NK094(nge)001:15553: de ltar gnyis su med pa 'i ngang lasa yang
NK094(nge)001:15554: dag pa'i don ma nor bar ma 'dres lhun rdzogs
NK094(nge)001:15555: su shar ba ni ranga bzhina gyi dkyil 'khora rang
NK094(nge)001:15556: gasla du rdzogs pa ste rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor rnam
NK094(nge)001:15557: gsum yang de kho na nyid do //
NK094(nge)001:15558: zhes bcom ldan 'adsa seng ge sgra ngo bo nyid dag pasa de skad ces gsungsa so //
NK094(nge)001:15559: gnyis pa sems nyid ston 'khor tha dad med par
NK094(nge)001:15560: gleng gzhi'i mdo don gcig tu 'du ba la gnyis
NK094(nge)001:15564: gzhan yang bcom ldan 'das mdzes pa'i tog /ces pa nas /
NK094(nge)001:15567: zhes pa'i bar tshan gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:15568: gazhana yanga bcom ldan 'adsa mdzesa pa'i tog ngo bo nyid dag pas nyid kyi dgongs pa gsungsa pa /
NK094(nge)001:15569: 'jiga rten pa'i chos dang 'jiga rten las 'adsa pa yi chos rnams kyi /
NK094(nge)001:15570: phyi ma la skye rga na 'chi dang /
NK094(nge)001:15571: 'jig chags stongs gnas dang bcas pa dag bral bar bde zhing skyid pa'i lhun la gnas pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:15572: snga ma la de dag gis mi bde bar nyam
NK094(nge)001:15573: thag pa'i rnam para nang ba ril kun gyi ngo
NK094(nge)001:15574: bo yang sems kyi de bzhina nyid de kho na
NK094(nge)001:15575: nyid du dbyer med par ro gcig tu gyur pasa
NK094(nge)001:15576: tshor ba bde sdug nyid ma 'gags par gang yang
NK094(nge)001:15577: dmigs su med par rang rig pa gcig gi ngo
NK094(nge)001:15580: yanga bcom ldan 'adsa mdzes pa'i rgyan ngo bo nyid
NK094(nge)001:15581: daga pasa nyid kyi dgongs pa ni 'di skad du
NK094(nge)001:15582: / gsang sngags ji bzhin ba de bzhina nyid kyi
NK094(nge)001:15583: dona ni gleng gzhi'i ngo bor bstan du mi btub
NK094(nge)001:15585: ston pa dag 'khor ril de bzhina nyid de kho
NK094(nge)001:15586: na nyid du kun nas mnyam par gcig pasa na
NK094(nge)001:15587: / ston pa gang gisa 'khor gang la chos gang zhig bstan te bshad pa dang bral ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:15588: 'o na gtan bshad pa 'gog go zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:15589: ston 'khor so sor snang ba nyid ngo bo tha
NK094(nge)001:15590: dad med pas nyid la nyid gleng zhing 'chad pa
NK094(nge)001:15591: kho nara zad de gleng gzhi yang 'dus so //
NK094(nge)001:15594: dus kyi mnyam nyid bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:15595: gnas kyi rang bzhin bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:15596: bstan pa'i de nyid bshad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:15598: dus kyi mtshan nyid mnyam pa dngos bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:15599: dus bzhi mnyam par rtogs pa'i yon tan bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:15601: gzhan yang bcom ldan 'das dri'i rgyal po /
NK094(nge)001:15603: bskal pa de skad cig /ces gsungs so //
NK094(nge)001:15604: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:15605: gazhana yanga bcom ldan 'adsa dri'i rgyal po ngo bo
NK094(nge)001:15606: nyid dag pasa nyid kyi dgongs pa 'di skad du
NK094(nge)001:15607: / de bzhina nyid kyi gnas lugs mu mtha' dang bral ba'i dbyingsa kyi ngang nyid la /
NK094(nge)001:15608: snga phyi'i dus kyi rgyud gsum dang dus bzhira snang
NK094(nge)001:15609: ba ma 'gags kyang ngo bo mi dmigas te rang
NK094(nge)001:15610: bzhin gang du'ang ma grub don dang rang snang gi
NK094(nge)001:15611: ye shesa ji lta bar rig pa'i ngo bo rang
NK094(nge)001:15612: gsal du khyab cing gdal ba'i khyad para lasa /
NK094(nge)001:15613: dus skad cig dang bskal pa chen por snang ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:15614: de yi yun dang skad cig ma kun sems nyid
NK094(nge)001:15615: du dbyer med yin pas sdud pa pos kyang bka'
NK094(nge)001:15619: gzhan yang bcom ldan 'das snying rje'i /
NK094(nge)001:15623: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:15624: gazhana yang bcom ldan 'adsa snying rje'i rgyal po ngo
NK094(nge)001:15625: bo nyid dag pas nyid kyi dgongs pa ni 'di
NK094(nge)001:15626: skad du / 'khor ba dang mya ngana las 'adsa pa gnyis kyi dngos po dang /
NK094(nge)001:15627: de gnyis dbyer med pa'i chos nyid kyi ngo bo
NK094(nge)001:15628: mi 'gyur bas rtag pa chen po ni de bzhina
NK094(nge)001:15629: nyid dam de kho na nyid kyi dbyingsa ril gyi
NK094(nge)001:15630: 'byung gnas chen po'i ngo bo nyid kyi ngang du
NK094(nge)001:15631: rang shar te ye nas mya ngana las 'adsa par
NK094(nge)001:15632: gyur pasa na srid pa 'khor ba'i ming yang med
NK094(nge)001:15633: pas 'bras bu rang bzhina lhun gyis grub ste tshogsa
NK094(nge)001:15634: gnyis ma btsal bar ye nas rdzogsa pa nyid do
NK094(nge)001:15637: phyi'i yul skye med chos kyi dbyings su bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:15638: zhing khams chos nyid kyi yon tan rin po che'i sprin du bkod par bshad pa /
NK094(nge)001:15639: gzhal yas khang de bzhin nyid las rgyal ba'i pho brang du bkod par bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:15641: yang bcom ldan 'das dga' ba'i spyan /
NK094(nge)001:15647: yang bcom ldan 'das gser gyi 'od zer /
NK094(nge)001:15651: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:15652: yanga bcom ldan 'adsa dag'a ba'i spyan ngo bo nyid dag pasa nyid kyi dgongs pa 'di skad du /
NK094(nge)001:15653: 'dus byas dang 'dus ma byas pa'i chos so cog
NK094(nge)001:15654: gi ranga bzhina ni dus gsum du ngo bo nyid
NK094(nge)001:15655: kyis mi rnyed par 'byung 'jug med pa'i ma skyes
NK094(nge)001:15656: pa lasa thamsa cad du skyes te cir yang snang
NK094(nge)001:15657: la / de ltar skyes pa nyid na'ang ngo bo
NK094(nge)001:15658: skye ba med pa ni bde ba chen po'i gnas
NK094(nge)001:15659: la / te / des na rigsa mchog gnyis med
NK094(nge)001:15660: mnyam pa de nyid ji ltar bar rig na rdo
NK094(nge)001:15661: rje theg pa'i skye gansa dama par gyur pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:15663: yanga bcom ldan 'adsa gsera gyi 'oda zera ngo bo
NK094(nge)001:15664: nyid dag pas nyid kyi dgongs pa 'di skad du
NK094(nge)001:15665: / dapaga tu med pa'i rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK094(nge)001:15666: rgyas rnams kyang ngo bo ji bzhina pa'i de bzhina
NK094(nge)001:15667: nyid kyi ngang la ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su bzhugs
NK094(nge)001:15668: pas de bzhina nyid dang gcig dang du ma las
NK094(nge)001:15669: grol ba'i tshul du thamsa cad kyang gnyis su meda
NK094(nge)001:15670: pa'i de bzhina nyid dang tha mi dad par bzhugs
NK094(nge)001:15671: pas na chos kyi dbyings kyi gnas sam gzhal yas
NK094(nge)001:15672: khang dam pa de nyid do //
NK094(nge)001:15674: yanga bcom ldan 'adsa 'od kyi dapala ngo bo nyid dag pas nyid kyi dgongs pa 'di skada du /
NK094(nge)001:15675: 'khora ba dang ni mya ngana las 'adsa pa'i dngos
NK094(nge)001:15676: po gnyis pa ril de kho na nyid du gnas
NK094(nge)001:15677: pas so sora tha dad du snang ba'i rang rgyud
NK094(nge)001:15678: pa'i dngos po yod pa ma yina te /
NK094(nge)001:15679: ji bzhin pa'i chos nyid de bzhina nyid du yang dag par ngesa pa'i don rtogs na /
NK094(nge)001:15680: rig pa de la 'khora ba'i ranga bzhina ma dag
NK094(nge)001:15681: pa'i snang ba med par chos nyid du gsal bas
NK094(nge)001:15682: mya ngan las 'das pa'ang 'di nyid yin pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:15686: yang bcom ldan 'das yongs su dgongs pa'i rgyal po /
NK094(nge)001:15690: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:15691: yang bcom ldan 'adsa yongas su dgongas pa'i rgyal po
NK094(nge)001:15692: ngo bo nyid daga pasa nyid kyi dgongs pa 'di
NK094(nge)001:15693: skad du / chos so cog de bzhina nyid de
NK094(nge)001:15694: kho na nyid du kun nas gnas pa'i riga cing
NK094(nge)001:15695: rtogs nas gnyis med du thag chod na /
NK094(nge)001:15696: de bzhin nyid mu mtha' med pa desa khyab pa'i
NK094(nge)001:15697: gara gnas pa nyid sangsa rgyas kyi zhing khams rnam
NK094(nge)001:15698: par dag pa'i yona tan lhun gyis grub pa nyid
NK094(nge)001:15699: 'dod rgu 'byung ba rina chen gyi sprin du bkoda
NK094(nge)001:15700: pa yin pas de la'ang dbyings kyi ngang la bkoda
NK094(nge)001:15701: par bya ba ci yang med pas ma bgrod par
NK094(nge)001:15706: yang bcom ldan 'das zhi ba'i dbang po /
NK094(nge)001:15710: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:15711: yanga bcom ldan 'adsa zhi ba'i dbang po ngo bo
NK094(nge)001:15712: nyid dag pas nyid kyi dgongs pa 'di skad du
NK094(nge)001:15713: / sems nyid de bzhina nyid kyi de kho na nyid ni mu mtha'i tshad dang bral bas /
NK094(nge)001:15714: dapaga cing gazhala bar byed pa'i mtha' las 'das te
NK094(nge)001:15715: gzhal yasa khang zhes pa'i ming yang 'grub pasa bzhugs
NK094(nge)001:15716: nas dam pa nyid de dapaga tu meda pa'i rgyal
NK094(nge)001:15717: ba'i pho brang yina pas de na sangs rgyas ril
NK094(nge)001:15718: kun ched du ma btsal bar rang snang gi bkoda
NK094(nge)001:15719: par lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang dera gciga tu gansa
NK094(nge)001:15720: shing dbyer med par bzhugs pa'i don du nges so
NK094(nge)001:15723: brjod bya don gyi bstan pa /
NK094(nge)001:15724: rjod byed tshig gi bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:15728: gnyis su med pa'i bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:15730: yang bcom ldan 'das sprin gyi dpal /
NK094(nge)001:15734: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:15735: yanga bcom ldan 'adsa sprin gyi dpal ngo bo nyid dag pasa nyid kyi dgongs pa 'di skad du /
NK094(nge)001:15736: chos nyid ci yang med pa las chos thamsa cad cir yang 'byung zhing 'char ba'i cho 'phrul yanga /
NK094(nge)001:15737: cir yanga 'gyur ba'i ye shes chen po thams cad
NK094(nge)001:15738: kyi dngos gzhi ngo bo ma nges pa nyid snang
NK094(nge)001:15739: ba ste / de la gdos par gyur pa'i chos
NK094(nge)001:15740: med cing ther zug dang bral basa gang ji ltar
NK094(nge)001:15741: dmigas shing bsam pa bzhina du sna tshogs su snang
NK094(nge)001:15742: ba 'byung ba ni dpe yid bzhin gyi nor bu
NK094(nge)001:15750: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:15751: yanga bcom ldan 'adsa yid 'ong dbyangs ngo bo nyid daga pasa nyid kyi dgongs pa 'di skad du /
NK094(nge)001:15752: 'jiga rten 'khora ba'i skye gnas su kha brgyud cing
NK094(nge)001:15753: skye bar byed pa'i rtsa ba ni ma rig pa'o
NK094(nge)001:15754: // ma riga pa'i ngo bo nyid gdod nas de
NK094(nge)001:15755: bzhina nyid kyi ye shes yin pas rten pa yi
NK094(nge)001:15756: gzhi dang bskyed pa'i rtsa ba meda par ci yang
NK094(nge)001:15757: mi 'gog pa'i skad cig ma yin la /
NK094(nge)001:15758: don de nyid phyin ci ma log par riga cing
NK094(nge)001:15759: rtogs na 'khor ba nyid bde ba chen po'i gnas
NK094(nge)001:15760: te / gzhan du bgrod du med pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:15763: yang bcom ldan 'das me long 'od snang /
NK094(nge)001:15767: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:15768: yanga bcom ldan 'adsa me longa 'od snang ngo bo nyid dag pasa /
NK094(nge)001:15769: nyid kyi dgongs pa 'di skad du /
