NK094(nge)001:17371: ye nyid nas mtha' gnyis kun gyi ranga bzhina stong
NK094(nge)001:17372: pa nyid du gsal bar mkhyen te phyogs ris bral
NK094(nge)001:17373: ba'i thig ler rdzogs pas stong pa nyid kyi ye
NK094(nge)001:17375: zhesa de kho na nyid rtogs pa'i ngo bor dgongs
NK094(nge)001:17376: pa ye shes lnga rgyun du 'char bar basngagasa so
NK094(nge)001:17382: zhes thams cad 'byung bar basngagasa so //
NK094(nge)001:17383: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:17384: yang kun mkhyen la la ni 'di skad du gsungs te /
NK094(nge)001:17385: sems kyi ngo bo ji bzhin pa'i ngang las snang
NK094(nge)001:17386: stong gi chos rnams kyi go 'byed cing snang la
NK094(nge)001:17387: kun la khyab par snums shing gsal bas nam mkha'a
NK094(nge)001:17388: yang yin no // ril ngang du theg pa'i thig
NK094(nge)001:17389: le chen po der rdzogs te dbyingsa la kun rten
NK094(nge)001:17390: pa'i gzhir gansa pas sa yang yin no //
NK094(nge)001:17391: gang du yang mi g.yo bas zhi bar gnas te
NK094(nge)001:17392: rdul dang bral ba sa rnam par daga pa ni
NK094(nge)001:17394: lhag mthonga gi ye shes chen pos mi bsgribs par gsal bas 'od zer 'abra ba'i me'o //
NK094(nge)001:17395: shes bya ril la thogsa pa med par rang rig
NK094(nge)001:17396: pa'i mngon sum du gsal ba la zin chags thams
NK094(nge)001:17397: cad 'thora te dag pa'i klong du spros mtha' med
NK094(nge)001:17398: par byed pas rlung chen po'o //
NK094(nge)001:17399: zhesa chos thamsa cad ye shes kyi 'byung ba chen po lngar 'dus para rab tu basngagasa so //
NK094(nge)001:17405: ces yon tan dam par basngagasa so //
NK094(nge)001:17406: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:17407: yang rnam 'dren la la ni 'di skad du gsungs te /
NK094(nge)001:17408: chos so cog ma 'dres la yongsa su rdzogas par gasla ba ni stong pa chen po'i gzugsa so //
NK094(nge)001:17409: ril la khyab par gasla ba'i ranga bzhina rig pa
NK094(nge)001:17410: la gnyis med du go bar brda sprod pa'i tshul
NK094(nge)001:17412: ngo bo nyid rdul dang bral te dang bas shes rab tshim par byed pas chos nyid kyi dri'o //
NK094(nge)001:17413: dona mchog mnyam pa nyid kyi bcud dam pa nyamsa su myong basa ro'o //
NK094(nge)001:17414: zug rngu thams cad dang bral ba'i bde chen mchog
NK094(nge)001:17415: gi don la blos rega pa med pa nyid rega
NK094(nge)001:17416: bya'o // zhesa 'dod yon lnga rang rig gi yona tan dama para basngagasa so //
NK094(nge)001:17417: de bas na 'dod yon lnga yang de kho na nyid du 'dus so //
NK094(nge)001:17420: ye shes lnga bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:17425: mi 'gyur gzhan phrag dog /ces blangs dor med par basngagasa so //
NK094(nge)001:17426: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:17427: yang ston pa la la ni 'di skad du gsungs te /
NK094(nge)001:17428: de kho na nyid kyi ngang gis cir yang mi
NK094(nge)001:17429: semas pas ris su mi 'byed pa'i mnyam pa ni
NK094(nge)001:17431: snang stong gi mtha' yi dngosa po dang dngos med
NK094(nge)001:17432: kun de kho na nyid kyi ngang du bcom ste
NK094(nge)001:17433: tshar gcod pas zhe sdang nyid dang /
NK094(nge)001:17434: thams cad ye nas 'byamsa pa'i chos nyid ma nor
NK094(nge)001:17435: ba'i bdag nyid du gsal te zla med pas nga
NK094(nge)001:17436: rgyal badga nyid che ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:17437: bde ba chen po nyid dngos po ril dang ranga
NK094(nge)001:17438: bzhina mi phyed pa rjes su chagas pa nyid 'dod
NK094(nge)001:17439: chags dang / log rtog dang mtha'i skyon gang du
NK094(nge)001:17440: yang mi 'gyur zhing gazhana gyi lta ba sna tshogs
NK094(nge)001:17441: kun ma spang mi chud pa'i phyir phrag dog go
NK094(nge)001:17442: chags dang / // zhes nyon mongs pa lnga yang
NK094(nge)001:17443: rang rig pa'i ye shes su blang dora med par
NK094(nge)001:17446: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes /
NK094(nge)001:17447: me long lta bu'i ye shes /
NK094(nge)001:17448: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes /
NK094(nge)001:17449: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes /
NK094(nge)001:17450: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes so //
NK094(nge)001:17456: ces bdud rtsi dam par basngagasa so //
NK094(nge)001:17457: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:17458: yang rgyal ba la la ni 'di skad du gsungs te /
NK094(nge)001:17459: chos rnams kun gyi rang bzhina bdag nyid chen po
NK094(nge)001:17460: gcig nyid shes shing rtogs pasa de nyid kyi dabnga
NK094(nge)001:17461: du thamsa cad 'dus te kun la dabnga bsgyur thob
NK094(nge)001:17462: pasa na rim pa dbang gis bgrod pa yang ye
NK094(nge)001:17463: dbang chena pora rdzogsa shing 'dus pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:17464: zhes shes rab kyi rtsal la rim pa dbang gis bgrod pa yang 'dus pa dama para basngagasa so //
NK094(nge)001:17465: thub pa la la ni 'di skad du gsungs te /
NK094(nge)001:17466: dngos po gnyis pa thams cad ril gyi don kun
NK094(nge)001:17467: 'dus pa'i rang bzhin nyid riga pa'i mdo yi rgyud
NK094(nge)001:17469: rgyud 'di'i ngo bo gsang ba dam pas chos kun
NK094(nge)001:17470: la bsnums par khyab cing gnas la ngo bo brtagsa
NK094(nge)001:17471: par mi nus pas gting dapaga daka'a ba zaba mo
NK094(nge)001:17472: ni rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangsa rgyas kyi spyod yul
NK094(nge)001:17473: yina gyi / gzhan gyis shin tu rtogs par dka'
NK094(nge)001:17474: ba'i rdo rje kun tu bkoda pa'i rgyud kyang de
NK094(nge)001:17475: kho na nyid rang bzhin gyi rnal 'byor sgro skur
NK094(nge)001:17476: med par grub pa'i lung chen po 'adi'o //
NK094(nge)001:17477: zhesa rang bzhin gyi rgyud la rkyen gyi rgyud yang
NK094(nge)001:17478: 'dus pas mi phyed pa'i bka' dam par basngagasa so
NK094(nge)001:17479: // 'dren pa la la ni 'di skad du gsungs te /
NK094(nge)001:17480: de kho na nyid thig le chen po'i ngang dera
NK094(nge)001:17481: ni chos kun mnyam par gcig pasa badga dang gazhana
NK094(nge)001:17482: gyi ris nyid du snang ba med pas mtha' rnams
NK094(nge)001:17483: stong pa nyid du ngang gis rnam par daga pa'i
NK094(nge)001:17484: chos nyid kyi nam mkha'a la gtsang smer rtog pa'i
NK094(nge)001:17485: dri ma'i dabye ba rdul tsam yanga med pas bdud
NK094(nge)001:17486: rtsi chen po'o // zhesa gtsang sme med par rtogs
NK094(nge)001:17487: na badud rtsi dam pa'i sman yin para basngagasa so
NK094(nge)001:17488: rtsi chen po'o // // gnyis pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:17493: zhes re dogs med par basngagasa so //
NK094(nge)001:17494: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:17495: yang sangs rgyas la la ni 'di skad du gsungs te /
NK094(nge)001:17496: ngo bo nyid kyi sku lnga lhun gyis grub pas
NK094(nge)001:17497: byang chub snying po mtha'i skyon gyi sa rdul dang
NK094(nge)001:17498: bral bas dwangsa pa la rnam par rtog pa'i rdul
NK094(nge)001:17500: bzang ngan gyi rtog pa de nyid byang chub kyi
NK094(nge)001:17501: sems chen pora 'ub chub cing gnyis med kyi ngang
NK094(nge)001:17502: du gcig par grol basa cis kyang mi bskyod de
NK094(nge)001:17503: 'pho 'gyur med par nyam mi nga zhing g.yo ba
NK094(nge)001:17505: zhesa re dogsa med pa'i dgongs pa dam para basngagasa so //
NK094(nge)001:17511: zhes rang bzhin dam par basngagasa so //
NK094(nge)001:17512: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:17513: yang ston pa la la ni 'di skad du gsungs te /
NK094(nge)001:17514: theg pa mchog gi don rtogs pa ni rnam par
NK094(nge)001:17515: rtog pa'i sgrib pa mtshan ma'i ri bo 'di nyid
NK094(nge)001:17516: gzhan du spang du med de /
NK094(nge)001:17517: dper na seng ge'i khog pa sems can gzhan gyis
NK094(nge)001:17518: 'jig par mi nus kyang rang las byung bas 'jiga
NK094(nge)001:17519: pa ltar ji bzhin pa'i stong pa nyid chen po'i
NK094(nge)001:17520: nganga du sgrib pa nyid rang bzhin rang grol nyid
NK094(nge)001:17522: gnyen po gazhana gyis 'jiga para ga la 'gyur te
NK094(nge)001:17523: mi 'gyur bas gnyen pos sel bar mi bzhed do
NK094(nge)001:17524: // zhesa mtshan ma rang grol gyi dgongs pa la
NK094(nge)001:17525: gnyen po med par ranga bzhina dama par basngagasa so
NK094(nge)001:17531: ces yongs su rtog pa las 'das par basngagasa so //
NK094(nge)001:17532: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:17533: yang rgyal ba la la ni 'di skad du gsungs te /
NK094(nge)001:17534: bde ba chen po 'dzin rtog dang bral te rnam
NK094(nge)001:17535: para rtog pa meda pas na legsa nyes gnyis ka
NK094(nge)001:17536: ru 'dzin pa'i rnam para rtog pa ni rang rtsal
NK094(nge)001:17538: de bas na rang rig pa bde ba chen por ngesa pa'i klong las ma nyams par zhugsa na /
NK094(nge)001:17539: mtha' snang ganga zhiga tu'ang rtog pa'i rnam para rtog
NK094(nge)001:17540: pa ni med de ma spangs bral ba kho na'o
NK094(nge)001:17541: // zhesa snang ba bde ba chen po las ma
NK094(nge)001:17542: nyams na yongsa su rtog pa lasa 'adsa te ma
NK094(nge)001:17543: spangs rang grol gyi dgongs pa dam para basngagasa so
NK094(nge)001:17549: zhes dam tshig dam par basngagasa so //
NK094(nge)001:17550: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:17551: yang rnam 'dren la la ni 'di skad du gsungs te /
NK094(nge)001:17552: sems kyi de kho na nyid de phyin ci ma
NK094(nge)001:17553: loga para rtogs nas gang bsrung bar bya ba la
NK094(nge)001:17554: blos mi rtog cing gang la yang mi gansa para
NK094(nge)001:17556: le lo dang g.yenga ba drug ni rnal 'byor gyi
NK094(nge)001:17557: nor 'phrog pa'i dgra yin pas skyon du mi 'dzin
NK094(nge)001:17558: par dbang du yang mi btang zhing bsrung bar bya
NK094(nge)001:17559: dgos te zab mo de bzhina nyid kyi don de
NK094(nge)001:17560: lasa 'ad'a bar mi bya ste dam tshig mi nyams
NK094(nge)001:17561: par bya'o // zhes dgra bzhi bzlog pa'i dama tshig ni bsrung ba'i mchog dang dama para basngagasa so //
NK094(nge)001:17563: 'og tu mjug rdzogs su nye ba na /
NK094(nge)001:17565: brtan g.yo dkyil 'khor phyag rgyar rdzogs //
NK094(nge)001:17568: zhes gsang sngags dam pa'i tshig go //
NK094(nge)001:17569: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:17570: yang skyob ba la la ni 'di skad du gsungs te /
NK094(nge)001:17571: snod bcud brtan g.yo thams chad sems kyi chos nyid
NK094(nge)001:17572: mtha' dang bral ba yin pas de nyid lha'i dkyil
NK094(nge)001:17573: 'khora ye shes kyi phyag rgyar rang shar du rdzogsa
NK094(nge)001:17574: pa'i phyir / 'gro ba'i rtog 'dzina dang sgra mtha'a
NK094(nge)001:17575: rnams rim pa bzhin du ting nge 'dzina dang gsang
NK094(nge)001:17576: sngagsa snying po'i rgyun du sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:17577: de bas na ngo bo nyid med pa'i rgyu las
NK094(nge)001:17578: cir yang btagsa pa ltar chagsa pa rnams ni bstan
NK094(nge)001:17579: pa gsum mtshon pa'i tshig tu shar bas rgyal ba'i
NK094(nge)001:17581: gang ltar bsams shing don du gnyer te bsgrub pas
NK094(nge)001:17582: 'grub pa dang bltas pa ltar snang ba ni ril
NK094(nge)001:17583: 'bras bu'o // de ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:17584: ngo bo nyid yin pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:17585: gzhan du mi rnyed pa'i phyir ro //
NK094(nge)001:17586: de ni gsang sngags kyi ngo bo nyid bstan pas mtshon pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:17587: zhes gsang sngags dama pa'i tshig go //
NK094(nge)001:17588: bzhi pa de dag gi don bsdus te bstan pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:17591: dpag tu med pa'i 'jig rten du //
NK094(nge)001:17594: ces dgongs pa gcig tu 'dus par basngagasa so //
NK094(nge)001:17595: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:17596: yang ston pa la la ni 'di skad du gsungs te /
NK094(nge)001:17597: gdul bya'i gnas dpag tu med pa'i 'jiga rten gyi
NK094(nge)001:17598: khams mang po nyid du ston mchog sprul pa'i sgron
NK094(nge)001:17599: ma mang po bsam gyis mi khyab pasa theg pa'i
NK094(nge)001:17600: sgo ji snyed pa yi chos mang por gsungs te
NK094(nge)001:17601: tshad las 'das par bstan pa mtha'a yasa pa'i dona
NK094(nge)001:17602: ni de kho na nyid ji bzhin pa las lhag
NK094(nge)001:17603: pa med pas dgongs pa dam pa byang chub kyi
NK094(nge)001:17604: sems gcig tu 'dus par zad do //
NK094(nge)001:17605: zhesa theg pa'i sgo du ma bstan yang nges don
NK094(nge)001:17606: theg pa mchog gi dgongsa pa gcig tu 'dus pa
NK094(nge)001:17607: kho nar nges par basngagasa so //
NK094(nge)001:17608: lnga pa de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi dgongs
NK094(nge)001:17609: pa bya ba med pa ye nas sangs rgyas par
NK094(nge)001:17612: kye grogs po dag /de ltar na /
NK094(nge)001:17615: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:17617: kye grogsa po dag /ces bos nas bshad pa la snyegs pa'i tshul de ltar na /
NK094(nge)001:17618: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas de
NK094(nge)001:17619: bzhina gshegsa pa thamsa cad kyi dgongas pa gsang ba
NK094(nge)001:17620: dam pa de kho na nyid lasa ji skad gsungs
NK094(nge)001:17621: pa spyi'i don du thos pa ni 'di skad du
NK094(nge)001:17622: nges te / 'khor ba'i chos thams cad dang mya
NK094(nge)001:17623: ngan las 'das par gyur pa'i chos thamsa cad du
NK094(nge)001:17624: snang ba bsam yas ji snyed pa brjod pa las
NK094(nge)001:17625: 'das pa ril ni gdul bya'i ngo la tshig gi
NK094(nge)001:17626: tha snyad las btags pa'i yod pa tsam dag lasa
NK094(nge)001:17627: ngo bo 'di 'drar bzung du med de mtha' thams
NK094(nge)001:17628: cad dang bral ba'i chos sku chen por sangs rgyas
NK094(nge)001:17629: nges te / pa 'di la / 'phral du rtsol
NK094(nge)001:17630: ba'i dgag sgrub kyi bya ba byas te thob par
NK094(nge)001:17631: bya ba ci yang med de /
NK094(nge)001:17632: chos so cog gi rang bzhina gdod nas de lta
NK094(nge)001:17633: bu'i ngo bo nyid du ye sangsa rgyas te 'pho
NK094(nge)001:17635: zhes pa'i don gyi dgongs pa mthar thug nges pa'i gsang ba chen por yang dag par nges pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:17636: a ho zhes pa'i yi ge gnyis ni ngo bo
NK094(nge)001:17637: med pa nyid cir yang snang bas gnyis med du
NK094(nge)001:17638: bstan pa'o // zhesa de skad ston pa'i rgyal ba
NK094(nge)001:17639: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas de bzhina gshegsa pa thamsa cad
NK094(nge)001:17640: ril gyi ngo bo'ang gcig dang du ma'i chos kyi
NK094(nge)001:17641: tshig gi tha snyad lasa grol bas mtha' kun las
NK094(nge)001:17642: bstan pa'o // 'das te / rang bzhin bdag nyid
NK094(nge)001:17643: chen por dbyer med pa'i ngang gis bde sdug gi
NK094(nge)001:17644: tha snyad med cing rgyu 'bras dang chos so cog
NK094(nge)001:17645: ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs pa'i phyogs bral bde ba
NK094(nge)001:17646: chen po'i ngo bo lhun mnyam yangs pa'i chos nyid
NK094(nge)001:17647: rang snang gi de kho na nyid mngon du gyur
NK094(nge)001:17648: bstan pa'o // 'das te / pas / gang dang
NK094(nge)001:17649: yang ma bral la rnam grangs lhan mi gcig par
NK094(nge)001:17650: ma gos dri rdul bral ba'i dwangsa pa chen po'i
NK094(nge)001:17651: ngo bor bzhugs par gyur to //
NK094(nge)001:17652: gsum pa bslab pa gces par gdams pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:17656: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:17657: bslab pa tha ma'i dpe don gsal bar bstan pa'i phyir /
NK094(nge)001:17658: rgyal ba ril gyi dgongs pa thos pa ma nor
NK094(nge)001:17659: bar 'gros pa'i rjes thog de nas yanga mdo don
NK094(nge)001:17660: gcig tu bsdu ba'i bslab pa nyid gces par dpes
NK094(nge)001:17661: bstan pa skyes bu gsang ba pa'i bdag po nyid
NK094(nge)001:17662: kyis tshigsa su bcad de smras shing gsungs pa ni
NK094(nge)001:17663: / dpera na chos mthun pa'i don tshong pa kun
NK094(nge)001:17664: tu rgyu ba'i mi dag gis rang rang gi khe
NK094(nge)001:17665: 'doda pa'i yul mang po nyid du ganga 'gro ba
NK094(nge)001:17666: rnams kyang bgrod pa'i yula gyi rnam pa mtha'a yasa
NK094(nge)001:17667: pa yod kyang tha ma bgroda yul kun gyi lam
NK094(nge)001:17668: gyi 'du sa rang gi gansa khang gcig lasa meda
NK094(nge)001:17670: dpe de bzhina du lam pas bslab pa bcu'i gcig
NK094(nge)001:17671: ma gtogs par bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i rnam grangsa
NK094(nge)001:17672: kyi chos sgo theg pa'i rim pa dang lam gyi
NK094(nge)001:17673: bgrod tshul bsam yas pa ji snyed pa rnams kyang
NK094(nge)001:17674: mi shes pa rnams bkri bas thabs kyis don la
NK094(nge)001:17675: drang ba'i tshig tsam du bstan pa yin pas de
NK094(nge)001:17676: dag nges pa'i lam dam pa kun gyi snying po
NK094(nge)001:17679: de ril gyi bsam pa'i yul gyi rtsa ba ni
NK094(nge)001:17680: chos rnams kyi de kho na nyid gsang ba dam
NK094(nge)001:17681: pa'i don du kun kyang gcig par 'dus pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:17682: des na de ni thams cad kyi dngos gzhi bas
NK094(nge)001:17683: de nyid rtogs na bslab pa ril chub pa'i don
NK094(nge)001:17684: to // de'i phyir na dona rnams gcig tu sdud
NK094(nge)001:17685: pa yi bslab para bya ba 'di nyid kun gyi
NK094(nge)001:17686: bslab bya'i snying po dama pa mchog ste /
NK094(nge)001:17687: ngesa par chos nyid kyi ngo bo thig le nyag
NK094(nge)001:17688: gcig sems kyi dkyil 'khor 'od gsal ba lasa gzhan
NK094(nge)001:17690: kun 'dus dama pa'i bslab pa la slob pa gces so //
NK094(nge)001:17691: 'di kho na gces pa ci'i phyir snyam pa la /
NK094(nge)001:17692: bslab pa dam pa 'dira bshad pa ltar rgyal ba'i
NK094(nge)001:17693: dgongs pa ma 'dus pa med pas kun gyi rtsa
NK094(nge)001:17694: ba rang rig pa 'di nyid ma nor bar shes
NK094(nge)001:17695: na / don la mkhas pa'i dam pa de yi
NK094(nge)001:17696: ye shes ni grangs dang tshad kyis gzung ba'i mtha'a
NK094(nge)001:17697: yasa par shes bya'i dkyil 'khor khyab pa yin te
NK094(nge)001:17698: na / / de nyid rnam pa thams cad mkhyen
NK094(nge)001:17699: pa'i ye shes dngos nyid du gyur pa yin pasa
NK094(nge)001:17700: mdo dona 'di nyid gcig tu 'dus para gsungsa pa
NK094(nge)001:17701: kho nar shes par bya ste /
NK094(nge)001:17702: gral gyi tha mar nges pa'ang de'i phyir ro //
NK094(nge)001:17703: bzhi pa zhabs bsdu ba ni /
NK094(nge)001:17706: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:17708: bslab pa bcu po ji ltar bshad pa'i ngo ti
NK094(nge)001:17709: bstan pa de daga ni sku lnga'i de bzhina gshegsa
NK094(nge)001:17710: pa thamsa cad kyi dgongas pa chos nyid de kho
NK094(nge)001:17711: na nyid gcig tu 'dus para phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i
NK094(nge)001:17712: de bzhina gashegs pa thamsa cad 'dus nasa nges pa
NK094(nge)001:17714: chos thamsa cad kyi mdo don sems kyi de kho
NK094(nge)001:17715: na nyid gcig tu 'dus par bshad pa de kho
NK094(nge)001:17717: skyes bu chen pos de skad ces smras te bslab
NK094(nge)001:17718: pa bcu'i ngo ti bgros shing bka' stsal pasa damna
NK094(nge)001:17719: pa dama pa rig 'dzin mi yi thod pa can
NK094(nge)001:17720: la sogs pas chos rnams ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs
NK094(nge)001:17721: pa'i don gcig tu ngesa para dam pa'i gdengs chen
NK094(nge)001:17722: po mthar thug pa nyid rnyed para gyur to //
NK094(nge)001:17723: zhes bgros pa'i yon tan bstan pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:17724: de la kun mkhyen dam pa rin po che'i zhal nas /
NK094(nge)001:17725: 'o na lta bas thag bcad par bslab pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:17726: don man ngag gis sgrub par bslab pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:17727: mdo don gcig tu 'du bar bslab pa gsum la khyad ci yod ce na /
NK094(nge)001:17728: thag lta bas bcad pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:17729: shes bya dngos po'i gnas lugs ji lta ba bzhin rtogs pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:17730: don man ngag gis sgrub pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:17731: spyod lam thams cad lta ba'i rtsis zin pas mtshan ma rang kha mar mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:17732: mdo don gcig tu bsdu ba ni /
NK094(nge)001:17733: chos thams cad kyi rtsa ba rang gi sems nyid du 'dus pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:17734: zhes bka' stsal bar mdzad do //
NK094(nge)001:17735: e ma lung mchog dpal ldan 'dus pa mdo'i //
NK094(nge)001:17736: bslab pa'i mtha' bcu nges pa'i chings chen 'di //
NK094(nge)001:17737: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i bslab bya'i yang snying ste //
NK094(nge)001:17738: theg mchog rgyal por 'jug pa'i gsang sgo yin //
NK094(nge)001:17739: de phyir 'di na phyi ma'i phyi ma yi //
NK094(nge)001:17740: bka' yi nges gsang bshad pa'i rgyud chen gyi //
NK094(nge)001:17741: dgongs don 'khrul med brgyud pa'i bka' srol bzhin //
NK094(nge)001:17742: man ngag tshad mar bsten nas gsal bar bshad //
NK094(nge)001:17743: ri bong 'dzin pas mtshan mo'i mun cha bsal //
NK094(nge)001:17744: rta bdun dbang pos gling bzhi rim snang byas //
NK094(nge)001:17745: lung rigs tshad mas don gyi mjug sdud bkral //
NK094(nge)001:17746: nges gsang 'dzin pa rnams la dgyes mchod 'bul //
NK094(nge)001:17748: gsum pa mjug gi don la gnyis te /
NK094(nge)001:17750: yongs su rdzogs pa'i bya ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:17753: mdzad pa chos nyid du grol zhing byin rlabs lha mi la grags pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:17761: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:17762: de nas ston pa gsang chen bka'i sdud pa po
NK094(nge)001:17763: 'chad pa'i skyes bu gasnga ba pa'i badga po chen
NK094(nge)001:17765: 'khor damna pa dama pa rigs can gyi byang chub
NK094(nge)001:17766: sems dpa' chen po de rnams gsang don rmad du
NK094(nge)001:17767: byung ba'i mdo chen po bka' stsal ba la dga'
NK094(nge)001:17768: ba'i sems kyis yida shin tu rangas te /
NK094(nge)001:17769: drin lan gyi tshul du sku lnga dang ldan pa'i
NK094(nge)001:17770: yon tan gyi sgo nas gus pa chen pos mngona
NK094(nge)001:17773: ston pa sku lnga'i bdag nyid du bstod pa /
NK094(nge)001:17774: bstan pa che ba bdun dang ldan par bstod pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:17779: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:17781: zhes shin tu ngo mtshar ba'i tshig gis dbu drangs te /
NK094(nge)001:17782: dus gsum kun tu gsang sngags kyi mnga' bdag tu
NK094(nge)001:17783: gyur pa mthu rtsal khyad par du 'phags par gyur
NK094(nge)001:17784: pas ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba'i ston pa 'chad
NK094(nge)001:17785: pa'i skyes bu chen po'i sku gasnga ba'i theg pa
NK094(nge)001:17786: sngags kyi mchog gi badga po chen po khyod nyid
NK094(nge)001:17787: yin no // zhes sku'i sgo nas bstod pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:17788: shes rab kyi rtsal 'bar chen po khyad par can
NK094(nge)001:17789: gyis gsang sngags gsang ba dam pa smra zhing ston
NK094(nge)001:17790: pa'ang dper na gangs kyi seng ge'i sgra yi nga
NK094(nge)001:17791: ro ltar zil gyis gnon pa'i gsung mchog rab tu
NK094(nge)001:17793: zhes gsung gi sgo nas bstod pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:17794: khyod ni gsang sngags zab mo ma 'dres yongs su
NK094(nge)001:17795: rdzogs pa'i de kho na nyid kyi ngo bor gyur
NK094(nge)001:17796: pas rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas de bzhina gshegsa
NK094(nge)001:17797: pa ma lus pa kun gyi thugsa kyi bdag nyid
NK094(nge)001:17799: zhes thugs kyi sgo nas bstod pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:17800: khyod ni gsang ba ji bzhin pa'i ngo bo rgyal
NK094(nge)001:17801: ba rdzogs pa'i sangsa rgyas kun bas sngon rol du
NK094(nge)001:17802: ye nasa ngo bo nyid skur byung ba'i yon tan
NK094(nge)001:17803: lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i rgyal ba ril gyi ston pa
NK094(nge)001:17804: yin pas / khyod nyid ni chos kyi sku ru
NK094(nge)001:17805: mngon par byang chub pa'i sangsa rgyas kun gyi mesa
NK094(nge)001:17807: zhes yon tan gyi sgo nas bstod pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:17808: zla dang bral bas gnyen po med pa'i bdag nyid
NK094(nge)001:17809: can gyi dpal ldan longs spyood rdzogs pa'i skyes bu
NK094(nge)001:17810: dam pa nyid du nges pas mthu stobs kyi khyad
NK094(nge)001:17811: par che ba'i mchog tu gyur pas rgyal po dang
NK094(nge)001:17812: 'dra ba'i rje btsun dama pa'i sku mchog phul du
NK094(nge)001:17813: byung ba'ang khyod nyid yin no //
NK094(nge)001:17814: zhes phrin las kyi sgo nas bstod pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:17815: sprul pa'i sku'i bkod pa thun mong dang khyad par
NK094(nge)001:17816: du ston pa'i dus gsum gyi bdera gshegsa rnam par
NK094(nge)001:17817: 'dren pa'i rgyal ba kun gyi yang dag pa'i bshesa
NK094(nge)001:17818: gnyen gsang sngags dam pa 'chad pa'i mnga' bdag 'gro
NK094(nge)001:17819: ba 'dul ba'i thabs mchog dpag tu med pa'i sprin
NK094(nge)001:17820: dpung gi bdag nyid kyang ston pa dam pa khyod
NK094(nge)001:17821: nyid do // zhes mkhyen pa'i sgo nas bstod pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:17822: gsang ba'i mnga' bdag semas dapa'a chen po'i cha lugs
NK094(nge)001:17823: su zhugs pa khyod ni dus gsum gyi rgyal ba
NK094(nge)001:17824: thams cad gcig du ma dang bral ba'i tshul gyis
NK094(nge)001:17825: rdzogs pas sangsa rgyas kun gyi dngosa gzhi sku lnga
NK094(nge)001:17826: dang mi phyed pa'i bdag nyid kyang ston mchog dam
NK094(nge)001:17827: pa khyod do // zhes ngo bo'i sgo nas bstod pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:17828: de lta bu'i ngo bo mngon du byed pa'i thabs
NK094(nge)001:17829: kyi gar mkhan chen po lags pas gsang ba'i sku
NK094(nge)001:17835: zhes pa'i bar gyi bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:17836: rtogs pa'i rgyud 'di la 'khor gyis bstod pa ni gang zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:17837: shin tu gsang ba'i bka' dam pa theg pa chen po thun mong ma yin ba'i rgyud 'di ni /
NK094(nge)001:17839: chos thams cad kyi me longa rab tu gasla ba /
NK094(nge)001:17840: bka'i phyogsa kun gasla bar byed pas lung gi spyi 'grel /
NK094(nge)001:17841: gsang ba chen po'i don ji bzhin par ngesa pa'i
NK094(nge)001:17842: mdo yin pas don gyi mjug sdud chen po yin
NK094(nge)001:17843: no bar bstod pa ste bshad pa bzhin no //
NK094(nge)001:17844: de lta bu'i thega pa chen po'i rgyud kyi rgyal
NK094(nge)001:17845: po bla med rmad du byung ba'i theg pa'i yang
NK094(nge)001:17846: rtse 'di nyid bdag cag dang lha mi'i yul du
NK094(nge)001:17847: gragsa pa ngo mtshar mchog tu che ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:17848: des na man ngag thams cad kyi rtsa ba gasnga
NK094(nge)001:17849: ba chena po zab cing rgya che ba 'di nyid
NK094(nge)001:17850: byung tshul bcu gnyis kyi dus su dus thams cad
NK094(nge)001:17851: du 'byung ba de ni ngo mtshar rab tu che'o
NK094(nge)001:17853: a ho zhes pa gnyis med kyi don mchog ston pa'i rgyud thos pas dga' ba ste /
NK094(nge)001:17854: ngesa pa don gyi rgyud kyi nang na yang mchog
NK094(nge)001:17855: dang dam pa yin no bar mngona para bstod pa
NK094(nge)001:17856: ched du brjod pa nyid do //
NK094(nge)001:17861: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:17862: de nasa spros mtha' cang mi damigs para chos nyid kyi ngang du gyur te /
NK094(nge)001:17863: 'khor rnams kyis chos kyi sku chen po mngon du byas pa'i phyir ro //
NK094(nge)001:17864: lung bstan brgyud pa'i gleng gzhi'i dbang gis gnas kyi dngos po ri ma la ya'i rtse gang du /
NK094(nge)001:17865: gsang bdag skyes bus gsang ba dam pa lang ka'i
NK094(nge)001:17866: mnga' bdag la sogs pa la ngesa par bgros te
NK094(nge)001:17867: bka' stsal pa'i gasnga ba'i gsang ba dam pa 'di
NK094(nge)001:17868: daga /byin gyis brlabs pa'i rtsal gyis lha dang mi'i
NK094(nge)001:17869: 'jiga rten gyi khams rnams kun tu rgya cher khyab
NK094(nge)001:17870: par gragsa shing / shin tu'ang de la mos te
NK094(nge)001:17871: spyod par dga' bas dam par byed pa'i phyir yongsa
NK094(nge)001:17872: su gragsa para gyur pa ste /
NK094(nge)001:17873: de ltar grags pa la dam pa'i rigs can lnga dang /
NK094(nge)001:17874: dman pa'i lus can so sos bzung nas mi nub
NK094(nge)001:17875: par byed pa'i phyir ched du gtad pa ma smos
NK094(nge)001:17876: pa'i don to // le'u'i mtshan ni /
NK094(nge)001:17877: sangsa rgyas kun gyi dgongas pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po lasa /
NK094(nge)001:17878: rdzogs pa'i sangsa rgyas kun gyi dgongas pa sems kyi
NK094(nge)001:17879: de kho na nyid gcig tu 'adus par bstan pa'i
NK094(nge)001:17880: le'u zhes bya ste bdun cu rtsa lnga pa nyid
NK094(nge)001:17881: gsal bar 'grel te dgongs don ji lta ba bzhin
NK094(nge)001:17882: du legs par bshad pa'o ////tshul de dag gi sgo
NK094(nge)001:17883: nas theg pa chen po nges par 'byung ba'i tshul
NK094(nge)001:17884: las / ston pa phyag na rdo rjes rgyal ba
NK094(nge)001:17885: sku lnga po gang gi dgongsa pa 'khor dam pa'i
NK094(nge)001:17886: rigs can lnga la rnam par bgros pa na yang
NK094(nge)001:17887: ma la ya'i rtser 'byung ba'i gtam rgyud brjod pa'i
NK094(nge)001:17888: tshul gyis brjod bya chos nyid don gyi phyag rgya'i
NK094(nge)001:17889: ye shesa ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su rjod byed dgongs
NK094(nge)001:17890: pa 'dus pa'i gsang ba chen po'i thabs kyi lung
NK094(nge)001:17891: gis dus ston mchog thub pa'i dbang po 'das nas
NK094(nge)001:17892: lo nyer brgyad du gyur pa na legs par rnam
NK094(nge)001:17893: para bgros te gsal ba bstan pa ste /
NK094(nge)001:17894: byung tshul bstan pa bcu gnyis pa'i tha ma nyid yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:17895: 'o na khyod kyis rtsa bshad du 'joga tshul 'di ltar na /
NK094(nge)001:17896: kun 'dus kyang rtsa rgyud du byed pa ni 'gal bar 'gyur te /
NK094(nge)001:17897: der byung tshul bcu gnyis ma bstan pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK094(nge)001:17898: gtan ma bstan pa yang min te /
NK094(nge)001:17900: gzhan gyi don du 'byung zhing 'gro ba'i tshul dang mthun pa'i phyir gnas su bskyod pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:17910: tsham ngam chen po sprul pa mdzad pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:17911: yongs su dag pa'i phyir 'byung tshul chen po zhes bya'o //
NK094(nge)001:17916: don mdzad tshul bcu gcig rnams su bshad pa'i phyir ro //
NK094(nge)001:17917: de'ang gnas su bskyod pa ni lhums su zhugs pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:17918: rmongs pa gdung ba sel ba'i byung tshul dang /
NK094(nge)001:17922: sgron ma bkod pa'i byung tshul dang /
NK094(nge)001:17923: phyogs ris med par don mdzad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:17926: nges ba rnyed pa'i byung tshul dang /
NK094(nge)001:17927: sku gsung thugs kyi mdzad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:17929: gzhon nu'i rol rtsed mdzad pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:17930: snying po byang chub tu nges pa'i byung tshul dang /
NK094(nge)001:17931: gdul bya dga' ba'i mdzad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:17934: dgongs pa nges par 'grel ba'i byung tshul dang /
NK094(nge)001:17938: gdul bya skabs la bab pa'i byung tshul dang /
NK094(nge)001:17939: sku'i ngo bo gang du'ang ma nges pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:17942: byin gyis brlabs kyi byung tshul dang /
NK094(nge)001:17945: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang /
NK094(nge)001:17946: brgyud pa thabs kyi grags pa'i byung tshul dang /
NK094(nge)001:17950: lung chen nges par bstan pa'i byung tshul dang /
NK094(nge)001:17954: gang gi ched du mdzad pa'i byung tshul lo //
NK094(nge)001:17955: tsham ngam chen po sprul pa mdzad pa ni /
NK094(nge)001:17957: las rgyud yongs su gcod pa'i byung tshul dang /
NK094(nge)001:17958: snga ma dang 'di gnyis sprul pa 'gyed pa'i mdzad pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:17961: dgongs pa rnam par bgro ba'i byung tshul dang /
NK094(nge)001:17962: zhing dang spyod yul kun tu don mdzad pa rnams
NK094(nge)001:17963: su mkhas grub snga ma dag la yongs su grags
NK094(nge)001:17964: pa'i phyir ro // de ltar ma 'dres yongs su
NK094(nge)001:17965: rdzogs pa'i rtsa ba dang bshad pa'i rgyud kyi zab
NK094(nge)001:17966: cing rgya che ba'i tshul gyi nges gsang bla na
NK094(nge)001:17967: med pa la blo gros kyi mkhyen rtsal mchog tu
NK094(nge)001:17968: yangs shing rgyas par byas te rgyal ba kun gyi
NK094(nge)001:17969: dgongs pa'i gnad kun 'dus pa'i bka'i gsang mdzod rmad
NK094(nge)001:17970: du byung ba la mi 'phrogs pa'i nges pa chen
NK094(nge)001:17971: pos gzhan dring mi 'jog par yang dag par 'jug
NK094(nge)001:17972: pa'i phyir ro // par bya'o // gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK094(nge)001:17973: rnam 'dren bzhi pa'i lung bstan brgyud pa'i bstan pa
NK094(nge)001:17974: rin po che ji ltar bgros pa'i mdzad byang bstan
NK094(nge)001:17975: pa / mdo chen po nyid lo pan gang gi
NK094(nge)001:17976: bka' drin gyis 'phags yul dang bru sha'i yul nas
NK094(nge)001:17977: bod yul du ji ltar zhus te gtan la phab
NK094(nge)001:17980: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa /
NK094(nge)001:17982: yongs su bgros pa rdzogs soha&a&a&a //
NK094(nge)001:17983: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:17984: sangsa rgyas kun gyi dgongsa pa 'dus pa'i mdo /
NK094(nge)001:17985: zhes pa le'u tha ma'i don nyid kyis 'grel to //
NK094(nge)001:17986: theg pa chen po'i mngona para rtogsa pa /
NK094(nge)001:17988: gsang chen theg mchog dam pa sgro skur med par ma tshon par byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK094(nge)001:17989: chos thams cad kyi me long /
NK094(nge)001:17990: zhes pa log pa'i lam dang yang dag pa'i lam kun gsal bar ston pa'i phyir ro //
NK094(nge)001:17992: zhes pa bka' ril gyi don kun 'dis ma 'dres
NK094(nge)001:17993: yongs rdzogs kyi gsang ba chen por gtan la 'bebs
NK094(nge)001:17994: pa'i phyir ro // de bzhin gshegsa pa kun gyi dgongsa pa dam pa gsang ba /
NK094(nge)001:17995: zhes pa gsang sngags mthar thug pa de blos reg cing bstan pa dang brtag par dka' ba'o //
NK094(nge)001:17996: ston pa bcom ldana 'adsa gasnga ba'i badga po phyag na rdo rjes /
NK094(nge)001:17997: gnas drag shul can gyi ri gnod sbyin 'du zhing srin po'i 'khra sa ma la ya'i rtser /
NK094(nge)001:17998: sdud pa po langa ka'i mnga' badga chen po la
NK094(nge)001:17999: sogas pa 'khor damna pa'i lus can gyi byang chub
NK094(nge)001:18000: semas dapa'a sems dpa' chen po rnams la bstan pa'i
NK094(nge)001:18001: gsang ba chen po rgya cher yongsa su bgros te
NK094(nge)001:18002: bka' stsal pa nyid kyi don ni mdo rgyud chen
NK094(nge)001:18003: po chos kyi me long 'di nyid yin no //
NK094(nge)001:18004: de lta bu'i gsang ba mchog gi theg pa'i rgyal
NK094(nge)001:18005: po nyid lhag ma med par yongs su rdzogsa so&a&a&aha
NK094(nge)001:18006: // zhes ma tshang ba med par bshad cing gtan la dbab zin pa'i don to //
NK094(nge)001:18010: zhus te gtan la phab pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:18011: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK094(nge)001:18012: dang po rgya gara gyi makhana po chen po pan+di ta d+harma bo d+hi dang /
NK094(nge)001:18013: bod kyi lo ts+aa ba dam pa che btsan skyes
NK094(nge)001:18014: kyis rgya gar las bru sha'i skad du bsgyur la
NK094(nge)001:18015: / de nas ring lugsa pa chen po pan+di ta d+ha na rak+shi ta dang /
NK094(nge)001:18016: zhu chen gyi lo ts+aa ba dam pa che btsan skyes kyis /
NK094(nge)001:18017: bru sha'i yi ge lasa bru sha'i yula gyi khrom du /
NK094(nge)001:18018: bod kyi yi ger bsgyur zhing zhus te gtan la phaba pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:18019: bka'a 'di la dbu zhabsa su rtsa ba byung tshul bcu gnyis dang /
NK094(nge)001:18020: le'u bdun cu rtsa lnga pa /
NK094(nge)001:18022: sho lo ka gnyis bargya lnga bcu rtsa gnyis so //
NK094(nge)001:18023: 'dir kun mkhyen dam pa rin po che'i phyag mchan gyi mjug tu /
NK094(nge)001:18024: mda' glan yang khyed dam pa'i rje gsum gyi /
NK094(nge)001:18025: phyag dpe 'grel chen kun don la //
NK094(nge)001:18026: lha rje zur gyis nan chags byas //
NK094(nge)001:18027: gong bu ba dag shangs pa la //
NK094(nge)001:18028: phyis ni yang dag zhus pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:18029: rjes su lha rje rnam gnyis la //
NK094(nge)001:18030: bde gshegs kyis zhus dam pa la //
NK094(nge)001:18031: ldom po bdag gis zhus pa'o //
NK094(nge)001:18033: gsang bdag chen po sgro phug pas sngon du mda'
NK094(nge)001:18034: glan yang khyed gsum la gsan pa nan chags su
NK094(nge)001:18035: byas pa ni gtso bor 'grel chen mun pa'i go
NK094(nge)001:18037: phyis su gong bu ba dang shangs pa las gsan
NK094(nge)001:18038: pa ni gtso bor lung bstan skor gyi lugs yin
NK094(nge)001:18039: no // de rjes lha rje smar dang gtsang pa
NK094(nge)001:18040: rnam gnyis la kun mkhyen dam pa bde gshegs kyis
NK094(nge)001:18041: no // zhus shing / chos rje dam pa rin
NK094(nge)001:18042: po che la gtsang ston rdo rje rgyal mtshan gyis
NK094(nge)001:18044: skyabs rje rgyal tshab rin po che'i zhal nas /
NK094(nge)001:18045: sngon smon thugs bskyed skya rengs kha lo yis //
NK094(nge)001:18046: nyer drangs nges gsang bstan mchog mkha' dbyings su //
NK094(nge)001:18047: legs bshad 'dod rgu'i snang ba 'bum 'jo bas //
NK094(nge)001:18048: chos kyi rgya mtsho nyin mor byed gang rgyal //
NK094(nge)001:18049: zhes basngagasa pa ltar pan chen si tu rin po
NK094(nge)001:18050: ches dwags lha sgam po'i phyag dpe mchan can gdan
NK094(nge)001:18052: lha rje sgro phug pa mda' tsha hor po'i mchan
NK094(nge)001:18053: 'bring po la mda' glan yang khyed gsum gyi gsung
NK094(nge)001:18054: sgros kyis zhabs tog bag tsam byas te /
NK094(nge)001:18055: gru gu'i ban+de dbus pa jo 'bum gyis bltas pas chog par nan tan bgyis pa lags so //
NK094(nge)001:18056: 'gro don du gyur cig /ces gsungs so //
NK094(nge)001:18057: yang dpe rnying mchan ma gcig gdan drangs pa'i mjug tu /
NK094(nge)001:18058: mdo chen po'i 'grel pa'i bye brag bzhi las mkhas
NK094(nge)001:18059: pa chen po s+thi ra ma ti'i lugs ltar 'gar
NK094(nge)001:18060: ston bzang po las rong zom pan+di tas gsan zhing
NK094(nge)001:18061: de las ru yong rin chen 'bar gyis zhus pa
NK094(nge)001:18062: la bdag 'dra 'brom ston 'theng pos zhus te phyag
NK094(nge)001:18063: dpe mchan bcas gsar du bzhengs par gsungs so //
NK094(nge)001:18064: de la sogs pa phyag dpe rnying pa mchan can bzhi ste mchan 'grel lnga dang /
NK094(nge)001:18065: gtsang dang 'jang yul nas mdo 'grel mun pa'i go cha spyan drangs pa dang /
NK094(nge)001:18066: gzhan yang kun mkhyen dam pa rin po che'i mdo yi khog dbub bka' 'grel /
NK094(nge)001:18067: sku bzhi'i gleng 'grel dang bsdus don rnams spyan drangs pa las /
NK094(nge)001:18068: bdag gis bka' 'grel mun pa'i go cha dang phyag mchan rnams kyis gzhi byas /
NK094(nge)001:18069: chos rje'i bsdus don ltar dka' 'grel yang skabs su
NK094(nge)001:18070: legs par sbyar nas tshad ma'i lung gis brgyan te
NK094(nge)001:18071: rang bzo med par yid ches nges pa'i gdeng dang
NK094(nge)001:18072: ldan par bris pa kho na yin no //
NK094(nge)001:18074: rnam 'dren sh+aakya'i tog dang gsang ba'i bdag po rdo rje 'dzin pa'i rgyal //
NK094(nge)001:18075: yang sprul dpa' bo dga' rab rdo rje theg mchog bstan pa'i shing rta che //
NK094(nge)001:18076: mkhyen gter thugs rje'i dbang phyug dam pa rigs bdag
NK094(nge)001:18077: bstan 'gro'i dpal mgon mchog /bka' drin gzhal med skyabs
NK094(nge)001:18078: gnas gang la mi phyed dad pas slar btud te
NK094(nge)001:18079: // sku bzhi'i khyab bdag lhun rdzogs dag pa'i ngo bo ye shes sgyu 'phrul spro ba'i dpyid //
NK094(nge)001:18080: chos nyid dbyings su gcig dang tha dad med bzhin mdzad pa'i rol mo 'byams klas par //
NK094(nge)001:18081: kun nas 'gyed pa'i mngon rdzogs rig pa'i ston pa rmad byung che ba'i snying po can //
NK094(nge)001:18082: gzhi rtsa kun grol rang byung don gyi 'dren pa ngang gi thig ler ches bkra ba'i //
NK094(nge)001:18083: phyogs dus rgyal ba'i ye shes bdag nyid mnga' dbang yongs rdzogs mgon po des //
NK094(nge)001:18084: chos dbyings rab 'byams zhing rnams kun tu sgron ma bkod pa'i dkyil 'khor na //
NK094(nge)001:18085: rgyal tshab skyes bu'i rnam 'phrul du mas rgyun dang gnas skabs bcu gnyis su //
NK094(nge)001:18086: gsang sngags kun gyi de nyid bgrod nas gtan la nges par dbab pa'i tshul //
NK094(nge)001:18087: sku bzhi'i ston pa gdul bya'i snod bzhir mtshon pa'i tshig bzhis bstan pa gang //
NK094(nge)001:18088: rgyud kyi rgyal po lung gi spyi 'grel man ngag
NK094(nge)001:18089: kun gyi rtsa ba mchog /bstan pa'i 'byung gnas chos
NK094(nge)001:18090: kyi me long don gyi mjug sdud theg pa'i rtse
NK094(nge)001:18091: // che ba bdun ldan sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po //
NK094(nge)001:18092: rig 'dzin klu dbang 'bum gyi gtsug rgyan snyan rgyud dam pa'i ded dpon gyis //
NK094(nge)001:18093: nyer blangs skal ldan dbul ba sel slad gsang ba'i mdzod du rgyas btab pa //
NK094(nge)001:18094: rnam par 'byed pa'i blo gros lde'u mig rdo rje rnon pos byin pa las //
NK094(nge)001:18095: sangs rgyas ye shes nyin byed shar bas gangs can
NK094(nge)001:18096: mun pa'i go skabs 'phrog /dpal mchog de dang dpal
NK094(nge)001:18097: gzhan gyis brgyan brtan pa'i 'khor lo zur phud can
NK094(nge)001:18098: // kun mkhyen bla ma shes rab seng ges phul byung bka' yi sgrom chen pos //
NK094(nge)001:18099: legs par bshad pa'i sgo mang phyes te bod chen ljongs kyi 'dzin ma'i gzhir //
NK094(nge)001:18100: 'chad nyan sprin gyi snang bas khyab cing kun nas yongs su rgyas par byas //
NK094(nge)001:18101: 'on kyang dus mtha'i rlung shugs bdo bas chu lha'i 'phang par spyan drangs shing //
NK094(nge)001:18102: bshad sgrub 'od snang yongs su bsdus nas ring zhig lon pa de lta na'ang //
NK094(nge)001:18103: chos kyi rgya mtsho bsrub pa'i thugs bskyed ri ltar brtan pa'i phrin las kyis //
NK094(nge)001:18104: slar yang 'grel chen pad+mo'i gnyen 'di las 'phro'i mkha' la gsal bar gyur //
NK094(nge)001:18105: de tshe mtshungs med dam pa'i mgon rnams kyis //
NK094(nge)001:18106: 'di don 'grel pas gsal bar gyis shig ces //
NK094(nge)001:18107: bka' lung kun gsal nor bu'i 'od kyi zer //
NK094(nge)001:18108: bdag blo dad pa'i ge sar la phog pas //
NK094(nge)001:18109: theg mchog rgyal po lung chen gsang ba'i khang bzang
NK094(nge)001:18110: ya ngas par rigs ldan blo yi smin legs ma
NK094(nge)001:18111: // lung dang brgyud pa'i gsung sgros mang pos rgyan
NK094(nge)001:18112: gyis nyer spras lhag bsam zur mig g.yo bzhin du
NK094(nge)001:18113: // // dkyil 'khor rnam gsum ma 'dres rdzogs pas
NK094(nge)001:18114: rigs pa'i rgyud mang rnam dpyod sor mos bsnun nas
NK094(nge)001:18115: // // kyang // dpal ldan mdo yi rnam bshad
NK094(nge)001:18116: gsal bar mgrin pa'i glu dbyangs snyan pa 'di ko
NK094(nge)001:18117: // // kyang // deng 'dir spel // tshul 'di mdo sngags bstan pa'i yang bcud de //
NK094(nge)001:18118: legs par rtogs na rtsol bcas theg pa'i tog /lung chen gsang ba'i dgongs pa mthar thug ste //
NK094(nge)001:18119: blo gros nam mkha'i mtha' ltar dpag par dka' //de phyir don 'dir ma 'dres yongs rdzogs pa'i //
NK094(nge)001:18120: nges pa rnyed tshe mchog tu gsang ba yi //
NK094(nge)001:18121: 'od gsal rdo rje snying po'i sgor zhugs te //
NK094(nge)001:18122: zab mo'i dgongs par tshad ma'i mig sgrubs mdzod //
NK094(nge)001:18123: blo gsal blo yi blo gros rgyas pa na //
NK094(nge)001:18124: chos dang chos mchog chos kyi bcud la dbang //
NK094(nge)001:18125: de bas de bzhin de gnad nges rnams kyis //
NK094(nge)001:18126: legs gsung legs bshad legs rgu'i mdzod 'di longs //
NK094(nge)001:18127: 'di la rang bzo'i dri ma ma mchis te //
NK094(nge)001:18128: rgyal ba'i spyod yul dpags daka'i gnas yin phyir //
NK094(nge)001:18129: byis pa'i blo can bdag 'dras smos ci tshal //
NK094(nge)001:18130: des na nongs par gyur gang mthol zhing 'chags //
NK094(nge)001:18131: gsang chen rgyud lung rgya mtsho'i yang snying dgongs pa kun 'dus yid bzhin nor //
NK094(nge)001:18132: zab mo'i lung gi snang ba la brten dngos stobs rigs pa'i 'phrul thabs kyis //
NK094(nge)001:18133: legs par drangs nas ma 'dres gsal ba'i rgyal mtshan rtse mor yongs mchod 'dis //
NK094(nge)001:18134: blo ldan yod na zab don 'dod rgu'i gru char 'bebs shing snyoms par 'gyed //
NK094(nge)001:18135: legs byas dge ba ston ka'i zla 'dra dri med des //
NK094(nge)001:18136: mkha' khyab 'gro kun lam mchog snang bas yongs grol nas //
NK094(nge)001:18137: 'bad rtsol med par rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i sar smin te //
NK094(nge)001:18138: sgrol byed rgyal po thugs rje'i mchog gi gnas thob
NK094(nge)001:18139: shog /khyad par du yang zab gsang chos kyi bcud
NK094(nge)001:18140: mchog 'dir // legs par zhugs nas thos bsam sgom gsum la brten te //
NK094(nge)001:18141: 'chad rtsom nyan pa'i rnam thar bzang por nges gyur kun //
NK094(nge)001:18142: 'gal rkyen med par legs tshogs mtha' dag 'phel gyur
NK094(nge)001:18143: cig /bdag kyang deng nas rdzogs pa spyir chibs kun
NK094(nge)001:18144: 'dus shing dgongs klong dag pa'i mkha' dbyings la //
NK094(nge)001:18145: rang dbang bsgyur te gang la gang 'dul thabs sprin rol pas zab rgya'i chos tshul thams cad la //
NK094(nge)001:18146: rmongs pa med par bstan pa'i yang snying mdo sgyu sems gsum 'od gsal snying po'i theg mchog bcas //
NK094(nge)001:18147: kun nas kun tu gsal bar 'grel zhing rab 'byams
NK094(nge)001:18148: zhing du yongs su 'gro ba'i dpal thob shog /gdod
NK094(nge)001:18149: nas rnam dag rgyal ba'i ye shes 'dus ma byas
NK094(nge)001:18151: 'gro ba'i rang bzhin sems kyi dkyil 'khor ngo bo nyid kyi 'od gsal ba //
NK094(nge)001:18152: gnyis su ma dmigs dbye ba byar med so so ma yin 'dus ma yin //
NK094(nge)001:18153: bden pa des kyang ye sangs rgyas pa'i gnas lugs rtogs pa'i shis pa stsol //
NK094(nge)001:18154: rgyud kyi ston pa sku lnga'i rgyal ba rgyal tshab
NK094(nge)001:18155: 'chad pa'i skyes bu'i bka' //gsang chen lung gi bstan
NK094(nge)001:18156: pa'i mdzod khang khyad par bdun ldan 'dus pa mdo
NK094(nge)001:18157: // gang gi dgongs don ji bzhin rtogs nas gsal mdzad dam pa'i rigs can sogs //
NK094(nge)001:18158: mchog gsum rin chen 'od kyi snang bas dge legs rgyas pa'i bkra shis stsol //
NK094(nge)001:18159: nyin mor bkra shis mtshan yang bkra shis nyin mtshan kun tu dge legs kyi //
NK094(nge)001:18160: bkra shis 'phel bas dus rnams rtag tu mchog gnas dam pa'i dpal gsum gyis //
NK094(nge)001:18161: bkra shing bzang pos phyogs kun yongs khyab theg chen lung don rab gsal te //
NK094(nge)001:18162: zab mo gsang ba'i chos mdzod rgyas nas mi nub
NK094(nge)001:18163: 'phel ba'i bkra shis shog /ces dpal gyi mdo dgongs
NK094(nge)001:18164: pa 'dus pa'i 'grel pa rnal 'byor nyi ma gsal
NK094(nge)001:18165: bar byed pa'i gzi ldan 'char kha'i 'od snang rig
NK094(nge)001:18166: 'dzin brgyud pa'i zhal lung zhes bya ba 'di nyid
NK094(nge)001:18167: / skyabs rje 'khor lo'i mgon po bka' drin mtshungs
NK094(nge)001:18168: med thub bstan dul ba'i sde rdo rje legs bshad
NK094(nge)001:18169: rtsal gyis snga mo zhig nas bka' stsal spyi bor
NK094(nge)001:18170: / son pa bzhin / rjes su mchog sprul phyag
NK094(nge)001:18171: tsha rin po che nas cha rkyen sbyar ba'i zhal
NK094(nge)001:18172: bzhes dang bcas pas bskul tshe mkhan chen rin po
NK094(nge)001:18173: che'i zhal nas slar yang nges par bri dgos zhes
NK094(nge)001:18174: / son pa bzhin / phebs pa ltar / rigs
NK094(nge)001:18175: bdag 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse rin po che chos kyi
NK094(nge)001:18176: / son pa bzhin / phebs pa ltar / blo
NK094(nge)001:18177: gros dang / 'jam mgon kong sprul rin po che
NK094(nge)001:18178: gzhan phan bzang po rnams kyi'ang gya nom pa'i skyes
NK094(nge)001:18179: dang bcas te bskul ba'i bka' lung gtsug gi rgyan
NK094(nge)001:18180: / son pa bzhin / phebs pa ltar / blo
NK094(nge)001:18181: gros dang / du bcing zhing / grub dbang thams
NK094(nge)001:18182: cad mkhyen pa'i zhal nas kyang bka'i gnang ba dngos
NK094(nge)001:18183: su thob pas shin tu bri 'dun yid la bcag
NK094(nge)001:18184: / son pa bzhin / phebs pa ltar / blo
NK094(nge)001:18185: gros dang / du bcing zhing / kyang / bar
NK094(nge)001:18186: skabs su mthun rkyen dkon par mthong nas 'jog par
NK094(nge)001:18187: / son pa bzhin / phebs pa ltar / blo
NK094(nge)001:18188: gros dang / du bcing zhing / kyang / sems
NK094(nge)001:18189: pa'i tshe / skyabs rje si tu rin po che'i
NK094(nge)001:18190: yang srid byams chen chos kyi nyi ma dpal bzang
NK094(nge)001:18191: po gang gi mkhyen pa'i thugs kyi rjes su dgongs
NK094(nge)001:18192: te mthun rkyen gnang ba'i zhal bzhes dang chab gcig
NK094(nge)001:18193: bri gzhi'i shog bu ldeb bdun cu'i nang tsam dang
NK094(nge)001:18194: bcas par bka' yis bskul ba nan zab slar gnang
NK094(nge)001:18195: / son pa bzhin / phebs pa ltar / blo
NK094(nge)001:18196: gros dang / du bcing zhing / kyang / sems
NK094(nge)001:18197: pa'i tshe / mdzad pa bzhin / dpal yul grub
NK094(nge)001:18198: dbang pad+ma nor bu'i yang srid 'jigs med thub bstan
NK094(nge)001:18199: bshad sgrub chos kyi sgra dbyangs dang /
NK094(nge)001:18200: sku chen rin po che rig pa 'dzin pa dpal chen che mchog drag po rtsal /
NK094(nge)001:18201: skyabs rje 'brug pa rin po che'i rigs sras dam
NK094(nge)001:18202: pa 'gyur med rdo rje rnams kyis dngos rdzas dang
NK094(nge)001:18203: bcas te bka'i gnang bskul stsal zhing /
NK094(nge)001:18204: mchog sprul blo gros bshad sgrub nyi ma dang /
NK094(nge)001:18205: mkhan sprul byang chub rdo rje zung nas dngos po'i
NK094(nge)001:18206: skyes dang bcas pas bskul ba nan tan mdzad pa
NK094(nge)001:18207: dang / chos kyi mched po mkhan chen pad+ma rab rgyas dang /
NK094(nge)001:18209: byang reb kong nas a lags rdzong sngon gyi sprul
NK094(nge)001:18210: sku kun mkhyen ngag dbang blo bzang sogs dam pa
NK094(nge)001:18211: du mas yang yang bskul ba la brten nas /
NK094(nge)001:18212: skyabs mchog pan grub rnam gnyis kyi zhabs rdul la
NK094(nge)001:18213: spyi bos reg pa'i btsun gzugs thub bstan mkhyen brtse
NK094(nge)001:18214: blo gros thig le rdzogs pa rtsal zhes 'bod pa'i
NK094(nge)001:18215: sbrang 'khyams 'on pa rol mo mkhan gyi brtul zhugs
NK094(nge)001:18216: can des 'og min chen po dpal kahthoga gi yang
NK094(nge)001:18217: dben gser khang ri khrod phrin las kun khyab gling
NK094(nge)001:18218: du dbu brtsams nas bla ma'i gdan sa ljon pa
NK094(nge)001:18219: lung gi dben khrod khu byug rol pa'i ljongs zhes
NK094(nge)001:18220: grags pa'i rang nyid sdod gnas kyi khang pa gsar
NK094(nge)001:18221: par lung rtogs sprul pa'i skus mthun rkyen mdzad cing
NK094(nge)001:18222: bri gzhi'i shog bu yang gnang ba la brten nas
NK094(nge)001:18223: ci rigs bris tshe bar skabs su nyer 'tshe'i tsha
NK094(nge)001:18224: gdung cung zad byung ba na /
NK094(nge)001:18225: skyabs mchog grub dbang 'gro 'dul dpa' bo rdo rje'i
NK094(nge)001:18226: gdan sa a 'dzom chos sgar chen po'i grub ri
NK094(nge)001:18227: dung dkar g.yas 'khyil gyi dben rtser mig sman thig
NK094(nge)001:18228: le'i lding khang la gnas te rigs bdag mchog sprul
NK094(nge)001:18229: rin po ches shog bu mang po dang mthun rkyen
NK094(nge)001:18230: legs par gnang ba'i thugs rje'i grib bsil la brten
NK094(nge)001:18231: nas zla ba bzhi'i bar du bris shing /
NK094(nge)001:18232: slar yang kun gzigs yang sprul rin po che'i bka'
NK094(nge)001:18233: don ltar dpal kahthoga gi gser khang yang dben bdud
NK094(nge)001:18234: 'dul phrin las kun khyab gling du dam pa nyid
NK094(nge)001:18235: kyis mthun rkyen mdzad cing shog bu gnang ba'i bka'
NK094(nge)001:18236: drin las gzhung don dngos legs par tshang ba'i bar
NK094(nge)001:18237: du bris nas / de rjes dpal yul rnam rgyal
NK094(nge)001:18238: byang chub gling chen gyi dben gnas brda go 'od
NK094(nge)001:18239: gsal theg mchog gling gi yang dben lha'i bkra shis
NK094(nge)001:18240: lhun po'i ri ngogs tsan+dana ljon bzang 'khrigs pa'i ma
NK094(nge)001:18241: la ya yi nags khrod gnyis pa lha bya skad
NK094(nge)001:18242: snyan tshal gyi bsti gnas mtsho gong dge 'phel chos
NK094(nge)001:18243: sgang gi sgrub khang lhag pa'i lha mchog dpal chen
NK094(nge)001:18244: bzhad pas thel sdings lung chen 'dus pa mdo yi
NK094(nge)001:18245: khang bzang gtsug lag rgya mtshos brgyan pa'i bsam 'grub
NK094(nge)001:18246: nor bu'i gling mchog dam pa skyabs rje grub dbang
NK094(nge)001:18247: rin po che'i yang srid sogs mchog sprul gsum gyis
NK094(nge)001:18248: gsar du bzhengs pa'i rdo rje'i khyung brag gi rdzong
NK094(nge)001:18249: gnas dge bar mkhas shing grub pa'i dbang phyug dpal
NK094(nge)001:18250: chen 'dus pa chos kyi glang po'i thugs bskyed dus
NK094(nge)001:18251: su smin pa'i rten 'brel bzang pos mtshams sbyar te
NK094(nge)001:18252: du bris nas / / dza lan+d+ha ra'i rgyan mchog
NK094(nge)001:18253: dam pa yang sprul thub bstan bshad sgrub chos kyi
NK094(nge)001:18254: sgra dbyangs kyi bka' lung bzhin du rab rgyal chu
NK094(nge)001:18255: 'brug lo'i zla 8tshes 13phun sum tshogs pa la mjug
NK094(nge)001:18256: yongs su rdzogs par bgyis pa 'dis kyang snga 'gyur
NK094(nge)001:18257: mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi ring lugs rmad du byung
NK094(nge)001:18258: ba nyid phyogs dus gnas skabs kun tu dar zhing
NK094(nge)001:18259: rgyas la yun ring du gnas pa'i rgyur gyur cig
NK094(nge)001:18263: sarba mang+ga lam ////skyabs rje thams cad mkhyen pa rigs
NK094(nge)001:18264: bdag byams chen chos kyi rgya mtsho dpal bzang po
NK094(nge)001:18265: nyid kyis gtsang bkra shis lhun por dpal ldan sngags
NK094(nge)001:18266: kyi srung mas brda lung dang mthun par mdo 'grel
NK094(nge)001:18267: mun pa'i go cha phyag tu son pa'i tshe zhal
NK094(nge)001:18268: nas ched du brjod pa bka' stsal pa /
NK094(nge)001:18269: 'og min lhun gyis grub pa'i gnas mchog tu //
NK094(nge)001:18270: rgyud kyi ston pa kun bzang thugs gsang mdzod //
NK094(nge)001:18271: rigs lnga'i rgyal ba lhun gyis grub par ston //
NK094(nge)001:18272: de las sprul sku thub chen dpa' bo yi //
NK094(nge)001:18273: thugs mtsho'i nor dbyig 'gro ba'i bsod nams dpal //
NK094(nge)001:18274: gsang bdag dpa' bos rigs can sems dpa' la //
NK094(nge)001:18275: yongs su bgro ba'i chos kyi dga' ston mchog /
NK094(nge)001:18276: 'dzam bu'i gling na gdams ngag rab kyi phul //
NK094(nge)001:18277: 'di ni sngon byon dam pa'i tshogs rnams kyi //
NK094(nge)001:18278: thugs dam dpag bsam thar 'dod ngal 'tsho'i gzhi //
NK094(nge)001:18279: skal bzang dam pa'i snying nor yin nges phyir //
NK094(nge)001:18280: 'bri klog 'chad nyan sgom pa bsten 'tshal lo //
NK094(nge)001:18281: sarba mang+ga la sh+r+ai d+aa ka l+ya n+aam b+ha wastu /
